Set nia aman Adão.
Sarani hotu tiha, Jesus husik mota Jordaun. Espiritu Santu domina Nia i lori Nia ba iha rai fuik maran.
Iha nebaa, diabu nia boot koko Jesus durante loron haat-nulu atu halo Nia monu ba sala. Iha tempu nee tomak, Jesus la haan buat ida, too Nia hamlaha atu-mate.
Depois diabu nia boot dehan ba Nia, “Se O Maromak nia Oan duni, haruka fatuk nee sai paun.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek,
‘Ema kriatura laos moris hosi hahaan deit.’ ”<a href='#note-531' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois diabu nia boot lori Jesus sae ba iha fatin aas ida, i hatudu kedas ba Jesus nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu tomak.
Diabu dehan, “Hau sei foo kbiit ba O para ukun nasaun sira nee hotu, i sei foo sira nia rikusoin hotu ba O. Tanba buat sira nee hotu hau nian ona, i hau bele foo ba see-see deit, konformi hau.
Hau foo hotu ba O, naran katak O hakneak hodi adora hau.”
Maibee Jesus hataan fali, “Iha Livru Sagradu haruka ema hotu-hotu nunee:
‘O tenki adora Maromak, o nia Nai,
i serbi mak Nia deit.’ ”<a href='#note-532' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois diabu nia boot lori Jesus ba iha sidade Jerusalém, i lori Nia baa hamriik iha uma kreda boot nia tutun. Diabu dehan, “Se O Maromak nia Oan duni, soe aan tuun ba rai.
Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan,
‘Nai Maromak sei haruka Nia anju sira
mai kuidadu O.
Sira sei tane O,
atu O nia ain la bele kona fatuk.’ ”<a href='#note-533' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Iha Livru Sagradu mos bandu ema dehan,
‘La bele koko Maromak, o nia Nai!’ ”<a href='#note-534' class='key'>✡</a>
Ho nunee diabu nia boot koko Jesus ho dalan oi-oin deit. Hotu tiha, diabu husik lai Jesus hodi hein fali tempu diak para koko tan.
Hotu tiha, Jesus fila fali ba provinsia Galileia, i Maromak nia Espiritu Santu domina hela Nia. Ema iha distritu nee tomak komesa konta baa-mai kona ba Nia.
Jesus hanorin iha ema Judeu sira nia uma kreda iha fatin-fatin, i ema hotu gaba Nia.
Iha loron ida, Jesus baa iha Nia aldeia Nazaré. Hanesan baibain iha loron Sabadu, Nia baa iha uma kreda. Depois Nia hamriik para lee Livru Sagradu.
Sira foo profeta Isaias nia livru, i Nia loke hodi buka liafuan nebee dehan,
“Nai Maromak nia Espiritu hamutuk ho Hau.
Tanba Nia foti ona Hau
para foo sai Liafuan Diak ba ema kiak sira.
Nia haruka ona Hau foo hatene dehan,
ema dadur sira sei livre fali,
sira nebee ema hanehan, sei moris livre,
i tempu too ona para Nai Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak.”<a href='#note-535' class='key'>✡</a>
Lee tiha hotu, Jesus taka livru hodi entrega fila fali ba responsavel, depois Nia tuur. Ema hotu-hotu iha uma kreda laran fihir ba Nia,
i Nia hatete ba sira, “Maromak nia liafuan nebee imi ohin rona nee, ohin loron sai realidade duni.”
Ema hotu komesa gaba Jesus. Sira admira tanba buat nebee Nia koalia nee kapaas loos. Maibee sira mos husu ba malu, “Nia nee José nia oan. Nusaa mak Nia bele koalia kapaas hanesan nee?!”
Jesus hatete ba sira, “Imi atu soe lia ida nee mai Hau, ‘Doutór, kura ita boot nia aan lai!’ Imi sei dehan, ‘Ami rona kona ba milagre nebee Ita Boot halo iha sidade Kafarnaum. Entaun halo took milagre nee iha Ita nia aldeia rasik!’
Maibee Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, ema nunka simu Maromak nia profeta iha nia aldeia rasik.<a href='#note-536' class='key'>✡</a>
Hanesan iha profeta Elias nia tempu, udan la monu rai durante tinan tolu ho balu, too rai hamlaha boot. Momentu nebaa, iha duni feto faluk barak iha Israel,
maibee Maromak la haruka Elias baa sira. Nia haruka fali baa iha inan faluk ida iha aldeia Sarepta besik sidade Sidon.<a href='#note-537' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos ho profeta Eliseu. Iha tempu nebaa, ema Israel barak moras lepra. Maibee Maromak la kura sira, Nia so kura deit Naaman hosi rai Síria.”<a href='#note-538' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona Jesus koalia nunee, ema hotu iha uma kreda laran hirus teb-tebes.
Sira hamriik rame-rame hodi duni Nia sai. Vila nee iha foho leten. Sira lori Jesus sai hosi vila, atu dudu tuun ba iha rai naruk.
Maibee Nia lao sai hosi sira nia klaran hodi baa liu fatin seluk.
Depois Jesus tuun baa sidade Kafarnaum iha provinsia Galileia. Iha loron Sabadu Nia hanorin iha uma kreda.
Nia hanorin nee halo ema admira, tanba Nia koalia hanesan ema nebee iha kbiit.<a href='#note-539' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha uma kreda laran, iha mos mane ida, diabu domina hela nia. I nia komesa hakilar makaas dehan,
“He! Jesus, Ema Nazaré. O hakarak halo saida ba ami? O mai atu halakon ami ka? Hau hatene O. O mak Ema Santu nebee Maromak haruka mai.”
Maibee Jesus siak diabu dehan, “Nonook! Sai hosi ema nee!” Derepenti diabu riba ema nee ba rai iha sira hotu nia oin, i sai hosi nia, la halo kanek nia.
Ema hotu admira hodi hatete ba malu, “Liafuan nee laos halimar! Ema nee foo orden ba diabu sai, i sira sai kedas.”
Entaun ema konta baa-mai kona ba Jesus iha rejiaun nee tomak.
Bainhira sira sai hosi uma kreda, Jesus baa iha Simão nia uma. Momentu nee Simão nia banin feto isin manas makaas, i nia maluk sira husu Jesus kura nia moras.
Entaun Jesus lao baa hamriik iha nia sorin hodi haruka nia isin manas sai. Derepenti nia moras nee lakon, i nia hadeer kedas baa prepara hahaan ba sira.
Bainhira loro monu dadauk, ema barak lori sira nia maluk sira nebee moras oi-oin ba Jesus. Nia tau liman ba sira ida-ida hodi kura sira nia moras hotu.
Nia mos haruka diabu sai hosi ema barak nia laran, i sira sai duni hodi hakilar dehan, “O mak Maromak nia Oan!” Maibee Jesus siak diabu sira nee i bandu sira la bele koalia, tanba sira hatene katak, Nia mak Kristu, Salvador nebee Maromak promete hori uluk ona atu haruka mai.
Iha fali aban dadeer rai huun mutin, Jesus husik tiha sidade hodi baa iha rai fuik ida. Ema barak buka Nia iha nebee-nebee. Kuandu sira hetan tiha Nia, sira husu ba Nia atu la bele husik hela sira.
Maibee Nia hataan, “Hau mos tenki baa iha aldeia sira seluk hodi foo sai Liafuan Diak kona ba oinsaa Nai Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. Tanba Nai Maromak haruka Hau mai hodi halo ida nee.”
Nunee Nia lao nafatin hosi aldeia ba aldeia iha provinsia Judeia hodi hanorin iha sira nia uma kreda.
Iha loron ida, Jesus hamriik iha tasi ibun Galileia nian hodi hanorin Nai Maromak nia liafuan.<a href='#note-540' class='key'>*</a> I ema barak mai hobur Nia hodi rona.
Iha nebaa iha mos peskador balu fasi hela redi iha tasi ibun. Jesus haree roo mamuk rua para hela iha tasi ninin.
Hanorin tiha hotu, Jesus dehan ba Simão, “Hean roo ba iha tasi klean hodi hatuun redi, para bele hetan ikan.”
Simão hataan, “Mestri, ami servisu makaas kalan tomak ona, la hetan buat ida. Maibee tanba Ita Boot haruka mak ami mos halo tuir.”<a href='#note-542' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee sira baa hatuun redi. Bainhira sira dada sae fali, sira hetan ikan barak teb-tebes too redi atu naklees.<a href='#note-543' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun sira halo sinal ba sira nia kolega iha roo seluk para mai ajuda. Sira mai, hotu-hotu hamutuk raut ikan tau ba roo rua nee nakonu, too roo besik atu mout.
8-10 Bainhira sira haree saida mak akontese, Simão Pedro ho nia kolega sira iha roo laran nee admira teb-tebes. Nia maluk peskador Tiago ho João, Zebedeu nia oan, mos admira. Entaun Simão baa hakneak kedas iha Jesus nia ain hodi dehan, “Nai, Ita Boot keta besik hau, tanba hau halo ona sala barak.”<a href='#note-544' class='key'>†</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Lalikan tauk. Imi baibain buka ikan. Maibee komesa agora imi sei buka fali ema para tuir Hau.”
Depois sira dada sira nia roo ba iha rai maran, i husik tiha buat hotu-hotu hodi tuir Jesus.
Iha aldeia ida, Jesus hasoru mane ida, nia isin nakonu ho moras lepra. Bainhira ema nee haree Jesus, nia baa hakneak hakruuk too rai iha Jesus nia oin hodi husu tulun dehan, “Nai, Ita Boot iha kbiit hodi kura hau, naran katak Ita Boot hakarak.”
Jesus lolo liman ba tau iha nia isin hodi dehan, “Hau hakarak. O diak ona ba!” I ema nee diak kedas.
Depois Jesus haruka nia, “La bele konta buat nee ba ema seluk. Maibee baa konsulta iha nai lulik, atu nia haree katak o nia isin moos ona. Depois foo oferta tuir lei nebee Nai Maromak foo ba Moisés, para ema hotu bele hatene katak o diak ona.”<a href='#note-545' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski Jesus bandu, maibee ema barak liu tan konta kona ba Nia, too iha fatin-fatin. Nunee ema barak nadodon mai para rona Nia hanorin i para bele hetan kura.
Maibee dala barak Jesus sees aan ba iha rai fuik hodi halo orasaun.
Iha loron ida, Jesus hanorin hela iha uma ida. Iha ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun balu tuur besik hodi rona. Sira balu hosi aldeia-aldeia iha provinsia Galileia, balu hosi provinsia Judeia, i balu hosi sidade Jerusalém. Tempu nee, Nai Maromak foo kbiit ba Jesus para kura ema moras.
Iha momentu nee, iha mos mane ain aat ida lao la diak, nia maluk sira hulan nia mai iha nia toba fatin. Sira hakaas aan atu lori ema nee tama ba uma laran atu hatoba iha Jesus nia oin.
Maibee iha uma laran ema nakonu, too sira obriga atu tama mos, tama la diak. Entaun sira lori nia sae ba iha uma leten, i sira sobu uma kakuluk halo kuak hodi hatuun nia ho nia toba fatin iha ema barak nia klaran, iha loos Jesus nia oin.
Jesus haree sira nia fiar, i hatete ba ema ain aat nee dehan, “Belun, o nia sala hamoos tiha ona.”
Rona Jesus koalia nunee, ema Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun sira komesa koalia ba malu dehan, “Nia hanoin Nia Maromak ka? So Nai Maromak deit mak bele hamoos ema nia sala! Nia liafuan nee hatete aat Nai Maromak.”
Maibee Jesus hatene sira nia hanoin, i Nia dehan, “Nusaa mak imi hanoin nunee?
Se Hau dehan ba ema nee katak, nia sala hamoos tiha ona, imi seidauk hatene, sai duni nunee ka lae. Maibee se Hau haruka nia hamriik ona hodi lao, imi bele haree ho matan.
Agora Hau sei hatudu mo-moos ba imi katak, iha mundu nee, Hau, Mane Maksoin, iha kbiit hodi hamoos ema nia sala.”
Nunee Jesus hatete ba ema ain aat nee dehan, “Hamriik ona! Foti o nia toba fatin hodi fila ba uma.”
Ema nee hamriik kedas iha ema hotu-hotu nia oin, foti nia toba fatin, i fila ba uma. Nia lao dadauk, hahii dadauk Nai Maromak iha dalan.
Ema hotu-hotu hakfodak i admira teb-tebes. Sira foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran hodi dehan, “Buat nebee ohin ita haree nee, milagre boot ida!”
Hotu tiha Jesus sai hosi uma nee, Nia hetan kobrador impostu ida naran Levi tuur hela iha nia servisu fatin.<a href='#note-546' class='key'>‡</a> Jesus dehan ba nia, “Mai tuir Hau!”
Levi hamriik kedas i husik tiha buat hotu-hotu hodi tuir Jesus.
La kleur, Levi halo festa boot ida hodi konvida Jesus baa iha nia uma. Nia mos konvida nia kolega kobrador impostu sira ho bainaka sira seluk.
Maibee iha mestri relijiaun ho ema boot balu tan hosi grupu Farizeu baa iha Jesus nia eskolante sira hodi kritika dehan, “Nusaa mak imi haan-hemu hamutuk ho kobrador impostu ho ema aat sira nee?”<a href='#note-547' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatete ba sira, “So ema moras mak presiza doutor, ema isin diak lae.
Hau mai atu bolu ema sala nain sira atu sira husik sira nia sala, laos atu bolu ema nebee konsidera nia aan moris loos ona.”
Jesus hataan ho komparasaun dehan, “Hau hanesan noivu ida iha nia festa kazamentu. Bainhira noivu sei hamutuk ho nia bainaka sira, sira la bele jejun, sira hotu sei haan rame-rame.
Maibee too iha loron ida, ema sei lori lakon tiha noivu nee. Iha loron nee mak nia bainaka sira sei jejun.”
Jesus halo tan komparasaun nunee: “La iha ema ida lees nia ropa foun hodi taka fali ba ropa bosan nebee kuak. Se nunee, nia estraga nia ropa ida foun nee. I hena foun ho hena bosan nee mos la haan malu.
Nunee mos ema halo tintu, la tau iha tua fatin nebee halo hosi kulit nebee tuan ona. Tanba tintu foun sempre nafurin sae, i sei halo kulit tuan nee nakfera tanba toos tiha ona. Nunee tua mos bele fakar sai.<a href='#note-548' class='key'>§</a>
Tua foun, tenki tau iha tua fatin foun.
Maibee kuandu ema hemu ona tintu nebee rai kleur, nia lakohi ona hemu tua nebee foun, tanba tuir nia hanoin, tua nebee rai kleur ona mak furak liu.”
Iha loron Sabadu ida, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao liu hosi ema nia toos. Nia eskolante sira korut dadauk trigu musan, i dulas halo moos hodi haan.<a href='#note-549' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu haree, i sira hasee Jesus dehan, “Nusaa mak imi servisu iha loron Sabadu? Ida nee kontra ita nia lei relijiaun!”
Jesus hataan, “Imi lee tiha ona liurai David nia istoria. Nusaa mak imi la kompriende nafatin? Iha loron ida nia ho nia ema sira hamlaha atu-mate.
Nia tama ba tenda orasaun. Iha nebaa iha paun nebee nai lulik sira oferese ona ba Maromak. Tuir lo-loos, so nai lulik sira deit mak bele haan paun nee, ema seluk la bele. Maibee liurai David foti tiha paun nee hodi haan, i nia fahe mos ba nia ema sira haan.”<a href='#note-550' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatutan tan, “Hau, Mane Maksoin, mak loron Sabadu nia Nain. Hau mak iha direitu atu desidi, ema bele halo saida iha loron nee.”
Iha loron Sabadu ida fali, Jesus baa hanorin iha uma kreda. Iha uma kreda laran, iha mane ida, nia liman sorin mate.
Iha mos ema Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun balu buka hela dalan atu foo sala ba Jesus. Entaun sira haree tu-tuir, Nia atu kura ema iha loron Sabadu ka lae.
Maibee Jesus hatene tiha ona sira nia hanoin. Nee mak Nia bolu ema liman sorin mate nee hodi dehan, “Mai hamriik iha oin.” I nia mos baa.
Depois Jesus husu ba ema sira nee, “Tuir ita nia lei relijiaun, ita bele halo saida iha loron Sabadu? Ita bele halo diak ka, aat? Ita bele salva ema ka, halakon ema nia moris?”
Jesus hateke ba sira ida-ida, depois Nia dehan ba ema liman sorin mate nee, “Lolo o nia liman mate nee mai!” Nia lolo ba, i nia liman diak kedas.
Haree nunee, ema Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun sira raan nakali. I sira komesa kombina oinsaa atu hamonu Jesus.
Iha loron seluk, Jesus sae ba foho ida hodi halo orasaun ba Nai Maromak. Nia halo orasaun durante kalan tomak.
Iha dadeer-saan fali, Nia bolu ema sira nebee tuir Nia. I hosi sira nee, Nia hili ema nain sanulu resin rua hodi foti sira sai Nia apostolu. Sira nee mak tuir mai nee:
Simão (Jesus mos bolu nia Pedro),
André (Simão nia alin),
Tiago,
João,
Filipe,
Bartolomeu,
Mateus,
Tomé,
Tiago (Alfeu nia oan),
Simão (nia tuir partidu Patriota),<a href='#note-551' class='key'>*</a>
Judas Iscariotes (ikus mai nia mak faan Jesus).
Hotu tiha Jesus ho Nia apostolu sira tuun mai hosi foho nee. Too iha rai tetuk oan ida, sira para, tanba iha ema lubuk boot ida hein hela sira iha nebaa. Hosi ema sira nee, iha barak mak baibain tuir Nia. Iha mos ema bara-barak mai hosi sidade Jerusalém ho provinsia Judeia tomak, i hosi sidade Tiru ho Sidon besik tasi ibun.
Sira mai atu rona Jesus koalia i atu husu para Jesus kura sira nia moras. I Jesus kura duni. Ema nebee diabu tama iha sira nia laran mos, Jesus duni sai diabu hodi kura sira nia moras.
Ema hotu-hotu buka dalan atu kona Jesus, tanba iha kbiit sai hosi Nia hodi kura sira hotu.
Jesus hateke ba Nia eskolante sira hodi dehan,
“Imi nebee kiak, sorti boot,
tanba Nai Maromak mak imi nia Liurai.
Imi nebee agora hamlaha, sorti boot,
tanba Maromak sei halo imi bosu.
Imi nebee agora tanis, sorti boot,
tanba imi sei hamnasa.
Bainhira ema odi imi, lakohi simu imi, tarata imi i duun dehan imi aat,
tanba tuir Hau, Mane Maksoin,
imi sorti boot.<a href='#note-552' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuandu ema halo imi terus nunee, haksolok deit ba, i haksoit ho kontenti, tanba Maromak sei foo premiu boot ba imi iha lalehan. Keta haluha katak, sira nia bei-ala sira uluk mos halo terus Maromak nia profeta hanesan nee.<a href='#note-553' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee imi nebee agora riku, sei terus,
tanba imi goza tiha hotu ona.
Imi nebee agora hahaan iha hela deit, sei terus,
tanba imi sei hamlaha boot.
Imi nebee agora hamnasa, sei terus,
tanba imi sei tanis halerik.
Imi nebee mak ema hotu-hotu gaba, sei terus,
tanba ema nebee gaba imi, sira nia bei-ala sira mos uluk gaba profeta falsu sira.”
Jesus hatutan tan dehan, “Imi nebee agora rona hela Hau, rona di-diak Hau nia liafuan nee: Hadomi o nia inimigu sira, i halo diak ba ema nebee odi o.
Harohan para Nai Maromak foo bensaun ba ema nebee foo malisan ba o. Husu para Nia tulun ema nebee halo aat ba o.
Se ema ruma basa o nia hasan sorin karik, foo tan hasan sorin ba. Se ema ruma hadau o nia faru manas, hasai tan o nia faru seluk foo ba nia.
Se ema husu o nia sasaan ruma, foo deit ba. Se ema hadau o nia sasaan ruma, husik deit ba, la bele baa husu fali.
Buat nebee mak o hakarak atu ema seluk halo ba o, o rasik mak tenki halo ba ema seluk.<a href='#note-554' class='key'>✡</a>
Se o hadomi deit ema nebee mak hadomi o, o atu manaan saida? Tanba ema aat sira mos hadomi ema nebee mak hadomi sira.
I se o foo empresta osan ba deit ema nebee bele selu fila fali, o atu manaan saida? Tanba ema aat sira mos foo empresta ba malu, naran katak selu fila fali.
Maibee tuir lo-loos hanesan nee: hadomi o nia inimigu sira, i halo diak ba sira. Foo empresta ba sira, i lalika hein atu sira selu fila fali. Ho nunee, o sei hetan premiu boot, i o sei hatudu katak, o Maromak Aas Liu nia oan. Tanba Maromak mos halo diak ba ema aat ho ema nebee la hatene foo obrigadu.
Nee duni, o tenki hadomi ema, hanesan mos o nia Aman iha lalehan hadomi sira.”
Jesus hanorin nafatin, dehan, “La bele ansi foo sala ba ema, para ema la bele ansi foo sala ba o. La bele hatudu liman ba ema, para ema la bele hatudu liman ba o. Foo perdaun ba ema, mak ema mos foo perdaun ba o.
Foo tulun ba ema, mak Maromak sei foo fila fali ba o barak liu too nakonu resin. Nee hanesan ema enxe sasaan nakonu, depois sena tan doko tan too fakar sai iha ita nia hitin. Se o foo uitoan, o simu fali mos uitoan. Maibee se o foo barak, o sei simu fali mos barak.”
Jesus mos halo komparasaun dehan, “Ema matan delek ida, nia la bele hatudu dalan ba ema matan delek seluk. Se lae sira nain rua monu hotu ba rai kuak.<a href='#note-555' class='key'>✡</a>
Estudante ida la bele boot liu nia mestri, maibee se nia estuda too remata, nia bele hanesan nia mestri.<a href='#note-556' class='key'>✡</a>
Nusaa mak o haree ai uut iha ema seluk nia matan, maibee ai kabelak nebee taka o nia matan rasik, o la senti?
Oinsaa mak o brani dehan, ‘Belun, mai hau hasai tiha ai uut nee hosi o nia matan.’ Afinal iha ai kabelak ida taka hela o nia matan. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk! Hasai tiha uluk ai kabelak iha o nia matan, mak foin o haree hetan para bele hasai ai uut hosi o nia maluk nia matan.”
Jesus halo tan komparasaun ida nunee: “Ai huun nebee diak, nunka foo fuan aat. Nunee mos ai huun nebee la diak, nunka foo fuan diak.
Ema hatene ai huun ida-idak liu hosi nia fuan. Ita la kuu uvas ka ai fuan figeira hosi ai tarak.<a href='#note-557' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos ho ema. Ema nebee diak koalia buat diak, tanba nia laran mos diak. I ema nebee aat koalia buat aat, tanba nia laran mos aat. Tanba buat nebee nia koalia, sai hosi nia laran.”<a href='#note-558' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatutan tan dehan, “Imi bolu beibeik Hau dehan, ‘Nai, Nai’. Maibee nusaa mak imi la halo tuir buat nebee Hau haruka?
Ema nebee rona Hau nia liafuan i halo tuir, nia hanesan
ema nebee harii uma forti ida. Nia kee rai halo klean hodi hatama uma riin ba, i tau tan fatuk hodi halo metin. Nunee kuandu mota boot tama i bee baku makaas mos, uma nee la nakdoko, tanba nia riin metin.
Maibee ema nebee rona Hau nia liafuan i la halo tuir, nia hanesan ema nebee harii uma, nia riin tidin deit iha rai leten. Bainhira mota boot tama, bee sobu rahun kedas.”
Jesus hanorin tiha hotu ema barak nee, Nia fila fali ba sidade Kafarnaum.
Iha nebaa iha komandante Roma ida. Nia atan ida nebee nia hadomi teb-tebes, moras todan, besik atu mate.
Bainhira komandante nee rona kona ba Jesus, nia haruka katuas lia nain Judeu balu baa bolu Jesus atu mai kura atan nee nia moras.
Too iha nebaa, sira husu ho laran tomak atu Jesus baa kura nia. Sira dehan, “Senhor komandante nee serve duni atu Ita Boot tulun nia,
tanba nia hadomi ita ema Judeu, i harii ona uma kreda ida ba ita.”
Entaun Jesus baa hamutuk ho sira.
Sira besik too ona iha uma, komandante haruka nia kolega sira baa hatete ba Jesus dehan, “Nai la presiza lao kole too mai, tanba hau la serve atu simu Ita Boot iha hau nia uma.
I hau mos la serve atu baa hasoru Ita Boot. Nai foo deit orden hosi nebaa mak hau nia atan hetan kura.
Hau hatene nunee tanba hau nia komandante sira mos iha kbiit atu foo orden mai hau. Nunee mos, hau iha kbiit atu foo orden ba hau nia soldadu sira. Se hau manda hau nia soldadu ida dehan, ‘Baa nebaa!’, nia mos baa. Se hau hatete, ‘Mai iha nee!’, nia mai. I se hau haruka hau nia atan dehan, ‘Halo ida nee!’, mak nia sei halo.”
Rona nunee, Jesus admira, i Nia fila oin ba ema barak nebee tuir Nia nee hodi hatete, “Hau seidauk haree ema Judeu ida ke fiar makaas hanesan ema Roma nee.”
Entaun komandante nia kolega sira nee fila fali. Too iha uma, sira haree atan nee diak tiha ona.
La kleur tan, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira baa iha aldeia ida naran Nain. Ema barak akompanha sira.
Bainhira sira besik ona portaun atu tama ba vila, ema barak sai mai lori mate isin ida atu baa hakoi. Ida mate nee, feto faluk ida nia oan mane mesak.
Jesus baa besik hodi tau liman ba hadak nebee mak tula mate isin nee, i ema sira nebee hulan mate nee para tiha. Depois Jesus dehan ba ema mate nee, “Anoo, hadeer ona.”
Joven nee mos hadeer tuur kedas hodi komesa koalia. I Jesus entrega nia fila fali ba nia inan.
Ema hotu iha nebaa tauk teb-tebes, i sira hahii Nai Maromak dehan, “Nai Maromak nia profeta boot ida mai tiha ona iha ita nia leet. Maromak mai ona hodi salva Nia povu.”
Buat nee, ema konta lemo-lemo iha provinsia Judeia tomak, ho mos too rai vizinhu sira.
João Sarani Nain nia eskolante sira konta ba João kona ba buat hotu-hotu nebee mak Jesus halo.<a href='#note-559' class='key'>*</a> Entaun nia haruka nain rua
baa hasoru Nai Jesus hodi husu, “Ita Boot mak Ema ida nebee Maromak promete atu haruka mai ka, ami tenki hein fali ema seluk?”
Sira too iha Jesus, sira mos husu, “João Sarani Nain haruka ami mai husu, Ita Boot mak Ema ida nebee Maromak promete atu haruka mai ka, ami tenki hein fali ema seluk?”
Iha tempu nee, Jesus kura hela ema moras barak. Nia duni sai diabu hosi ema lubuk ida, i halo ema matan delek barak mos haree.
Entaun Jesus hataan ba João nia eskolante sira nunee: “Imi fila baa konta ba João kona ba buat hotu-hotu nebee imi ohin haree ho rona rasik,
‘Ema matan delek, bele haree.
Ema ain aat, bele lao.
Ema moras lepra, isin sai moos.
Ema tilun diuk, bele rona.
Ema mate, moris fila fali.
Ema kiak, rona Liafuan Diak.’<a href='#note-560' class='key'>†</a>
Hatete tan ba João dehan, ‘Ema nebee fiar nafatin mai Hau, nia sorti boot.’ ”
Bainhira sira nain rua fila tiha, Jesus koalia ba ema barak nee kona ba João, dehan, “Uluk imi baa iha rai fuik maran atu haree see loos? Imi baa atu haree ema nebee halai baa-mai tuir anin hanesan fali duut manlain ka? Lae!
Entaun imi baa atu haree saida? Atu haree ema nebee hatais ropa folin karu ka? Lae! Ema nebee hatais ropa diak i moris diak, hela iha uma ema boot nian.
Entaun imi baa atu haree saida? Imi hanoin atu haree Nai Maromak nia profeta ka? Loos duni! Maibee João nee boot liu tan.
Nai Maromak nia liafuan hakerek ona kona ba João nia knaar dehan,
‘Rona mai! Hau haruka Hau nia ema ida
baa uluk hodi prepara dalan ba O.’<a href='#note-561' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete ba imi, hori uluk kedas, la iha ema ida iha mundu nee boot liu João. Maski nunee, komesa agora ba oin, see mak hakruuk ba Maromak nudar Liurai, bele ema nee kiik mos, nia sei sorti boot liu fali João.
Ema hotu-hotu nebee rona Jesus nia liafuan nee, liu-liu kobrador impostu sira, sira rekonhese katak, Maromak nia dalan mak loos, nee mak uluk João sarani sira.
Maibee ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu sira ho mestri relijiaun Judeu sira lakohi tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak. Nee mak sira lakohi atu João foo sarani sira.<a href='#note-562' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus husu, “Ema agora dadauk nee, oinsaa? Hau atu kompara sira ho saida?
Sira hanesan labarik nebee tuur iha merkadu hodi hakilar ba malu, dehan,
‘Ami toka muzika kapaas loos,
maibee imi la dansa.
maibee imi la tanis.’
Nunee mos João Sarani Nain la hemu tua, i sempre jejun, depois imi dehan, diabu tama iha nia laran.
Maibee Hau, Mane Maksoin, haan ho hemu tua hanesan ema baibain, i imi dehan, Hau kaan-teen ho lanu-teen, i halo belun ho kobrador impostu sira ho ema sala nain sira.
Maibee ema hotu-hotu nebee moris tuir Maromak nia matenek, sira hatudu katak Maromak nia matenek nee loos duni.”
Iha ema Farizeu ida naran Simão, nia konvida Jesus baa haan iha nia uma. Entaun Jesus baa. Too iha uma, sira tuur iha meza para haan.
Iha sidade nee, iha mos feto aat ida, nia rona katak Jesus haan iha Simão nia uma. Nia tama ba uma laran, lori ho mina morin botir ida nebee karu teb-tebes.
Nia baa hamriik iha Jesus nia kotuk, besik loos Nia ain. Nia tanis too nia matan been turu kona Jesus nia ain, depois hamaran matan been nee ho nia fuuk. I nia mos rei Jesus nia ain fila-fila hodi kose mina morin ba.<a href='#note-563' class='key'>✡</a>
Haree feto nee nia hahalok, uma nain ema Farizeu nee, hanoin dehan, “Se Jesus nee Nai Maromak nia profeta karik, entaun Nia sei hatene feto nebee kona Nia nee, feto aat ida.”
Maibee Jesus hatene uma nain nia hanoin, i Nia dehan, “Simão, Hau hakarak hatete buat ida ba ita.”
Simão hataan, “Bele, mestri, koalia deit.”
Depois Jesus soe lia ba nia dehan, “Iha senhor ida foo empresta osan ba ema nain rua. Ba ida, nia foo osan mutin atus lima, ba ida seluk, nia foo deit osan mutin lima-nulu.
Maibee too iha loron atu foo fila fali osan nee, sira nain rua selu la bele. Entaun senhor nee hamoos tiha sira nain rua nia tusan. Tuir ita nia hanoin, hosi sira nain rua nee, ida nebee mak sei hadomi liu osan nain nee?”
Simão hataan, “Ida nebee tusan boot liu karik.”
Jesus dehan, “Loos duni!”
Depois Nia fila oin ba feto nee, i hatete ba Simão, “Ita haree took feto nee. Ohin Hau tama iha ita nia uma, ita la prepara bee hodi fasi Hau nia ain tuir ita nia lisan. Maibee nia habokon Hau nia ain ho nia matan been, depois nia hamaran ho nia fuuk.
I ohin Hau tama iha ita nia uma, ita la rei Hau tuir ita nia lisan. Maibee feto nee, komesa ohin Hau tama mai iha nee, nia rei Hau nia ain fila-fila.
Ita mos haluha tau mina mai Hau nia ulun, maibee nia tau mina morin ba Hau nia ain.
Nunee, Hau hatete ba ita katak, feto nee sala barak duni, maibee nia sala hamoos hotu tiha ona. Nee mak nia hatudu domin boot mai Hau. Maibee se karik ema halo sala uitoan deit, bainhira nia sala nee hamoos tiha ona, ema nee hadomi mos uitoan deit.”
Depois Jesus hatete ba feto nee, “O nia sala hamoos tiha hotu ona.”
Ema sira nebee tuur haan hamutuk ho Jesus nee komesa bis-bisi ba malu, dehan, “Nia hanoin Nia nee see?! Too Nia bele brani dehan Nia hamoos ema nia sala?”
Maibee Jesus hatete ba feto nee, “Tanba o fiar Hau, nee mak Maromak salva ona o. Fila ho laran hakmatek.”
Hotu tiha, Jesus lao hosi sidade ba sidade ho aldeia ba aldeia hodi foo sai Liafuan Diak kona ba oinsaa Nai Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua akompanha Nia.
Iha mos feto balu nebee tuir. Sira nee uluk iha moras oi-oin, balu diabu tama iha sira nia laran, maibee Jesus kura tiha hotu. Ida mak Maria Madalena, uluk Jesus duni sai diabu hitu hosi nia.
Iha mos Joana ho Susana. Joana nia kaben Kuza mak toma konta liurai Herodes nia uma. Sei iha tan feto barak lao hamutuk ho Jesus. Sira hodi sira nia osan rasik sustenta Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira.<a href='#note-564' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida, ema hosi aldeia barak mai iha Jesus. Bainhira ema barak halibur hamutuk ona, Jesus halo komparasaun ida hanesan nee,
“Iha toos nain ida baa kari fini iha nia toos. Fini balu monu iha dalan. Ema sama deit, i manu fuik mai hili tiha hotu.
Fini balu monu iha fatuk leten. Fini nee moris duni, maibee la kleur namlaik tiha, tanba rai uitoan deit.
Fini balu monu iha duut tarak laran. Buat rua nee moris hamutuk, maibee la kleur duut tarak nee habit mate tiha.
Iha tan fini balu monu iha rai bokur, i moris too foo isin. Fini sira nee, ida-idak foo fali musan atus ida.”
Depois Jesus nia eskolante sira husu ba Nia, komparasaun nee dehan saida.
Jesus hataan, “Uluk ema seidauk hatene, oinsaa mak Nai Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. Agora Hau foo sai mo-moos ba imi. Maibee ba ema seluk, Hau hanorin uza deit komparasaun, atu nunee
‘Sira haree,
maibee hanesan la haree.
Sira rona,
maibee la kompriende.’ ”<a href='#note-565' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatutan tan, “Komparasaun nee dehan nunee: Fini nee mak Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
Fini nebee monu iha dalan, mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia lafuan, maibee diabu nia boot mai hadau tiha hosi sira nia laran. Entaun sira la fiar ba Maromak, i la hetan salvasaun.
Fini nebee monu iha fatuk leten, mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia liafuan i simu ho haksolok, maibee sira nia abut la tama ba rai. Sira fiar duni, maibee kuandu provasaun ruma kona sira, sira husik fali.
Fini nebee monu iha duut tarak laran, mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia liafuan, maibee sira preokupa ho sira nia moris ho sira nia rikusoin, i buka goza deit. Nunee, sira nia fiar la baa oin, i sira nia moris nunka foo rezultadu diak.
Maibee fini nebee monu iha rai bokur, mak ema nebee moris loos ho laran moos. Bainhira sira rona Nai Maromak nia liafuan, sira rai di-diak iha sira nia laran hodi kaer metin nafatin too foo rezultadu diak teb-tebes.”
Jesus halo tan komparasaun ida nunee: “La iha ema ida mak sunu ahi-oan, depois taka tiha ho sanan rai ka tau fali iha kama okos. Maibee ahi-oan, ema tenki tau iha fatin aas, atu bele foo naroman ba ema nebee tama mai.<a href='#note-566' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos, buat hotu-hotu nebee agora sei subar hela, iha loron ida sei hatudu mo-moos. I buat hotu-hotu nebee agora taka hela, iha loron ida sei nakloke para ema bele hatene.<a href='#note-567' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, imi tenki rona Hau nia hanorin ho atensaun. Tanba ema nebee rona ho atensaun, Maromak sei halo nia kompriende liu tan. Maibee ema nebee lakohi rona, maski nia hanoin dehan nia kompriende uitoan, maibee nia sei sai beik liu tan.<a href='#note-568' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida, Jesus nia inan ho Nia alin sira mai atu hasoru Nia, maibee sira la konsege besik, tanba ema barak haleu hela Nia.
Iha ema ida foo hatene ba Jesus dehan, “Ita Boot nia inan ho alin sira iha hela liur. Sira hakarak hasoru Ita Boot.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Hau nia inan ho Hau nia alin sira mak ema nebee rona Nai Maromak nia liafuan hodi halo tuir.”
Iha loron ida, Jesus hatete ba Nia eskolante sira, “Mai ita baa iha tasi sorin.” Entaun sira sae roo hodi baa.
Roo lao dadauk, Jesus toba dukur tiha. La kleur anin boot mai, halo tasi been tama ba roo laran, too roo atu mout sal-sala.
Haree nunee, eskolante sira fanu Jesus, dehan, “Mestri, mestri, ita atu mout ona!”
Jesus hadeer hodi siak anin ho laloran boot nee. Anin para kedas, tasi mos hakmatek fali.
Depois Nia siak Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Nusaa mak imi la fiar Hau?”
Sira tauk ho admira hodi husu ba malu dehan, “Ema nee see loos? Nia foo orden ba anin ho laloran, sira mos halo tuir!”
Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira ho roo lao too rai Gerasa, iha tasi Galileia nia sorin ba.
27-29 Iha fatin nee, iha mane ida, diabu tama iha nia laran kleur ona. Nia hosi sidade, maibee la hela iha uma, hela deit iha rate, i la hatais buat ida. Diabu sira ataka nia dala barak ona. Ema kesi nia liman-ain beibeik ho korenti besi i hein nia loron-kalan, maibee nia sempre rasta kotu tiha korenti. I diabu sira obriga nia halai ba iha rai fuik.
Momentu Jesus tuun hosi roo, ema bulak nee mai hasoru Nia. Ema nee hakilar i hakneak hakruuk too rai iha Jesus nia ain. Depois Jesus haruka diabu sai hosi nia.
Ema bulak nee hakilar dehan, “Jesus, Nai Maromak Aas Liu nia Oan. O hakarak halo saida mai hau? Hau husu boot, keta kastigu hau!”
Jesus husu ba nia, “O naran saa?”
Nia hataan, “Batalhaun”. Nia hataan nunee tanba diabu barak loos hela iha nia laran.
Iha momentu nebaa, iha fahi barak teb-tebes haan hela iha foho lolon. Diabu sira husu fila-fila ba Jesus para husik sira tama iha fahi sira nee. I Jesus foo lisensa.
Entaun diabu sira sai tiha hosi ema nee baa tama fali iha fahi sira. I fahi sira nee halai saruntu malu tuun hosi foho nee, monu hotu ba bee laran, i mout too mate hotu.
Fahi atan sira haree saida mak akontese, i sira halai baa konta sai iha sidade ho fatin sira nebee besik.
Rona nunee, ema barak sai baa atu haree rasik ho matan. Too iha nebaa, sira haree ema nebee uluk diabu domina nee, diak tiha ona. Nia tuur hakmatek hela iha Jesus nia ain, hatais tiha ona hena, i hanoin normal fali ona. Haree nunee, sira hotu tauk.
Ema sira nebee ohin haree Jesus duni sai diabu nee, sira konta ba sira nebee foin mai, kona ba oinsaa mak Jesus kura ema nee.
Depois ema hotu-hotu iha rai Gerasa husu atu Jesus sai tiha hosi nebaa, tanba sira tauk atu-mate.
Entaun Jesus baa sae roo atu fila fali ba iha tasi sorin.
Ema nebee ohin diabu sai hosi nia nee, husu atu bele tuir Jesus.
Maibee Jesus hataan,
“Diak liu o fila ba uma hodi konta saida mak Nai Maromak halo ona ba o.”
Entaun ema nee baa lao lemo-lemo iha sidade nee tomak hodi konta sai kona ba buat hotu nebee Jesus halo ba nia.
Bainhira Jesus fila fali hosi tasi sorin, ema barak hein hela Nia, i simu Nia ho haksolok.
41-42 Iha nebaa iha ema ida naran Jairo, nia mak responsavel uma kreda iha sidade nee. Nia oan ida deit, feto ida ho tinan sanulu resin rua. Labarik nee moras boot, besik atu mate. Entaun Jairo baa hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha Jesus nia oin hodi husu ho laran tomak para Jesus baa iha nia uma.
Jesus lao dadauk ba Jairo nia uma, ema barak akompanha Nia too sena malu.
Iha ema lubun boot nee, iha feto ida, nia fulan mai la para durante tinan sanulu resin rua. Nia faan tiha nia sasaan hotu hodi baa konsulta iha doutor, maibee la iha ema ida mak bele kura nia moras.<a href='#note-569' class='key'>*</a>
Feto nee bes-besik ba iha Jesus nia kotuk, nia kona Jesus nia hena tutun, i nia raan para kedas.
Jesus husu, “See mak ohin kona Hau nee?”
Sira hotu dehan, lae. Pedro mos hatete, “Mestri, iha ema barak mak sena malu ho Ita Boot.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Lae, ohin Hau senti iha kbiit sai hosi Hau. Nee mak Hau hatene, iha ema ida kona Hau.”
Bainhira feto nee hatene katak nia la bele subar, nia tauk teb-tebes ho nakdedar, i nia baa hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha Jesus nia ain. Depois nia konta nia problema nee ba Jesus iha ema hotu-hotu nia oin, i foo hatene katak, momentu nia kona Jesus, nia moras diak kedas.
Jesus dehan ba nia, “Hau nia oan, o hetan kura tanba o fiar mai Hau. Fila ho laran hakmatek.”
Jesus sei koalia hela, ema ida mai hosi Jairo nia uma foo hatene ba Jairo, “Senhor nia oan iis kotu tiha ona. Lalikan halo kole tan mestri.”
Rona nunee, Jesus hatete ba Jairo, “Lalikan tauk. Fiar deit, mak ita nia oan sei moris fali.”
51-53 Bainhira sira too iha Jairo nia uma, ema barak iha tiha ona nebaa, sira tanis lelir hela. Jesus hatete ba sira, “Imi lalika tanis tan ona. Labarik nee la mate ida, nia toba deit!”
Maibee sira hamnasa fali Jesus, tanba sira rasik haree labarik nee mate tiha ona. Jesus husu ba labarik nia inan-aman, ho mos Pedro, João ho Tiago, tama ba laran hamutuk ho Nia. Sira seluk Nia haruka hein iha liur.
Sira tama tiha ba laran, Jesus kaer labarik nia liman hodi dehan, “Hau nia oan, hadeer ona!”
Derepenti deit, labarik nee nia iis iha fila fali, nia hadeer i hamriik kedas. Jesus haruka sira foo hahaan ba nia.
Labarik nia inan-aman admira teb-tebes. Maibee Jesus bandu sira para la bele konta sai ba ema seluk, buat nebee mak akontese.
Iha loron ida, Jesus halibur Nia apostolu nain sanulu resin rua hodi foo kbiit ba sira atu bele duni sai diabu i kura ema nia moras.
Nia hatete ba sira, “Imi lao, la bele lori buat ida. La bele lori ai tonka, pasta, bukae, ka osan. Hena hodi troka mos la bele.
Kuandu ema simu imi iha sira nia uma, hela deit iha uma nee too imi sai fali ba aldeia seluk.
Maibee se imi tama iha aldeia ida mak ema lakohi simu imi, husik tiha aldeia nee. I baku rai rahun hosi imi nia ain okos hodi hatudu katak, Maromak sei kastigu sira.”<a href='#note-570' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois apostolu sira lao hosi aldeia ba aldeia hodi foo sai Nai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak i kura ema moras.
Liurai Herodes<a href='#note-571' class='key'>*</a> rona kona ba buat hotu-hotu mak Jesus halo. Nia konfuzaun, tanba iha ema balu dehan, “Jesus mak João Sarani Nain, nia moris fila fali ona.”
Balu tan dehan, “Nia Maromak nia profeta Elias mak mosu fali.”
Iha seluk tan dehan, “Nia nee profeta seluk ida nebee mate kleur ona, i agora moris fali.”<a href='#note-572' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Herodes dehan, “Hau rona buat oi-oin kona ba ema ida nee. João nia kakorok, hau haruka tesi tiha ona. Entaun ema ida nee see tan?” Nunee Herodes buka atu hasoru malu ho Jesus.
Bainhira Jesus nia apostolu sira fila fali mai, sira konta ba Jesus buat hotu-hotu nebee sira halo ona. Depois Jesus lori sira sees aan baa iha aldeia Betsaida.
Maibee ema barak rona katak Jesus atu baa nebaa, i sira mos tuir. Jesus simu sira ho diak. Nia foo sai ba sira kona ba oinsaa Nai Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, i kura sira nia moras hotu.
Loro atu monu ona, apostolu nain sanulu resin rua baa Jesus hodi dehan, “Diak liu haruka ema sira nee baa buka hahaan iha aldeia-aldeia nebee besik, i haruka sira mos baa buka fatin hodi toba, tanba iha nee rai fuik.
Jesus hataan, “Imi mak foo haan sira.”
Nia eskolante sira protesta dehan, “Ita so iha paun fuan lima ho ikan rua deit. Halo nusaa mak ita bele sosa hahaan ba ema barak hanesan nee?!”
Tanba ema iha nebaa maizoumenus rihun lima, nee mane deit, seidauk konta feto ho labarik.<a href='#note-573' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus dehan ba sira, “Haruka sira hotu tuur tuir grupu. Grupu ida ema nain lima-nulu.”
Sira mos halo tuir. Kuandu ema tuur hotu ona,
Jesus foti paun fuan lima ho ikan rua nee, i Nia hateke ba lalehan hodi foo agradese ba Nai Maromak. Nia silu paun ho ikan halo rohan-rohan, i foo ba Nia eskolante sira hodi baa fahe ba ema barak nee.
Sira hotu haan too bosu. I eskolante sira baa tau hamutuk hahaan restu sira nee iha bote sanulu resin rua nakonu.
Iha loron ida, Jesus halo hela orasaun mesa-mesak iha fatin ida, i Nia eskolante sira besik Nia. Hotu tiha, Nia husu ba sira, “Tuir ema konta, Hau nee see?”
Sira hataan, “Iha balu dehan, Ita Boot João Sarani Nain. Balu tan dehan, Maromak nia profeta Elias. Se lae profeta seluk ida nebee mate kleur ona, i agora moris fali.”<a href='#note-574' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus husu tan, “Tuir imi rasik, Hau nee see?”
Pedro hataan, “Ita Boot nee Kristu, Salvador nebee Maromak promete hori uluk ona atu haruka mai.”<a href='#note-575' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-576' class='key'>✡</a>
I Jesus bandu sira para la bele foo hatene ba see-see deit.
Jesus hatutan dehan, “Hau, Mane Maksoin tenki simu terus oi-oin. Nai ulun Judeu sira, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira sei la simu Hau. Ema sei oho tiha Hau, maibee too iha loron tolu, Maromak sei halo Hau moris fila fali.”
Depois Nia foo hatene ba sira hotu dehan, “Ema nebee hakarak tuir Hau, nia tenki husik tiha nia hakarak rasik. Nia tenki tuir nafatin Hau, maski ema halo terus nia, hanesan ema nebee loro-loron lori nia krus too mate.<a href='#note-577' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba see mak hakarak salva nia aan, nia sei lakon fali. I see mak lakon nia moris tanba nia tuir Hau, nia sei hetan moris rohan-laek.<a href='#note-578' class='key'>✡</a>
Se ema hetan buat hotu-hotu iha mundu nee, maibee nia lakon tiha nia moris ho Maromak, nia manaan saida loos?
Se ema ruma moe atu simu Hau i lakohi simu Hau nia liafuan, aban-bainrua Hau, Mane Maksoin mos sei moe rekonhese nia bainhira Hau fila fali mai hosi lalehan. Hau sei tuun mai ho naroman lalehan nian, ho Aman Maromak nia kbiit tomak, i Maromak nia anju sira nabilan haleu Hau.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, hosi imi sira nee, balu sei moris too haree Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, mak foin mate.”
Jesus halo hela orasaun, Nia oin fila aan tiha, i Nia hena mos sai mutin nabilan hanesan rai lakan.
Derepenti deit, Maromak nia profeta nain rua, Moisés ho Elias, mosu mai
ho naroman lalehan nian hodi koalia ho Jesus. Sira nain tolu koalia kona ba Jesus nia mate, tanba la kleur tan Nia sei mate iha Jerusalém hodi kumpri Maromak nia planu.
Momentu nee, Pedro ho nia kolega nain rua nee toba dukur tiha. Sira hadeer mai, haree Jesus naroman nabilan loos, hamriik hela ho ema nain rua nee.
Bainhira Moisés ho Elias atu baa ona, Pedro nia hanoin lakon tiha, i nia koalia arbiru deit dehan, “Mestri, ita hamutuk iha nee, furak teb-tebes. Diak liu ami halo tenda tolu, ida ba Ita Boot, ida ba Moisés, i ida tan ba Elias.”
Pedro sei koalia hela nunee, kalohan ida tuun mai falun tiha sira, halo eskolante nain tolu nee tauk.
I lian ida hosi kalohan nee dehan, “Nee Hau nia Oan, Hau hili ona Nia. Imi tenki rona Nia.”<a href='#note-579' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona tiha lian nee hotu, eskolante sira la haree tan ema ida, so Jesus deit. Iha tempu nebaa, sira nain tolu la konta sai ba ema seluk kona ba buat nebee mak sira haree.
Aban fali, Jesus tuun fali hosi foho nee hamutuk ho Nia eskolante nain tolu, i ema barak teb-tebes mai hasoru Nia.
Hosi ema barak nia leet nee, iha senhor ida bolu ho lian makaas dehan, “Mestri, favor ida, haree lai hau nia oan mane. Nia hau nia oan mesak.
Iha diabu ida dala barak ataka nia halo nia hakilar derepenti i tebe liman tebe ain too kabeen mutin sai hosi ibun. Diabu nee book nia beibeik i halo terus liu nia.
Hau husu tiha ona ba Ita Boot nia eskolante sira atu duni sai tiha diabu nee, maibee sira la bele halo buat ida.”
Jesus siak sira hotu dehan, “Imi ema nebee sempre halo aat i la fiar ba Maromak. Hau tenki hela ho imi too bainhira tan? Hau tenki pasiensia ho imi too iha nebee!?”
Depois Nia hatete ba senhor nee, “Lori ita nia oan mai.”
Labarik nee lao dadauk ba Jesus, diabu riba nia ba rai i halo nia tebe liman tebe ain. Maibee Jesus foo orden ba diabu para sai hosi labarik nee, i nia diak kedas. Depois Jesus entrega fali labarik nee ba nia aman.
Ema hotu-hotu admira tanba haree Nai Maromak nia kbiit boot nee.
Momentu ema hotu-hotu sei admira hela ho milagre oi-oin nebee Jesus halo, Nia hatete ba Nia eskolante sira,
“Imi rona di-diak saida mak Hau atu hatete nee. La kleur tan, ema sei faan Hau, Mane Maksoin ba ema aat.”<a href='#note-580' class='key'>‡</a>
Maibee Nia eskolante sira la kompriende. Tanba liafuan nia signifikadu sei taka hela, atu sira la bele hatene. I sira mos tauk atu husu ba Jesus.
Jesus nia eskolante sira komesa haksesuk malu kona ba ida nebee mak boot liu.<a href='#note-581' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hatene sira nia hanoin. Entaun Nia bolu labarik oan ida mai hamriik iha Nia sorin.
Nia hatete ba sira, “See mak simu labarik nee hodi Hau nia naran, nia simu Hau. I see mak simu Hau, nia simu mos Ida nebee haruka Hau mai. Ema nebee haraik aan nudar ema kiik, nia mak boot liu iha Maromak nia oin.”<a href='#note-582' class='key'>✡</a>
João foo hatene ba Jesus dehan, “Mestri, ami haree ema ida duni sai diabu hodi Ita Boot nia naran. Ami bandu nia, tanba nia laos ita nia ema.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “La bele bandu! Tanba ema nebee la kontra imi, nia hamutuk ho imi.”
Jesus nia loron atu sae ba lalehan besik ona, entaun Nia desidi, bele halo nusaa mos, Nia tenki baa iha sidade Jerusalém.
Nia haruka ema balu baa uluk, i sira tama iha aldeia ida iha provinsia Samaria atu prepara fatin ba Nia.
Maibee ema iha nebaa lakohi simu Jesus, tanba sira hatene katak Nia atu baa iha Jerusalém.<a href='#note-583' class='key'>§</a>
Bainhira Jesus nia eskolante Tiago ho João haree ema Samaria sira nia hahalok nee, sira husu ba Jesus, “Nai, se Ita Boot hakarak, ami haruka ahi tuun mai hosi lalehan haan motuk tiha sira.”<a href='#note-584' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus fila ba sira nain rua hodi siak sira.
Bainhira Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao dadauk, ema ida dehan ba Jesus, “Ita Boot baa nebee deit, hau prontu atu tuir.”
Jesus hataan, “Asu fuik iha nia fatin hodi hela. Manu fuik mos iha nia knuuk. Maibee Hau, Mane Maksoin la iha fatin ida hodi tau Hau nia ulun ba.”
Jesus hatete ba ema ida seluk dehan, “Mai tuir Hau.”
Ema nee hataan, “Nai, husik hau fila baa hakoi hau nia aman lai, mak foin hau tuir.”<a href='#note-585' class='key'>*</a>
Jesus hatete ba nia, “Ema nebee lakohi rona Maromak, sira mos hanesan ema mate. Husik sira mak hakoi sira nia mate. Maibee o nia servisu mak baa foo sai kona ba oinsaa Nai Maromak ukun nudar Liurai.”
Iha ema ida tan dehan, “Nai, hau hakarak tuir Ita Boot, maibee husik hau baa halo despedida lai ho hau nia familia mak foin hau tuir.”<a href='#note-586' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Ema nebee komesa ona tuir Hau, maibee haree fali ba kotuk, nia la merese servii Nai Maromak nudar nia Liurai.”
Liu tiha, Jesus baa iha provinsia Judeia, ho fatin-fatin iha mota Jordaun nia sorin balu ba. Ema barak mai haleu Nia, i Jesus hanorin sira hanesan baibain.
Iha mos ema Farizeu balu mai ho intensaun atu hamonu Nia. Sira husu nunee, “Tuir ita nia relijiaun nia hanorin, se mane ida kaben tiha ona, nia bele soe nia kaben, ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “Hanoin lai! Lei kona ba feto ho mane, nebee Moisés foo ba ita, dehan halo nusaa?”
Sira hataan, “Lei Moisés nian dehan, ‘Ema bele fahe malu, naran katak foo uluk surat soe malu nian ba nia kaben.’ ”<a href='#note-420' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan fila fali, “Tanba imi nia ulun toos, mak Moisés hakerek hanesan nee.
Imi keta haluha istoria uluk liu kona ba Nai Maromak halo lalehan ho rai. Istoria nee hatete katak,
‘Nai Maromak halo ema, mane ho feto.<a href='#note-421' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni, mane sei husik hela nia inan-aman,
i baa moris neon ida laran ida ho nia kaben,
i sira nain rua, hamutuk ida deit.’<a href='#note-422' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba Nai Maromak hatete ona dehan, sira nain rua hamutuk ida deit, nee duni, ema la bele fahe sira.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira tama ba iha uma ida. Iha nee, sira husu ba Jesus kona ba nia liafuan ohin nee.
Jesus hataan, “Se mane ida soe nia kaben, i kaben fali ho feto seluk, ema nee halo sala.
I feto mos hanesan. Se nia soe tiha nia kaben, i kaben fali ho mane seluk, nia mos halo sala.”<a href='#note-423' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida, ema lori sira nia oan ba Jesus, i sira husu ba Nia atu tau liman hodi foo bensaun ba sira. Maibee Jesus nia eskolante sira bandu netik.
Jesus haree nunee, Nia hirus Nia eskolante sira hodi dehan, “Husik labarik sira mai Hau. Keta bandu! Tanba ema hanesan sira nee, mak Nai Maromak nia ema.
Imi hanoin di-diak! See mak atu sai Nai Maromak nia ema, nia tenki hanoin Nai Maromak hanesan labarik sira hanoin sira nia inan-aman. Se lae, sira la serve atu sai Nai Maromak nia ema.”<a href='#note-424' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee Jesus hakuak labarik oan sira nee, i tau liman ba ida-idak nia ulun, hodi foo bensaun ba sira.
Kuandu Jesus atu sai ona, ema riku ida halai mai hasoru Jesus. Nia hakruuk iha Jesus nia oin, hodi husu, “Mestri mak hau respeita, Ita Boot mak diak. Hau atu husu buat ida nunee: Hau atu halo saida, para hau bele hatene lo-loos katak, hau bele tama lalehan i moris hamutuk ho Nai Maromak?”
Jesus hataan, “Tanba saa mak o dehan, Hau ema diak? La iha ema ida mak diak, so Nai Maromak deit.
O hatene ona, Nai Maromak nia ukun fuan nebee dehan:
‘La bele oho ema.
La bele naok.
La bele foo testemunha falsu.
La bele han-matak ema nia sasaan.
I respeita o nia inan-aman.’ ”<a href='#note-425' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nee hataan, “Loos, mestri! Dezde hau sei kiik, ukun fuan sira nee, hau tuir hotu ona.”
Jesus hadomi ema nee, i dehan, “Nee loos! Maibee sei falta tan buat ida. Agora o fila ona, i baa faan tiha o nia rikusoin hotu. Nia osan nee, o fahe ba ema kiak ho ema susar sira. Foin o mai tuir Hau. Depois Nai Maromak sei foo fali ba o, riku seluk iha lalehan.”
Ema nee rona Jesus dehan nunee, nia laran susar tebe-tebes. Nia fila ho laran tristi atu mate, tanba nia ema riku boot.
Entaun Jesus haree ba-mai, i hatete ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Rona mai! Ema riku, susar tebe-tebes atu tama ba lalehan.”
Rona nunee, Nia eskolante sira mos hakfodak. Maibee Jesus hatete tan, “Rona mai! Atu sai Nai Maromak nia ema, susar tebe-tebes. Keta hanoin dehan ‘fasil’.
Kuda kamelu tama ba nia luhan liu hosi daun kuak, susar liu! Maibee susar liu tan, ema riku atu sai Nai Maromak nia ema, i tama ba lalehan.”
Jesus dehan nunee, halo sira bilaan liu tan. Depois sira husu ba malu, “Se nunee tebes, Nai Maromak salva see?”
Jesus haree ba sira ida-idak, hodi dehan, “Ba ema, la bele duni. Maibee, ba Nai Maromak, buat hotu-hotu bele!”
Depois Pedro hatete ba Jesus, “Amu, ami husik tiha ami nia sasaan hotu-hotu ona, hodi tuir Amu. Maibee ami simu saida?”
29-30 Jesus hataan, “Hau hatete ba imi nunee: See mak tuir Hau, i husik hela nia inan-aman, nia maun-alin, nia oan sira, nia toos, nia servisu, i nia uma laran tomak, hodi foo sai Nai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak, Nai Maromak sei foo fali dala atus ida. Buat hotu-hotu nebee nia husik nee, nia sei simu fali barak liu tan. Nia mos sei hetan terus, tanba nia tuir Hau. Maibee kuandu mundu nee remata, nia sei moris hamutuk ho Nai Maromak tinan ba tinan. Ida nee mak nia simu.
Hanoin di-diak! See mak foti aan boot, tuir Nai Maromak nia hanoin, nia ema kiik liu. Maibee see mak haraik aan hanesan ema kiik, tuir Nai Maromak nia hanoin, nia ema boot.”<a href='#note-426' class='key'>*</a>
Iha tempu nee, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao dadauk ba iha Jerusalém. Jesus lao iha oin. I Nia eskolante sira ho ema seluk tuir Nia. Sira hanoin buat nebee Nia koalia tiha ona uluk, i sira laran rua-rua i tauk. Nunee Jesus bolu deit Nia eskolante sira mesak, hodi foo hatene tan ba sira, saida mak ema atu halo ba Nia iha Jerusalém.
Nia hatete, “Imi rona di-diak! Ita agora atu baa Jerusalém, tanba Hau Mane Maksoin. Maibee iha nebaa, ema sei faan Hau, foo ba mestri relijiaun ho nai lulik nia ulun sira. Depois sira sei tesi lia dehan, Hau tenki mate. Depois sira entrega Hau ba ema sira nebee la konhese Nai Maromak.
I ema sira nee tarata Hau. Sira tafui kabeen ba Hau. Sira baku Hau nia isin hodi sikoti too kanek. Nee hotu tiha, sira oho mate Hau. Hau mate duni. Maibee iha loron tolu,<a href='#note-427' class='key'>†</a> Hau sei moris fali.”
Iha tempu nee, Zebedeu nia oan, Tiago ho João, mai ba Jesus. Sira husu, “Amu, ami presiza Ita Boot.”
Jesus husu, “Imi presiza saida?”
Sira hataan, “Amu, aban-bainrua, kuandu Amu tuur kaer ona ukun, ami husu atu Amu foo fatin ba ami: ida tuur iha Amu nia sorin loos, ida iha sorin karuk. Para ami mos bele kaer ukun.”
Jesus hataan ba sira, “Imi nain rua nee la komprende saida mak imi husu. La kleur tan, Hau hetan terus tebe-tebes. Nunee oinsaa? Imi hanoin katak imi bele terus hamutuk ho Hau too mate ka?”<a href='#note-428' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira hataan, “Ami bele, Amu!”
Jesus hatete tan ba sira, “Loos duni. La kleur tan, imi mos hetan terus hanesan Hau.
Maibee kona ba tuur iha Hau nia sorin loos ka sorin karuk, nee laos Hau nia direitu. Nee Nai Maromak nia direitu. Nia desidi tiha ona, see mak bele tuur iha fatin nee.”
Kuandu Jesus nia eskolante sira seluk rona dehan Tiago ho João husu nunee, sira hirus.
Depois Jesus bolu sira hotu, hodi dehan, “Ema boot sira iha mundu nee, ukun nunee: Sira sempre hanehan sira nia reinu, too reinu sira book aan la diak. Ulun sira hosi nasaun nebee la konhese Nai Maromak, sira mos foo orden todan liu, too sira nia reinu la bele halo buat ida.
Maibee imi la bele halo nunee! See mak atu sai boot, nia tenki haraik aan, i serbi ema seluk.<a href='#note-429' class='key'>✡</a>
I see mak atu sai nai ulun, nia tenki haraik aan, i sai atan ba ema hotu.<a href='#note-430' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira too iha sidade Jerikó. Kuandu sira lao sai hosi sidade nee, ema barak mos tuir. Iha dalan ninin, ema matan aat ida, tuur hela hodi husu ezmola. Nia naran Bartimeu, Senhor Timeu nia oan.
Kuandu nia rona dehan, ema ida liu nee, Jesus hosi Nazaré, nia bolu kedas, “Senhor Jesus, liurai David nia jerasaun! Hanoin lai hau!”
Rona nia bolu nunee, ema hirus nia hodi bandu, dehan, “He! No-nook!”
Maibee nia bolu ho lian makaas liu tan, “Senhor Jesus, liurai David nia jerasaun! Hadomi hau lai!”
Nunee Jesus mos para tiha, hodi dehan, “Imi bolu nia mai!”
I sira dehan ba ema matan aat nee, “Senhor Mestri rona o ona, i Nia bolu o. Hamriik ona!”
Rona nunee, Bartimeu soe tiha nia manta, hamriik kedan, i baa hasoru Jesus.
Jesus husu, “O hakarak saida?”
Ema matan aat nee hataan, “Mestri, hau husu atu hau bele haree.”
Jesus hatete tan, “Tanba o fiar katak Hau bele kura o, agora o nia matan diak ona.”
I nia matan mos diak kedan. Hotu tiha, nia tuir kedan Jesus.
Kuandu sira besik ona sidade Jerusalém, sira too iha aldeia Betfage ho Betánia, iha Foho Oliveira nia lolon.<a href='#note-431' class='key'>*</a> Jesus haruka Nia eskolante nain rua baa uluk,
dehan, “Imi nain rua baa uluk iha aldeia ida nebaa. Too iha nebaa, imi sei haree kuda buru oan ida kesi hela, nebee ema seidauk sae. Imi baa kore tiha, i lori mai iha nee.
Maibee se ema husu karik, ‘Nusaa mak imi lori tiha kuda buru nee?’ Imi hataan nunee, ‘Nai presiza nia. Hotu tiha, Nai haruka fila fali kedan.’ ”
Entaun, ema nain rua nee baa ona. Sira hetan kuda buru oan nee kesi hela iha uma oin, iha dalan ibun. Kuandu sira kore hela kuda oan nee,
ema husu, “Nusaa mak imi kore tiha ema nia kuda buru oan nee?”
Sira hataan, “Nai presiza nia. Hotu tiha, Nai haruka fila fali kedan.” Nunee ema husik sira baa.
Sira lori kuda buru nee ba Jesus. Sira kahe sira nia manta ba kuda nia kotuk, ba Jesus sae.
Kuandu sira tama iha sidade, ema barak hasai sira nia manta hodi nahe iha dalan. Balu mos baa taa ramus tahan hodi tau iha dalan.<a href='#note-432' class='key'>†</a> Sira halo nunee hatudu katak sira simu Nai Jesus ho respeita, hanesan sira simu ema boot ida.
I sira balu lao iha Jesus nia oin, balu iha Nia kotuk. Sira komesa haklalak,
“Hosana! Ami hahii Nai Maromak!<a href='#note-433' class='key'>‡</a>
Nia foo bensaun ba Ema nebee mai hodi Nia naran!<a href='#note-434' class='key'>✡</a>
Hosana! Ami hahii Nai Maromak!
Nia atu harii fali liurai David nia ukun.
Hosana! Ami hahii Nai Maromak iha fatin aas liu!”
Too iha sidade Jerusalém, Jesus tama ba iha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot. Iha nebaa, Jesus haree fatin sira nee hotu. Maibee, tanba tempu la iha tan, maka Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira fila fali ba aldeia Betánia.
Aban fali, sira sai hosi Betánia, baa fali iha sidade Jerusalém. Iha dalan klaran, Jesus senti hamlaha.
Nia haree ai figeira ida. Ai figeira nee, ema sempre haan nia fuan. Nunee Jesus baa besik ai huun nee, hodi haree took, iha fuan ka lae. Maibee Nia too iha ai huun nee, la haree ai fuan ida. Tanba laos tempu nia foo fuan. Ai nee foin dikin.
Jesus hatete ba ai nee, “Tanba o la foo fuan ba Hau haan, nee duni, komesa agora, o la foo tan fuan ona!”
Sira too iha Jerusalém, Jesus baa tama iha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot. Iha Uma oin, ema halo hanesan basar. Sira faan manu pombu, nebee ema hodi foo oferta ba Nai Maromak. Jesus haree nunee, Nia duni sai ema sira nee hotu. Meza sira nebee ema uza hodi troka osan, Nia halo baku-fila hotu. Banku hodi faan manu pombu mos, Nia halo baku-fila hotu.
Nia mos bandu ema hotu la bele lori sasaan tama-sai liu hosi uma kreda boot nia oin.
Depois Nia hanorin sira nunee, “Nai Maromak nia ema uluk hakerek tiha ona dehan ‘Hau halo Hau nia Uma nee, para ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu bele mai harohan iha nee.’ Maibee imi halo tiha Uma nee, hanesan ema naok-teen sira nia fatin.”<a href='#note-435' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira mestri relijiaun ho nai lulik nia ulun sira rona katak Jesus halo hanesan nee, sira hirus tebe-tebes. Nunee sira mos buka dalan hodi bele oho mate Nia. Maibee sira la brani, tanba ema barak mak sei gosta rona Nia liafuan.
Rai komesa kalan ona, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira sai hosi Jerusalém, i fila baa toba iha Betánia.
20-21 Aban dadeer-saan, sira fila ba Jerusalém. Iha dalan klaran sira haree ai figeira horiseik nee. Ai nee maran tiha ona, komesa hosi tutun too abut. Pedro hanoin too Jesus nia liafuan horiseik nee. Nia dehan, “Amu, haree took ai ida horiseik Amu foo malisan nee. Mate tiha ona!”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Loos duni! Imi mos tenki fiar ba Nai Maromak nunee.
Se imi fiar tebe-tebes, imi bele haruka foho ida soe aan tiha ba tasi laran. I Nai Maromak sei muda foho nee, naran katak imi fiar tebes.<a href='#note-436' class='key'>✡</a>
Hanoin di-diak! Buat hotu nebee imi husu ba Nai Maromak, se imi fiar tebes katak Nia sei foo, Nia sei foo duni.
Maibee se imi harohan, i imi hirus hela ema ruma, imi tenki baa diak lai ho ema nee. Nunee foin Nai Maromak iha lalehan mos diak ho imi, i sei hamoos imi nia sala.
[Se imi hirus hela ema ruma, i lakohi diak ho ema nee, Nai Maromak mos la diak ho imi, i la hamoos imi nia sala.]”<a href='#note-437' class='key'>§</a> <a href='#note-438' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira kontinua lao too iha Jerusalém, i tama fali ba uma kreda boot. Iha nebaa, ema barak mak hein hela sira: nai lulik nia ulun sira, mestri relijiaun sira, ho nai ulun sira.
Sira koko Jesus nunee, “See mak haruka O mai halo rungu-ranga horiseik iha nee? See mak foo direitu ba O?”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Hau mos atu husu ba imi. Se imi hataan uluk Hau, mak Hau foin hataan ba imi.
Hau husu nunee: Imi hotu konhese João Sarani Nain. See mak haruka nia baa sarani ema? Nai Maromak ka, ema?”
Rona nunee, sira hanoin ba-mai, i koalia ba malu dehan, “Ita la bele koalia tan ona! Se ita hataan, ‘Aman Maromak mak haruka,’ mak Nia sei hataan fali, ‘Se nunee, nusaa mak imi la fiar ba João?’
Ita mos la brani dehan, ‘Ema mak haruka,’ tanba ema hotu bele hirus. Tanba sira fiar katak João nee, Nai Maromak nia profeta.”
Entaun sira hataan deit ba Jesus nunee, “Ami la hatene.”
Jesus hataan fali, “Se nunee, Hau mos lakohi foo hatene, see mak foo direitu nee ba Hau.”
Jesus koalia nafatin ho nai lulik nia ulun, ho mestri relijiaun, ho nai ulun sira. Nia dehan, “Hau konta istoria ida nunee: Loron ida, iha ema ida baa lere nia rai hodi kuda ai uvas. I nia halo lutu haleu, ho tanki ida hodi sama uvas fuan para hasai nia been. I nia halo mos uma oan ida hodi hein. Depois nia foo toos nee ba ema aluga. Sira promete atu fahe uvas been ho toos nain. Depois toos nain nee baa tiha rai dook.<a href='#note-439' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuandu too ona tempu kuu uvas, toos nain haruka nia ema ida baa husu ona nia uvas been.
Maibee nia foin too, ema aluga toos nee, kaer nia i baku nia. I sira haruka nia fila ho liman mamuk.
Tuir fali mai, toos nain nee haruka tan ema ida baa. Maibee ema aluga toos nee, kaer nia i baku nia ulun too kanek. Sira tarata nia, i duni sai hosi nebaa.
Tuir fali mai, toos nain haruka tan nia ema ida baa. Maibee sira oho tiha nia. Bele sira halo nusaa deit mos, toos nain haruka nafatin nia ema baa. Maibee ema aluga toos nee, baku balu, i oho balu.
Agora hela ema ida deit, toos nain nia oan mane. Nia oan mesak ida deit, i nia hadomi tebe-tebes. Tanba la iha tan dalan seluk, nee duni nia haruka nia oan rasik mak baa. Nia hanoin katak, ‘Hau nia oan rasik nee, sira tenki simu ho diak, i tenki rona nia.’
Nunee nia haruka nia oan rasik baa. Maibee kuandu ema aluga toos nee, haree nia oan nee mai, sira koalia ba malu dehan, ‘Haree lai! Aman katuas haruka nia oan rasik mak mai. Se aban-bainrua, aman katuas mate, nia oan nee mak hetan nia riku hotu. Mai ita oho tiha nia, para ita bele hetan nia riku nee!’
Nunee sira rame-rame kaer tiha nia, i oho tiha nia. Depois sira soe sai tiha nia toos. Istoria nee too iha nee deit.”
Depois Jesus husu ba ema boot sira, “Tuir imi nia hanoin, toos nain nee atu halo saida ba ema aluga toos nee? Tuir Hau nia hanoin, toos nain sei baa iha toos nee, i sei oho tiha sira hotu. Depois nia foo fali nia toos nee ba ema seluk aluga.
Ita hotu lee tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
Maibee agora, fatuk nee sai fali fatuk nebee prinsipal liu.
Nai Maromak rasik mak hili fatuk nee.
Tanba nee, mak ita admira, “Nee diak tebe-tebes!” ’ ”<a href='#note-440' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, ema boot sira komprende ona katak, Jesus koalia kona ba sira liu hosi komparasaun. Sira hanesan ho ema aluga toos nee. Tanba nee, sira buka dalan hodi kaer Nia. Maibee sira la brani, tanba ema barak mak gosta rona Nia. Nunee sira baa ona, husik hela Nia.
Liu tiha nee, nai lulik ho ema boot sira haruka ema Farizeu balu ho liurai Herodes nia ema balu, ba Jesus ho intensaun aat atu koko Nia.
Too ba Jesus, sira hatete, “Senhor, ami hotu hatene katak Senhor nia liafuan loos, i Senhor la fihir ba ema kiik ka boot, maibee haree deit ba ema nia laran. Ita la fila lia tuun-sae, maibee Ita hanorin Nai Maromak nia liafuan ho lo-loos deit. Ami atu husu liafuan ida. Tuir ita nia relijiaun, ita tenki selu osan impostu ba estadu Roma nia liurai boot,<a href='#note-441' class='key'>*</a> ka lae?”
Maibee Jesus hatene ona sira mai ho laran makerek, para halo Nia koalia kontra estadu Roma. Entaun Nia hataan ba sira, “Nusaa mak imi kasa Hau? Foo lai osan moeda ida mai Hau haree took.”
Depois sira foo osan moeda ida ba Jesus, i Nia husu ba sira, “Figura nee, see nia oin? Naran nee, see nian?”
Sira hataan, “Nee Sesar, estadu Roma nia liurai boot.”
Entaun Jesus dehan tan ba sira, “Se nunee, imi foo ba estadu buat nebee mak estadu nian. I foo ba Nai Maromak buat nebee mak Nai Maromak nian.”
Rona Nia hataan nunee, sira hotu admira, tanba Nia koalia nee loos. Nunee sira kasa Jesus mos, la hetan.
Nee hotu tiha, iha ema hosi grupu relijiaun seluk baa koko tan Jesus. Sira hosi grupu Saduseu. Sira hanorin katak, ema mate la bele moris fali.<a href='#note-442' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira koalia ho Jesus, dehan, “Senhor, Moisés hakerek hela liafuan nee ba ita: ‘Se mane ida mate husik hela nia kaben feto, maibee la iha oan, mane nia alin tenki kaben fali ho feto faluk nee, para bele foo jerasaun ba nia maun.’<a href='#note-443' class='key'>✡</a>
Agora ami konta istoria ida ba Senhor. Iha maun-alin mane nain hitu. Maun boot kaben uluk, depois nia mate, la iha oan.
Depois nia alin ida tuir nia nee, kaben fali ho feto faluk nee. La kleur nia mos mate, la iha oan. Nunee mos ho alin ida terseiru. Nia kaben ho feto faluk nee, maibee nia mos mate, la iha oan.
Nunee nafatin, too nain hitu nee mate hotu, la iha oan. Tuir mai feto nee mos mate tan.
Agora ami husu nunee: Feto nee kaben ho mane nain hitu. Kuandu Nai Maromak halo moris fali ema mate sira, feto nee kaben loos ho mane ida nebee?”
Jesus hataan, “Se imi husu nunee, nee hatudu katak imi la komprende Nai Maromak nia liafuan iha Livru Sagradu. I imi mos la komprende Nia forsa. Nunee imi sala duni.
Rona di-diak! Nai Maromak nia anju sira iha lalehan la kaben. Bainhira Nai Maromak halo ema mate moris fali, sira mos la kaben ona.
Agora, Hau koalia fali kona ba ema mate bele moris fali ka lae. Iha Moisés nia liafuan, iha istoria ida kona ba ahi lakan iha ai huun badak ida, maibee ahi la haan. Imi hatene ka? Tempu nee, Nai Maromak foo hatene ba Moisés katak, ‘Hau mak Nai Maromak, nebee o nia bei-ala sira adora. Avoo Abraão, avoo Isac ho avoo Jacó. Sira hotu adora nafatin Hau too agora.’<a href='#note-444' class='key'>✡</a>
Se ita lee nunee, ita hatene avoo sira uluk nee moris hela. Tanba Nai Maromak hatete sira adora Nia too agora. Ema mate la bele adora Nai Maromak, maibee ema moris deit mak bele. Nunee, se imi fiar katak ema mate la bele moris fali, imi sala duni.”
Iha loron nee, mestri relijiaun ida rona Jesus diskuti hela ho ema hosi grupu relijiaun Saduseu sira. Nia rona Jesus hataan loos duni sira nia liafuan. Nunee nia husu ba Jesus, “Senhor, hau atu husu liafuan ida. Tuir ita nia relijiaun, iha orden barak tebe-tebes hosi Moisés. Orden ida nebee mak prinsipal liu?”
Jesus hataan, “Orden prinsipal liu mak ida nee:
‘Ema hotu-hotu iha rai Israel, rona di-diak!
Nai Maromak nee, ita nia Maromak, i ita nia Liurai Boot.
La iha tan seluk,
Nia mesak deit!
Nunee ita tenki hadomi Nai Maromak ho neon ho laran tomak.
Ita tenki hanoin nafatin Nia.
i hakaas aan hodi tuir Nia hakarak.’<a href='#note-445' class='key'>✡</a>
I orden segundu mak ida nee:
‘Ita tenki hadomi ema seluk,
hanesan ita hadomi ita nia aan rasik.’
Orden rua nee mak boot liu orden hotu-hotu.”<a href='#note-446' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois mestri relijiaun nee dehan tan ba Jesus, “Nee loos duni, Senhor! Nai Maromak nee ida deit. La iha tan Maromak seluk.<a href='#note-447' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee, ita tenki hadomi Nia liu buat hotu-hotu. Ita tenki hanoin nafatin Nia. Ita tenki rona nafatin Nia Liafuan, i hakaas aan hodi tuir Nia hakarak. I ita mos tenki hadomi ema seluk hanesan ita hadomi ita nia aan rasik. Nee mak Nai Maromak hakarak, duke ita tuir deit relijiaun nia hanorin. Hadomi nunee diak liu, duke ita oho animal hodi halo sakrifisiu i foo oferta ba Nia.”<a href='#note-448' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nia hataan nunee, Jesus hanoin katak, mestri relijiaun nee komprende duni Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Nunee Nia dehan, “O besik ona atu sai Nai Maromak nia ema.”
Hotu tiha, la iha ema mak brani atu koko tan Jesus.<a href='#note-449' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus sei hanorin hela ema sira iha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot. Nia husu ba sira, “Oinsaa? Mestri relijiaun sira hanorin kona ba Kristu nebee Nai Maromak hili ona hori uluk kedan. Sira hanorin dehan, Kristu nee liurai David nia jerasaun deit. Maibee nee seidauk too.
Tanba hori uluk Nai Maromak nia Espiritu Santu uza liurai David hodi hakerek nunee:
‘Nai Maromak hatete ona ba hau nia Liurai dehan,
“Mai tuur iha Hau nia sorin loos, fatin ema boot nian.
Hau sei halo o nia inimigu sira, hakruuk ba o.’ ”<a href='#note-450' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee liurai David rasik bolu Kristu, ‘hau nia Liurai’. Nee duni, se ema dehan Kristu nee, liurai David nia jerasaun deit, nee seidauk too. Tanba Nia mos liurai David nia Liurai!”
Jesus dehan kuidadu ho mestri relijiaun sira, tanba sira gosta fila lia tuun-sae
(Mateus 23:1-36; Lucas 20:45-47)
Ema barak nebee rona Jesus nia hanorin nee, sira gosta loos.
Depois Jesus hatete tan ba sira nunee, “Imi tenki kuidadu di-diak ho mestri relijiaun sira. Sira gosta pasiar ho batina naruk, para ema haree sira, i komprimenta sira hanesan ema boot.
Kuandu sira baa iha uma kreda ka, baa iha festa, sira sempre buka tuur iha fatin ida diak liu, para ema hotu bele gaba sira, i hodi dehan sira, ema boot.
Maibee imi tenki kuidadu! Tanba sira fila lia hodi han-matak feto faluk sira, too hadau sira nia uma hotu. Maibee iha ema barak nia oin, sira finji harohan nar-naruk, hodi taka falta sira nia hahalok aat nee. Para ema bele dehan, sira ema moos. Maibee Nai Maromak sei foo kastigu todan liu ba sira.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus tuur hela besik kaixa oferta iha uma kreda boot laran, hodi haree ema baa tau osan oferta ba kaixa. Iha ema riku barak baa tau osan boot ba kaixa nee.
Iha mos feto faluk kiak ida mai harohan. Nia baa tau doit rua ba iha kaixa laran. Osan nee folin kiik liu.
Depois Jesus bolu Nia eskolante sira hodi hatete, “Imi haree took feto faluk kiak nee. Nia foo osan doit rua deit, maibee nia foo boot liu ema hotu-hotu.
Ema sira seluk foo oferta hosi sira nia osan resin. Maibee feto faluk kiak nee, foo tiha nia osan hotu ba Nai Maromak. Hodi hola hahaan mos, la iha ona.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira sai hosi uma kreda boot. Sira foin sai nunee, Nia eskolante ida hatudu ba uma kreda nee, hodi dehan, “Senhor, haree took ba! Uma kreda nee kapaas loos. I fatuk boot ema hada nee, kapaas tebe-tebes.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Uma kreda nee kapaas duni. Maibee la kleur tan, ema sei baku rahun tiha hotu.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus baa iha foho Oliveira. Nia tuur hodi hateke hela ba Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot. Depois Nia eskolante nain haat baa koalia ho Nia. Ema nain haat nee, Pedro, Tiago, João ho André.
Sira husu, “Senhor, halo favor, foo hatene fali kona ba Ita nia liafuan ohin nee. Bainhira mak tempu nee too? Ho sinal-sinal saida mak sei mosu?”
Tanba ema barak sei mai dehan, ‘Hau nee Kristu, ida nebee Nai Maromak promete hori uluk ona.’ Nunee sira sei bosok ema barak.
Se imi haree ema funu, ou imi rona lia kontadu dehan ema funu iha fatin-fatin, imi keta tauk. Tanba buat sira nee tenki mosu uluk, molok mundu nee remata.
Suku sei funu hasoru suku. Nasaun sei funu hasoru nasaun. Rai sei nakdoko iha fatin-fatin. I rai sei hamlaha boot. Buat sira nee hotu sinal, hanesan feto ida foin komesa kanotak moras, atu besik tuur-ahi.
Nee duni, imi tenki atensaun di-diak! Tanba ema sei mai kaer imi, hodi baa iha tribunal relijiaun nian. Ema sei baku imi iha uma kreda laran, i sei kesi imi lori ba iha ukun nain sira, tanba imi tuir Hau. Maibee imi tenki foo sai Hau nia Liafuan Diak ba sira.
Tanba ema hosi suku hotu-hotu iha mundu tomak tenki rona uluk Hau nia Liafuan Diak, foin mundu nee remata.
Hanoin di-diak! Kuandu ema kesi i lori imi ba tribunal, imi lalika hakfodak. La bele tauk kona ba saida mak imi atu koalia. Imi tenki koalia deit tuir saida mak Espiritu Santu foo hatene ba imi.<a href='#note-451' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha uma laran ida, se iha ema balu fiar ba Hau, nia maun-alin rasik mak sei buka dalan hodi oho nia. I se oan mak fiar, nia aman rasik mak sei oho. Nunee mos, se inan-aman mak fiar ba Hau, nia oan mak sei oho.
Nunee ema sei odi makaas imi, tanba imi fiar ba Hau. Maibee see mak fiar nafatin ba Hau too mate, Nai Maromak sei salva nia.”<a href='#note-452' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus koalia tan, “Iha Ema Aat Liu sei mai. Nia sei tama baa hamriik iha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot laran, iha fatin ida nebee lulik liu. Tuir loos, nia la iha direitu atu tama iha fatin nee. Nee duni, tanba nia tama ona, ema hotu sei hakribi fatin nee, i Nai Maromak mos fila kotuk tiha. Se imi haree nunee, kuidadu di-diak! (See mak lee ida nee, nia mos tenki komprende i kuidadu.) Sinal nee hatudu katak, loron terus besik ona. Se haree ona nunee, ema iha provinsia Judeia tenki halai ona ba foho.<a href='#note-453' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira tenki halai lailais, para la bele hetan susar. Ema nebee sai ona hosi uma, la bele fila fali baa foti sasaan.
Nunee mos ema nebee mak iha toos, la bele fila fali baa foti tan nia hena. Nia tenki halai ba oin nafatin.<a href='#note-454' class='key'>✡</a>
Tempu nee susar liu ba feto sira nebee mak sei isin-rua, ho sira nebee mak sei foo susu ba sira nia oan. Tanba sira halai la bele.
Nee duni, diak liu imi harohan hodi husu tempu aat nee, la bele monu iha tempu udan.
Tanba tempu terus nee, susar atu mate. Komesa Nai Maromak halo mundu nee too agora, ema seidauk hetan terus boot ida nunee. Nee liu tiha, ema sei la haree tan terus boot ida hanesan nee.<a href='#note-455' class='key'>✡</a>
Se Nai Maromak mak la halo badak tempu terus nee, la iha tan ema ida atu moris. Maibee tanba Nia hadomi Nia ema sira nebee Nia hili ona, nunee Nia habadak tempu terus nee.
Iha tempu nee, imi sei rona ema dehan, ‘Haree took! Kristu iha nee!’ I ema seluk dehan, ‘Kristu iha nebaa!’ Maibee imi keta rona.
Tanba ema sei mai foti aan, dehan, ‘Hau nee mak Kristu!’ Iha seluk tan dehan, ‘Hau nee Nai Maromak nia profeta nebee tatoli Nia liafuan. Imi rona mai!’ Sira sei halo milagre oi-oin ho diabu nia forsa hodi bosok ema. Sira mos hakaas aan atu halo Nai Maromak nia ema sira monu.
Nee duni, imi tenki kuidadu di-diak! Tanba tempu terus nee seidauk too mai, maibee Hau foo hatene kedan ba imi ona.”
Depois Jesus foo hatene tan ba Nia eskolante sira nunee, “Kuandu tempu terus nee hotu tiha ona,
‘Loro matan sei nakukun,
fulan mos la naroman tan.<a href='#note-456' class='key'>✡</a>
Fitun sira monu hosi lalehan,
i forsa hotu-hotu iha lalehan sei nakdoko arbiru.’<a href='#note-457' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee liu tiha, foin ema haree Hau, Mane Maksoin, tuun mai ho kalohan. Nunee ema sei haree Hau nia naroman nabilan, ho Hau nia forsa boot.<a href='#note-458' class='key'>✡</a>
I Hau sei haruka Nai Maromak nia anju sira hosi lalehan baa halibur ema hotu-hotu nebee Hau hili tiha ona, hosi mundu tomak. Hosi rai ulun too rai ikun, hosi loro-sae too loro-monu, hosi tasi feto too tasi mane.”
Hau halo komparasaun hosi ai huun ida. Kuandu ai tahan kinur ona, nee hatudu katak besik ona bailoro.
Nunee mos, kuandu tempu terus nebee Hau hatete ba imi, too ona, nee hatudu katak Hau besik fila ona.
Agora, rona di-diak! Hosi ema hotu nebee moris agora, iha balu sei moris too tempu terus nee too mai.
Lalehan ho mundu nee sei remata, maibee Hau nia Liafuan sei la lakon.
Nee duni, imi tenki neon moris matan moris! Tanba imi la hatene loron nebee mak Hau sei fila mai.
La kleur tan, Hau husik hela imi ona, maibee Hau sei fila fali mai. Hanesan ema ida baa rai dook. I nia haruka nia ema uma laran tau matan ba nia uma nee. I nia fahe servisu ba ema ida-idak. I nia foo orden ba ema seguransa atu hein uma nee di-diak too nia fila.<a href='#note-460' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos, imi tenki hein loron-kalan, tanba imi la hatene bainhira mak uma nain fila. Fila lokraik ka, kalan boot ka, dadeer-saan nakukun ka, meiu-dia ka, imi la hatene.
Keta halo be nia fila derepenti, imi toba nakoron hela.
Nunee, saida mak Hau hatete ba imi nee, Hau hatete mos ba ema hotu-hotu, ‘Imi tenki neon moris matan moris, hodi hein Hau mai.’ ”
[Too iha nee, Nai Jesus mos para ona koalia ho Nia eskolante sira iha foho Oliveira.]
1-2 Nee liu tiha, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira buka tempu diak hodi kaer Jesus ho nonook para oho. Maibee sira dehan, “Hein lai. Ita la bele kaer lai Nia, tanba loron boot besik ona. Keta halo be ema barak halo rungu-ranga.”
Sira koalia nunee, tanba loron rua tan, ema Judeu sira nia loron boot, ida nebee sira bolu festa ‘Paskua’, ho ‘Festa Paun la Tau Fermentu’. Iha loron festa nee, sira hanoin fali tempu uluk, nebee sira nia bei-ala sira sai hosi Rai Ejiptu.<a href='#note-461' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha aldeia Betánia, iha ema ida naran Simão. Uluk ema hotu hakribi nia, tanba nia hetan moras lepra. Maibee agora nia diak tiha ona.
Antes loron boot too, Jesus baa haan iha Simão nia uma. Momentu sira haan hela, iha feto ida mai hasoru Jesus. Nia lori mina morin botir ida. Mina morin nee folin karu tebe-tebes.<a href='#note-462' class='key'>*</a> Depois nia baku rahun tiha botir nia ibun, i fui mina morin nee ba Jesus nia ulun. Nee hatudu katak nia respeita Jesus hanesan ema boot.
Maibee iha fatin nee, iha mos ema seluk. Kuandu sira haree nia halo nunee, sira hirus nia. I sira dehan ba malu, “See mak feto ida nee? Nusaa mak nia bele fui saugati tiha mina morin ida karu tebe-tebes nee?!
Diak liu nia faan deit mina morin nee. I nia osan hodi baa foo ba ema kiak sira. Tanba mina morin nee folin karu, hanesan badaen ida manaan osan iha tinan ida nia laran.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Imi keta hirus feto nee. Husik ba. Hau kontenti, tanba nia tau ona mina morin nee ba Hau nia isin.
Ema kiak sira sempre hamutuk ho imi. Nunee imi bele ajuda sira iha loron nebee deit. Maibee la kleur tan, Hau la hamutuk ho imi ona. Tanba Hau nia mate besik ona.<a href='#note-463' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema atu hakoi Hau. Maibee feto nee tau kedan ona mina morin ba Hau. Nunee, nia halo buat diak ida.
Hanoin di-diak! Bainhira ema foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan iha mundu tomak, sira mos sei konta kona ba feto nee nia hahalok diak nee. Nunee, ema hotu bele hanoin kona ba nia.”
Nee liu tiha, Jesus nia eskolante ida hosi sira nain sanulu resin rua nee, sai hosi Simão nia uma. Nia Judas Iscariotes. Nia baa buka nai lulik nia ulun sira, atu faan Jesus ba sira.
Hasoru tiha sira, nia kontratu atu entrega Jesus ba sira. Kuandu sira rona nia koalia nunee, sira gosta tebes. I sira promete dehan, “Se o halo nunee, ami sei foo osan.” Depois Judas sai baa buka dalan hodi foo Jesus ba sira.
Depois ema Judeu sira nia loron boot komesa. Iha loron primeiru sira tunu paun, maibee la tau fermentu. I sira mos oho bibi malae hodi halo festa. Nunee Jesus nia eskolante sira mai husu ba Nia, “Senhor, ita hakarak ami baa prepara festa Paskua iha nebee?”
Jesus haruka Nia eskolante nain rua dehan, “Imi baa uluk iha sidade Jerusalém. Imi sei hetan mane ida hasaan bee iha sanan rai ida. Imi tuir deit nia.
Nia tama ba uma nebee, imi tuir deit nia. Depois imi hatete ba uma nain nunee, ‘Senhor, ami nia Mestri husu fatin ida, para nia uza hodi halo festa Paskua ho Nia eskolante sira.’
Depois ema nee sei hatudu kuartu boot ida iha uma andar leten. Nia prepara kompletu tiha fatin nee ona. Hela deit imi nain rua baa prepara hahaan.”
Nunee sira nain rua baa ona iha sidade. Iha nebaa sira hetan buat hotu-hotu tuir Jesus hatete ona ba sira. I sira prepara hahaan festa Paskua nian. Depois sira baa bolu Jesus.
Lokraik ona, Jesus ho Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua baa iha nebaa.
Sira tuur hodi haan hamutuk. Sira sei haan hela, Jesus komesa koalia, “Imi rona mai! Iha ema ida hosi imi mak sei faan Hau ba ema seluk.”<a href='#note-464' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, sira laran susar tebe-tebes. I sira ida-idak husu ba Jesus dehan, “Senhor, laos hau, to?”
Jesus hataan, “Ema nebee hoban nia paun hamutuk ho Hau iha manko nee, nia mak sei faan Hau.
Rona di-diak! Hau, Mane Maksoin. Hau tenki mate duni tuir saida mak sira hakerek ona iha Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Maibee imi tenki kuidadu! Ema nebee faan Hau nee, nia rasik sei lori nia todan. Diak liu nia inan la bele hahoris nia iha mundu nee.”
Sira sei haan hela, Jesus foti paun fuan ida, hodi foo agradese ba Nai Maromak. Depois nia silu paun nee i fahe ba Nia eskolante sira. Nia hatete, “Paun nee Hau nia isin. Simu hodi haan ba.”
I Nia hatete, “Tua nee Hau nia raan. Raan nee, sei fakar hodi salva ema barak. Raan nee hatudu katak buat nebee mak Nai Maromak promete ona, agora mosu tiha ona. Simu hodi hemu ba.<a href='#note-465' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona di-diak! Komesa kalan nee, Hau la hemu tan tua ona. Too Hau tuur hodi ukun ho Hau nia Aman iha lalehan, foin Hau hemu fali.”
Nee hotu tiha, sira kanta hamutuk hodi hahii Nai Maromak. Depois sira sai, hodi baa iha foho Oliveira.
Iha dalan klaran, Jesus hatete ba sira, “Orsida kalan, imi hotu-hotu sei halai husik hela Hau mesak. Nee tuir Nai Maromak nia liafuan nebee ema hakerek tiha ona:
‘Hau sei oho tiha bibi atan.
Nunee nia bibi sira sei halai namkari.’<a href='#note-466' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau sei mate duni. Maibee kuandu Hau moris fali, Hau baa uluk imi iha provinsia Galileia.”<a href='#note-467' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, Pedro kontra kedas Jesus hodi dehan, “Amu, bele ema hotu halai husik hela Amu, maibee hau mak lae duni. Hau sei la husik Amu hela mesak.”
Jesus hataan, “Apeu, hanoin di-diak! Orsida kalan, molok manu kokoreek dala rua, o sei nega Hau dala tolu.”
Pedro simu tan, “Lae, Amu! Bele ema atu oho hau mos, hau sei la nega Amu!”
Pedro nia kolega sira mos hatete nunee.
Nee liu tiha, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao nafatin too iha plantasaun ida iha foho Oliveira. Fatin nee naran Getsemani. Jesus hatete ba Nia eskolante sira, “Imi tuur lai iha nee. Hau sei baa harohan iha nebaa.”
Nia lori deit Pedro, Tiago ho João ba hamutuk ho Nia. Momentu nee, Nia laran komesa susar i tristi tebe-tebes.
Nia hatete ba sira, “Hau nia laran susar liu! Too Hau senti atu mate deit. Imi hein lai iha nee.”
35-36 Depois Jesus lao ba oin uitoan. Nia monu ba rai, i harohan ho laran susar. Nia dehan nunee, “Apaa doben. Se Apaa hataan, Hau lalika simu terus too mate hanesan nee. Apaa bele halo buat hotu-hotu. Nunee, se bele, Apaa hasai tiha terus nee hosi Hau. Maibee la bele tuir Hau nia hakarak. Tuir deit Apaa nia hakarak.”
Liu tiha, Nia fila ba Nia eskolante nain tolu nee, maibee sira toba dukur hela. I Nia fanu sira, hodi dehan ba Pedro, “Apeu,<a href='#note-468' class='key'>†</a> o toba ka?! Hau iha nebaa la kleur ida. Nusaa mak imi la bele hein uitoan?!
Hadeer ona! Imi nia laran hakarak duni halo buat diak, maibee imi nia isin mak fraku. Tanba nee, imi tenki harohan, para kuandu hetan tentasaun ruma, imi la monu.”<a href='#note-469' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus baa harohan dala ida tan. Nia husu fali ba Nai Maromak para Nia la bele simu terus boot nee.
Depois Nia mai, haree Nia eskolante nain tolu nee. Maibee sira toba hela tan, tanba sira matan dukur atu mate. I Nia fanu fali sira, maibee sira la hatene saida mak sira atu hataan ba Nia.
Nee liu tiha, Jesus husik hela sira, hodi baa harohan tan. Nee dala tolu ona. Liu tiha, Nia mai fanu sira. Nia dehan, “Imi sei toba tan ka?! Too ona! Hau Mane Maksoin. Agora, ema mai kaer Hau, hodi entrega ba ema aat sira nia liman.
Hadeer ona! Loke imi nia matan hodi haree took. Ema ida atu faan Hau nee, mai ona. Mai ita baa hasoru sira.”
Jesus sei koalia hela, Judas mos mai ho ema barak. Sira lori ai dona ho punhal hodi kaer Jesus. Sira tuir orden hosi nai lulik nia ulun sira, mestri relijiaun sira, ho nai ulun sira.
Antes sira mai, Judas foo sinal kedas dehan, “Imi haree di-diak! Ema ida hau baa rei nee, Nia mak nee. Imi kaer kedan Nia i lori ba.”
Nunee, kuandu Judas too ba, nia baa kedas Jesus hodi hatete, “Mestri!” I nia mos rei Jesus.
Haree Judas nia sinal, ema barak mai kaer Jesus.
Maibee Jesus nia eskolante ida losu espada, hodi tesi tiha ema ida nia tilun. Ema kanek nee, nai lulik boot nia atan.
Jesus mos hatete ba ema sira nebee kaer Nia, “Nusaa! Imi hanoin Hau ema naok-teen ka? Nee mak imi mai atu kaer Hau lori ai dona ho espada!
Loro-loron Hau hanorin hela imi iha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot laran, maibee la iha ema ida atu kaer Hau. Agora, mai kaer Hau ona ba! Tanba nee, hakerek tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu.”<a href='#note-470' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus nia eskolante sira tauk atu mate. I sira hotu halai namkari soe hela Jesus mesak deit.
maibee sira kaer deit mak nia hena, i nia halai ho isin molik deit, tanba nia tauk atu mate.
Liu tiha nee, sira lori Jesus ba iha nai lulik boot nia uma. Iha uma nee, ema Judeu nia ema boot sira halibur malu hodi foo justisa ba Jesus. Sira nai lulik nia ulun sira, mestri relijiaun sira, ho nai ulun sira.
Kuandu ema kaer ona Jesus hodi ba, Pedro mos tuir subar hosi kotuk, too iha nai lulik boot nia uma. Nia mos tama ba iha kintal laran, i baa haneruk ahi hamutuk ho ema sira iha nebaa.
Iha uma laran, nai lulik nia ulun sira koalia ho membru sira hosi Konselhu Relijiaun Judeu nian. Sira hotu buka Jesus nia sala atu hamonu Nia, para bele kastigu mate Nia. Maibee sira buka Jesus nia sala, la hetan.
Sira bolu ema barak mak mai foo testemunha. Maibee testemunha sira nee, liafuan la haan malu.
Iha ema balu hamriik foo testemunha falsu, hodi hatete,
“Ami rona ema nee dehan, ‘Hau sei halo rahun tiha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot, nebee ema halo ho liman. Depois, iha loron tolu,<a href='#note-471' class='key'>‡</a> Hau sei harii fila fali uma nee, maibee la uza ona ema nia liman.’ ”<a href='#note-472' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee sira nia liafuan nee mos, la haan malu.
Depois nai lulik boot hamriik iha ema barak sira nia oin, hodi husu ba Jesus, “Ema barak foo sala ba o. Nusaa mak o nonook deit?”
Maibee Jesus la hataan liafuan ida. Nai lulik boot husu dala ida tan ba Nia, “O hatete lai! Nai Maromak promete ona hori uluk atu haruka Kristu mai. O mak Kristu, Nai Maromak nia Oan, ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “Loos duni! Hau mak Kristu. Imi sei haree Hau, Mane Maksoin, tuur iha Nai Maromak nia liman loos hodi ukun hamutuk ho Nia, Ida nebee Forsa tebe-tebes. I imi sei haree Hau tuun ho kalohan hosi lalehan mai.”<a href='#note-473' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona Jesus koalia nunee, nai lulik boot hirus aat liu, too nia lees tiha nia hena. Depois nia hatete ba ema barak nee, “Ita la presiza tan testemunha ona.
Imi rona ona ho tilun rasik, Nia rasik dehan, Nia mak Nai Maromak nia Oan rasik. Hanesan nee, Nia hatete aat Nai Maromak. Tuir ita nia lei relijiaun, see mak foti aan hanesan ho Nai Maromak, ema nee tenki oho mate. Agora, ita tesi halo nusaa?”
Sira hotu-hotu tesi nunee, “Ema ida nee sala duni. Nia tenki mate!”<a href='#note-474' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois ema balu tafui kabeen ba Jesus. Sira taka tiha Nia matan, i tuku Nia hodi husu, “He! O siik took. See mak tuku O nee?” Depois sira foo orden ba ema seguransa sira hosi uma kreda boot atu mai lori Jesus. I ema seguransa sira mos baku Nia.
66-67 Iha momentu nee, Pedro sei tuur hela iha kintal laran hodi haneruk ahi. Nai lulik boot nia kriada ida, baa fihir di-diak Pedro nia oin, hodi hatete, “Ohin o mos hamutuk ho Jesus, ema Nazaré nee. Loos ka lae?”
Pedro hataan, “Lae ida! Nusaa mak o husu nunee?! Hau la konhese Nia.” Depois Pedro hamriik, baa tiha iha portaun. [Iha momentu nee duni, manu mos kokoreek.]<a href='#note-475' class='key'>§</a>
Depois kriada nee haree tan Pedro. Feto nee komesa hatete ba ema hotu-hotu iha kintal laran, “Nia nee hosi sira nia ema.”
Pedro hataan ho makaas, “O bulak karik! Ema ida nee, hau la konhese duni.”
La kleur, ema ida tan hatete ba Pedro nunee, “He! Nusaa mak o sei fila lia tuun-sae, dehan o la konhese ema nee?! Hau hatene imi hotu ema Galileia.”
Maibee Pedro nega tan, dehan, “Hau jura! Hau la konhese ema nee.”
Nia foin koalia nunee, manu mos kokoreek dala ida tan. Pedro hanoin too Jesus nia liafuan nebee dehan, “Molok manu kokoreek dala rua, o sei nega Hau dala tolu.”
Nunee Pedro tanis.
Rai huun mutin, ema boot sira tesi dehan Jesus tenki mate. Depois sira kesi tiha Jesus, i lori ba governador Pilatus.
Kuandu sira too iha Pilatus, nia husu ba Jesus, “Nusaa? O mak ema Judeu sira nia liurai duni ka?”
Jesus hataan, “Loos. Ita Boot dehan nee, loos duni.”
Depois nai lulik nia ulun sira koalia ho governador Pilatus, dehan, “Ema ida nee halo sala barak ona.” I sira foo sai Nia sala ida-idak.
Depois governador Pilatus husu dala ida tan ba Jesus, “O la rona sira nia koalia nee? Sira foo sala barak ba o. Nusaa mak o la defende aan?”
Maibee Jesus la hataan liafuan ida, too halo governador nee mos admira.
Iha loron nee, iha ema kastigu ida iha kadeia, naran Barabás. Uluk ema kaer nia, tanba nia kontra estadu Roma, i nia mos oho ema.
Tanba festa Paskua besik ona, ema barak baa iha governador Pilatus. Sira husu dehan, “Senhor governador, loron Paskua too ona. Se bele, senhor governador hasai ema ida hosi kadeia hanesan baibain.”
Governador hataan fali dehan, “Hau atu hasai see? Imi hakarak hau hasai mak ema Judeu sira nia liurai nee? Imi hataan ka lae?”
Governador koalia nunee, tanba nia hatene ona katak nai lulik nia ulun sira odi tebe-tebes Jesus.
Maibee nai lulik nia ulun sira, tau lia ba ema barak nee, atu sira husu ba governador, “Ami lakohi simu Nia. Hasai mak Barabás.”
Rona nunee, governador husu tan fali, “Se nunee, hau tenki halo saida ba Jesus nee, ida nebee imi bolu liurai Judeu?”
Sira hotu-hotu hakilar hodi dehan, “Oho tiha Nia! Prega tiha Nia ba krus!”
Depois governador husu tan, “Maibee Nia sala saida? Tuir hau nia hanoin, Nia la iha sala ida.”
Maibee sira hotu-hotu hakilar makaas liu tan dehan, “Oho tiha Nia! Prega tiha Nia ba krus ona!”
Tanba governador atu halo ema barak laran kontenti, nia hasai Barabás hosi kadeia, tuir sira nia hakarak. Depois nia foo orden ba soldadu sira baku Jesus ho sikoti.<a href='#note-476' class='key'>*</a> Baku tiha hotu, sira lori Jesus atu prega iha krus too mate.
Nee liu tiha, soldadu sira lori Jesus ba iha sira nia akampamentu.<a href='#note-477' class='key'>†</a> Depois sira bolu soldadu hosi batalhaun tomak mai hamutuk.
Sira foo batina kor mean ida ba Jesus hatais. Batina hanesan nee, liurai sira mak hatais. I sira halo mos koroa ida hanesan liurai sira mak tau. Maibee koroa ida atu tau ba Jesus nee, sira halo hosi ai tarak. I sira hanehan koroa nee ba Nia ulun. Nunee, sira halo Jesus hodi halimar hanesan atu foti Nia sai liurai.
Tuir mai sira halo trosa ba Nia hodi hatete, “Ita Boot, mak ema Judeu sira nia liurai.”
Sira mos finji hakneak ho hakruuk iha Jesus nia oin. I sira tafui kabeen fila-fila ba Nia oin. I sira baku Nia ulun beibeik ho ai.
Sira tarata tiha hotu Nia, sira hasai tiha batina, i foo hatais fali ho Nia hena rasik. Tuir mai, sira lori Jesus sai hosi sidade Jerusalém atu baa prega iha krus too mate.
Iha loron nee, iha ema ida hosi sidade Sirene, atu tama ba iha Jerusalém. Nia naran Simão, Alexandre ho Rufo sira nia aman. Kuandu soldadu sira lori Jesus sai hosi Jerusalém, sira hasoru Simão nee. Sira kaer tiha nia, hodi obriga nia hasaan Jesus nia krus.<a href='#note-478' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira lori Jesus baa iha fatin ida naran Golgota. Nee katak, ‘fatin ulun ruin nian’.
Too iha fatin nee, sira atu foo tua siin ho ai moruk ba Jesus hemu, para Nia bele aguenta terus. Maibee Nia lakohi hemu.
24-25 Depois soldadu sira latan Jesus iha ai krus hodi prega Nia. Depois sira harii tiha ai krus nee, iha tuku sia dadeer-saan. I sira halo rifa para hatene see mak bele hetan Jesus nia hena.<a href='#note-479' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois sira hakerek iha ai kabelak ida, dehan nunee,
Ema ida nee Judeu sira nia liurai.
I sira prega ai kabelak nee iha Jesus nia ulun leten. Sira hakerek nunee, hodi hatudu tan saa mak sira iha direitu atu oho Jesus.
Iha fatin nee, sira prega mos ema naok-teen boot nain rua. Ida iha krus iha Jesus nia liman loos, ida iha Nia liman karuk.
[Nunee tuir Nai Maromak nia liafuan nebee hakerek ona: “Ema sei halo Nia hanesan ema aat ida.”]<a href='#note-480' class='key'>‡</a> <a href='#note-481' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha mos ema nebee liu hosi fatin nee. Kuandu sira haree Jesus prega hela iha krus, sira doko ulun, hodi hatete aat, atu halo moe Nia, “He! O mak dehan atu halo rahun tiha Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot, i depois O atu harii fali iha loron tolu.<a href='#note-482' class='key'>§</a> <a href='#note-483' class='key'>✡</a>
O tuun took hosi krus nee. Salva O nia aan rasik. Nunee ami bele fiar katak, O Nai Maromak nia Oan duni.”
Nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira mos hatete aat Jesus dehan, “Nia bele salva ema seluk. Maibee Nia la bele salva Nia aan rasik.
Uluk Nia hatete ona, Nia mak Kristu, ema ida nebee Nai Maromak promete ona hori uluk. Nia mos dehan, Nia ema Judeu sira nia liurai. Se loos nunee, husik Nia mesak tuun hosi krus nee. Ita tenki haree rasik ho ita nia matan, foin ita fiar ba Nia.”
Sira nain rua nebee prega hamutuk ho Nia mos, tarata Nia.
Iha lokraik tuku tolu, Jesus hakilar ho Nia lian, “Eloi! Eloi! Lama sabaktani!” Nee katak, “Hau nia Nai! Hau nia Maromak! Nusaa mak O husik hela Hau nunee?”<a href='#note-484' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-485' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema balu besik krus nee, rona Jesus nia lian. I sira dehan ba malu, “Imi rona took. Nia bolu Elias, Nai Maromak nia profeta uluk.”
I iha ema ida halai baa foti esponza, halo bokon ho tua siin. Depois nia tuu iha ai naruk ida, i halolo ba Jesus nia ibun, para Nia hemu. I ema nee dehan, “Mai ita haree took! Elias keta mai hatuun Nia hosi krus karik.”<a href='#note-486' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus hakilar dala ida tan, i Nia mate.
Iha kortina ida iha uma kreda boot hodi haketak Nai Maromak nia fatin santu. Natoon loos Jesus mate, kortina nee mos naklees ba rua, hosi leten too kraik.<a href='#note-487' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Golgota, iha komandante ida hamriik besik Jesus nia krus. Bainhira nia haree Jesus nia mate, nia admira hodi hatete, “Tebes duni! Ema ida nee Nai Maromak nia Oan.”
40-41 Iha mos feto barak mak haree Jesus nia mate hosi dook deit. Sira mos tuir Jesus. Uluk sira serbi Jesus iha Galileia, depois sira mai iha Jerusalém hamutuk ho Nia. Entre feto sira nee, iha Salome, Maria hosi rai Madala, ho Maria ida tan (Tiago kiik ho José sira nia inan).<a href='#note-488' class='key'>✡</a>
42-43 Liu tiha nee, iha ema ida buka dalan atu hatuun Jesus nia isin hosi krus. Ema nee naran José, hosi sidade Arimateia. Nia mos membru hosi Konselhu Relijiaun Judeu nian. Nia laran diak. I nia sempre hein Nai Maromak nia ukun atu mai.
Jesus mate iha loron Sesta. Aban fali, ema Judeu sira nia loron hodi harohan. Loron nee, sira la bele halo buat ida. Tanba nee mak José atu tau kedan Jesus nia isin ba rate. Nia foo brani nia aan, hodi baa husu lisensa iha governador Pilatus atu hatuun Jesus nia isin.
Kuandu governador rona José husu nunee, nia hakfodak hodi dehan, “Nusaa mak ema nee mate lailais nunee?! Hau hanoin katak, Nia seidauk mate.”
Nunee nia haruka ema baa bolu komandante mai, hodi husu, “Oinsaa? Jesus nee mate tiha ona ka, seidauk?”
Komandante nee hataan, “Nia mate tiha ona, senhor.” Governador rona nunee, nia foo lisensa ba José para bele baa hatuun Jesus nia isin.
Nunee José sosa hena foun ida nebee karu tebes. Depois nia baa iha Golgota, i baa hatuun Jesus nia isin hosi krus. Nia falun mate nee halo di-diak hodi hena foun nee. Iha rate ida, ema foin bahat hotu iha fatuk lolon. José sira lori Jesus nia isin baa hatama iha fatuk kuak nee. Depois sira duir fatuk boot ida, hodi taka netik fatuk kuak nee. Hotu tiha, José sira fila ona.
Maria hosi rai Madala, ho Maria (José nia inan), sira nain rua haree José sira hatama Jesus nia isin ba fatuk kuak nee. I sira haree di-diak hodi hatene dalan ba fatin nee.
Aban fali, loron Sabadu, ema Judeu sira nia loron hodi deskansa. Kalan nee kedas, Salome, ho Maria hosi rai Madala, ho Maria ida tan (Tiago nia inan), sira baa hola mina morin. Tanba aban fali, sira atu baa hisik Jesus nia isin, tuir Judeu sira nia kostumi.
Iha loron Domingu, dadeer-saan nakukun, sira nain tolu baa iha rate.
3-4 Iha dalan klaran, sira hatete ba malu, “Orsida see mak atu duir fatuk hosi rate ibun ba ita? Ita nain tolu la iha forsa atu dudu fatuk nee, tanba todan tebe-tebes.”
Maibee bainhira sira too iha fatin nee, sira haree fatuk boot nee muda sees tiha ona.
Depois sira tama ba fatuk kuak laran. I sira hakfodak tebe-tebes, tanba sira haree mane klosan ida tuur hela iha sira nia liman loos. Nia hena, mutin loos.
I mane nee hatete ba sira nunee, “Imi keta tauk. Hau hatene imi mai buka Jesus hosi rai Nazaré, ida nebee ema oho iha krus. Nia la iha nee tan ona. Tanba Nia moris fali ona. Mai imi haree rasik fatin nebee sira latan Nia isin. Mamuk tiha ona.
Imi fila lailais ona! Imi baa foo hatene ba Pedro sira katak, Jesus moris fali ona. Nia baa uluk sira iha Galileia, i sira sei hasoru Nia iha nebaa. Tuir buat nebee uluk Nia promete ona ba sira. Agora, imi fila ona.”<a href='#note-489' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira feto sira nee baa haree fatin nee mamuk duni, sira hakfodak! Sira halai sai kedas, i fila lailais. Iha dalan, sira la foo hatene ba ema ida, tanba sira tauk atu mate.
[Dokumentu Gregu balu hakerek tan hanesan tuir mai nee
Kuandu feto nain tolu nee too ba iha Pedro sira, sira foo hatene kona ba mane klosan ida ohin koalia ho sira iha rate laran.<a href='#note-490' class='key'>*</a>  Liu tiha nee, Jesus rasik foo orden ba Nia eskolante sira, para sira baa foo sai Nia Liafuan Diak nee iha fatin hotu-hotu, hosi rai ulun too rai ikun. Liafuan Diak nee katak, Nai Maromak mak salva ema hosi sira nia sala.
Liafuan nee loos tebe-tebes, i nafatin too tinan ba tinan.]
Iha loron Domingu dadeer-saan, Jesus hatudu aan ba Maria hosi Madala. Feto nee, uluk Jesus hasai espiritu aat hitu hosi nia laran.<a href='#note-491' class='key'>†</a>
Nia haree tiha Jesus, nia baa foo hatene kedas ba ema sira uluk tuir Jesus nee. Ema sira nee sei tristi ho tanis hela, hanoin Jesus nia mate.
I Maria foo sai ba sira dehan, “Lalikan tristi ona, tanba Jesus moris fali ona! Hau foin hasoru malu ho Nia!”
Maibee sira hataan, “O bosok!”
Depois sira nain rua fila fali hodi foo hatene ba sira nia kolega sira, “Imi rona lai. Foin dadauk nee, ami hasoru Jesus iha dalan.”
Maibee sira nia kolega hataan, “Bosok! Ami la fiar ida.”
Nee liu tiha, Jesus hasoru malu ho Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin ida, natoon sira haan hela. Nia hatete, “Imi nee ulun fatuk toos duni! Ema hatete ona ba imi katak, sira haree Hau ho sira nia matan rasik, maibee imi la fiar! Imi dehan, sira bosok. Agora, Hau rasik mak mai nee. Hau mate tiha ona, maibee Hau moris fali ona. Imi haree rasik ba.
Nee duni, imi tenki baa iha mundu tomak, i foo sai Hau nia Liafuan Diak nee ba ema hotu-hotu.<a href='#note-492' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak fiar ba Hau, i sarani, Nai Maromak sei salva nia, i nia sei moris hamutuk ho Nai Maromak iha lalehan. Maibee see mak la fiar, Nai Maromak sei kastigu nia, i sei la simu nia iha lalehan.
I ema sira nebee fiar ba Hau, sira sei halo milagre oi-oin, too ema hotu hatene katak, sira nia forsa nee mai hosi Nai Maromak. I sira sei duni sai espiritu aat, hodi Hau nia naran. I Nai Maromak sei halo sira koalia lian oi-oin nebee sira nunka aprende.
I se sira kaer samea nebee iha veneno, ou sira hemu sala veneno, sira la hetan susar. I kuandu sira tau liman ba ema moras, ema moras nee sei sai diak.”
Jesus koalia tiha hotu, Nai Maromak hasae Nia ba lalehan. Nia tuur iha Nai Maromak nia liman loos hodi ukun hamutuk.<a href='#note-493' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee liu tiha, Nia ema sira halo tuir Nia orden. Sira baa iha mundu tomak, hodi foo hatene kona ba Jesus nia Liafuan Diak. I Nai Maromak foo poder ba sira, para sira bele halo milagre, tuir Jesus hatete ona. Nunee ema barak fiar ba Jesus, tanba sira hatene katak Liafuan Diak nee, loos duni.]
Nee istoria diak ida, kona ba Maromak nia Oan,<a href='#note-352' class='key'>*</a> Jesus Kristu. Maromak hili kedan Nia hori uluk ona. Nia istoria komesa nunee:
Antes Jesus atu halao Nia servisu, Maromak haruka ema ida mai uluk tiha ona. Ema nee naran João. João nee tenki mai uluk loke dalan hodi hein Nai Jesus. Maibee molok João mai, Maromak haruka tiha ona Nia profeta ida, naran Isaias. Hori uluk liu, nia hakerek ona nunee:
“Hotu-hotu rona mai!
Hau sei haruka Hau nia ema ida baa uluk, hodi loke dalan ba O.<a href='#note-353' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nee sei baa iha rai ida nebee la iha ema.
I nia koalia ho lian makaas dehan nunee:
‘Hotu-hotu tenki prepara, hamoos dalan hodi simu Nai.
Hadia dalan halo kabeer hodi simu Nia.’ ”<a href='#note-354' class='key'>✡</a>
4-6 João nee, ema sempre bolu, Sarani Nain. Nia hela iha rai fuik. Nia ropa halo hosi kuda kamelu nia fulun. I nia sintu halo hosi animal nia kulit. Nia hahaan mak gafanhotu ho bani been.<a href='#note-355' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia hatete dehan, “Imi tenki foo sai imi nia sala hotu, i la bele halo tan, atu Maromak hamoos imi nia sala. Depois imi tenki sarani uluk, hanesan sinal ida katak imi diak malu fali ona ho Maromak.”
Ema hosi sidade Jerusalém, ho provinsia Judeia, sira hotu mai hasoru João iha nia fatin. Sira hakarak haree nia i rona rasik nia liafuan. Sira foo sai sira nia sala, depois João foo sarani sira iha mota Jordaun.
Nia hatete, “La kleur tan, iha ema ida sei mai, i Nia boot liu hau. Atu sai deit Nia atan mos, hau la serve.<a href='#note-356' class='key'>†</a>
Hau sarani imi hodi bee deit, maibee Nia sei halo liu fali hau. Nia sei foo Maromak nia Espiritu Santu ba imi.”
Iha tempu nee, Jesus mai hosi aldeia Nazaré iha Galileia hodi hasoru malu ho João. Depois João sarani Nia iha mota Jordaun.
Sarani tiha hotu, bainhira Jesus sai hosi bee laran nee mai, derepenti Nia haree lalehan nakloke. I Maromak nia Espiritu tuun mai Jesus, hanesan manu pombu ida.
Depois Maromak nia lian tuun hosi lalehan, hatete nunee,
“O mak Hau nia Oan Doben;
O sempre halo Hau nia laran kontenti.”<a href='#note-357' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee liu tiha, Maromak nia Espiritu obriga Jesus baa iha rai fuik maran ida.
Nia hela iha nebaa, durante loron haat-nulu, kalan haat-nulu. Nia hela hamutuk ho animal fuik sira. Iha nebaa, diabu sira nia boot mai intenta Jesus para tuir nia hakarak, maibee Nia la tuir. Depois Maromak nia anju sira hosi lalehan mai serbi Nia.
Iha nebaa Nia hatete dehan,
“Rona mai! Agora, Maromak nia tempu too ona.
Agora, ema hotu-hotu bele hatene katak Maromak mak ukun.
Tanba nee, imi tenki husik ona imi nia sala,
i tuir deit Maromak nia dalan.”<a href='#note-358' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida, Jesus lao tuir tasi ibun Galileia. Nia haree ema peskador nain rua. Ida, naran Simão, ho nia alin, André. Sira nain rua soe hela dai hodi kaer ikan.
Jesus bolu sira dehan, “Rona mai! Mai tuir Hau! Imi uluk buka ikan, maibee agora Hau hanorin imi atu buka ema hodi tuir Maromak.”
Rona Jesus dehan nunee, sira husik tiha sira nia dai, i baa tuir kedas Jesus.
Liu tiha nee, Jesus lao seidauk dook, Nia hetan tan Zebedeu nia oan sira. Maun, naran Tiago; nia alin, naran João. Sira nain rua hadia hela redi iha bero laran.
Jesus bolu sira nain rua tan, dehan, “Mai tuir Hau!” Nunee sira husik kedan sira nia aman, ho ema nebee servisu ho sira. I sira nain rua baa tuir Jesus.
Depois Jesus ho sira nain haat nee, lao baa too iha sidade ida, naran Kafarnaum. Iha loron Sabadu, ema Judeu sira sempre baa harohan.<a href='#note-359' class='key'>‡</a> I Jesus mos tama ba uma kreda laran, hodi hanorin sira.
Ema hotu admira, bainhira rona Nia koalia, tanba Nia hatene duni buat hotu nebee Nia hanorin. Nia hanorin oin seluk, la hanesan mestri Judeu sira.<a href='#note-360' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha fatin nee, iha ema ida, espiritu aat tama iha nia laran. Kuandu Jesus hanorin hela, ema nee tama ba iha uma kreda laran. I nia hakilar, dehan,
“Hoi, Jesus, ema Nazaré! Nusaa? O hakarak saida?! O mai estraga ami ka? Ami konhese O! O Ema La Iha Sala. O mak Maromak promete ona hori uluk atu haruka mai.”
Maibee Jesus koalia makaas ba espiritu aat nee dehan, “No-nook! Taka o nia ibun! Sai ona hosi ema nee!”
I espiritu aat nee soe ema nee ba rai. Nia sai hosi ema nee, i hakilar makaas.
Liu tiha nee, ema hotu iha uma kreda laran nee, hakfodak. I sira komesa husu ba malu, “Saida mak nee? Nee hanorin foun ka? Senhor nee, Nia liafuan makaas duni. Nia haruka espiritu aat sira sai, i sira mos rona.”
Entaun ema hotu konta ona ba-mai, hosi uma ba uma, too iha aldeia hotu iha provinsia Galileia tomak.
Bainhira sira foin sai hosi uma kreda nee mai, Jesus baa iha Simão ho André nia uma.
Simão nia banin feto isin manas, toba hela. Kuandu Jesus tama ba uma laran, ema foo hatene kedas, dehan, “Simão nia banin feto isin manas.”
Entaun Jesus baa haree ferik nee. I Nia kaer nia liman, hodi foti halo hadeer. Nunee nia moras lakon kedas. Depois ferik nee sai ba liur hodi serbi sira.
Loron atu besik monu ona, ema lori tan ema moras, ho ema nebee mak espiritu aat tama iha sira nia laran. Sira lori ba Jesus, hodi husu ajuda.
Ema hotu iha sidade laran mai hamutuk iha uma oin.
Sira iha moras oi-oin, i Jesus kura tiha hotu. I Nia duni sai mos espiritu aat hosi ema barak. Maibee Jesus la foo lisensa ba espiritu aat sira koalia, tanba sira konhese see mak Nia.
Dadeer-saan nakukun, Jesus hadeer ona. Nia sai tiha hosi uma, baa iha fatin ida nebee ema la iha. Iha nebaa, Nia harohan ba Maromak.
Kuandu Simão sira hadeer, sira la haree tan Jesus ona, i sira baa buka Nia.
Bainhira sira hetan ona Nia, sira dehan, “Senhor, mai ita fila ona. Tanba ema barak mak buka Ita.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Diak liu ita baa iha aldeia-aldeia nebee besik. Para Hau bele foo sai mos Liafuan Diak ba sira. Tanba Hau nia servisu mak nee duni.”
Liu tiha nee, Nia lao lemo iha provinsia Galileia tomak, hodi hatoo Maromak nia liafuan, hosi uma kreda ba uma kreda. I Nia mos duni sai espiritu aat hosi ema sira nia laran.<a href='#note-361' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun Jesus hadomi ema nee, i Nia lolo liman ba kona ema nee, hodi dehan, “Hau hakarak. Agora, o diak ona!”
Derepenti deit, ema nee nia moras lakon tiha. I nia diak kedan.
Depois Jesus foo hanoin ba nia, dehan,
“Hanoin di-diak! O diak ona. Maibee o keta konta ba ema seluk. O tenki tuir Moisés nia lei hori uluk nian. Nunee o baa uluk nai lulik Judeu sira, para nia bele haree lai o nia moras nee, lakon tebes ka lae. Depois o tenki foo oferta hanesan obrigadu ba Maromak, para ema hotu hatene katak o diak tebes ona.”<a href='#note-362' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee ema nee sai, i nia baa konta iha fatin ba fatin. Depois ema barak baa buka Jesus, too Nia la hatudu oin tan iha sidade. Nunee Nia baa hela tiha dook hosi sidade, iha fatin nebee hakmatek. Maibee ema hosi fatin hotu-hotu, nadodon mai nafatin atu hasoru Nia.
Liu tiha loron ida-rua, Jesus fila fali ba Kafarnaum. Ema nebee haree Nia, baa foo hatene iha sidade laran katak, Jesus mai fali iha uma ona.
Nunee ema mai hosi sidade tomak. Sira nadodon mai hamutuk, too sena malu metin iha uma laran; too iha odamatan oin mos, ema nakonu. Depois Jesus hatoo ba sira, Maromak nia liafuan.
Nia sei koalia hela, ema nain haat hulan ema ain aat ida ba Jesus.
Maibee, tanba ema barak liu, sira la konsege lori ema nee tama ba Jesus. Nunee sira sae ba iha uma leten, i sira halo kuak ida. Depois sira hatuun ema nee hodi biti iha Jesus nia oin.<a href='#note-363' class='key'>*</a>
Bainhira Jesus haree sira, Nia hatene katak sira fiar tebes duni ba Nia. I Nia hatete ba ema ain aat nee, “Alin, o nia sala hamoos tiha ona.”
Maibee iha fatin nee, iha mos mestri relijiaun balu tuur hela. Bainhira sira rona Jesus koalia nunee, sira senti la diak,
tanba sira hanoin nunee, “Nusaa mak Nia koalia fali nunee? Nai Maromak mesak deit mak bele hamoos ema nia sala. Maibee Nia halo nia aan hanesan fali Nai Maromak. Nia liafuan nee kontra ona Nai Maromak!”
Maibee Jesus hatene tiha ona sira nia laran. I Nia dehan, “Imi keta hanoin hanesan nee!
9-10 Ida nebee mak fasil liu? Se Hau hatete ba ema ain aat nee dehan, ‘O nia sala hamoos tiha ona,’ imi la hatene se sai nunee ka lae. Maibee, se Hau hatete dehan, ‘Hadeer ona! Foti o nia biti, hodi fila ona.’ Se nia hamriik duni, imi foin hatene katak Hau./ I Hau mos iha direitu para bele hamoos ema nia sala.”
Depois Jesus hatete ba ema ain aat nee dehan,
“Rona mai! Agora o diak ona. Hadeer ona, foti o nia biti, hodi fila ona.”
Rona nunee, nia hadeer kedan, foti nia biti, hodi sai ba liur. Ema hotu-hotu iha fatin nee, haree ho matan rasik. Sira hotu admira, i dehan, “Ita foin mak haree buat hanesan nee. Nai Maromak nee boot tebe-tebes!”
Nee hotu tiha, Jesus fila ba iha tasi Galileia. Ema barak mai hasoru Nia, i Nia foo sai Nai Maromak nia hakarak.
Iha fatin nee, iha ema ida, naran Levi, Alfeu nia oan. Nia servisu mak kobra osan impostu ba estadu Roma. Natoon Jesus liu hosi nebaa, Nia hetan Levi tuur hela, Nia hatete, “Mai tuir Hau!”
Nia rona Jesus dehan nunee, nia hamriik, i tuir kedan Jesus.
Depois Jesus baa iha Levi nia uma. Iha uma nee, Levi nia kolega kobrador impostu sira, ho ema seluk tan nebee ema Judeu sira dehan, sira ema aat. Sira hotu haan hamutuk ho Jesus. Hosi sira nee, ema barak mak gosta rona Jesus nia liafuan.
Iha tempu nee, iha mestri relijiaun balu hosi grupu Farizeu, haree Jesus tuur haan hamutuk hela ho ema kobrador impostu sira, ho ema hahalok aat sira. Depois sira husu ba Jesus nia eskolante sira dehan, “Tanba saa, mak imi nia Mestri tuur haan hamutuk ho ema kobrador ho ema aat sira?”
Kuandu Jesus rona sira husu hanesan nee, Nia hataan kedan, dehan, “Rona mai! Ema moras mak presiza doutor, maibee ema isin diak la presiza. Hau mai atu halibur ema sala nain sira para tuir Hau. Laos ema nebee foti aan katak sira mak loos liu.”
Iha loron ida, ema hosi grupu Farizeu sira halo jejun. João Sarani Nain nia eskolante sira mos jejun. Maibee ema la haree Jesus nia eskolante sira jejun. I sira mai husu ba Jesus, “Senhor, ema hosi grupu Farizeu sira halo jejun. João nia eskolante sira mos jejun. Nusaa mak Ita Boot nia eskolante sira la jejun?”
Depois Jesus hataan, “Imi hatene ona, bainhira iha festa kazamentu ida, ema la jejun, maibee ema tenki haan too bosu. Bainhira noivu sei iha, sira hotu-hotu haan ho rame-rame.
Maibee too iha loron ida, se ema seluk mai lori lakon tiha noivu nee, foin nia kolega sira senti laran susar tebes. Nunee sira foin halo jejun hodi harohan.”
Jesus foo tan komparasaun nunee, “Kuandu ropa kuak, ita la taka ho hena foun. Tanba kuandu fasi, hena foun nee sei dada ropa bosan nee, halo naklees liu tan.
Nunee mos, ema la uza au lahuk hodi tau tua foun, tanba tua bele turu sai hotu. Se tua nee foun, ita tenki uza au foun, para bele rai kleur.”<a href='#note-364' class='key'>†</a>
Iha loron Sabadu, ema Judeu sira nia loron hodi harohan, i sira la bele servisu. Iha loron nee duni, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao liu hosi toos rohan. Nia eskolante sira korut dadauk trigu.<a href='#note-365' class='key'>✡</a>
25-26 Jesus hataan, “Imi la hanoin kona ba David nia istoria ka? Tempu nee, amu Abiatar hanesan nai lulik boot. Avoo David ho nia ema sira hamlaha atu mate. Depois sira tama ba iha Nai Maromak nia Tenda Harohan Nian, i sira baa foti paun ida nebee nai lulik sira foo tiha ona ba Nai Maromak, i sira haan tiha. Tuir lo-loos, nai lulik sira mak bele haan; ema seluk la bele. Maibee David sira haan tiha, i la iha ema ida foo sala ba sira.”<a href='#note-366' class='key'>✡</a>
I Jesus dehan tan nunee, “Imi la bele haluha katak Nai Maromak foo ona loron deskansa, atu halo diak ba ita ema. Nia halo ita ema laos para hodi tuir deit loron deskansa nia hanorin.
Hau Mane Maksoin. Hau mak iha direitu atu hatete ba ema, saida mak sira bele halo iha loron deskansa, i saida mak sira la bele halo.”
Iha loron Sabadu ida, Jesus fila fali ba iha uma kreda laran. Iha nebaa, Nia haree ema ida, nia liman sorin mate tiha.
Iha mos ema balu buka hela dalan atu foo sala ba Jesus. Sira sempre haree tu-tuir Nia, hodi buka hatene Nia atu kura ema iha loron la bele servisu, ka lae.
Nunee Jesus bolu ema liman sorin mate nee, dehan, “O mai hamriik iha nee.”
Nia husu ba ema sira hotu, dehan, “Tuir ita nia lei relijiaun nian, ita bele halo saida iha loron deskansa? Ita bele halo buat diak ka, buat aat? Ita bele ajuda ema ka, oho ema?” Maibee sira hotu nonook hela.
I Jesus nia laran susar tebe-tebes, tanba sira interese mak sira nia lei deit, i la hanoin ema liman sorin mate nee. Depois Nia fihir sira ho hirus. I Nia haruka ema nee, “Lolo liman mai!” Ema nee foo nia liman ba, i derepenti deit nia liman nee mos diak kedan.
Liu tiha nee, ema Farizeu sira sai hosi uma kreda laran. Depois sira baa kombina ho ema partidu Herodes sira, atu buka dalan hodi oho Jesus.
7-8 Iha loron ida, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira baa fali iha tasi ibun Galileia. Ema barak rona ona buat nebee mak Nia halo. Tanba nee, sira hotu mai hosi aldeia-aldeia hodi tuir Nia. Sira mai hosi provinsia Galileia, Judeia, ho Idumeia. Balu mai hosi sidade Jerusalém, Sidon, ho Tiru. Ho mos hosi mota Jordaun nia sorin.
Tanba ema barak tebes, nunee Jesus haruka Nia eskolante sira baa buka bero ida, atu Nia bele sae iha bero leten, para ema la bele sena malu ho Nia.
Tanba uluk Nia kura ema barak nia moras, nunee agora ema moras hotu hadau malu atu kona Nia.<a href='#note-367' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha fatin nee mos, iha ema sira nebee espiritu aat tama iha sira nia laran. Momentu sira hetan Jesus, sira monu iha Nia oin. I sira hakilar, dehan, “O Nai Maromak nia Oan duni!”
Maibee Nia bandu makaas sira, dehan, “Imi keta foo hatene ba ema kona ba see mak Hau.”
Depois Jesus sae ba iha foho leten ida. Nia bolu ema nebee Nia hakarak. I sira mai ba Nia.
Nunee Nia hili ema nain sanulu resin rua. I Nia dehan ba sira, “Hau hili ona imi atu imi tuir Hau. Hau sei haruka imi baa foo sai Nai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak ba ema hotu.
I Hau sei foo poder ba imi, para imi bele duni sai espiritu aat hosi ema nia laran.”
16-19 Ema nain sanulu resin rua nee, sira nia naran mak nee:
Simão (nebee Jesus foo tan naran Pedro),
Tiago,
João (Tiago nia alin. Sira nain rua, Zebedeu nia oan. Jesus tau sira nia naran ‘Boanerjes’, nee katak ‘hanesan rai tarutu’.)<a href='#note-368' class='key'>*</a>
André,
Filipe,
Bartolomeu,
Mateus,
Tomé,
Tiago (Alfeu nia oan),
Tadeu,
Simão (nia tuir partidu Zelote),<a href='#note-369' class='key'>†</a>
Nee liu tiha, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira tuun fila fali hosi foho mai, i sira tama ba uma laran. Ema barak mak mai hobur Nia, too Jesus mos la iha tempu atu haan.
Haree nunee, ema dehan, “Haree took Jesus! Nia la interese tiha Nia aan deit.” Nia familia sira rona ema konta nunee. Nee duni, sira mai atu lori tiha Nia.
Iha tempu nee, mestri relijiaun balu mai hosi sidade Jerusalém. Sira dehan ba ema nebee rona Jesus, “Rona mai! Imi la bele tuir Jesus nee. Tanba diabu sira nia boot, nebee ema bolu Belzebu, tama ona iha Nia laran. I nia mak foo forsa ba Jesus para duni sai diabu sira.”<a href='#note-370' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus rona nunee, Nia bolu sira mai, dehan, “Nee la tama Hau nia laran! Halo nusaa diabu nia boot bele duni sai nia aan rasik?!” I Nia foo komparasaun nunee,
“Se iha estadu ida, ninia povu sira haan malu, estadu nee la bele dura.
I se iha familia ida mak sobu malu, familia nee la iha tan futuru.
Nunee mos diabu sira, kuandu sira kontra malu, sira namkari, i rahun.
Kuandu ema atu mai naok sasaan iha ema forti ida nia uma, nia tenki kesi metin ema nee uluk lai. Depois foin bele foti nia sasaan.<a href='#note-371' class='key'>‡</a>
Tanba nee, mak Hau dehan kedan ba imi: Nai Maromak sempre prontu atu hamoos ema nia sala. Se ema koalia aat ema seluk, Nai Maromak bele hamoos nia sala.
Maibee kuandu ema koalia aat Espiritu Santu, Nai Maromak la hamoos tan nia sala nee ona, too tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-372' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatete nunee, tanba ema balu dehan, “Ema nee, espiritu aat tama ona iha Nia laran.”
Nee liu tiha, Jesus nia inan ho alin sira mai iha uma nee, atu hasoru Nia. Too iha uma, sira hamriik deit iha liur, i haruka bolu Jesus atu sai mai.
Momentu nee, Jesus tuur koalia hela ho ema barak. Iha ema balu foo hatene ba Jesus, dehan, “Senhor, Ita nia inan ho alin sira hein hela iha liur. Sira hakarak atu hasoru Senhor.”
Maibee Jesus husu fali, “Hau nia familia lo-loos, mak see?”
Depois Jesus haree ba ema lubuk boot tuur haleu Nia. I Nia hatete nunee, “Tuir lo-loos, imi sira nee Hau nia familia hotu.
Tanba see mak halo tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak, sira mak Hau nia familia.”
Iha loron ida, Jesus baa fali tan iha tasi Galileia. Ema barak mai hobur Nia. Iha fatin nee, bero ida para hela iha bee laran. Depois Jesus sae tiha ba bero leten, i Nia tuur, hodi komesa hanorin. Ema iha bee ibun nee, rona hotu Nia koalia.<a href='#note-373' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hanorin sira buat barak liu hosi komparasaun, dehan,
“Rona di-diak! Iha ema ida baa kari fini iha nia toos.
Momentu nia kari fini nee, iha fini balu monu iha dalan klaran. I manu fuik mai hili tiha hotu.
5-6 Iha fini balu tan, monu iha rai fatuk. Fini nee tubun lailais. Maibee, tanba rai uitoan deit, abut la tama too laran. Kuandu loron manas ona, tubun nebee foin moris nee, namlaik too maran tiha hotu.
Iha fini balu tan, monu iha duut tarak laran. Fini nee moris duni. Maibee duut tarak habit hela deit, too nia la foo isin.
Maibee iha fini balu tan, monu iha rai bokur. Fini nee moris diak, buras, too foo isin barak. Iha fini balu, bote ida bele foo fali too bote tolu-nulu, i balu foo too bote neen-nulu, i balu tan foo too bote atus ida.
See mak rona, hanoin di-diak ba.”
Bainhira Jesus mesak hela, Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua, ho ema balu nebee rona ona Jesus nia hanorin nee, sira mai husu hatene kona ba saida mak komparasaun nee.
Depois Jesus hataan fali ba sira, “Tanba imi hakarak duni atu hatene Nai Maromak nia Dalan, Hau sei foo sai ba imi. Maibee, ba ema seluk, Hau hanorin deit hosi komparasaun.
Nai Maromak nia profeta ida hakerek ona hori uluk, kona ba ema hanesan sira nee, dehan,
‘Sira haree ona, maibee lakohi hatene.
Sira rona ona, maibee lakohi komprende.
Para Nai Maromak mos lalika hamoos sira nia sala.’ ”<a href='#note-374' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus dehan, “Se imi la komprende komparasaun ida nee, halo nusaa mak imi bele komprende komparasaun sira seluk?
Komparasaun nee nunee: Ema ida nebee kari fini nee, hanesan ema nebee mak foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
I fini nebee monu iha dalan klaran, too manu fuik mai hili tiha hotu, hanesan ema nebee rona Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Maibee diabu sira nia boot mai hadau tiha Liafuan nee hosi ema nia laran.
I fini nebee monu iha rai fatuk, hanesan ema nebeel rona ona Nai Maromak nia liafuan, i simu liafuan nee ho laran kontenti.
Maibee Liafuan nee la hela metin iha nia laran. Tanba nia simu Liafuan nee, ema seluk ameasa nia, i nia husik tiha kedan.
I fini nebee monu iha duut tarak laran, hanesan mos ema nebee rona ona Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
Maibee nia fadigadu demais ho nia servisu oi-oin, hanesan nia buka riku, nia buka sai ema boot, ho nia goza tuun-sae. Too nia la interese Nai Maromak. Nunee nia husik tiha Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
Maibee fini nebee monu iha rai bokur, hanesan ema nebee rona ona Nai Maromak nia liafuan, i halo tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak. Tanba nee, nia sempre halo buat diak deit, hanesan fini nebee foo isin barak.”
Jesus koalia nafatin iha bero leten. Nia aumenta tan komparasaun ida, nunee, “Nusaa? Kuandu ema sunu ahi-oan, sira doku tiha ho bote ka? Ou sira tau iha kama okos ka? Lae! Se tau iha fatin hanesan nee, ahi-oan nee la foo tan naroman. Ema tenki tau ahi-oan nee iha fatin nebee aas, atu bele naroman ba hotu-hotu.<a href='#note-375' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat nebee mak agora subar hela, aban-bainrua sei bele hetan. Buat nebee mak agora ita la hatene, aban-bainrua sei bele hatene.<a href='#note-376' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak rona, hanoin di-diak ba.”
Depois Jesus kontinua hanorin, dehan, “Hanoin di-diak ba Hau nia Liafuan. Se imi la hanoin di-diak, imi sei laduun komprende. Maibee se imi hanoin di-diak, imi sei komprende barak, i Hau sei hanorin imi barak liu tan.<a href='#note-377' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-378' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee buka tebe-tebes Nai Maromak nia hakarak, nia sei hatene liu tan. Maibee ema nebee la interese Nai Maromak nia hakarak, nia sei beik liu tan.”<a href='#note-379' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus dehan nunee, “Nai Maromak nia reinu aumenta barak ba beibeik, hanesan mos fini nebee ema kari iha nia toos laran.
Bele ema nee fila tiha ba uma, halo fali buat selu-seluk, i la hanoin tan nia toos. Maibee fini nee buras i boot ba beibeik.
Fini nee mesak tubun. Depois komesa iha sanak, funan, too nia iha isin.
Kuandu tasak ona, toos nain hatene mai koa deit. Nunee mos, Nai Maromak mak halo Nia reinu aumenta barak liu tan.”<a href='#note-380' class='key'>✡</a>
Liu tiha nee, Jesus dehan tan, “Hau foo sai tan komparasaun ida. Imi bele hanoin Nai Maromak nia reinu sira hanesan nee: Sira komesa hosi uitoan liu, maibee kleur-kleur tan, sira aumenta ba beibeik too barak tebe-tebes.
Nee hanesan ai musan ida kiik-oan liu.
Kuandu ai musan nee ita kuda ona, nia moris sai ai huun boot la halimar. Too manu fuik sira mos mai hamahon, i halo knuuk iha ai leten nee.”
Jesus nia hanorin hanesan nee, tuir buat nebee sira bele komprende.
Nia baibain hanorin ema barak ho komparasaun. Maibee ba Nia eskolante sira, Nia foo hatene komparasaun sira nee nia signifikadu, para sira bele komprende di-diak.
Too loro tuun ona, Jesus sei iha bero leten nafatin, hodi hanorin ema sira nee. Depois Nia hatete ba Nia eskolante sira, “Mai ita baa tasi nia sorin ba.”
Entaun sira sae tan baa hamutuk ho Jesus. I sira husik hela ema barak iha bee ninin nee. Maibee iha ema balu sae bero seluk hodi tuir Jesus.
37-38 Jesus tau ulun iha sumasu, i Nia toba dukur loos iha bero laran. La kleur, anin boot mosu.<a href='#note-381' class='key'>†</a> Laloran baku bero baa-mai, i bee tama bero laran nebee Jesus sae nee, too bee besik nakonu. Nunee Jesus nia eskolante sira tauk atu mate. Depois sira mai fanu Nia, hodi dehan, “Mestri, hadeer lai! Ita atu mate ona! Maibee Mestri la interese.”
Rona nunee, Jesus mos hadeer, hodi hatete ba anin ho laloran nee nunee, “Para ona!” Anin mos para, i bee mos hakmatek kedan.
Depois Jesus hatete makaas ba Nia eskolante sira, “Nusaa mak imi tauk demais hanesan nee? Imi la fiar Hau ka?”
Sira hotu tauk ho admira. Depois sira koalia ba malu, dehan, “Ema nee see loos? Nia koalia deit mos, anin ho laloran rona ona!”
2-6 Iha fatin nee, iha mane ida, espiritu aat domina nia hori uluk kedas. Nia hela iha rate laran.
Loron-kalan nia lao tuun-sae foho, i hakilar beibeik. Loro-loron nia tuku nia aan rasik ho fatuk, too kanek tiha hotu. Mane nee forti la halimar. Ema kesi beibeik nia liman-ain ho korenti. Maibee korenti besi mos, nia rasta kotu hotu kedan. I argola iha nia ain mos, rahun.
Bainhira Jesus tuun hosi bero, ema espiritu aat hela iha nia laran nee, haree Nia hosi dook. Depois nia sai kedan hosi rate laran, i nia baa iha Jesus nia oin, hodi hakneak i hahii ba Nia.
7-8 Kuandu Jesus haree ema nee, Nia hatete, “Espiritu aat, sai hosi ema nee!”
Depois ema nee hakilar, “O atu halo saida mai hau?! Hau hatene katak, Nai Maromak Mak Boot Tebes. I O Jesus, Nai Maromak nia Oan. Hau husu ba O atu la bele halo susar hau.”
Depois Jesus husu ba nia, “O naran saa?”
Ema nee hataan, “Hau nia naran, Lejiaun. Tanba ami espiritu barak tebe-tebes, hanesan tropas sira nia lejiaun.”<a href='#note-382' class='key'>*</a>
I espiritu aat sira uza ema nee hodi husu ba Jesus, atu keta duni sira sai hosi rai nee.
11-13 Besik fatin nee, iha ema balu hein hela fahi rihun rua iha foho lolon. Nunee espiritu aat sira husu ba Jesus, “Haruka deit ami baa tama iha fahi sira nebaa.”
Rona nunee, Jesus mos konkorda. I espiritu aat sira sai kedan hosi ema nee, baa tama fali iha fahi sira. Fahi sira halai saruntu malu too iha rai naruk ida, i monu hotu ba bee laran. Nunee fahi rihun rua nee mout too mate hotu.
Haree hanesan nee, fahi atan sira tauk atu mate. I sira halai baa foo hatene iha aldeia-aldeia. Too ema barak mai haree saida mak mosu.
Kuandu sira hetan Jesus, sira mos haree mane nebee uluk espiritu aat tama nee, tuur hakmatek hela, i hatais fali hena ona. Nia hanoin normal fali ona. Entaun ema sira tauk, tanba sira hatene ona, ema ida nebee duni sai espiritu aat nee, Nia forsa tebe-tebes.
Depois fahi atan sira konta ba ema nebee mai hosi aldeia-aldeia nee, dehan, sira haree rasik ho matan ema bulak nee diak tiha ona, i fahi sira nee mout too mate tiha hotu.
Depois ema iha rai nee husu ba Jesus atu sai tiha hosi sira nia rain.
Bainhira Jesus atu sae fali ba bero nee, ema nebee espiritu aat sai ohin nee, mai husu ba Jesus para nia mos atu tuir.
Maibee Jesus lakohi. Nia dehan, “Diak liu, o fila baa konta ba o nia familia sira hotu, saida mak Nai Maromak halo ona ba o. I foo hatene mos katak, Nai Maromak hadomi tebes o.”
Nunee ema nee lao lemo-lemo iha rai ida naran ‘Dekápolis’. (Nee katak, rai nee iha sidade sanulu.) I nia konta saida mak Jesus halo ba nia. Ema hotu nebee rona nia koalia nee, sira admira tebe-tebes, dehan, “Nai Jesus nee forsa duni!”
Nunee Jesus sae fali bero hodi baa iha tasi sorin ba. Bainhira Nia foin tuun hosi bero, ema barak mai hobur Nia.
Iha mos ema ida naran Jairo. Nia toma-konta uma kreda iha sidade nee. Bainhira nia haree Jesus, nia baa hakruuk to-rai iha Jesus nia oin,
hodi husu dehan, “Senhor, tulun hau lai! Hau nia oan feto moras todan, besik mate ona. Nia foin tinan sanulu resin rua.”<a href='#note-383' class='key'>†</a>
Nunee Jesus tuir kedan Jairo ba iha nia uma.
Maibee bainhira sira lao ba, ema barak mos tuir Nia, too sena malu.
Iha ema sira nee, iha feto ida, nia fulan mai la para, durante tinan sanulu resin rua.
Nia gasta osan barak too nia faan nia sasaan hotu hodi selu deit doutor barak. Maibee la iha ema ida mak bele kura nia. Nia moras nee aumenta ba beibeik.
27-29 Feto nee rona ona buat barak kona ba Jesus. Nunee nia sena malu hosi ema barak nia leet, atu baa besik Jesus nia kotuk. Nia hanoin iha nia laran dehan, “Naran katak hau kona kois deit Nia hena mos, hau diak ona.”
Nunee nia foin kona Jesus nia hena, derepenti nia raan mos para. Nia senti diak kedan.
Iha momentu nee, Jesus senti iha forsa ida sai hosi Nia laran. I Nia fila ba kotuk, hodi haree ema barak nee. Nia husu, “See mak kona Hau nia hena nee?”
Nia eskolante sira hataan, “Senhor rasik haree deit ba. Ema iha nee barak la halimar! Halo nusaa mak Senhor husu fali, ‘See mak kona Hau nia hena nee?’!”
Maibee Jesus haree ba-mai, atu buka hatene see loos mak kona Nia hena.
Depois Jesus dehan, “Tanba ita fiar tebe-tebes mai Hau, nee duni mak ita diak ona. Ita la hetan tan terus ida nee ona. Agora ita fila ona ho paz.”
Jesus sei koalia hela nunee, iha ema ida mai hosi Jairo nia uma, foo hatene, “Koitadu! Oan feto mate tiha ona. Nee duni, lalika halo kole tan mestri. Senhor lalika baa tan uma ona.”
Maibee Jesus lakohi rona ema nee nia koalia. I Nia hatete ba Jairo, “La bele laran susar! Ita fiar deit.”
Nunee Jesus lao husik hela Nia eskolante balu. I Nia lori deit Pedro, Tiago ho João. Sira mesak deit mak baa ho Jairo.
Bainhira sira too iha Jairo nia uma, sira haree ema barak rungu-ranga hela ho tanis hakilar.
Jesus tama ba iha uma laran. I Nia husu ba sira dehan, “Tanba saa mak imi hotu fadigadu i tanis loos hanesan nee? Labarik nee la mate ida. Nia toba deit.”
Rona Jesus dehan hanesan nee, sira hotu goza ho hamnasa fali Nia.
Depois Nia haruka sira hotu sai. Nunee Nia bolu labarik nee nia inan-aman, ho Nia eskolante nain tolu nee, para sira tama hamutuk ba iha labarik nee nia kuartu laran.
Depois Jesus kaer labarik nee nia liman, hodi dehan ho sira nia lian nunee, “Talita kum!” Nee dehan katak, “Noi, hadeer ona!”
42-43 Derepenti deit, anoi hadeer i lao kedan. Nunee Jesus hatete ba labarik nee nia inan dehan, “Foo hahaan ona ba labarik nee.”
Ema hotu admira tebes. Maibee Jesus bandu makaas ba sira dehan, “Imi la bele konta sai ba ema seluk, dehan Hau mak halo moris fali labarik nee.”
Hotu tiha, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira fila fali ba iha Nia aldeia Nazaré.
Too ona loron Sabadu, ema Judeu sira nia loron hodi harohan. I Jesus tama ba iha uma kreda laran hodi hanorin. Iha loron nee, ema barak mak baa harohan. Bainhira sira rona Jesus nia hanorin, sira hotu admira loos, i dehan, “Ema nee matenek tebes. Nia mos iha forsa! Nusaa mak Nia bele hanesan nee?
Afinal Nia badaen ai ida. Ita hotu konhese Nia inan Maria ho Nia alin sira: Tiago, José, Judas ho Simão. Ita konhese mos Nia alin feto sira. Ita hotu hela iha aldeia nee.” Tanba nee, sira laran moras, too lakohi rona tan Nia.
Rona nunee, Jesus hatete, “Nee loos duni! Ema respeita liu Nai Maromak nia ema nebee mai hosi fatin seluk, duke sira rona ema hosi sira nia aldeia rasik.”<a href='#note-384' class='key'>✡</a>
5-6 Maibee ema sira nee ulun toos liu, too lakohi fiar tan Jesus. Tanba nee, Jesus hakfodak, i doko ulun. I Nia la uza tan Nia forsa iha aldeia nee, so kura ema uitoan deit.
Nai Jesus haruka Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua
(Mateus 10:5-15; Lucas 9:1-6)
Liu tiha nee, Jesus lao tama-sai ba aldeia-aldeia nebee besik, hodi hanorin kona ba Nai Maromak nia hakarak.
Nia bolu Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua nee, i haruka sira lao nain rua-rua baa foo sai Nai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak ba ema hotu. Nia mos foo forsa para bele duni sai espiritu aat.
8-9 Nia haruka sira nunee, “Imi la bele lori buat ida iha dalan. La bele lori bukae, osan, ou pasta. Tau deit xinelus iha ain, ho hena tahan ida iha isin. I kaer deit ai tonka ida.
Se iha ema ruma simu imi iha sira nia uma, imi tenki hela nafatin iha uma nee, too imi sai fali ba fatin seluk.
Maibee se ema lakohi simu imi, i lakohi rona buat nebee mak imi hanorin ba sira, imi tenki sai kedas hosi fatin nee. I baku rai rahun hosi imi nia ain okos, hanesan sinal ida katak, ‘Tanba imi lakohi rona Nai Maromak nia liafuan, nee duni, imi rasik mak lori todan nee.’ ”<a href='#note-385' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee sira lao baa hatoo Nai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak, hodi hanorin, “Imi tenki husik imi nia sala ona, i tuir Nai Maromak nia dalan.”
I sira duni sai espiritu aat hosi ema. Sira mos tau mina ba ema moras sira nia ulun, hodi halo orasaun, i sira mos diak.<a href='#note-386' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nee, ema iha fatin hotu-hotu hatene ona kona ba Jesus. I liurai Herodes mos rona kona ba Jesus nia forsa. Iha ema balu dehan, “Jesus nee João Sarani Nain. Nia moris fali iha Jesus nia Aan. Tanba nee mak Nia bele halo milagre barak.”
Iha ema seluk hatete, “Laos! Jesus nee Nai Maromak nia profeta Elias mak moris fali ona.” Iha ema balu tan dehan, “Jesus nee profeta ida, hanesan Nai Maromak nia profeta sira uluk.”<a href='#note-387' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira liurai Herodes rona sira koalia hanesan nee, nia dehan, “Loos duni! Jesus nee João Sarani Nain. Foin dadauk nee, hau haruka tesi tiha nia kakorok. Agora nia moris fali ona!”
17-18 Liurai Herodes hatete nunee, tanba iha problema boot ho João. Nia istoria hanesan nee: Liurai Herodes kaben fali ho nia alin Filipe nia kaben, naran Herodias, maski Filipe ho Herodias seidauk soe malu. Nunee João kritika liurai Herodes dehan, “Liurai, tuir loos Ita boot la bele kaben fali ho Ita nia alin nia feen. Nee bandu makaas!” Maibee liurai Herodes la interese, i haruka ema baa kaer João baa hatama iha kadeia.<a href='#note-388' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira nia hatama João ba iha kadeia, nia haruka soldadu sira hein halo di-diak. Liurai Herodes sei laran susar hela ba João. Tanba nia hatene João nee, Nai Maromak mak haruka mai, i nia mos laran diak. Liurai Herodes gosta rona João nia koalia. Maibee dalaruma, kuandu nia rona João nia koalia, nia laran la hakmatek.
Too iha loron ida, feto Herodias hetan tempu diak hodi halo lakon João. Iha loron nee, ema halo liurai Herodes nia tinan. Sira konvida ema bo-boot mai iha festa nee. Konvidadu sira nee, balu hosi estadu nian, balu komandante tropas sira, ho mos nai ulun sira hosi rai Galileia.
Iha festa klaran, senhora Herodias nia oan feto tama baa dansa. I nia dansa kapaas tebe-tebes, halo liurai Herodes ho konvidadu sira laran haksolok. Depois liurai Herodes bolu menina nee, hodi promete ba nia, “O hakarak husu saida ba hau, husu deit! Hau sei foo duni.
Bele o husu hau nia riku balu mos, hau foo. Hau jura hodi Aman Maromak nia naran!”
Depois menina nee baa husu ba nia inan, “Amaa! Amaa hakarak hau husu saida mak diak liu?”
Nia inan hataan, “O baa husu deit João nia ulun fatuk.”
I menina nee baa iha liurai Herodes hodi husu, “Amu, hau husu deit João nia ulun, tau iha bandeja ida ba hau. Agora kedas!”
Rona nunee, liurai Herodes laran lakon kedan. Maibee nia tenki halo tuir deit, tanba nia jura tiha ona, i ema barak mos rona.
Depois nia foo orden ba komandante ida baa lori João nia ulun hosi kadeia mai.
Nunee sira tesi tiha João nia kakorok, i depois tau nia ulun iha bandeja ida, hodi mai foo ba menina nee. Nia simu tiha bandeja nee, nia kous hodi baa foo nia inan.
Kuandu João nia eskolante sira rona dehan ema mai lori tiha João nia ulun, sira mos baa foti tiha João nia isin baa hakoi.
Nunee mak João nia mate.
Iha loron ida, Jesus nia eskolante sira nebee Nia haruka baa nee, sira fila fali mai hamutuk ho Nia. I sira konta ba Jesus buat hotu-hotu nebee mak sira halo ona, ho mos buat nebee mak sira hanorin ona ba ema.
Maibee momentu nee, ema barak mai buka Jesus. Too Nia ho Nia eskolante sira mos la konsege haan. Nee duni, Jesus hatete ba Nia eskolante sira, “Mai ita baa buka fatin ida nebee dook hosi ema, para ita bele deskansa uitoan.”
Nunee sira hotu sae bero hodi baa dook tiha hosi aldeia laran.
Maibee ema barak haree sira nia bero liu hosi tasi ibun. Entaun ema hosi aldeia-aldeia halai liu hosi rai maran, i sira too uluk Jesus.
Jesus foin too ho bero, Nia haree ema barak nee hein hela ona Nia. Nunee Nia mos hadomi sira, tanba sira la hatene atu halo saida, hanesan bibi malae nebee la iha atan. I Jesus hanorin Nai Maromak nia liafuan ba sira,<a href='#note-389' class='key'>✡</a>
35-36 komesa meiu-dia too lokraik. Depois Nia eskolante sira hatete ba Nia, “Senhor, diak liu Senhor haruka ema sira nee baa sosa hahaan iha aldeia nebee bes-besik iha nee. Tanba lokraik ona, i la iha hahaan iha nee.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Lalikan! Imi deit mak foo hahaan ba sira.”
Maibee sira hataan fali, “Se ita foo hahaan ba ema barak nunee, ita tenki hasai osan barak tebe-tebes, hanesan ema badaen simu osan iha tinan ida nian. Halo nusaa ita bele hetan osan barak ida nee?!”<a href='#note-390' class='key'>*</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Imi baa husu took, see mak lori bukae iha nee.”
Nunee sira baa buka hatene, depois sira mai dehan fali, “Iha paun fuan lima ho ikan rua deit.”
Depois Jesus haruka ema sira tuur tiha ba rai.
I sira tuur tiha hotu tuir grupu-grupu. Grupu balu iha ema nain atus ida, i balu iha nain lima-nulu.
Depois Jesus foti paun fuan lima ho ikan rua nee. I Nia hateke ba leten hodi foo agradese ba Nai Maromak. Tuir mai Nia silu fahe paun sira nee, halo rohan-rohan, i Nia foo ba Nia eskolante sira, hodi fahe ba ema barak nee hotu. Sira lori mos ikan rua nee baa fahe.
I sira hotu haan too bosu.
Haan hotu tiha, Nia eskolante sira baa aruma paun restu nee, tau iha bote, too bote sanulu resin rua nakonu.
Ema sira nee maizoumenus rihun lima. Nee mane deit. Feto ho labarik seidauk sura.
Nee liu tiha, Jesus haruka Nia eskolante sira baa sae bero hodi baa uluk iha aldeia Betsaida, iha tasi sorin. Maibee Nia sei hela iha fatin nee, hodi haruka ema barak nee fila ba ida-idak nia uma.
47-50 Rai atu besik kalan ona, Jesus haree Nia eskolante sira ho bero too ona iha tasi klaran. Sira hean bero nee ho forsa tebe-tebes, tanba anin boot. Atu besik loron ona, Jesus tuir ba sira, lao deit iha bee leten. Nia atu foin lao liu bero nee, sira mos haree Nia. Sira hakfodak, ho tauk atu mate. I sira husu ba malu, “Saida mak nee? Klamar ka, saida?”
Maibee Jesus bolu ba sira, “Imi la bele tauk! Hau nee Jesus!”
Jesus foin sae ba bero laran, anin boot nee mos para kedas. Nia eskolante sira admira tebe-tebes.
Sira foin haree Jesus uza Nia forsa hodi foo hahaan ba ema rihun lima resin. Maibee sira seidauk komprende di-diak Nia forsa, tanba sira nia ulun toos.
Sira too iha tasi sorin, sira para iha aldeia ida naran Genesaré.
Sira foin tuun hosi bero, ema barak haree kedan sira. I ema hotu nee haklalak, “Jesus mai ona!”
55-56 Sira baa foo hatene ba ema hotu. I ema lori moras sira mai Jesus.
Depois Jesus lao hosi fatin ba fatin. Kuandu ema hatene ona katak Jesus iha fatin ida, sira rame-rame hulan ema moras hodi baa hatoba iha nebaa. Tanba sira hanoin: “Naran katak ema moras nee kona kois Jesus nia hena, sira diak kedas.” Nee loos duni. See mak kona deit Nia hena, diak kedas.
Iha ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu, ho mestri relijiaun balu mai hosi Jerusalém atu hasoru Jesus.
2-5 Ema Farizeu sira halo tuir lo-loos kostumi Judeu nian. Sira hanorin nunee: Kuandu atu haan, tenki fasi liman uluk tuir kostumi. I kuandu fila hosi merkadu, tenki hariis lai. I kuandu atu uza sasaan dapur nian, tenki fasi uluk. Hanesan bikan, kopu, buli, ou sanan. Nee hotu tenki halo tuir kostumi.
Se iha ema Judeu ruma mak la tuir kostumi nee, ema Farizeu sira hirus.
Tanba nee mak sira hirus kuandu sira haree Jesus nia eskolante sira haan la fasi liman tuir kostumi nia hanorin. Nee duni, sira foo sala ba Jesus, dehan, “Nusaa mak O nia eskolante sira haan la fasi liman uluk? Imi kontra ita nia kostumi hosi bei-ala sira!”
6-7 Maibee Jesus hataan, “Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk! Hori uluk Nai Maromak nia profeta Isaias hakerek ona dehan,
‘Ema sira nee adora Hau ho ibun deit,
maibee la ho laran.
Adora hanesan nee, la iha folin ida.
Sira la interese Hau nia hakarak.
Maibee sira hanorin deit mak ema nia lei.’<a href='#note-391' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mos nunee.
8-9 Imi husik tiha ona Nai Maromak nia orden, i imi tuir deit ema nia kostumi. Para atu halo tuir ema nia hakarak, imi matenek la halimar!
Hori uluk kedas, Moisés foo sai Nai Maromak nia orden dehan, ‘Respeita imi nia inan-aman.’ I Moisés hatete tan, ‘See mak tolok nia inan-aman, ema nee tenki mate.’<a href='#note-392' class='key'>✡</a>
11-12 Nai Maromak hanorin nunee, maibee imi hanorin oin seluk fali. Kuandu ema promete atu foo nia sasaan ida ba Nai Maromak, maski nia inan-aman susar atu mate, imi dehan la bele foo nia sasaan nee ba sira, tanba nia promete tiha ona atu foo ba Nai Maromak.
Tanba nee mak ohin Hau hatete ona, imi la moris tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak. Maibee imi troka tiha ona ho lei foun. Iha lei barak mak imi troka tiha ona hanesan nee.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus bolu tan ema barak hodi hatete, “See tilun mai, para imi bele komprende.
Buat nebee mak tama ba ema nia laran la halo foer nia. Maibee buat nebee mak sai hosi ema nia laran, nee mak halo foer nia.
[See mak rona, hanoin di-diak ba!]”<a href='#note-393' class='key'>*</a>
Depois Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira husik hela ema barak nee. I sira baa tama iha uma ida. I Nia eskolante sira husu ba Nia, “Komparasaun ohin nee dehan saida?”
Jesus hataan, “Imi beik ka? Komparasaun nee dehan nunee: Buat nebee mak ema haan, la halo foer ema. Maibee buat nebee sai hosi ema nia laran, nee mak halo foer nia.
Tanba buat saida mak ema haan, tama ba kabun, depois sai fila fali. (Nunee Nai Jesus hatete dehan ema bele haan hahaan hotu-hotu. La iha bandu.)
Tanba buat aat barak mak sai hosi ema nia laran. Hanesan: hanoin aat; halo sala ho feto, halo sala ho mane; naok; oho ema;
halo sala ho ema nia kaben; kaan-teen, halo buat aat; han-matak ema; halo tuir deit nia hakarak rasik; laran moras ema; hatete aat Nai Maromak, hatete aat ema; foti aan; ukun la iha, i lakohi rona ema seluk.
Buat aat sira nee hotu sai hosi ema nia laran. Nee mak halo foer ema. I Nai Maromak mos hakribi.”
Liu tiha nee, Jesus baa iha sidade ida, naran Tiru. Too iha nebaa, Nia tama liu ba iha uma ida, tanba Jesus lakohi atu ema hatene katak Nia iha fatin nee. Maibee Nia subar aan la bele.
25-26 Iha fatin nee, iha feto ida, maibee nia laos ema Judeu. Nia moris iha rai Fenísia iha provinsia Síria nebaa. Kuandu nia rona dehan Jesus mai, nia baa hasoru kedas, i nia husu ba Jesus atu duni sai diabu hosi nia oan feto.
Maibee Jesus soe lia deit hodi dehan, “Oan sira tenki haan uluk, foin nia restu foo ba asu.” [Nee katak, Jesus tenki ajuda uluk Nia ema Judeu sira, mak foin bele ajuda ema seluk.]
Maibee feto nee hataan fali dehan, “Nee loos, Amu! Maibee asu nee iha hela meza okos. Nia mos haan hahaan restu nebee mak monu hosi oan nia bikan.” [Nee katak, kuandu oan sira haan, asu mos bele haan. Jesus bele ajuda Nia ema, maibee Nia mos tenki ajuda ema seluk.]
Rona nunee, Jesus hataan feto nee dehan, “O dehan nee, loos duni! Tanba o hataan nunee, diabu nee sai tiha ona hosi o nia oan. O bele fila ona.”
I feto nee fila ona ba nia uma. Too iha uma, nia haree nia oan toba hela. Diabu nee sai tiha ona.
Liu tiha nee, Jesus sira husik tiha sidade Tiru, i baa fali iha sidade Sidon. Depois Nia lao too iha tasi Galileia. Depois Nia baa iha rai Dekápolis.<a href='#note-394' class='key'>†</a>
Iha fatin nee, iha ema ida monok ho tilun diuk. Nia maluk sira lori nia ba Jesus. I sira husu ba Nia, “Senhor, favor ida, ajuda lai. Tau liman ba nia, hodi kura nia.”
Nunee Jesus husik hela ema barak nee, i Nia sai ho ema monok nee mesak deit. Depois Jesus hatama nia liman fuan ba iha ema nee nia tilun rua. I Nia mos tau kabeen iha Nia liman, i tau ba ema nee nia nanaal.
Depois Jesus hateke ba leten. Nia dada iis, hodi hatete, “Efata!” (Nee katak, “Nakloke ona ba!”)
Nia hatete deit nunee, ema nee nia tilun mos rona. I nia nanaal toos nee mos sai mamar, i nia koalia diak kedan.
Nee tiha hotu, sira nain rua fila fali ba ema lubuk ida ohin nee. Jesus bandu ba sira dehan, “Rona mai! Imi la bele konta ba ema, dehan Hau mak kura ema nee.” Bele Jesus bandu makaas, maibee sira baa konta iha fatin hotu-hotu.
I ema sira nebee rona novidade nee, sira hakfodak tebe-tebes. Sira foo hatene ba malu dehan, “Ema nee laos halimar! Ema ida nee bele halo buat hotu-hotu sai diak. Ema tilun diuk bele rona. Ema monok mos bele koalia.”
1-3 Iha loron ida, ema barak mai hamutuk hodi rona Nai Jesus nia koalia. Ema sira nee hamutuk ho Nia loron tolu kalan tolu ona, too sira nia bukae mos hotu ona. Tanba nee, Jesus bolu Nia eskolante sira, dehan, “Hau hadomi ema sira nee. Sira iha nee loron tolu kalan tolu ona, too sira la iha hahaan tan ona. Sira la bele fila ho kabun mamuk, tanba balu mai hosi rai dook. Keta halo be sira oin nakukun iha dalan, tanba hamlaha.”
Jesus nia eskolante sira hataan, “Senhor, fatin nee dook hosi aldeia. Halo nusaa mak ita bele foo hahaan ba ema barak ida nee?!”
Maibee Jesus husu ba sira, “Imi iha paun fuan hira?”
Sira hataan, “Senhor, ami iha paun fuan hitu deit.”
Depois Jesus haruka ema barak nee tuur tiha iha rai. Tuir mai Nia foti paun fuan hitu nee, foo agradese ba Nai Maromak. Nia silu fahe paun nee, depois Nia foo ba Nia eskolante sira hodi baa fahe ba ema barak nee.
Sira mos iha ikan uitoan. Jesus foo tan agradese ba Nai Maromak ba ikan nee, depois Nia haruka Nia eskolante sira fahe tan ikan ba ema barak nee.
8-9 Ema sira nee maizoumenus rihun haat. Sira hotu haan too bosu. Haan tiha, Nia eskolante sira baa aruma paun restu nee. Iha bote boot hitu kedan. Hotu tiha, Jesus haruka sira fila ona.
Sira fila tiha, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira, baa sae bero, liu hosi tasi ba iha rai ida naran Dalmanuta.
Jesus foin too iha Dalmanuta, iha ema balu hosi grupu Farizeu mai hasoru Nia. Sira mai ho intensaun atu koko Nia. Sira husu ba Nia nunee, “Senhor, halo milagre ruma para hatudu katak O simu forsa hosi Nai Maromak.”<a href='#note-395' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus dada iis, hodi dehan, “Tanba saa mak imi husu milagre ba Hau?! Milagre iha duni, maibee Hau la halo ba imi.”<a href='#note-396' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha, Jesus husik hela sira. Nia ho Nia eskolante sira sae fali bero, hodi baa iha tasi sorin.
Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira too tiha ona iha tasi klaran, foin Nia eskolante sira hanoin katak sira haluha tiha lori bukae. Sira lori deit paun fuan ida.
Rona sira koalia kona ba paun, Jesus dehan, “Imi tenki kuidadu ho liurai Herodes ho ema Farizeu sira. Imi la bele fiar liu sira! Tanba sira bele domina imi i halo imi konfundi tiha, hanesan mos fermentu domina halo trigu sae.”<a href='#note-397' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hatene saida mak sira hanoin. Nia dehan, “Nusaa mak imi koalia deit kona ba paun?! Imi seidauk komprende ka? Imi nia laran toos tebe-tebes.
Imi haree ona ho imi nia matan rasik, maibee imi la komprende nee dehan saida. Imi rona ho imi nia tilun rasik, maibee imi la komprende buat ida. Imi haluha ona<a href='#note-398' class='key'>✡</a>
paun fuan lima nebee Hau silu fahe hodi foo haan ema rihun lima nee, ka? Loron ida nee imi aruma paun restu bote hira?”
Sira hataan, “Senhor, resin bote sanulu resin rua.”
Jesus dehan tan, “Hanesan mos foin dadauk, Hau silu fahe paun hodi foo haan ema rihun haat. Imi haluha ka? Imi aruma paun restu bote boot hira?”
Sira hataan, “Senhor, resin bote boot hitu.”
Jesus dehan, “Nee loos duni! Imi haree ona ho matan rasik, maibee nusaa mak imi seidauk komprende Hau nia forsa nee?”
Depois Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira too iha aldeia Betsaida. Iha fatin nee ema lori ema matan aat ida, hodi baa aprezenta ba Jesus. Sira husu ba Jesus para bele kura nia.
Nunee Jesus kaer ema matan aat nee nia liman i lori sai hosi aldeia. Nia tafui kabeen ba ema nee nia matan, i tau liman ba. Depois Nia husu, “Nusaa? O bele haree ona buat ruma?”
Ema nee foti oin hodi haree ba karuk-loos, i nia hataan, “Wei! Hau haree ema lao! Maibee hanesan ai huun mak lao.”
Depois Jesus tau tan nia liman ba ema nee. Nunee nia matan mos diak, i bele haree kedas buat hotu-hotu ho moos.
Hotu tiha, Jesus haruka ema nee fila ba nia uma, dehan, “O bele fila ona, maibee liu hosi dalan seluk. La bele baa fali Betsaida.”
Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira baa iha aldeia-aldeia iha Sezareia Filipi. Iha dalan klaran, Nia husu ba sira: “Tuir ema konta, Hau nee see?”
Sira hataan, “Ema balu dehan, ‘João Sarani Nain’. Balu tan dehan, ‘Profeta Elias’. I seluk tan dehan, ‘Amu nee, Nai Maromak nia profeta ida seluk.’ ”<a href='#note-399' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus husu tan ba sira, “Maibee tuir imi nia hanoin, see mak Hau?”
Pedro simu hodi hatete, “Ita Boot nee Kristu, nebee Nai Maromak hili hori uluk kedan.”<a href='#note-400' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus bandu sira, “Imi la bele konta ba ema seluk!”
Nee liu tiha, Jesus komesa foo hatene ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Hau Mane Maksoin. La kleur tan, Hau tenki hetan terus tebe-tebes, hosi nai ulun sira, nai lulik nia ulun sira, ho mestri relijiaun sira. Sira hotu sei lakohi simu Hau. Sira sei oho mate Hau, maibee iha loron tolu,<a href='#note-401' class='key'>*</a> Hau sei moris fali.”
Jesus hatete mo-moos deit, depois Pedro dada Jesus ba sorin hodi hirus, “Amu la bele koalia nunee! Hau la husik ema foti liman hasoru Amu.”
Jesus fila oin ba Nia eskolante sira hodi hirus Pedro. Tanba nia koalia nee, la tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak. I Nia hatete ba Pedro, “Nee, diabu nia boot mak koalia. Satanás, sai hosi nee! O hanoin deit ema nia hakarak, laos Nai Maromak nia hakarak.”
Depois Jesus bolu Nia eskolante sira ho tan ema seluk, hodi hatete ba sira, “See mak hakarak tuir Hau, nia tenki tuir nafatin. Nia tenki husik tiha buat nebee mak nia hakarak, hodi tuir deit mak Nai Maromak nia hakarak. Bele ema atu oho nia, nia tenki tuir deit, hanesan ema nebee hasaan krus too mate.<a href='#note-402' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee mak mate tanba tuir Hau ho foo sai Hau nia Liafuan, nia sei hetan moris nafatin ho Nai Maromak. Maibee ema nebee mak moris deit ba nia aan rasik, nia sei lakon nia moris.<a href='#note-403' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona di-diak! Bele ema manaan buat hotu iha mundu nee, maibee se Nai Maromak soe nia, nia manaan saida loos?
La iha buat ida iha mundu nee, mak ema bele uza hodi troka nia klamar.
Agora nee, ema mesak aat deit. Sira la interese atu tuir Nai Maromak. Nee duni, see mak moe tanba Hau, i la brani foo sai Hau nia Liafuan, Hau mos sei la simu nia. Tanba Hau, Mane Maksoin sei mai fali ho Nai Maromak nia anju sira hosi lalehan. Ami sei tuun mai ho Nai Maromak nia forsa. Foin ema hatene see mak Hau.
Imi keta haluha Hau nia liafuan nee: Hosi imi nee hotu, balu sei moris too haree Nai Maromak tuur kaer hela ukun ho forsa.”
Liu tiha loron neen, Jesus lori Pedro, Tiago, ho João, sae ba iha foho aas ida. Iha nebaa la iha ema. Kuandu sira too iha foho, sira hakfodak, tanba sira haree Jesus fila aan tiha.
Nia hena mos mutin nabilan tiha. Iha mundu nee, la iha buat ida mak mutin nabilan liu Nia hena nee.
Derepenti deit sira haree Jesus koalia hela ho Elias ho Moisés, Nai Maromak nia profeta hori uluk nian.
Depois kalohan tuun mai falun tiha sira. I sira rona lian ida sai hosi kalohan nee dehan, “Rona mai! Jesus nee Hau nia Oan doben. Imi tenki rona di-diak ba Nia!”<a href='#note-404' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuandu Pedro sira rona liafuan nee, sira haree ba-mai, maibee la haree ema ida. Sira haree mak Jesus mesak deit.
Nee liu tiha, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira tuun fila fali hosi foho nee mai. Jesus bandu sira hodi hatete, “Buat nebee ohin imi haree nee, imi la bele konta sai ba ema. Hau Mane Maksoin. Hau tenki mate. Kuandu Hau moris fali ona, foin imi bele foo hatene ba ema.”
Sira kaer metin liafuan nebee Jesus hatete nee. Sira la konta ba ema. Maibee sira nain tolu husu ba malu dehan, “Nia dehan Nia sei mate i moris fali. Halo nusaa mak nee?”
Nunee sira husu ba Jesus, “Tuir mestri relijiaun sira dehan, ‘Avó Elias tenki mai uluk, foin Kristu mai.’ Maibee tuir Amu nia hanoin, oinsaa?”<a href='#note-405' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Loos duni. Avoo Elias tenki mai uluk hodi loke dalan ba Kristu. Kristu mak Nai Maromak hili hori uluk kedan. Nai Maromak nia liafuan hakerek ona kona ba Mane Maksoin, dehan nunee: Kuandu Nia mai, ema sei halo terus i oho mate Nia. Nusaa mak imi seidauk komprende?
Imi tenki rona di-diak! Avoo Elias mai tiha ona. Maibee ema halo susar nia, tuir sira nia hakarak. Buat sira nee hotu hodi kumpri saida mak Nai Maromak nia profeta sira hakerek tiha ona hori uluk.”
Kuandu Jesus ho Nia eskolante nain tolu nee, hasoru malu fali ho Nia eskolante sira seluk, sira haree ema barak mak halibur malu hela. I Jesus nia eskolante balu diskuti hela ho mestri relijiaun sira.
Bainhira ema barak nee haree Jesus, sira hakfodak, tanba sira hanoin Nia sei iha hela foho leten. Nunee sira halai baa hasoru Nia.
Depois Jesus husu ba sira, “Imi diskuti saida nee?”
Maibee iha ema ida dehan, “Amu, favor ida. Hau lori hau nia oan mane atu Amu kura. Nia monok, tanba espiritu aat tama iha nia.
Kuandu espiritu aat nee ataka ona, nia riba labarik nee ba rai. Nia kabeen mutin sai, i halo nia ruun nehan. Depois nia isin toos tiha, hanesan ai. Hau husu ona ba Amu nia eskolante sira, para duni sai tiha espiritu aat nee. Maibee sira la bele halo buat ida.”
Rona nunee, Jesus koalia makaas ba Nia eskolante sira, “Imi nee demais ona! Hau hanorin beibeik ba imi, maibee imi la komprende nafatin deit. Imi seidauk fiar deit Hau. Hau tenki pasiensia ba imi too bainhira?! Lori labarik nee mai iha nee!”
Nunee sira lori labarik nee ba Jesus. Maibee espiritu aat nee foin hetan Jesus, nia riba kedan labarik nee ba rai, too nia duir ba duir mai, i kabeen mutin mos sai hosi ibun.
Haree nunee, Jesus husu ba labarik nia aman, “O nia oan moras nunee, kleur ona ka?”
Nia aman hataan, “Komesa nia sei kiik.
Kleur ona espiritu aat nee atu oho labarik nee. Nia soe hau nia oan beibeik ba ahi ho ba bee laran. Nee duni Senhor, ajuda lai. Se bele, Senhor hadomi ami, kura labarik nee.”
Jesus hataan, “Nusaa mak o dehan ‘se bele’? Hau bele halo buat hotu-hotu, naran katak ema fiar.”
Nee hotu tiha, katuas nee hataan ho laran susar, “Amu, hau fiar ona. Maibee tulun hau para hau nia fiar nee bele makaas liu tan.”
Kuandu Jesus haree ema barak halai mai hamutuk iha fatin nee, Nia hatete ba espiritu aat nee, “Espiritu aat nebee halo labarik nee diuk ho monok, sai ona hosi nia! I o la bele tama tan ba nia ona.”
Rona Jesus koalia nunee, espiritu aat nee hakilar makaas. Nia halo labarik nee monu ba rai, i tebe liman tebe ain. Depois nia sai kedan hosi labarik nee. I labarik mos dezmaia, sai hanesan tiha ema mate ida. Too ema koalia ba malu dehan, “Nia mate tiha ona!”
Maibee Jesus kaer labarik nia liman hodi foti nia. I nia hadeer kedan.
Depois Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira husik hela tiha fatin nee, i baa tama iha uma ida. Kuandu sira mesak ona, sira husu ba Jesus, “Amu, tanba saa mak ami la bele duni sai espiritu aat nee?”
Jesus hataan, “Rona di-diak. Espiritu aat sira, aat duni. Tanba nee, se imi la harohan husu ajuda ba Nai Maromak, mak imi la iha forsa hodi duni sai espiritu hanesan nee.”<a href='#note-406' class='key'>*</a>
Hotu tiha nee, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira husik hela tiha uma nee, i sira baa iha provinsia Galileia. Jesus lakohi atu ema hatene katak Nia iha fatin nee,
tanba Nia atu hanorin deit Nia eskolante sira. Nia hatete ba sira, “La kleur tan, ema sei faan Hau ba ema seluk. Depois sira sei oho mate Hau, Mane Maksoin nee. Hau mate duni. Maibee iha loron tolu,<a href='#note-407' class='key'>†</a> Hau moris fali.”
Jesus foo hatene nunee, maibee Nia eskolante sira konfundi hela. Sira la brani husu tan Jesus kona ba Nia koalia nee.
Liu tiha nee, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira too iha sidade Kafarnaum. Sira tama iha uma laran, i Jesus husu ba Nia eskolante sira, “Ohin iha dalan, imi diskuti saida?”
Maibee la iha ema ida brani atu hataan. Sira moe, tanba iha dalan sira diskuti malu kona ba see mak boot.<a href='#note-408' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus baa kous tiha labarik oan ida, hodi baa iha sira nia klaran. I Nia hatete,
“See mak tuir Hau, nia tenki simu ema kiik, hanesan labarik oan nee. Kuandu halo hanesan nee, nia mos simu Hau. I see mak simu Hau, nia simu mos Nai Maromak, ida nebee haruka Hau mai iha mundu nee.”<a href='#note-410' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus nia eskolante ida, naran João, hatete, “Amu, iha loron ida, ami haree ema duni sai espiritu aat hodi Amu nia naran. Maibee ami bandu ema nee, tanba nia laos ita nia ema.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Imi la bele bandu nia! Tanba see mak uza Hau nia naran hodi halo milagre, nia sei la hatete aat Hau nia naran.
See mak la kontra ita, nia ita nia ema.<a href='#note-411' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni, hanoin di-diak. Se ema hatene katak imi tuir Kristu, mak nia ajuda imi, Nai Maromak mos la haluha ema nee nia kole. Bele nia foo deit bee kopu ida, Nai Maromak la haluha nia.”<a href='#note-412' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus hatete tan ba sira, “Se ema ruma halo labarik oan ida tuir dalan sala, too labarik nee la fiar tan Hau, kuidadu, é! Diak liu ba ema nee, kesi foti fatuk boot ida<a href='#note-413' class='key'>‡</a> ba nia kakorok, hodi baa soe tiha ba tasi laran.
Se o halo sala ho o nia liman, tesi soe tiha liman nee! Tanba diak liu o tama lalehan ho liman ida deit, duke o iha liman rua, maibee o tama ba infernu.<a href='#note-414' class='key'>✡</a>
[Infernu nee fatin terus nian. Iha nee, ular sira nunka mate. I ahi mos nunka mate.]<a href='#note-415' class='key'>§</a>
Se o halo sala ho o nia ain, tesi soe tiha ain nee! Tanba diak liu o tama lalehan ho ain ida deit, duke o iha ain rua, maibee o tama ba infernu.
[Infernu nee fatin terus nian. Iha nee, ular sira nunka mate. I ahi mos nunka mate.]<a href='#note-416' class='key'>*</a>
Se o halo sala ho o nia matan, sukit soe tiha matan nee! Tanba diak liu o tama ba lalehan ho matan ida deit, duke o iha matan rua, maibee o tama ba infernu.<a href='#note-417' class='key'>✡</a>
Infernu nee fatin terus nian.
Iha nee, ular sira nunka mate.
I ahi mos nunka mate.<a href='#note-418' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau nia hanorin nee, todan tebes. Nee duni, see mak atu tuir Hau, nia tenki tuir nafatin. Hanesan ema tau masin ba naan, i tamun ba ahi, para naan nee bele rai kleur.
Masin nee diak duni, tanba halo hahaan furak. Maibee se masin nee, nia meer la iha tan ona, nia la folin ona. Soe tiha deit! Imi mos tenki hanesan masin. Imi tenki moris paz ho ema hotu-hotu.
Nee duni, para ona ho imi nia diskuti kona ba see mak boot, see mak kiik.”<a href='#note-419' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida Jesus halibur Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua. Nia foti sira sai Nia apostolu hodi foo kbiit ba sira atu duni sai diabu hosi ema i kura ema nia moras oi-oin.
Sira nain sanulu resin rua nia naran mak hanesan tuir mai nee:
Primeiru, Simão (ema mos bolu nia Pedro), ho nia alin André,
Tiago ho nia alin João (sira nain rua Zebedeu nia oan),
Filipe ho Bartolomeu,
Tomé ho Mateus (nia kobrador impostu),
Tiago (nia Alfeu nia oan) ho Tadeu,
Simão (nia tuir partidu Patriota),<a href='#note-169' class='key'>*</a>
ho Judas Iscariotes (ikus mai nia mak faan Jesus).
5-6 Jesus foo knaar ba Nia apostolu nain sanulu resin rua hanesan nee: “Imi baa ona. Imi tenki baa iha ema Israel sira deit, tanba sira hanesan bibi malae nebee lao sala dalan ona. La bele baa tama iha ema jentiu sira nia leet. Ema Samaria nia aldeia mos la bele tama.
Baa foo hatene ema Israel sira dehan, ‘Tempu besik ona atu Maromak ukun imi.’
La bele lori osan mean ka osan mutin, atu doit ida mos la bele.
Lalika lori pasta, hena tahan rua ka sandalias atu troka iha dalan, i lalika lori imi nia ai tonka. Tanba ema nebee servisu, nia iha direitu atu ema foo buat nebee mak nia presiza.<a href='#note-170' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira imi tama iha sidade ida ka aldeia ida, baa buka uluk ema ida nebee laran diak, i hela iha nia uma too imi sai fali hosi fatin nee.
Bainhira imi tama iha uma laran, harohan ba Maromak atu foo bensaun ba uma kain nee.
Se uma nain simu imi ho diak, sira sei hetan duni bensaun nee. Se lae, dada fila fali imi nia liafuan bensaun nee.
Se imi baa too iha uma ida ka aldeia ida nebee la simu imi ka lakohi rona imi nia liafuan, husik tiha fatin nee, i baku rai rahun hosi imi nia ain okos nudar sinal katak sira rasik mak sei lori todan.<a href='#note-171' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, ema iha aldeia nee sei simu kastigu todan liu fali ema aat sira nebee uluk hela iha rai Sodoma ho Gomora.”<a href='#note-172' class='key'>✡</a>
“Rona di-diak, Hau haruka imi baa hanesan bibi malae nebee tama iha asu siak nia leet. Imi tenki matenek hanesan samea. I imi nia laran tenki moos hanesan manu pombu.<a href='#note-173' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuidadu, tanba ema sei mai kaer imi hodi lori imi ba iha tribunal. Sira sei baku imi ho sikoti iha sira nia uma kreda laran.
Sira mos sei foo sala ba imi iha liurai ho nai ulun sira nia oin. Buat sira nee hotu sai nunee tanba imi tuir Hau. Nee oportunidade ba imi atu foo Liafuan Diak ba sira ho mos ba ema nebee mak laos Judeu.
Bainhira ema lori imi baa hataan iha tribunal, lalika preokupa atu koalia saida ka atu hataan oinsaa. Tanba iha oras nee duni Maromak sei foo hatene ba imi liafuan nebee mak imi atu koalia sai.
Iha tempu nee, laos imi mak koalia, maibee imi nia Aman nia Espiritu mak koalia liu hosi imi.<a href='#note-174' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha uma laran ida, se iha ema ida mak fiar mai Hau, nia maun-alin rasik mak sei entrega nia ba nai ulun sira para oho. Se oan ida fiar mai Hau, nia aman rasik mak entrega nia ba ema seluk para oho. I se inan-aman mak fiar, sira nia oan rasik mak hamriik hasoru sira hodi foo ba ema oho.<a href='#note-175' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema iha nebee-nebee deit sei odi imi tanba imi tuir Hau. Maibee ema nebee mak aguenta nafatin too rohan, Maromak sei salva sira.<a href='#note-176' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira ema halo terus imi iha sidade ida tanba imi fiar mai Hau, halai ba sidade seluk. Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, imi seidauk haleu sidade hotu iha Israel laran, Hau, Mane Maksoin mai fali ona.
Estudante ida la bele boot liu nia mestri, i atan ida la bele boot liu fali nia patraun.<a href='#note-177' class='key'>✡</a>
Se estudante ida sai hanesan nia mestri, nee too ona. I atan ida sai hanesan nia patraun, nee mos too ona. Hau hanesan imi nia xefi familia, maibee ema hatete aat Hau dehan, Hau diabu nia boot Belzebu. Entaun imi nebee tama iha Hau nia familia mos, ema sei hatete imi aat loos.”<a href='#note-178' class='key'>✡</a>
“Nunee lalika tauk ema sira nee. Tanba buat hotu-hotu nebee agora taka hela, loron ida sei nakloke. I buat hotu-hotu nebee agora subar hela, aban-bainrua ema sei hatene.<a href='#note-179' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat nebee mak Hau foo hatene ba imi iha kotu-kotuk, imi tenki hatete sai. I saida mak Hau hanorin bis-bisu deit ba imi, imi tenki foo sai ho lian makaas iha ema barak nia oin.
La bele tauk ema nebee mak hakarak oho imi, tanba sira so bele oho deit imi nia isin, imi nia klamar sira la bele oho. Diak liu imi tauk mak Maromak, tanba Nia iha kbiit atu oho imi nia isin i soe imi nia klamar iha infernu laran.
Hanoin took manu liin. Manu liin rua, ema faan sentavus ida deit. Maski baratu liu, maibee la iha ida mak monu ba rai, se imi nia Aman iha lalehan la foo lisensa.
Laos nee deit, maibee Maromak mos hatene lo-loos imi nia fuuk lahan hira mak iha imi nia ulun.
Nee duni, lalika tauk, tanba imi folin boot liu manu liin barak.”
“See mak foo sai iha ema nia oin katak nia fiar mai Hau, aban-bainrua Hau mos sei foo sai iha Hau nia Aman iha lalehan nia oin katak, nia Hau nia ema.
Maibee see mak foo sai iha ema nia oin katak nia la konhese Hau, aban-bainrua Hau mos sei foo sai iha Hau nia Aman iha lalehan nia oin katak, nia laos Hau nia ema.”<a href='#note-180' class='key'>✡</a>
“Keta hanoin dehan Hau mai iha mundu nee atu lori dame. Hau mai laos atu lori dame, maibee atu lori konflitu.
Hau mai para halo ‘oan mane kontra nia aman, oan feto kontra nia inan, feto foun kontra nia banin feto.
Ema nia inimigu mai hosi nia uma laran rasik.’<a href='#note-181' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak hadomi liu nia inan-aman duke nia hadomi Hau, nia la serve atu sai Hau nia ema. Nunee mos ema nebee mak hadomi nia oan mane ka oan feto liu fali Hau, nia la serve sai Hau nian.
Ema nebee hanoin liu nia moris iha mundu nee, sei lakon fali nia moris. Maibee see mak lakon nia moris iha mundu nee tanba nia tuir Hau, nia sei hetan moris rohan-laek.”<a href='#note-183' class='key'>✡</a>
“See mak simu imi, nia simu ona Hau. See mak simu Hau, nia simu ona Ida nebee mak haruka Hau mai.<a href='#note-184' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak simu profeta ida tanba profeta nee foo sai Maromak nia liafuan, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak selu profeta sira nia kolen, ema nee mos simu hanesan. I see mak simu ema ida nebee moris loos tanba nia moris nee loos, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak selu ema moris loos sira nia kolen, ema nee mos simu hanesan.
Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, see mak foo tulun ba ema kiik ida tanba ema nee tuir Hau, maski nia foo bee kopu ida deit mos, Maromak la haluha nia kolen.”
Bainhira Jesus hanorin tiha buat sira nee hotu ba Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua, Nia husik tiha fatin nee. Depois Nia lao hosi aldeia ba aldeia iha rejiaun nee hodi hanorin ema i foo sai Maromak nia liafuan.
Iha tempu nebaa João Sarani Nain dadur tiha ona iha kadeia. Nia rona buat nebee Kristu halo. Nunee nia haruka nia eskolante balu baa hasoru Jesus hodi husu,
“Ita Boot mak Ema ida nebee Maromak promete atu haruka mai ka, ami tenki hein fali ema seluk?”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Imi fila baa konta ba João kona ba buat hotu-hotu nebee imi ohin rona ho saida mak imi haree.
Ema matan delek bele haree. Ema ain aat bele lao. Ema moras lepra, isin sai moos. Ema tilun diuk bele rona. Ema mate moris fila fali. Ema kiak rona Liafuan Diak.<a href='#note-185' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-186' class='key'>✡</a>
Hatete tan ba João dehan, ‘Ema nebee fiar nafatin mai Hau too rohan, nia hetan bensaun.’ ”
Bainhira João nia eskolante sira fila dadauk, Jesus komesa koalia kona ba João. Nia husu ema barak nebee haleu Nia nunee: “Uluk imi baa iha rai fuik maran atu haree see loos? Imi baa atu haree ema nebee nakdoko ba-mai tuir anin hanesan fali duut manlain ka? Lae!
Entaun imi baa atu haree see? Imi baa atu haree ema nebee hatais hena folin karun ka? Lae! Ema nebee hatais hena folin karun hela iha uma liurai nian.
Entaun imi baa atu haree see? Imi hanoin atu haree Maromak nia profeta ka? Loos duni! Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, João nee boot liu fali profeta.
Nia nee uluk kedas Livru Sagradu temi tiha ona dehan,
‘Rona mai! Hau haruka Hau nia ema ida baa uluk
hodi prepara dalan ba O.’<a href='#note-187' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, hori uluk kedas, la iha ema ida iha mundu nee mak hetan bensaun boot liu João Sarani Nain. Maski nunee, komesa agora ba oin, see mak hakruuk ba Maromak nudar Liurai, bele ema nee kiik mos, nia sei hetan bensaun boot liu fali João.<a href='#note-188' class='key'>†</a>
Hosi tempu João Sarani Nain mai too agora, iha ema uza violensia kontra Maromak nia reinu atu hatuun Maromak nudar Liurai.<a href='#note-189' class='key'>‡</a>
Molok João mai, profeta sira ho mos Moisés nia lei foo sai antes tiha ona kona ba saida mak akontese agora dadauk.<a href='#note-190' class='key'>✡</a>
Se imi hakarak fiar buat nebee mak loos, entaun imi sei hatene katak João nee mak profeta Elias durante nee ema hein hela.<a href='#note-191' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak ba!”
Jesus dehan tan, “Ema agora dadauk nee, Hau atu kompara ho saida? Sira hanesan labarik nebee tuur iha merkadu hodi hakilar ba sira nia kolega halimar dehan,
‘Ami toka muzika kapaas loos,
maibee imi la dansa.
Ami tanis lelir,
maibee imi la tanis.’
Nunee mos João mai, nia sempre jejun i la hemu tua, depois ema dehan, diabu tama iha nia laran.
Maibee Hau, Mane Maksoin mai, Hau haan ho hemu tua hanesan ema baibain, i ema dehan, Hau kaan-teen ho lanu-teen, i halo belun ho kobrador impostu sira ho ema aat sira. Maibee ema hotu-hotu nebee moris tuir Maromak nia matenek, sira hatudu katak Maromak nia matenek nee loos duni.”
Depois Jesus komesa kritika ema iha aldeia balu, tanba iha aldeia hirak nee mak Nia halo milagre barak liu, maibee ema sira nee lakohi hakribi sira nia sala.
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, imi sei simu kastigu todan liu fali ema Tiru ho ema Sidon.
Nunee mos imi ema Kafarnaum sira, keta hanoin katak, Maromak sei foti sae imi ba lalehan. Lae! Nia sei soe imi ba infernu. Se karik uluk ema jentiu sira iha sidade Sodoma haree milagre nebee Hau halo iha imi nia rai nee, entaun sira husik sira nia sala, i Maromak la sunu mutuk sidade nee.<a href='#note-193' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau dehan ba imi, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema nia lia, Maromak sei foo kastigu ba imi todan liu fali ema Sodoma sira nian.”<a href='#note-194' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nee, Jesus hahii Maromak dehan, “Hau nia Aman, lalehan ho rai nia Nain, Hau hahii Ita Boot, tanba Ita Boot taka buat sira nee ba ema matenek ho ema eskola boot, maibee Ita hatudu fali ba ema nebee kiik.
Hau nia Aman, ida nee halo Ita Boot nia laran haksolok duni.”
Hotu tiha, Jesus koalia ba ema iha nebaa nunee: “Hau nia Aman foo ona kbiit ho matenek hotu-hotu mai Hau. La iha ema ida konhese lo-loos Hau, so Hau nia Aman deit. I la iha ema ida mak konhese lo-loos Hau nia Aman, so Nia Oan, Hau deit. I Hau mos hili ema seluk hodi hatudu Hau nia Aman ba sira, para sira mos bele konhese Nia.<a href='#note-195' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee kole, imi nebee lor-loron lori naha todan, mai iha Hau, i Hau sei halo kamaan imi nia todan.
Mai aprende hosi Hau i moris tuir Hau nia hanorin, tanba Hau nee laran maus ho haraik Aan. Nunee imi nia laran bele senti kamaan.<a href='#note-196' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba buat nebee Hau hanorin la susar, i naha nebee Hau foo ba imi atu lori mos la todan.”
Iha loron Sabadu ida, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira lao liu hosi ema nia toos. Nia eskolante sira hamlaha, entaun sira komesa korut trigu musan hodi haan.<a href='#note-197' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu haree, i sira hasee Jesus dehan, “Haree took. Ita Boot nia eskolante sira servisu fali iha loron Sabadu. Ida nee kontra ita nia lei!”
Jesus hataan, “Imi lee tiha ona liurai David nia istoria. Nusaa mak imi la kompriende nafatin? Iha loron ida David ho nia ema sira hamlaha loos.
Nia tama ba tenda orasaun. Iha nebaa iha paun nebee nai lulik sira oferese ona ba Maromak. Tuir lo-loos, so nai lulik sira deit mak bele haan paun nee, liurai David ho nia ema sira nee la bele. Maibee David foti tiha paun nee, i nia ho nia ema sira haan.<a href='#note-198' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mos lee tiha ona Moisés nia lei. Tuir lei nee dehan, se nai lulik ida nia loron atu servisu iha uma kreda boot monu iha Sabadu, entaun nia tenki servisu duni. Maski kontra lei Sabadu nian, maibee Maromak la foo sala ba nia.<a href='#note-199' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau dehan ba imi, agora iha imi nia leet iha Ema ida boot liu uma kreda nee.
Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan, ‘Hau hakarak atu imi hatudu laran diak ba malu. Se lae imi lori sakrifisiu foo mai Hau mos la iha folin.’ Maibee liafuan nee, karik imi la simu. Nee mak imi hatudu liman ba ema nebee mak la sala.<a href='#note-200' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau, Mane Maksoin, mak loron Sabadu nia Nain. Hau mak iha direitu atu desidi, ema bele halo saida iha loron nee.”
Depois Jesus lao hosi toos nee, baa tama fali iha uma kreda.
Iha nebaa, iha mane ida nia liman sorin mate. Ema Farizeu sira buka dalan atu foo sala ba Jesus. Entaun sira husu ba Jesus dehan, “Tuir lei Moisés nian, bele kura ema moras iha loron Sabadu ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “Se loron Sabadu mak imi nia bibi ida monu tama ba rai kuak laran karik, imi baa hasai ka lae?<a href='#note-201' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun halo buat diak ba ema iha loron Sabadu mos la kontra lei. Tanba kompara ho bibi, ema mak folin boot liu.”
Depois Nia dehan ba ema liman sorin mate nee, “Lolo o nia liman mate nee mai!” Ema nee lolo ba, i nia liman diak kedas hanesan fali nia liman sorin.
Maibee ema Farizeu sira sai tiha ba liur hodi kombina malu para oho Jesus.
Jesus hatene hela ema Farizeu sira nia planu, nunee Nia husik tiha fatin nee. Ema barak tuir Nia, i Nia kura sira nia moras hotu.
Maibee Nia bandu sira atu la bele hatete sai kona ba Nia.
Nunee Nia halo tuir buat nebee mak Maromak foo sai tiha ona liu hosi profeta Isaias. Maromak dehan,
“Haree ba! Nee Hau nia Atan,
Hau mak hili Nia.
Hau hadomi Nia,
Hau sei tau Hau nia Espiritu iha Nia,
i Nia sei foo sai lia loos ba ema hosi suku hotu-hotu.
Nia la diskuti malu ho ema, i la hakilar.
Nia la koalia ho lian makaas tuir dalan.
Ai sanak lotuk nebee mak besik atu tohar, Nia la silu tohar.
Ahi oan nebee mak besik atu mate, Nia la huu mate.
Nia sei hatudu Nia laran luak beibeik too lia loos mak manaan.
Ema iha suku hotu-hotu sei laran metin ba Nia.”<a href='#note-202' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois ema balu lori mane ida ba Jesus. Ema nee diabu domina too nia matan delek i la hatene koalia. Jesus kura nia, nunee nia bele koalia ho haree fila fali.
Ema hotu admira hodi dehan, “Keta halo be Ema nee mak David nia Jerasaun nebee Maromak promete atu haruka mai?”
Maibee bainhira ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu rona nunee, sira dehan, “Ema nee bele duni sai diabu tanba deit Nia simu kbiit hosi diabu nia xefi Belzebu.”<a href='#note-203' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hatene sira hotu nia hanoin. Nunee Nia hatete ba sira, “Se iha nasaun ida, nia povu haan malu hela deit, nasaun nee sei rahun. Se iha sidade ida ka uma kain ida, nia ema sira istori malu hela deit, sira sei naksobu.
Se Satanás mak duni sai Satanás, entaun diabu sira haan malu hela deit, i Satanás nia ukun sei la dura.
Imi duun Hau dehan, hodi Belzebu nia kbiit mak Hau duni sai diabu. Entaun bainhira imi nia eskolante sira duni sai diabu, sira mos uza Belzebu nia kbiit ka? Lae! Imi nia eskolante sira rasik mak sei hatete sai katak, buat nebee imi duun Hau nee, la loos.
Hau duni sai diabu hodi Maromak nia Espiritu. Nee hatudu katak Maromak ukun ona iha imi nia leet nudar Liurai.
Hau foo ezemplu tan. Se ema ida hakarak tama ba foti sasaan hosi ema forti ida nia uma, nia tenki futu metin tiha ema forti nee uluk mak foin bele lalin sasaan sai hosi nia uma.<a href='#note-204' class='key'>*</a>
Ema nebee la hamutuk ho Hau, nia kontra Hau. I ema nebee la servisu hamutuk ho Hau, nia estraga Hau nia servisu.<a href='#note-205' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee Hau dehan ba imi, ema nebee halo sala, too hatete aat Maromak mos, Maromak sei foo perdaun. Maibee see mak hatete aat Maromak nia Espiritu, Maromak la foo perdaun ba nia.
Nunee mos ema nebee mak koalia aat Hau, Mane Maksoin, nia sei hetan perdaun. Maibee see mak koalia aat Espiritu Santu, Maromak la foo perdaun ba nia too tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-206' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus koalia nafatin ba ema Farizeu sira dehan, “Ai huun nebee diak sei foo fuan diak. Maibee ai huun nebee la diak sei foo fuan la diak. Tanba ai nee nia fuan mak hatudu sai katak ai huun nee diak ka la diak.<a href='#note-207' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nee samea nia oan! Imi ema laran aat bele koalia buat diak ka? Lae! Tanba buat nebee mak rai iha ema nia laran, ida nee mak sei sai hosi nia ibun.<a href='#note-208' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee diak koalia liafuan diak, tanba nia laran nakonu ho buat diak. I ema nebee aat koalia buat aat, tanba nia laran nakonu ho buat aat.
Hanoin di-diak! Iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, Nia sei tetu ema nia liafuan ida-ida. Imi nia liafuan nebee mak imi koalia arbiru, imi tenki hataan iha Maromak nia oin.
Atu Maromak desidi foo kastigu ka, desidi dehan imi la sala, depende ba imi nia liafuan.”
Depois ema Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun balu husu ba Jesus dehan, “Mestri, ami hakarak haree milagre hosi Ita Boot hodi hatudu katak Ita Boot nia kbiit mai hosi Maromak.”<a href='#note-209' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Imi ema agora nee mesak aat deit i la foo laran ba Maromak! Imi husu Hau halo milagre hanesan sinal atu imi bele fiar. Maibee Hau sei la halo. Milagre nebee Maromak uluk halo liu hosi profeta Jonas too ona.<a href='#note-210' class='key'>✡</a>
Jonas hela iha ikan boot nia kabun laran loron tolu kalan tolu. Nunee mos Hau, Mane Maksoin sei hela iha rai okos loron tolu kalan tolu.<a href='#note-211' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, ema jentiu sira hosi sidade Nínive sei hamriik hodi foo sala ba imi, tanba uluk, bainhira Jonas baa foo sai Maromak nia liafuan ba sira, sira husik kedas sira nia sala. Agora iha imi nia leet iha Ema ida nebee boot liu fali Jonas, maibee imi lakohi husik imi nia sala.<a href='#note-212' class='key'>✡</a>
Laos povu Nínive deit mak sei foo sala ba imi. Liurai feto hosi rai Seba mos sei moris fali, i hamriik hodi foo sala ba imi nebee moris agora, tanba uluk nia mai hosi rai dook atu rona rasik liafuan matenek nian hosi liurai Salomão. Afinal agora iha imi nia leet iha Ema ida ke boot liu fali liurai Salomão. Maibee imi lakohi rona Nia.”<a href='#note-213' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun nia dehan, ‘Diak liu hau fila fali ba hau nia hela fatin uluk.’ Kuandu nia fila, nia haree fatin nee mamuk, hamoos tiha ona i buat hotu-hotu tau tuir nia fatin.
Depois espiritu aat nee baa bolu tan espiritu hitu nebee aat liu fali nia, i sira hotu baa hela iha ema nee. Nunee, ema nee nia moris aat liu fali uluk. Ema aat nebee moris agora mos sei sai hanesan nee.”
Jesus sei koalia hela ba ema lubun boot, Nia inan ho Nia alin mane sira mai hamriik iha liur atu koalia ho Nia.
Iha ema ida foo hatene ba Jesus dehan, “Ita Boot nia inan ho alin sira hamriik iha liur. Sira husu atu koalia ho Ita Boot.”<a href='#note-214' class='key'>†</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan ba ema nee dehan, “Hau nia inan mak see? I Hau nia alin sira mak see?
Depois Nia hatudu ba Nia eskolante sira hodi dehan, “Sira nee mak Hau nia inan ho Hau nia alin sira.
Tanba see mak halo tuir Hau nia Aman iha lalehan nia hakarak, sira nee mak Hau nia inan ho Hau nia alin sira.”
Iha loron nebaa, Jesus sai hosi uma nee i baa tuur iha tasi ibun.
Ema barak teb-tebes mak mai haleu Nia, nunee Nia baa tuur iha roo laran, i ema sira nee hamriik deit iha tasi ibun.<a href='#note-215' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia hanorin buat barak uza komparasaun, nunee: “Iha toos nain ida baa kari fini iha nia toos.
Bainhira nia kari fini nee, balu monu iha dalan. I manu fuik mai hili tiha hotu.
Fini balu monu iha fatuk leten, fini nee moris lalais deit tanba rai mihis.
Maibee kuandu loro matan sae, loro manas sunu fini nebee foin moris sai mai nee too namlaik tiha, tanba abut la tama iha rai okos.
Fini balu monu iha duut tarak laran. Fini nee moris, maibee duut tarak habit tiha too la buras sae.
Iha fini balu tan monu iha rai bokur, fini nee moris too foo isin barak, balu too musan atus ida, balu too musan neen-nulu i balu too tolu-nulu.
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak ba!”
Depois Jesus nia eskolante sira mai husu Nia dehan, “Nusaa mak Ita Boot hanorin sira uza fali komparasaun?”
Jesus hataan, “Uluk ema seidauk hatene, oinsaa mak Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. Agora Hau foo sai mo-moos ba imi deit, ba ema seluk lae.
Tanba ema nebee kompriende ona, Maromak sei halo nia kompriende liu tan. Maibee ema nebee lakohi hatene, buat uitoan nebee nia kompriende tiha ona mos, Maromak sei hasai tiha hosi nia hanoin.<a href='#note-216' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hanorin sira uza komparasaun tanba:
‘Sira haree hela,
maibee hanesan la haree.
Sira rona hela,
maibee hanesan la rona i la kompriende.’
Maromak nia liafuan liu hosi profeta Isaias kona loos sira. Maromak dehan,
‘Imi sei rona beibeik,
maibee la kompriende nafatin.
Imi sei haree beibeik,
maibee nafatin la hatene tuir.
sira lakohi rona ho sira nia tilun,
sira nia matan taka metin.
Sira halo nunee atu sira nia matan la bele haree,
sira nia tilun la bele rona,
i sira nia laran la bele kompriende.
Nunee sira la bele fila fali mai Hau,
atu Hau salva sira.’<a href='#note-217' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee imi nee hetan bensaun tanba imi nia matan haree, imi nia tilun rona.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, uluk profeta barak ho ema seluk nebee moris loos, hakarak teb-tebes atu haree buat nebee mak agora imi haree, maibee sira la haree. Sira hakarak teb-tebes atu rona buat nebee agora imi rona, maibee sira la rona.”<a href='#note-218' class='key'>✡</a>
“Entaun rona mai, istoria kona ba ema kari fini nee dehan saida?
Fini nebee monu iha dalan mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia liafuan kona ba oinsaa Nia ukun ema nudar Liurai, maibee nia la kompriende. Depois diabu nia boot mai hadau tiha liafuan nebee iha tiha ona nia laran.
Fini nebee monu iha fatuk leten mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia liafuan, i simu kedas ho laran haksolok.
Maibee liafuan nee la iha abut. Nunee nia fiar duni maibee la kleur ida. Bainhira susar kona nia, ka ema seluk halo terus nia tanba nia simu liafuan nee, nia husik tiha kedas.
Fini nebee monu iha duut tarak laran mak ema nebee rona Maromak nia liafuan, maibee nia preokupa ho nia moris lor-loron nian, i matan naklosu ba rikusoin mundu nian. Nia preokupasaun nee la foo fatin ba Maromak nia liafuan, nunee liafuan nee la muda nia moris.
Maibee fini nebee monu iha rai bokur mak ema nebee rona hodi kompriende Maromak nia liafuan. Nunee ema nee moris tuir, hanesan fini nebee moris too foo isin, balu too musan atus ida, balu musan neen-nulu, i balu musan tolu-nulu.”
Depois Jesus halo tan komparasaun dehan, “Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, nee hanesan toos nain ida baa kari fini diak iha nia toos.
Kalan boot ema hotu toba dukur tiha, toos nain nia inimigu ida mai kari tan duut nia musan ba iha toos nee nia laran. Hotu tiha inimigu nee fila.
Bainhira fini nee moris i fulin komesa sai mai, duut fuik mos moris buras.
Haree nunee, atan sira nebee mak servisu iha toos nee baa foo hatene toos nain dehan, ‘Patraun, uluk ita kari deit fini diak. Nusaa mak duut fuik mosu hotu?’
Toos nain nee hataan, ‘Hau nia inimigu mak halo ida nee.’
Atan sira dehan tan, ‘Se patraun hakarak, ami baa fokit sai tiha.’
Maibee toos nain hataan dehan, ‘La bele. Keta fokit lai, tanba se imi fokit sai duut fuik nee, imi mos bele fokit sai fini diak nebee moris ona nee.
Husik sira moris hamutuk. Bainhira too nia tempu atu koa mak hau haruka ema nebee servisu atu baa fokit sai duut nee hodi futu hamutuk ba sunu tiha. Depois toos nia rezultadu tau hamutuk hodi rai iha armazen laran.’ ”
Jesus halo tan komparasaun dehan, “Maromak nia reinu hanesan ai musan kiik-oan loos nebee mak ema kuda iha nia toos.
Maski ai musan nee kiik liu musan sira seluk, maibee nia moris i buras too sai ai huun ida nebee mak boot liu iha toos laran. Nunee manu fuik sira mai halo knuuk iha nia sanak.”<a href='#note-219' class='key'>*</a>
Jesus halo tan komparasaun seluk dehan, “Maromak nia reinu hanesan fermentu nebee senhora ida kahur ho trigu saka ida hodi halo paun. Too ikus, fermentu uitoan nee halo trigu tomak sae.”<a href='#note-220' class='key'>†</a>
Jesus esplika reinu lalehan ba ema lubun boot nee ho komparasaun oi-oin. Nia sempre hanorin sira uza komparasaun.
Nunee Nia halo tuir saida mak Maromak nia profeta hakerek tiha ona dehan,
“Hau sei hanorin uza komparasaun.
komesa hosi Maromak halo mundu too agora.”<a href='#note-221' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus sai tiha hosi ema barak nee nia leet hodi tama ba iha uma laran. Nia eskolante sira mai tuir Nia hodi husu dehan, “Esplika mai ami komparasaun kona ba duut fuik nee.”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Ema nebee mak kari fini diak mak Hau, Mane Maksoin.
Toos mak mundu nee. Fini diak mak Maromak nia reinu, i duut fuik mak ema nebee tuir diabu nia boot.
Inimigu nebee kari duut fuik nee mak diabu nia boot. Tempu koa nian mak bainhira mundu remata, i ema nebee hatama rezultadu toos mak Maromak nia anju sira.
Duut fuik fokit tiha hodi sunu iha ahi laran. Nunee mos bainhira mundu nee atu remata.
Hau, Mane Maksoin sei haruka Hau nia anju sira baa iha Hau nia povu nia leet hodi fokit sai see-see deit mak halo sala ho mos ema nebee mak halo ema seluk too monu ba sala.
Hau nia anju sira sei soe ema aat sira nee ba iha ahi lakan laran, iha nebaa sira sei tanis hakilar i ruun nehan.
Maibee ema nebee mak moris loos, sira sei tama iha lalehan hodi hela hamutuk ho Maromak, Nia mak sira nia Aman ho sira nia Liurai. Iha nebaa sira sei nabilan hanesan loromatan. See mak iha tilun, rona di-diak ba!”
“Maromak nia ukun, ita bele kompara ho rikusoin ida karun teb-tebes nebee subar hela iha rai okos. Iha ema ida hetan rikusoin nee. Nia kontenti loos, entaun nia hakoi fila fali, i baa faan tiha nia sasaan hotu-hotu hodi sosa rai nee, para rikusoin nee bele sai ninian.
Maromak nia ukun, ita mos bele kompara hanesan nee: Iha kontratu nain ida buka hela buat murak-mean atu sosa.
Bainhira nia hetan ida nebee diak liu, nia baa faan tiha nia sasaan hotu-hotu hodi sosa buat murak-mean nee.”
“Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, bele mos kompara hanesan nee. Iha peskador balu hatuun redi ba iha tasi laran hodi hetan ikan oi-oin deit.
Bainhira redi nee ikan nakonu ona, sira dada sai ba iha tasi ibun. Depois sira tuur hodi hasai tiha ikan barak nee hosi redi. Ikan diak nian sira hatama ba iha nia fatin, ikan nebee mak aat, sira soe tiha.
Nunee mos bainhira mundu nee atu remata, anju sira sei mai haketak tiha ema aat hosi ema nebee mak moris loos.
Ema aat, sei soe ba iha ahi lakan laran, iha nebaa sira sei tanis hakilar i ruun nehan.”
Depois Jesus husu Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Buat nebee ohin Hau hanorin nee imi kompriende hotu ka lae?”
Nia eskolante sira hataan, “Ami kompriende.”
Jesus dehan, “Se nunee imi hanesan mestri relijiaun nebee hatene ona Maromak nia liafuan uluk nian i hatene mos buat nebee mak agora Hau hanorin kona ba Maromak nia ukun. Imi hanesan uma nain nebee mak rai rikusoin antigu nian ho rikusoin foun hamutuk iha fatin ida, depois hatudu sai ba ema.”
Bainhira Jesus hanorin hotu komparasaun hirak nee, Nia husik tiha fatin nee
hodi baa fali iha Nia aldeia rasik. Iha nebaa Nia tama iha uma kreda hodi hanorin. Ema nebee rona Nia admira hodi husu ba malu, “Ema nee hetan matenek hosi nebee? Nia hetan kbiit hosi nebee mak bele halo milagre boot hanesan nee?
Ita hatene hela Nia. Nia aman badaen ai ida. Nia inan mak Maria, i nia alin sira Tiago, José, Simão ho Judas.
Nia alin feto sira mos hela iha nee hotu. Entaun Ema nee hetan buat sira nee hosi nebee?”
Nunee sira laran moras too lakohi simu Nia.
Maibee Jesus hatete ba sira, “Ema iha nebee-nebee deit respeita Maromak nia profeta. So ema hosi nia aldeia rasik ho nia familia rasik mak la respeita nia.”<a href='#note-222' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun Jesus halo milagre uitoan deit iha sira nia leet, tanba sira lakohi fiar ba Nia.
Iha tempu nebaa liurai Herodes mak ukun iha provinsia Galileia. Nia rona buat oi-oin kona ba Jesus,
too nia hatete ba nia funsionariu sira, “Keta halo be Ema nee João Sarani Nain mak moris fali ona hosi mate. Nee mak Nia iha kbiit hodi halo milagre.”
3-4 João Sarani Nain ho Herodes nia istoria nunee: Uluk Herodes hola fali nia alin Filipe nia kaben, naran Herodias. Iha tempu nebaa, João hasee nia fila-fila dehan, “Ita la bele hola fali ita nia alin nia kaben, hahalok nee kontra Maromak nia lei!” Tanba nee Herodes haruka ema kaer João i futu nia hodi hatama ba iha komarka.<a href='#note-223' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida Herodes halo nia tinan, i Herodias nia oan feto mai dansa iha bainaka sira nia oin. Menina nee nia dansa halo Herodes nia laran kontenti teb-tebes,
too nia jura ba menina nee atu foo saida deit mak nia husu.
Menina nia inan rona kona ba juramentu nee, i nia hamaus nia oan atu husu João Sarani Nain nia ulun. Entaun menina nee husu ba Herodes, “Hau hakarak João nia ulun, tau iha bandeja ida, entrega kedas mai hau.”
Liurai laran susar teb-tebes. Maibee tanba nia jura tiha ona iha bainaka sira nia oin, entaun nia haruka ema baa halo tuir saida mak menina nee husu.
Sira baa iha komarka hodi tesi tiha João nia ulun,
i tau iha bandeja foo ba menina nee. Depois menina nee lori baa entrega ba nia inan.
Hotu tiha João nia eskolante sira baa lori sai João nia mate isin baa hakoi tiha. Depois sira baa foo hatene Jesus.
Jesus rona katak ema oho tiha ona João. Entaun Nia husik tiha fatin nee hodi sae roo ba iha rai fuik ida. Maibee ema rona katak Nia atu baa iha nebaa, nunee ema barak hosi aldeia oi-oin lao liu hosi tasi ibun hodi tuir Nia.
Bainhira Jesus tuun hosi roo, Nia haree ema lubun boot hein hela Nia iha nebaa. Nia hanoin loos sira, i Nia kura sira nebee mak moras.
Bainhira lokraik ona, Jesus nia eskolante sira mai foo hatene Nia dehan, “Iha nee rai fuik, rai mos besik kalan ona. Diak liu haruka ema sira nee baa iha aldeia hodi sosa hahaan rasik.”
Maibee Jesus dehan, “Lae, sira la presiza baa sosa hahaan. Imi mak foo hahaan ba sira.”
Nia eskolante sira hataan, “Ami iha deit paun fuan lima ho ikan rua.”
Jesus hataan fali, “Lori mai.”
Depois Jesus haruka ema lubun boot nee tuur hotu iha duut leten. Nia foti paun fuan lima ho ikan rua nee, i hateke ba lalehan hodi foo agradese ba Maromak. Nia silu paun ho ikan halo rohan-rohan, i foo ba Nia eskolante sira. Depois Nia eskolante sira hodi baa fahe ba ema lubun boot nee.
Sira hotu haan too bosu, hahaan mos resin. Nia eskolante sira tau hamutuk hahaan restu sira nee iha bote sanulu resin rua nakonu.
Ema nebee haan nee maizoumenus rihun lima. Nee foin sura mane deit, feto ho larabik la sura.
Hotu tiha, Jesus haruka kedas Nia eskolante sira sae roo hodi baa uluk iha tasi sorin. Maibee Nia sei hela iha nebaa, atu haruka ema lubun boot nee fila.
Bainhira sira fila hotu ona, Jesus mesak sae ba foho ida hodi halo orasaun. Rai besik kalan ona, Nia mes-mesak iha foho leten.
Iha momentu nebaa, roo nebee Nia eskolante sira sae nee iha tiha ona tasi klaran. Roo nee halai hasoru anin boot, laloran mos baku makaas.
Iha dadeer-saan nakukun Jesus lao iha bee leten baa hasoru Nia eskolante sira.
Bainhira Nia eskolante sira haree Nia lao iha bee leten, sira tauk hodi hakilar makaas dehan, “Mate klamar mai nee!”
Maibee Jesus hataan kedas, “Brani ba! Nee Hau. La bele tauk!”
Pedro hataan, “Nai, se Nai mak iha nebaa duni, entaun haruka hau lao iha bee leten baa hasoru Ita Boot.”
Jesus dehan, “Mai ba!” Nunee Pedro tuun hosi roo i lao iha bee leten atu baa Jesus.
Maibee bainhira Pedro haree anin boot, nia komesa tauk i mout dadauk iha tasi laran. Nia hakilar makaas ba Jesus dehan, “Nai, salva hau ba!”
Jesus lolo kedas Nia liman ba Pedro hodi kaer nia dehan, “O nee fiar fraku! Nusaa mak o duvida hanesan nee?”
Depois sira nain rua tama iha roo laran. I anin mos para kedas.
Sira hotu nebee iha roo laran komesa adora Jesus dehan, “Ita Boot mak Maromak nia Oan duni!”
Bainhira too iha tasi sorin, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira tuun iha rai Genesaret.
Sira husu ba Jesus atu ema moras sira nee bele kona deit Nia hena rohan. I ema moras sira nebee konsege kona Nia hena rohan, sira hetan kura hotu.
Loron ida ema balu hosi grupu Farizeu ho mestri relijiaun balu mai hosi Jerusalém atu hasoru malu ho Jesus. Too iha nebaa sira husu Nia,
“Tuir ita nia bei-ala sira nia lisan, molok atu haan tenki fasi liman lai. Maibee Ita Boot nia eskolante sira lae. Nusaa mak sira kontra fali ita nia lisan nee?”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Nusaa mak imi kontra Maromak nia lei tanba deit imi hakarak tuir imi nia lisan?
Tanba Maromak hatete, ‘Respeita o nia inan-aman.’ Nia mos dehan, ‘See mak koalia liafuan aat hasoru nia inan-aman, ema nee sei hetan kastigu mate.’<a href='#note-224' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee imi hanorin oin seluk fali. Tuir imi, ema bele hatete ba nia inan-aman dehan, ‘Sasaan nebee apaa ho amaa presiza, hau la bele foo, tanba hau promete ona atu foo ba Maromak.’
Nunee imi hanorin ema atu la respeita sira nia inan-aman. Imi halakon tiha Maromak nia lei tanba deit imi hakarak halo tuir imi nia lisan.
Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk! Buat nebee hori uluk kedas profeta Isaias hakerek, kona loos imi. Nia foo tutan Maromak nia liafuan nunee:
‘Ema sira nee hahii Hau ho ibun tutun deit,
maibee sira nia laran dook hosi Hau.
Sira adora Hau
maibee la iha folin.
Sira hanorin deit lei ema nian,
maibee bosok fali dehan, sira nia hanorin nee mai hosi Hau.’ ”<a href='#note-225' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus bolu ema hotu iha nebaa atu mai besik. Nia dehan ba sira, “Rona mai, i kompriende di-diak Hau nia liafuan nee.
Hahaan saida mak hatama hosi ema nia ibun, nee la halo foer nia iha Maromak nia oin. Maibee liafuan nebee mak sai hosi ema nia ibun, nee mak halo foer nia.”
Jesus nia eskolante sira mai dehan ba Nia, “Ita Boot hatene ka lae? Ita Boot nia liafuan ohin nee xoke loos ema Farizeu sira.”
Maibee Jesus soe lia hodi hataan sira dehan, “Ai horis hotu-hotu nebee laos Hau nia Aman iha lalehan mak kuda, Nia sei fokit sai tiha.
Husik sira hirus ba! Sira nee hanesan ema matan delek nebee hakarak hatudu dalan ba ema matan delek seluk, too ikus sira monu hotu ba rai kuak.”<a href='#note-226' class='key'>✡</a>
Pedro husu, “Ohin Mestri koalia kona ba buat nebee halo foer ema. Liafuan nee dehan saida?”
Jesus hataan, “Imi la kompriende nafatin ka?
Imi hatene katak buat nebee ema haan liu hosi nia ibun sei tama iha nia kabun laran depois sai fali.
Maibee buat nebee mak sai hosi ema nia ibun mai hosi nia laran. Ida nee mak halo foer nia.<a href='#note-227' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba hanoin aat nebee mosu hosi ema nia laran mak lori nia ba oho ema, halo sala ho ema nia feen ka laen ho sala seksual selu-seluk, naok, foo sasin falsu i hatete aat ema seluk.
Hahalok sira nee mak halo ema sai foer iha Maromak nia oin. Laos haan la fasi liman mak halo sira sai foer.”
Depois Jesus husik tiha fatin nee hodi baa fali iha rai ida besik sidade Tiru ho sidade Sidon.
Iha nebaa, iha feto Kanaán ida hosi rai nee mai hasoru Jesus. Nia husu fila-fila ho lian makaas dehan, “Nai, Liurai David nia Jerasaun, hanoin hau ba! Hau nia oan feto, diabu tama iha nia laran halo nia terus liu.”
Maibee Jesus la hataan buat ida. Nunee Nia eskolante sira mai hatete ba Nia dehan, “Senhora nee hakilar la para iha ita nia kotuk, diak liu haruka nia fila.”
Maibee Jesus hataan dehan, “Maromak haruka Hau mai atu ajuda deit ema Israel, tanba sira hanesan bibi malae nebee lao sala dalan ona.”
Jesus soe lia dehan, “La bele foti labarik nia hahaan hodi soe fali ba asu. Nee la loos.”<a href='#note-228' class='key'>*</a>
Senhora nee hataan fali dehan, “Loos duni Nai, maibee asu sira bele hili labarik nia hahaan nebee mak monu iha meza okos.”
Rona nunee Jesus dehan, “Senhora, ita nia fiar makaas! Saida mak ita husu sei akontese duni.” Iha oras nee kedas senhora nee nia oan feto diak fali.
Depois Jesus husik tiha fatin nee, lao tuir tasi Galileia nia ninin. Nia sae foho ida hodi tuur,
i ema barak teb-tebes mai iha Nia. Sira lori sira nia maluk nebee aleijadu oi-oin, hanesan ain mate, ain aat, matan delek, koalia la diak, ho ema moras oi-oin tan. Sira tau ema sira nee iha Jesus nia oin, i Nia kura sira hotu kedas.
Bainhira sira haree saida mak Jesus halo nee, sira hotu admira. Ema nebee uluk koalia la diak agora bele koalia, ema ain mate ho ain aat bele lao, i ema matan delek bele haree. Entaun sira hotu hahii Israel nia Maromak.
Depois Jesus bolu Nia eskolante sira hamutuk, foin Nia dehan ba sira, “Hau hanoin loos ema barak nee. Sira hamutuk ho Hau loron tolu ona, i sira nia hahaan la iha ona. Hau lakohi haruka sira fila ho kabun mamuk. Se lae sira oin nakukun, bele monu iha dalan.”
Nia eskolante sira hataan, “Rai nee fuik. Ita atu hetan hahaan hosi nebee mak atu foo hahaan ba ema barak hanesan nee?”
Jesus husu, “Imi sei iha paun fuan hira?”
Sira hataan, “Iha deit paun fuan hitu ho ikan kiik-oan balu.”
Depois Jesus haruka ema lubun boot nee tuur hotu iha rai.
Nia foti paun fuan hitu ho ikan nee hodi foo agradese ba Maromak. Nia silu halo rohan-rohan tiha, i foo ba Nia eskolante sira. Depois Nia eskolante sira fahe ba ema lubun boot nee.
Sira hotu haan too bosu, hahaan mos resin. Nia eskolante sira tau hamutuk hahaan restu sira nee iha bote hitu nakonu.
Ema nebee haan nee, rihun haat. Nee foin sura mane deit, feto ho labarik la sura.
Hotu tiha Jesus haruka ema lubun boot nee fila. Depois Nia baa sae roo hodi baa iha rai Magadán.
Iha loron ida ema balu hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu ho Saduseu mai koko Jesus. Sira husu para Nia halo tan milagre hodi hatudu katak Nia kbiit nee mai duni hosi Maromak.<a href='#note-229' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Bainhira loromatan atu besik monu, imi haree kalohan mihis sai mean, imi siik dehan, aban la udan.
Iha dadeer-saan fali, bainhira imi haree loromatan leno kalohan mahar, imi siik dehan, karik orsida udan. Imi hatene siik sinal nebee mosu iha kalohan. Maibee sinal nebee mak akontese iha imi nia oin agora dadauk nee, imi la hatene siik.
Imi ema agora nee mesak aat deit i la foo laran ba Maromak! Imi husu Hau halo milagre hanesan sinal atu imi bele fiar. Maibee Hau sei la halo. Milagre nebee Maromak uluk halo liu hosi profeta Jonas too ona.” Koalia tiha hotu, Jesus lao husik tiha sira.<a href='#note-230' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-231' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira baa iha tasi sorin. Too iha nebaa Nia eskolante sira foin hanoin katak sira haluha lori paun.
Depois Jesus hatete ba sira, “Kuidadu! Hadook aan hosi ema Farizeu ho Saduseu sira nia fermentu.”<a href='#note-232' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee Nia eskolante sira komesa hatete ba malu dehan, “Karik Nia koalia hanesan nee tanba ita la lori paun.”
Jesus hatene hela saida mak sira koalia. Entaun Nia hatete, “Imi nee fiar fraku! Nusaa mak imi diskuti malu fali kona ba paun?
Imi seidauk kompriende ka? Imi haluha ona paun fuan lima nebee mak Hau fahe ba ema rihun lima ka? Iha tempu nebaa imi tau hamutuk hahaan restu too bote hira?<a href='#note-233' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois oinsaa ho paun fuan hitu nebee Hau fahe ba ema rihun haat? Imi tau hamutuk hahaan restu too bote hira?<a href='#note-234' class='key'>✡</a>
Nusaa mak ohin Hau temi fermentu, imi hanoin kedas Hau koalia kona ba paun? Laos nunee! Maibee Hau foo hanoin ba imi atu kuidadu ho ema Farizeu ho Saduseu sira nia fermentu.”
Nee mak foin Nia eskolante sira kompriende katak, Nia laos koalia kona ba fermentu nebee mak halo trigu sae. Maibee Nia koalia kona ba ema Farizeu ho Saduseu sira nia hanorin nebee mak lori ema lao sala dalan.
Depois Jesus baa iha rai ida nebee besik sidade Sezareia Filipi. Too iha nebaa Nia husu ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Tuir ema konta, Hau, Mane Maksoin nee see?”
Sira hataan, “Iha balu dehan, Ita Boot João Sarani Nain. Balu tan dehan, profeta Elias. Seluk tan dehan, Jeremias ka profeta ida seluk.”<a href='#note-235' class='key'>✡</a>
Simão Pedro hataan, “Ita Boot nee Kristu, Salvador nebee Maromak promete hori uluk ona atu haruka mai. Ita Boot mak Maromak Moris nia Oan.”<a href='#note-236' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus dehan, “Simão, Jonas nia oan, o hetan bensaun, tanba laos ema mak foo hatene ba o kona ba buat nee. Maibee Hau nia Aman iha lalehan mak foo hatene ba o.
Hau hatete ba o, Hau bolu o Pedro, nee dehan katak fatuk isin. Hau sei harii Hau nia povu iha fatuk nee nia leten, hanesan igreja ida nebee hamriik metin, too mate mos la bele manaan sira.
Hau sei foo xavi reinu lalehan nian ba o. Saida mak o bandu iha mundu nee, Maromak iha lalehan mos bandu. I saida mak o foo lisensa atu halo iha mundu nee, Maromak iha lalehan mos foo lisensa.”<a href='#note-237' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-238' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus bandu Nia eskolante sira atu la bele hatete sai ba see-see deit katak Nia mak Kristu.
Komesa hosi loron nee, Jesus hatete sai ba Nia eskolante sira katak, Nia tenki baa iha Jerusalém i tenki simu terus oi-oin. Nai ulun Judeu sira, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira sei halo terus Nia. Ema sei oho tiha Nia, maibee too iha loron tolu, Maromak sei halo Nia moris fila fali.
Rona nunee, Pedro dada Jesus ba sorin hodi siak Nia dehan, “Lae, Nai! Maromak sei la foo lisensa atu buat nee akontese.”
Maibee Jesus fila ba Pedro hodi siak fali nia dehan, “Satanás, sees tiha hosi Hau nia oin! O atu taka dalan mai Hau! O nia hanoin nee laos mai hosi Maromak, maibee mai hosi ema nia hanoin.”
Depois Jesus dehan ba Nia eskolante sira, “See mak hakarak tuir Hau, nia tenki husik tiha nia hakarak rasik, i tenki prontu simu terus, hanesan ema nebee lor-loron lori nia krus too mate. I nia tenki tuir Hau nafatin.<a href='#note-239' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba see mak hakarak salva nia aan, nia sei lakon fali. I see mak lakon nia moris tanba nia tuir Hau, nia sei hetan moris rohan-laek.<a href='#note-240' class='key'>✡</a>
Se ema ida hetan rikusoin mundu nian hotu-hotu, maibee too ikus la hetan moris rohan-laek karik, nia manaan saida loos? La iha buat ida mak nia bele foo hodi troka nia klamar.
Tanba aban-bainrua Hau, Mane Maksoin sei fila fali mai hosi lalehan ho Hau nia Aman nia kbiit tomak, i Nia anju sira haleu Hau. Iha tempu nee mak Hau sei foo justisa ba ema ida-idak tuir saida mak nia halo.<a href='#note-241' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, hosi imi sira nee, balu sei moris too haree Hau, Mane Maksoin mai ukun nudar Liurai, mak foin sira mate.”
Liu tiha loron neen, Jesus lori Pedro, Tiago ho Tiago nia alin João, sira mes-mesak baa sae foho aas ida.
Too iha nebaa Nia eskolante nain tolu nee haree Jesus nakfilak tiha. Nia oin nabilan hanesan loromatan, i Nia hena sai mutin nabilan.
Derepenti sira mos haree profeta Moisés ho Elias koalia hela ho Jesus.
Depois Pedro dehan ba Jesus, “Nai, ita hamutuk iha nee, furak teb-tebes. Se Nai hakarak, hau halo tenda tolu iha nee, ida ba Ita Boot, ida ba Moisés, ho ida tan ba Elias.”
Pedro sei koalia hela nunee, derepenti kalohan nabilan ida mai falun tiha sira. I lian ida sai hosi kalohan nee dehan, “Ida nee Hau nia Oan doben. Nia halo Hau nia laran haksolok teb-tebes. Imi tenki rona Nia!”<a href='#note-242' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona lian nee, sira nain tolu tauk teb-tebes, i sira taka rabat iha rai.
Maibee Jesus mai kaer sira hodi dehan, “Hamriik ona! Keta tauk.”
Bainhira sira hateke sae, sira la haree tan ema seluk, so Jesus deit.
Hotu tiha Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira tuun fali hosi foho. Sira lao tuun dadauk, Jesus bandu dehan, “Saida mak ohin imi haree nee, la bele hatete ba ema ida. Bainhira Maromak halo Hau, Mane Maksoin moris fali hosi mate mak foin imi bele foo sai ba ema.”
Depois Nia eskolante sira husu ba Jesus dehan, “Entaun nusaa mak mestri relijiaun sira dehan, Elias tenki mai uluk mak foin Kristu mai?”<a href='#note-243' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Loos duni, Elias mai atu prepara buat hotu-hotu.
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, Elias mai tiha ona, i ema la hatene nia, too halo aat nia tuir sira nia hakarak. Hau, Mane Maksoin mos sira sei halo terus hanesan nee.”<a href='#note-244' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, Nia eskolante sira foin kompriende katak Elias ida nebee Jesus konta nee mak João Sarani Nain.
Bainhira Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira fila fali ba iha ema barak nia leet, iha mane ida mai hakneak iha Jesus nia oin
hodi dehan, “Nai, hanoin hau nia oan ba! Nia moras bibi maten, i terus liu. Dala barak nia monu tama ba ahi laran ka bee laran.
Hau lori ona nia ba Ita Boot nia eskolante sira, maibee sira la bele kura nia.”
Depois Jesus foo orden ba diabu. Diabu mos sai hosi labarik nee, i labarik nee diak kedas.
Bainhira Jesus mesak fali, Nia eskolante sira mai besik hodi husu, “Nusaa mak ami ohin la bele duni sai diabu nee?”
Jesus hataan, “Tanba imi nia fiar fraku liu. Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, se imi nia fiar kiik-oan hanesan mostarda musan ida mos, imi bele foo orden ba foho ida dehan ‘Muda hosi nee, baa iha nebaa.’ I foho nee sei muda duni. Imi atu halo saida deit, bele.<a href='#note-245' class='key'>✡</a>
[Maibee atu duni sai diabu hanesan ida ohin nee, imi tenki halo orasaun i halo jejun.]”<a href='#note-246' class='key'>*</a>
Iha loron ida, Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira halibur hamutuk iha provinsia Galileia. Iha nebaa Jesus hatete ba sira, “Aban-bainrua, ema sei faan Hau, Mane Maksoin ba ema aat.
Sira sei oho Hau, maibee iha loron tolu Maromak sei halo Hau moris fali.” Rona nunee, Nia eskolante sira tristi loos.
Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira too iha sidade Kafarnaum. Iha nebaa kobrador impostu balu mai husu Simão Pedro dehan, “O nia mestri baibain selu impostu ba iha uma kreda boot ka lae?”<a href='#note-247' class='key'>✡</a>
Pedro hataan, “Nia selu.”
Bainhira Pedro tama ba uma laran, Jesus husu kedas nia dehan, “Simão, hanoin took. Liurai sira iha mundu nee husu impostu hosi see? Hosi sira nia oan rasik ka hosi ema seluk?”
Pedro hataan, “Hosi ema seluk.”
Jesus dehan, “Se nunee, liurai nia oan rasik la selu ida.
Maibee atu sira la bele laran moras ba ita tanba deit ita la selu impostu nee, o baa kail ikan iha tasi. Ikan primeiru nebee o hetan, loke tiha nia ibun, foin foti osan mutin ida iha ikan nee nia ibun laran. Osan nee too atu selu ita nain rua nia impostu.”
Iha tempu nebaa, Jesus nia eskolante sira mai husu Nia dehan, “Ema nebee mak boot liu iha Maromak nia reinu?”<a href='#note-248' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun Jesus bolu labarik ida mai hamriik iha sira nia klaran,
i Nia dehan ba sira, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, see mak atu sai Maromak nia reinu, nia tenki muda nia moris hodi sai hanesan labarik kiik ida. Se lae, la bele.<a href='#note-249' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee see mak haraik aan nudar labarik nee, nia mak boot liu iha Maromak nia reinu.
See mak simu labarik ida hanesan nee hodi Hau nia naran, nia simu Hau.
Maibee see mak halo labarik kiik ida monu ba sala too nia la fiar mai Hau, nia sei simu kastigu todan. Se kompara ho ema kesi fatuk boot ida iha nia kakorok hodi soe nia tama ba tasi laran, Maromak nia kastigu sei todan liu fali ida nee.
Koitadu, mundu nee sei terus tanba iha buat barak mak halo ema monu ba sala. Loos duni, buat hanesan nee sempre iha. Maibee see mak lori ema seluk atu monu ba sala, nia sei terus.
Se o nia liman ka o nia ain halo o monu ba sala karik, tesi i soe tiha. Diak liu o tama iha lalehan ho liman ka ain sorin deit duke o tama ba iha infernu ho liman-ain kompletu.<a href='#note-250' class='key'>✡</a>
Se o nia matan halo o monu ba sala karik, sukit sai tiha o nia matan nee i soe tiha. Diak liu o tama ba iha lalehan ho matan sorin deit duke o tama ba iha infernu ho matan kompletu.”<a href='#note-251' class='key'>✡</a>
“Kuidadu, keta hanoin dehan ema kiik sira nee la iha folin, atu hatuun ema kiik ida mos la bele. Hau hatete ba imi, anju sira iha lalehan nebee mak tau matan ba sira sempre hamriik iha Hau nia Aman iha lalehan nia oin hodi husu atu tulun ema kiik sira nee.
[Hau, Mane Maksoin mai atu salva ema nebee mak lao sala dalan.]<a href='#note-252' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nia hanoin oinsaa? Se ema ida iha bibi atus ida, depois bibi ida lao sala dalan, bibi nain sei halo saida? Nia sei husik hela bibi sia-nulu resin sia iha foho, i baa buka tuir bibi ida nebee lao sala dalan nee.
Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, kuandu nia hetan ona bibi nee, nia kontenti liu ho bibi ida nee duke bibi sia-nulu resin sia seluk nebee nunka lao sala dalan.<a href='#note-253' class='key'>*</a>
Nunee mos imi nia Aman iha lalehan, Nia lakohi atu ema ida lakon, atu ema kiik ida lakon mos Nia lakohi.”
Jesus hatutan tan dehan, “Se o nia maluk ida halo sala hasoru o, baa koalia ho nia hodi foo hatene nia sala, maibee imi nain rua deit, la bele iha ema nia oin. Se nia simu o nia liafuan, entaun o diak malu fali ho nia.<a href='#note-254' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee se nia lakohi rona o, entaun lori ema ida-rua baa koalia tan ho nia, atu sira sai sasin ba buat nebee imi koalia. Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan, ‘Tenki iha sasin nain rua ka tolu mak foin bele tesi lia.’<a href='#note-255' class='key'>✡</a>
Se nia lakohi rona imi, baa foo hatene Maromak nia povu. Se Maromak nia povu mos nia lakohi rona, lalika liga nia, konsidera nia hanesan kobrador impostu ida ka ema ida nebee mak la konhese Maromak.
Iha tan buat ida mak Hau hakarak hatete: Hosi imi sira nee, se iha nain rua mak lian ida iha mundu nee hodi husu buat ruma ba Hau nia Aman iha lalehan, entaun Nia sei foo saida mak imi husu.
Tanba se iha ema nain rua ka tolu halibur hamutuk hodi Hau nia naran, Hau mos iha sira nia klaran.”
Depois Pedro mai husu Jesus, “Nai, se hau nia maluk halo sala fila-fila hasoru hau karik, hau tenki perdua nia dala hira? Too dala hitu ka?”
Jesus hataan, “Lae, laos dala hitu deit! Maibee o tenki perdua nia fila-fila too hitu-nulu dala hitu.<a href='#note-258' class='key'>‡</a> <a href='#note-259' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba Maromak ukun nudar Liurai hanesan komparasaun nee: Iha loron ida, liurai ida hakarak sura tuir nia osan nebee mak nia funsionariu sira deve.
Bainhira nia hahuu sura, iha ema balu lori nia funsionariu ida mai. Funsionariu nee deve osan mean bornal rihun sanulu.
Maibee funsionariu nee la iha kbiit atu selu. Entaun liurai foo orden ba nia soldadu sira atu baa faan tiha ema nee, nia feen ho oan sira ho mos nia rikusoin hotu.
Rona nunee, funsionariu nee hakneak hakruuk too rai iha liurai nia ain hodi husu dehan, ‘Favor ida, foo tempu mai hau! Hau sei selu hotu hau nia tusan nee.’
Liurai hanoin loos nia, too hamoos tiha nia tusan hotu hodi husik nia baa ho livre.
Bainhira funsionariu nee sai mai, nia hetan nia maluk funsionariu ida nebee mak deve nia osan mutin atus ida deit. Nia baa kaer ema nee i buti nia kakorok hodi sisi dehan, ‘O tenki selu hotu o nia tusan nee!’
Rona nunee, nia maluk funsionariu nee hakneak hakruuk too rai hodi husu dehan, ‘Favor ida, foo tempu mai hau! Hau sei selu hau nia tusan nee.’
Maibee funsionariu nee la simu, nia sulan nia maluk nee ba iha komarka too selu hotu nia tusan.
Bainhira liurai nia funsionariu sira seluk haree, sira nia laran susar teb-tebes i sira baa kesar iha liurai.
Depois liurai bolu funsionariu nee hodi dehan, ‘Funsionariu laran aat! O nia tusan hau hamoos hotu tiha ona tanba o hakneak hodi husu mai hau.
Hau hatudu tiha ona laran luak ba o. Nusaa mak o la hatudu laran luak ba o nia maluk nee?’
Liurai nee hirus teb-tebes too haruka ema baa lori funsionariu aat nee kastigu iha komarka laran too selu hotu nia tusan.”
Jesus taka Nia istoria dehan, “Hau nia Aman iha lalehan mos sei halo nunee ba imi ida-idak, se imi la perdua imi nia maluk ho laran tomak.”
Jesus hanorin hotu tiha, Nia lao sai hosi Galileia hodi baa iha provinsia Judeia iha mota Jordaun nia sorin ba.
Ema barak teb-tebes tuir Nia, i Nia kura sira nia moras.
Depois ema balu hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu mai koko atu hamonu Nia. Sira husu dehan, “Tuir Moisés nia lei, laen soe nia feen ho razaun saida deit, bele ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “Imi la lee iha Livru Sagradu kona ba Maromak halo ema ka? Iha nebaa hakerek dehan, ‘Nia halo sira mane ho feto.’<a href='#note-260' class='key'>✡</a>
I hakerek tan dehan,
‘Tanba nee, mane sei husik nia inan-aman
hodi baa moris neon ida laran ida ho nia feen,
i sira nain rua sai ida.’<a href='#note-261' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun sira laos ona ema nain rua, maibee sai ona ida. Nee duni se Maromak tau feto ho mane hamutuk sai feen-laen ona, ema keta fahe fali.”
Depois ema Farizeu sira nee husu fali ba Jesus, “Se nunee, nusaa mak Moisés dehan, laen bele soe nia feen, naran katak nia foo surat deklarasaun soe malu nian?”<a href='#note-262' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Moisés nia lei foo lisensa atu imi soe imi nia feen tanba imi nia ulun toos. Maibee fo-foun Maromak halo lalehan ho rai laos nunee.
Hau hatete ba imi, mane so bele soe nia feen kuandu nia feen halo ona sala seksual ho ema seluk. Se nia feen la halo sala nee, maibee mane nee soe nia hodi hola fali feto seluk, mane nee halo sala seksual.”<a href='#note-263' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hataan, “Laos ema hotu-hotu mak bele simu liafuan nee. So ema nebee Maromak foo kbiit ba sira mak bele simu.
Iha ema balu la kaben tanba moris mai sira la bele duni. Iha ema balu la kaben tanba ema seluk mak halo sira nunee. Iha mos ema balu la kaben tanba sira hakarak foo aan tomak atu serbi Maromak nudar Liurai. See mak bele simu liafuan nee, simu ba.”
Depois ema balu mai lori labarik ba Jesus atu Nia tau liman ba sira hodi husu Maromak foo bensaun ba sira. Maibee Jesus nia eskolante sira bandu.
Entaun Jesus siak Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Husik labarik sira nee mai iha Hau, la bele bandu. Tanba ema hanesan labarik sira nee mak sai Maromak nia reinu.”
Nia tau liman ba labarik sira nee, depois Nia sai hosi nebaa.
Iha loron ida, iha mane joven ida mai husu Jesus dehan, “Mestri, hau tenki halo buat diak saida para hau bele hetan moris rohan-laek?”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Nusaa mak ita husu mai Hau kona ba saida mak diak? So Maromak deit mak diak. Se ita hakarak hetan moris rohan-laek, halo tuir Nia ukun fuan.”
Joven nee husu fali, “Ukun fuan nebee?”
Jesus hataan, “La bele oho ema, la bele halo sala ho ema nia kaben, la bele naok, la bele foo sasin falsu,<a href='#note-264' class='key'>✡</a>
respeita o nia inan-aman, i hadomi ema seluk hanesan o hadomi o nia aan rasik.”<a href='#note-265' class='key'>✡</a>
Joven nee hataan dehan, “Ukun fuan sira nee hau halo tuir hotu ona. Saida mak sei falta?”
Jesus hataan, “Se ita hakarak moris kompletu, entaun baa faan tiha ita nia rikusoin hotu, i osan nee fahe ba ema kiak. Nunee mak ita sei hetan fali rikusoin iha lalehan. Fahe hotu tiha, mai tuir Hau.”
Bainhira joven nee rona nunee, nia fila ho laran susar tanba nia riku teb-tebes.
Depois Jesus dehan ba Nia eskolante sira, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, susar teb-tebes ema riku ida atu sai Maromak nia reinu.
Dala ida tan Hau dehan ba imi, kuda kamelu tama liu hosi daun kuak susar teb-tebes. Maibee susar liu tan, ema riku ida atu sai Maromak nia reinu hodi hakruuk ba Nia nudar Liurai.”
Bainhira Jesus nia eskolante sira rona nunee, sira admira teb-tebes hodi husu, “Se nunee, see loos mak sei hetan salvasaun?”
Jesus hateke ba sira hodi dehan, “Ba ema, la bele duni. Maibee ba Maromak, buat hotu-hotu bele.”
Depois Pedro dehan, “Ami husik tiha ona buat hotu-hotu hodi tuir Ita Boot. Entaun ami sei hetan saida?”
Jesus hatete ba sira, “Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, iha mundu foun, Hau, Mane Maksoin sei tuur iha kadeira ukun, i naroman lalehan nian haleu hela Hau. Imi sira nebee agora tuir Hau, imi mos sei tuur iha kadeira ukun sanulu resin rua hodi ukun suku sanulu resin rua iha Israel.<a href='#note-266' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak husik ona nia uma, nia maun-alin, nia inan-aman, nia oan sira ka nia rai tanba nia tuir Hau, ema nee sei simu fali dala atus ida i sei hetan moris rohan-laek.
Maibee ema barak nebee agora boot sei sai kiik. I ema barak nebee agora kiik sei sai boot.”<a href='#note-267' class='key'>✡</a>
Livru nee koalia kona ba Jesus Kristu. Jesus hosi liurai David nia jerasaun, i David nee Abraão nia jerasaun.
Jesus nia bei-ala sira nia naran komesa hosi Abraão too liurai David hanesan tuir mai nee:
Abraão nia oan Isac.
Isac nia oan Jacó.
Jacó nia oan Judá ho ninia maun-alin sira.
Judá nia oan Perez ho Zera, sira nia inan naran Tamar.
Perez nia oan Hesron.
Hesron nia oan Ram.
Aminadab nia oan Nahason.
Nahason nia oan Salmon.
Salmon nia oan Boaz, nia inan naran Rahab.
Boaz nia oan Obed, nia inan naran Rute.
Obed nia oan Jessé.
Jessé nia oan liurai David.
Jesus nia bei-ala sira hosi liurai David too nia jerasaun nebee mak militar lori baa dadur iha rai Babilónia, sira nia naran mak tuir mai nee:
David nia oan Salomão, nia inan nee uluk Urias nia feen.
Salomão nia oan Roboão.
Roboão nia oan Abias.
Abias nia oan Aza.
Aza nia oan Josafat.
Josafat nia oan Jorão.
Jorão nia oan Uzias.
Uzias nia oan Jotam.
Jotam nia oan Ahaz.
Ahaz nia oan Ezequias.
Ezequias nia oan Manassés.
Manassés nia oan Amon.
Amon nia oan Jozias.
Jozias nia oan mak Jekonias ho nia alin sira. Iha sira nia tempu mak militar lori povu Israel baa dadur iha Babilónia.<a href='#note-92' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus nia bei-ala sira hosi tempu dadur nee ba oin mak tuir mai nee:
Jekonias nia oan Salatiel.
Salatiel nia oan Zorobabel.
Zorobabel nia oan Abiud.
Abiud nia oan Eliakim.
Eliakim nia oan Azur.
Azur nia oan Zadok.
Zadok nia oan Jakim.
Eliud nia oan Eleazar.
Eleazar nia oan Matan.
Matan nia oan Jacó.
Jacó nia oan José.
José kaben ho Maria, i Maria mak kous Jesus. Jesus nee, ema mos bolu Nia Kristu, nee dehan katak, Salvador nebee Maromak promete hori uluk ona atu haruka mai.
Nunee, komesa hosi Abraão too David hamutuk jerasaun 14. Hosi David too militar lori povu Israel baa dadur iha Babilónia mos jerasaun 14. I hosi jerasaun nebee dadur iha Babilónia too Jesus Kristu hamutuk jerasaun 14 tan.
Istoria kona ba Jesus Kristu nia moris hanesan nee:
Nia inan Maria troka prenda ona ho José. Maibee bainhira sira nain rua seidauk moris hamutuk nudar feen ho laen, Maria hatene ona katak nia isin rua liu hosi Espiritu Santu nia kbiit.<a href='#note-93' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira José hatene katak Maria isin rua ona, nia hakarak atu hakotu sira nain rua nia relasaun. Maibee José lakohi halo moe Maria iha ema barak nia oin, tanba nia ema ida nebee laran moos. Nunee nia desidi atu hakotu nonook deit.
Maibee bainhira José hanoin hela buat nee, Nai Maromak nia anju ida mai hatudu aan ba nia liu hosi mehi hodi dehan, “José, liurai David nia jerasaun, la bele tauk atu kaben ho Maria, tanba labarik nebee mak iha Maria nia kabu-laran nee mai hosi Espiritu Santu.
Maria sei tuur ahi oan mane ida. O tenki foo naran Jesus, tanba Nia mak sei salva Nia povu hosi sira nia sala.”<a href='#note-94' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-95' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat hirak nee hotu sai nunee tuir saida mak Nai Maromak nia profeta hori uluk kedas hakerek ona dehan,
“Aban-bainrua iha feto raan ida sei isin rua hodi tuur ahi oan mane ida. Labarik nee nia naran Emanuel.” Nee dehan katak “Maromak hamutuk ho ita.”<a href='#note-96' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira José hadeer, nia halo tuir saida mak anju nee hatete ba nia. Nia kaben ho Maria.
Maibee nia la halo relasaun ho Maria hanesan feen-laen too Maria tuur ahi. I José foo naran ba labarik nee, Jesus.<a href='#note-97' class='key'>✡</a>
“Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, nee hanesan komparasaun tuir mai: Iha toos nain ida, dadeer-saan deit nia baa iha merkadu hodi buka ema atu servisu iha nia toos uvas nian.
Hetan tiha ema, nia konkorda malu ho sira atu selu loron ida osan mutin ida, i nia haruka sira baa servisu kedas iha nia toos.
Tuku sia dadeer, toos nain baa fali merkadu, nia haree tan ema balu hamriik hela, la halo buat ida.
Nia hatete ba sira, ‘Imi baa servisu iha hau nia toos, hau sei selu imi ho lo-loos.’
I sira mos baa.
Tuku sanulu resin rua, toos nain sai baa bolu tan ema seluk. Nunee mos tuku tolu lokraik.
Tuku lima mos, nia baa merkadu, hetan ema seluk tan nebee hamriik hela deit. Nia husu sira, ‘Nusaa mak loron tomak imi hamriik iha nee deit, la halo buat ida?’
Sira hataan, ‘La iha ema ida mak foo servisu mai ami.’
Toos nain dehan, ‘Se nunee, imi baa servisu iha hau nia toos deit.’
Rai besik kalan ona, nia hatete ba mandor dehan, ‘Baa bolu ema sira nebee mak servisu iha toos hodi selu sira ida-ida. Maibee selu uluk ema sira nebee mak tama ikus. Sira nebee mak tama uluk, selu ikus.’<a href='#note-268' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mandor bolu uluk ema nebee mak mai servisu iha tuku lima lokraik, i sira ida-ida simu osan mutin ida.
Entaun ema sira nebee mak mai servisu hosi dadeer-saan hanoin katak sira atu simu barak liu fali. Afinal sira mos simu osan mutin ida.
Bainhira sira simu hotu sira nia osan, ema nebee mak tama servisu hosi dadeer nee mai murmura ba toos nain
dehan, ‘Sira nebee mai ikus servisu oras ida deit. Nusaa mak sira simu osan hanesan fali ho ami? Ami nee servisu mate aan hosi dadeer too lokraik, loron manas mos ami servisu nafatin.’
Foti o nia osan nee hodi fila ona. Hau hakarak atu ema nebee tama servisu ikus mos simu osan hanesan ho imi.
Nee hau nia osan. Hau iha direitu atu uza tuir hau nia hakarak. Keta halo be o laran moras ba hau tanba hau halo buat diak ba ema seluk.’ ”
Jesus taka Nia liafuan dehan, “Nunee mos ema nebee mak ikus aban-bainrua sai fali primeiru. I ema nebee mak primeiru sai fali ikus.”<a href='#note-269' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus lao dadaun ba sidade Jerusalém, Nia halibur Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua hamutuk hodi koalia ba sira deit dehan,
“Rona mai, ita lao dadaun ba Jerusalém. Too iha nebaa, ema sei entrega Hau, Mane Maksoin ba iha nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira. Ema sira nee sei tesi Hau nia lia katak Hau tenki hetan kastigu mate.
Sira sei entrega Hau ba iha ema nebee la konhese Maromak. I ema sira nee sei tarata Hau, baku Hau ho sikoti, i prega Hau iha krus. Maibee iha loron tolu Maromak sei halo Hau moris fali hosi mate.”
Depois Zebedeu nia feen mai hamutuk ho nia oan Tiago ho João. Senhora nee mai hakneak iha Jesus nia oin hodi husu atu Jesus foo buat ruma ba nia.
Jesus husu, “Senhora hakarak saida?”
Senhora nee hataan, “Hau husu atu aban-bainrua kuandu Ita Boot ukun nudar Liurai, hau nia oan nain rua nee, ida tuur iha Ita Boot nia sorin loos, ida seluk tuur iha Ita Boot nia sorin karuk.”
Maibee Jesus hatete ba Tiago ho João dehan, “Imi la kompriende saida mak imi husu. La kleur Hau sei simu terus todan. Imi mos prontu simu terus nee ka lae?”
Sira hataan, “Ami prontu.”
Jesus hatete ba sira, “Loos duni, imi sei simu duni terus hanesan Hau. Maibee Hau la iha direitu atu hili see mak atu tuur iha Hau nia sorin loos ho sorin karuk. Kona ba ida nee Hau nia Aman iha lalehan desidi tiha ona.”
Bainhira eskolante nain sanulu rona buat nebee mak Tiago ho João husu, sira hirus maun-alin nain rua nee.
Entaun, Jesus bolu sira hamutuk hodi dehan, “Imi hatene katak, iha nasaun selu-seluk, nai ulun sira manda ema tuun-sae, i ukun nain sira hanehan sira nia povu.
Maibee imi la bele halo hanesan nee. Hosi imi sira nee, see mak hakarak sai boot, nia tenki haraik aan hodi serbi nia maluk sira seluk.<a href='#note-270' class='key'>✡</a>
I see mak hakarak sai ema boot liu, nia tenki serbi nia maluk sira seluk hanesan atan.<a href='#note-271' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia tenki hanesan Hau, Mane Maksoin. Hau mai iha mundu nee laos atu ema serbi Hau. Maibee Hau mai atu serbi ema seluk i foo Aan ba mate atu ema barak hetan liberdade.”
Depois Jesus ho nia eskolante sira sai hosi sidade Jerikó, i ema lubun boot mos tuir Nia.
Iha nebaa iha ema matan delek nain rua tuur hela iha dalan ninin. Bainhira sira rona katak Jesus mak liu, sira bolu ho lian makaas dehan, “Nai, liurai David nia Jerasaun, hadomi ami ba!”
Ema lubun boot nee siak sira nain rua i haruka sira nonook. Maibee sira nain rua bolu makaas liu tan dehan, “Nai, liurai David nia Jerasaun, hadomi ami ba!”
Rona nunee, Jesus mos para, i bolu sira mai hodi husu, “Imi hakarak Hau halo saida ba imi?”
Sira hataan, “Nai, ami hakarak haree.”
Rona nunee, Jesus hanoin sira nain rua. Nia tau liman ba sira nia matan, i sira haree kedas. Depois sira tuir Jesus.
Bainhira Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira besik ona sidade Jerusalém, sira too iha aldeia Betfagé iha foho Oliveira nia lolon, Nia haruka Nia eskolante nain rua baa uluk.
Nia dehan ba sira, “Imi baa iha aldeia nebaa. Bainhira imi tama, imi hetan kedas kuda buru inan ida kesi hela, nia oan iha hela nia sorin. Imi kore tiha dada mai.
Se iha ema ruma husu imi karik, foo hatene dehan, ‘Nai mak presiza.’ Ema nee sei haruka imi dada kedas kuda buru nee.”
Nee tuir saida mak Maromak koalia liu hosi Nia profeta hori uluk kedas dehan,
“Hatete ba Jerusalém oan sira nunee:<a href='#note-272' class='key'>*</a>
‘Haree ba, imi nia Liurai mai iha imi.
sae deit kuda buru oan.’ ”<a href='#note-273' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois eskolante nain rua nee baa halo tuir saida mak Jesus haruka.
Sira dada kuda buru inan nee ho nia oan lori ba Jesus. Too iha nebaa sira hasai sira nia hena tau ba iha kuda nia kotuk, depois Jesus sae.
Ema barak hasai sira nia hena hodi nahe tu-tuir dalan. Iha mos ema balu taa ramus latan tuir dalan.
Ema balu lao uluk iha Jesus nia oin, iha balu lao hosi kotuk. Sira hotu haklalak hahii Maromak dehan,
“Hosana, liurai David nia Jerasaun!
Maromak foo bensaun ba Ida nebee mak mai lori Nai Maromak nia naran.
Hosana,
hahii Nia iha fatin aas liu!”<a href='#note-274' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira Jesus tama iha Jerusalém, ema hotu iha sidade nee hakfodak hodi husu malu tuun-sae dehan, “Ema nee see loos?”
Ema barak nebee mak lao hamutuk ho Jesus nee hataan dehan, “Nia nee Jesus, Maromak nia Profeta hosi Nazaré iha provinsia Galileia.”
Depois Jesus tama iha area uma kreda boot nian, Nia duni sai ema sira nebee mak halo kontratu iha fatin nee. Nia halo baku fila tiha meza nebee mak ema uza hodi troka osan, i banku nebee mak ema tuur hodi faan manu pombu mos Nia halo baku fila hotu.
Nia siak sira dehan, “Iha Maromak nia liafuan hakerek tiha ona dehan, ‘Tuir lo-loos Hau nia uma nee fatin para halo orasaun.’ Maibee imi halo fali hanesan ema naok-teen sira nia subar fatin.”<a href='#note-275' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha, ema matan delek ho ema ain aat sira mai hasoru Jesus iha area uma kreda boot nee, i Nia kura sira hotu.
Bainhira nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira haree milagre nebee mak Jesus halo, sira hirus. Sira mos hirus tanba labarik sira haklalak dehan, “Hosana, liurai David nia Jerasaun!”
Nunee sira hasee Jesus dehan, “Labarik sira haklalak saida ba O nee?! O la rona ka?”
Jesus hataan, “Hau rona. Maibee iha Livru Sagradu dehan, ‘Maromak, Ita Boot hanorin labarik sira ho kiik-oan sira nebee sei susu hela atu hahii Ita Boot.’ Liafuan nee imi la lee ka?”<a href='#note-276' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus husik tiha sira hodi baa fali iha aldeia Betánia, i Nia hela iha nebaa kalan ida.
Aban dadeer-saan fali, Jesus fila ba iha Jerusalém. Iha dalan Nia hamlaha.
Nia haree ai figeira huun ida iha dalan ninin, i Nia baa besik ai huun nee hodi buka nia fuan. Maibee la iha, tahan deit mak iha. Haree nunee, Jesus hatete ba ai huun nee dehan, “O sei la foo fuan tan!” Deperenti ai nee namlaik tiha.
Bainhira Jesus nia eskolante sira haree, sira admira hodi husu dehan, “Nusaa mak ai huun nee namlaik tiha derepenti hanesan nee?”
Jesus hataan, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, se imi nia fiar la nakdoko maibee metin nafatin, imi mos bele halo saida mak Hau halo tiha ona ba ai figeira huun nee. Laos ida nee deit, maibee imi mos bele haruka foho nee muda ba iha tasi laran, i sei muda duni.<a href='#note-277' class='key'>✡</a>
Saida deit mak imi husu liu hosi orasaun, imi sei hetan, naran katak imi fiar.”
Jesus tama iha area uma kreda boot hodi hanorin iha nebaa. Nia sei hanorin hela, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira mai husu dehan, “O iha direitu saida para halo buat sira nee? See mak foo direitu nee ba O?”
Jesus hataan, “Hau mos atu husu buat ida. Se imi hataan ho lo-loos mak Hau foo hatene imi, see mak foo direitu mai Hau hodi halo buat sira nee.
Hau nia pergunta mak nee: See mak foo direitu ba João Sarani Nain hodi foo sarani ema? Maromak mak foo ka, ema mak foo?”
Sira diskuti malu dehan, “Ita susar ona. Se ita hataan, ‘Maromak mak foo direitu ba nia’, Jesus sei husu fali ita dehan, ‘Entaun, nusaa mak imi la fiar ba nia?’
Maibee se ita dehan, ‘Ema mak foo direitu’, entaun ita tauk povu, tanba povu sira hanoin dehan, João nee Maromak nia profeta.”
Entaun sira hataan dehan, “Ami la hatene.”
Depois Jesus hatete ba nai ulun relijiaun sira dehan, “Imi hanoin took komparasaun nebee Hau atu koalia nee. Iha senhor ida iha oan mane nain rua. Loron ida nia hatete ba nia oan mane boot dehan, ‘Oan, loron ida nee o baa servisu iha toos uvas nian.’
Nia oan mane boot hataan, ‘Hau lakohi.’ Maibee too ikus nia arepende i baa duni servisu iha toos.
Depois senhor nee haruka tan nia oan kiik atu baa servisu iha toos.
Nia oan mane kiik hataan, ‘Diak apaa, hau sei baa.’ Maibee too ikus nia la baa.”
Konta tiha hotu, Jesus husu ba sira dehan, “Tuir imi nia hanoin, oan ida nebee mak halo tuir nia aman nia hakarak?”
Sira hataan, ‘Oan mane boot.’
Jesus dehan ba sira, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, kobrador impostu ho feto luroon sira sei tama iha Maromak nia reinu uluk liu fali imi.
Tanba uluk João Sarani Nain mai hanorin imi oinsaa mak bele moris loos, i imi lakohi rona. Maibee kobrador impostu sira ho feto luroon sira rona hodi halo tuir. Imi haree hela sira hakribi sira nia sala, maibee imi rasik lakohi hakribi imi nia sala i la simu nafatin João nia liafuan.”<a href='#note-278' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatutan tan dehan, “Rona tan komparasaun ida nee. Iha toos nain ida kuda uvas iha nia toos ida tomak. Nia halo lutu haleu tiha toos nee, i halo tanki ida atu sama uvas. Nia mos harii fatin aas ida ba seguransa sira atu hein toos nee. Hotu tiha, nia foo ba ema aluga, depois nia baa hela iha rai liur.<a href='#note-279' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira uvas besik tasak ona, toos nain haruka nia atan balu fila baa hodi simu uvas nebee mak ema aluga toos nee tenki foo ba nia.
Maibee ema aluga toos nee kaer tiha atan sira nee. Ida sira baku, ida sira tuda ho fatuk, ida seluk sira oho.
Depois toos nain haruka nia atan barak liu tan. Maibee ema aluga toos nee halo aat nafatin.
Too ikus toos nain haruka nia oan rasik mak baa, tanba nia hanoin dehan, ‘Sira sei respeita hau nia oan.’
Maibee bainhira ema aluga toos nee haree toos nain nia oan, sira dehan ba malu, ‘Nia mak sei hetan nia aman nia rikusoin tomak. Diak liu ita oho tiha nia, atu toos nee sai ita nian fali.’
Nunee sira kaer nia, rasta nia sai hosi toos laran, i oho tiha nia.”
Konta hotu tiha, Jesus husu ba nai ulun relijiaun sira dehan, “Tuir imi nia hanoin, bainhira toos nain nee fila fali mai, nia sei halo saida ba ema sira nebee aluga toos nee?”
Sira hataan dehan, “Nia sei kastigu mate tiha ema aat sira nee. I nia sei foo fali toos ba ema diak mak aluga, atu nunee too tempu kuu uvas, sira prontu foo toos nain nia parte.”
Depois Jesus hatete ba sira, “Iha Livru Sagradu kompara Kristu hanesan fatuk ida. Imi nunka lee ka? Iha nebaa dehan,
‘Iha fatuk ida nebee badaen fatuk sira lakohi uza,
maibee agora fatuk nee mak sai fali fatuk nebee prinsipal.
Nai Maromak rasik mak hili fatuk nee,
ita haree ba furak teb-tebes.’ ”<a href='#note-280' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-281' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus foo atensaun ba sira dehan, “Imi la simu Fatuk nee. Nee duni Hau dehan ba imi, Maromak sei hasai imi sira nee hosi Nia reinu. Nia sei hili fali povu seluk, i sira sei moris tuir Nia hakarak.
[Ema nebee monu kona Fatuk nee, nia sei nakfera. I se Fatuk nee mak monu kona ema ruma, ema nee sei rahun.]”<a href='#note-282' class='key'>‡</a>
Bainhira nai lulik nia ulun sira ho ema Farizeu sira rona komparasaun hirak nee, sira hatene katak Jesus soe lia ba sira.
Entaun sira buka dalan atu kaer Jesus, maibee sira tauk ema lubun boot nee, tanba povu fiar katak Jesus nee profeta ida.
Depois Jesus koalia tan ho sira uza komparasaun dehan,
“Maromak ukun ema nudar Liurai, hanesan istoria tuir mai nee: Iha liurai ida halo preparasaun ba nia oan mane nia festa kazamentu.
Bainhira buat hotu besik prontu ona, liurai haruka nia atan sira baa foo hatene fali ema nebee mak nia konvida tiha ona hodi bolu sira mai ona. Maibee konvidadu sira hotu lakohi baa festa nee.
Atan sira mos baa, maibee konvidadu sira nee la interese nafatin. Sira balu baa fali sira nia toos, balu baa sira nia servisu fatin.
Konvidadu sira seluk kaer tiha atan sira nee hodi halo terus sira i oho sira.
Rona nunee, liurai hirus teb-tebes i haruka nia soldadu sira baa oho tiha ema oho door sira nee i sunu mutuk sira nia sidade.
Depois liurai hatete ba nia atan sira dehan, ‘Festa kazamentu prontu ona, maibee ema nebee mak hau konvida la serve atu tuir festa nee.
Agora imi baa iha estrada boot iha sidade laran. See-see deit mak imi hetan iha nebaa, bolu sira mai deit.’
Nunee atan sira baa iha estrada bo-boot. See-see deit mak sira hetan, atu ema diak ka ema aat, sira halibur hotu, too halo nakonu fatin kazamentu nee.
Depois liurai tama iha fatin kazamentu atu hasoru bainaka sira. Iha nebaa nia haree ema ida la hatais ropa festa nian.<a href='#note-283' class='key'>*</a>
Entaun nia husu, ‘Belun, o la hatais ropa festa nian, oinsaa mak o bele tama mai?’ Maibee ema nee la hataan buat ida.
Nunee liurai hatete ba nia atan sira dehan, ‘Futu ema nee nia liman-ain i soe sai ba iha fatin nakukun. Iha nebaa ema sei tanis hakilar i ruun nehan.’ ”<a href='#note-284' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus taka komparasaun nee dehan, “Nunee mos Maromak konvida ema barak, maibee uitoan deit mak Nia hili atu sai Nia reinu.”
Depois ema Farizeu sira sai hosi nebaa hodi kombina malu atu hamonu Jesus liu hosi pergunta oi-oin.
Nunee sira haruka ema balu baa atu koko Jesus. Ema sira nee mak Farizeu nia eskolante ho partidu Herodes nia membru. Sira finji husu ba Jesus dehan, “Mestri, ami hatene katak Ita Boot ema nebee mak moris loos i sempre hanorin Maromak nia dalan ho lo-loos. Ita Boot la preokupa ema seluk nia hanoin, tanba Ita Boot la fihir ema.
Ita Boot nia hanoin oinsaa? Tuir ita nia lei relijiaun, ita selu impostu ba estadu Roma nia liurai boot César nee, loos ka la loos?”
Maibee Jesus hatene sira nia hanoin aat, i Nia dehan ba sira, “Imi nee laran makerek! Nusaa mak imi hakarak hamonu Hau?
Hatudu took mai Hau osan nebee mak uza hodi selu impostu.” Depois sira lori osan mutin ida foo ba Nia.
Jesus husu ba sira, “See nia oin mak iha osan nee? I see nia naran?”
Sira hataan, “Liurai boot César nian.”
Jesus hatete ba sira, “Se nunee, foo ba estadu buat nebee mak estadu nian, i foo ba Maromak buat nebee mak Maromak nian.”
Bainhira sira rona Jesus nia liafuan nee, sira hotu admira, i sira husik hela Jesus iha nebaa hodi baa fali fatin seluk.
Iha loron nee ema hosi grupu relijiaun Saduseu mos mai koko Jesus. Ema Saduseu sira hanorin dehan, ema mate sei la moris fali. Entaun sira husu ba Jesus,<a href='#note-285' class='key'>✡</a>
“Mestri, Moisés dehan, se mane ida mate, maibee la iha oan, mane nia alin tenki kaben fali feto faluk nee para bele foo jerasaun ba nia maun.<a href='#note-286' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun, hanesan nee: uluk iha ami nia rain iha maun-alin nain hitu. Maun boot kaben, depois nia mate, la iha oan. Entaun alin ida tuir nia nee kaben fali ho feto faluk nee.
Nia mos mate, la iha oan. Nunee beibeik too alin ikun mos kaben ho feto faluk nee, depois mate, la iha oan.
Too ikus feto faluk nee mos mate.
Agora ami husu nunee: feto nee kaben ho mane nain hitu. Aban-bainrua kuandu Maromak halo moris fali ema mate, feto nee nia kaben mak ida nebee loos?”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Imi nia hanoin nee la loos tanba imi la hatene saida mak hakerek iha Livru Sagradu, i la kompriende Maromak nia kbiit.
Bainhira ema mate moris fila fali, sira la kaben tan ona. Maibee sira hanesan anju sira iha lalehan.
Kona ba ema mate moris fali, Maromak koalia ona ba imi iha Livru Sagradu. Imi lee tiha ona ka lae? Maromak dehan,
‘Hau mak o nia bei-ala Abrãao nia Maromak, Isác nia Maromak ho Jacó nia Maromak, sira hotu adora nafatin Hau too agora.’ Nee hatudu katak ema mate sei moris fali. Tanba so ema moris deit mak bele adora Maromak, ema mate lae.”<a href='#note-287' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema Farizeu sira rona katak Jesus halo ema Saduseu sira la brani atu koalia tan. Nunee Farizeu sira halibur malu atu koko tan Jesus.
Entaun mestri relijiaun ida hosi sira mai husu Jesus,
“Mestri, iha Moisés nia lei, ukun fuan ida nebee mak importante liu?”
Jesus hataan, “O tenki hadomi Maromak, o nia Nai, ho o nia aan tomak, ho laran tomak, ho neon tomak.’<a href='#note-288' class='key'>✡</a>
Ida nee mak ukun fuan nebee boot liu i importante liu.
Iha tan ukun fuan ida nebee atu hanesan: ‘O tenki hadomi ema seluk hanesan o hadomi o nia aan rasik.’<a href='#note-289' class='key'>✡</a>
Moisés nia lei tomak ho profeta sira nia liafuan hotu nia huun mak ukun fuan rua nee.”<a href='#note-290' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira ema Farizeu sira sei halibur malu iha nebaa, Jesus husu ba sira dehan,
“Imi hanoin saida kona ba Kristu? Kristu nee see nia Jerasaun?”
Sira hataan, “Nia nee liurai David nia Jerasaun.”
Jesus husu tan dehan, “Se nunee, nusaa mak Maromak nia Espiritu foo hanoin ba liurai David atu bolu Kristu nee ‘Nai’? David hakerek dehan,
‘Nai Maromak hatete ona ba hau nia Nai, dehan,
“Mai tuur iha Hau nia sorin loos,
too Hau hamonu O nia inimigu sira iha O nia ain okos.’ ”<a href='#note-291' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha nee, liurai David rasik bolu Kristu nee nia Nai. Entaun oinsaa mak Kristu nee bele sai fali David nia Jerasaun?”<a href='#note-292' class='key'>†</a>
Sira hotu la bele hataan. Komesa iha loron nee la iha ema ida brani atu husu tan pergunta ba Nia.
Hotu tiha Jesus foo hanoin ba Nia eskolante sira ho ema barak nebee mak halibur hamutuk iha fatin nee. Nia dehan nunee:
“Mestri relijiaun sira ho mos ema Farizeu sira iha direitu atu hanorin Moisés nia lei.
Nee duni imi tenki rona sira i halo tuir sira nia hanorin. Maibee la bele halo tuir sira nia hahalok, tanba sira la moris tuir buat nebee mak sira rasik hanorin.
Sira foo regulamentu todan liu ba povu, maibee sira la ajuda netik ema atu bele halo tuir.
Sira halo saida deit, sira halo so atu ema seluk bele haree hodi gaba. Ezemplu, sira hakerek Maromak nia liafuan taka ba sira nia reen toos i suku fita iha sira nia batina tutun tuir lei Moisés nian. Maibee sira halo sira nian boot liu atu ema seluk gaba.<a href='#note-293' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-294' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuandu iha festa ka iha uma kreda laran, sira gosta tuur iha oin hanesan ema boot.
Sira gosta ema kumprimenta sira iha merkadu, i gosta ema bolu sira ‘mestri’.
Maibee imi la bele halo tuir sira nia hahalok nee. Imi la bele husik ema gaba imi hodi bolu imi ‘mestri’, tanba imi nia Mestri ida deit, i imi hotu mesak maun-alin.
Imi la bele foti aas ema ida iha mundu nee dehan ‘aman’, tanba imi nia Aman iha ida deit, Nia iha lalehan.
Imi la bele husik atu ema bolu imi ‘xefi’, tanba imi nia Xefi iha ida deit, Nia mak Kristu.
Hosi imi sira nee, see mak boot liu, nia sei haraik aan hodi serbi nia maluk sira seluk.<a href='#note-295' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba see mak foti aan sai boot, Maromak sei hatuun nia. Maibee see mak haraik aan, Maromak sei foti sae nia.”<a href='#note-296' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus hatete ba nai ulun relijiaun sira dehan, “Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Imi rasik lakohi tama Maromak nia reinu. Se iha ema seluk hakarak tama mos, imi taka odamatan ba sira, atu sira la bele tama.
Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Imi baa iha nebee-nebee too hakur tasi hodi buka ema ida atu tuir imi nia hanorin. Maibee bainhira imi hetan tiha, imi halo nia moris aat liu tan too nia merese hetan kastigu iha infernu todan liu fali imi dala rua.
Imi mestri matan delek! Imi sei terus. Imi hanorin dehan, ‘Se ema ida jura temi uma kreda boot nia naran, nia la halo tuir mos la buat ida. Maibee se nia jura temi osan mean nebee mak iha uma kreda laran, entaun nia tenki halo tuir.’
Imi matan delek i beik-teen! Ida nebee mak importante liu? Osan mean ka Maromak nia uma kreda boot nebee mak halo osan mean nee sai lulik?
Imi mos hanorin dehan, ‘Se ema ida jura temi meza sakrifisiu iha uma kreda boot, nia la halo tuir mos la buat ida. Maibee se nia jura temi oferta nebee mak iha meza nee nia leten, nia tenki halo tuir.’
Imi nee matan delek duni! Ida nebee mak importante liu? Oferta ka meza sakrifisiu nebee mak halo oferta nee sai lulik?
Nee duni, se ema jura temi meza sakrifisiu, nee dehan katak nia temi mos buat hotu-hotu nebee mak iha meza nee nia leten.
Se nia jura temi uma kreda boot, nee dehan katak nia temi mos Maromak tanba Nia mak hela iha uma kreda nee.
I se nia jura temi lalehan, nee dehan katak nia temi Maromak nia kadeira ukun i temi mos Maromak tanba Nia mak tuur iha kadeira nee.<a href='#note-298' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Bainhira imi kuu modo tahan, imi badinas foo parte ida hosi sanulu nudar oferta ba Maromak. Too modo tahan kikoan-kikoan hanesan ortelaun ho ruku mos imi foo. Maibee imi la interese kona ba buat nebee mak importante liu iha Maromak nia lei, hanesan justisa, hadomi ema kbiit-laek ho foo laran ba Maromak. Tuir loos buat sira nee mak tenki halo uluk. Maibee keta haluha foo mos parte ida hosi sanulu ba Maromak.<a href='#note-299' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mestri matan delek! Imi bele taes bee hodi hasai lalar nebee mak monu tama ba imi nia kopu laran, maibee kuda kamelu imi tolan tomak!<a href='#note-300' class='key'>‡</a>
Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Imi badinas hamoos kopu ho bikan nia liur. Maibee imi nia laran foer nafatin tanba imi gosta hadau ema nia sasaan hodi hanoin deit imi nia aan.
Imi Farizeu matan delek duni! Fasi uluk bikan nia laran, mak nia liur sai moos hotu.
Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Imi hanesan rate nebee mak ema pinta mutin. Hosi liur haree ba furak, maibee iha laran iha mate ruin ho buat oi-oin nebee halo ema hakribi.<a href='#note-301' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mos nunee. Bainhira ema haree imi hosi liur, imi ema diak. Afinal imi nia laran hakarak kontra Maromak nia ukun fuan i imi finji sai ema nebee moris loos.
Imi mestri relijiaun sira ho Farizeu sira, imi sei terus. Imi koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk. Imi hada Maromak nia profeta sira nia rate halo bo-boot, ema moris loos sira nia rate mos imi enfeita halo kapaas.
Depois imi dehan, ‘Se ami moris iha ami nia bei-ala sira nia tempu karik, ami lakohi hamutuk ho sira hodi oho profeta sira nee.’
Afinal imi nia liafuan nee hatudu sai katak, imi nee jerasaun hosi ema sira nebee mak oho profeta.
Entaun buat aat nebee mak imi nia bei-ala sira husik hela ba imi, husik imi hatutan ba too hotu!
Samea nia oan! Oinsaa mak imi bele halai sees hosi kastigu nebee atu kona imi iha infernu?
Tanba nee, rona di-diak! Hau sei haruka nafatin profeta ho ema matenek ho mos mestri nebee mak hanorin Maromak nia liafuan. Maibee imi sei oho balu, i prega balu ba iha krus. Sira seluk imi baku ho sikoti iha imi nia uma kreda i duni husi aldeia ba aldeia.
Nunee, ema moris loos hotu-hotu nebee imi nia bei-ala sira oho, imi nebee moris agora mak sei lori todan. Nee sura hosi Abel, ema ida nebee moris loos, too iha Zacarias, Barakias nia oan. Ema oho Zacarias iha area uma kreda boot besik meza sakrifisiu.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, sira hotu nia mate, imi nebee moris agora mak tenki lori todan.”
“Koitadu, imi ema Jerusalém! Imi oho Maromak nia profeta sira, i ema nebee Maromak haruka ba imi, imi tuda ho fatuk too mate. Dala barak Hau hakarak halibur imi hanesan manu inan halibur nia oan sira para luut, maibee imi lakohi.
Rona mai, Maromak husik tiha ona imi nia hela fatin. Agora imi mesak ona.
Hau hatete ba imi, imi sei la haree tan Hau too imi foo sai dehan, ‘Maromak foo bensaun ba Ema ida nebee mai lori Nai Maromak nia naran.’ ”
Koalia hotu tiha, Jesus lao sai hosi uma kreda boot. Nia lao dadaun, Nia eskolante sira mai besik hodi hatudu uma kreda nia furak ba Nia.
Maibee Jesus hataan dehan, “Imi haree di-diak ba! Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, too loron ida, buat sira nee sei rahun hotu. Fatuk sira nee hotu sei tetuk too rai.”
Depois Jesus lao baa tuur mesak iha foho Oliveira. Nia eskolante sira baa besik Nia hodi husu, “Hatete took mai ami, buat nebee ohin Ita Boot koalia nee, bainhira mak sei akontese? Kuandu Ita Boot atu fila fali mai, sinal saida mak sei mosu? I sinal saida mak sei hatudu katak mundu atu remata ona?”
Jesus hataan dehan, “Kuidadu di-diak para ema la bele bosok imi.
Imi sei rona kona ba funu oi-oin, i ema sei konta tutan kona ba funu iha fatin-fatin. Maibee keta tauk. Buat sira nee tenki akontese uluk, maibee nee laos dehan mundu atu remata ona.
Nasaun sei funu hasoru nasaun, estadu sei funu hasoru estadu. Sei iha rai hamlaha boot, i rai sei nakdoko iha fatin-fatin.
Maibee susar sira nee foin mak hahuu, hanesan feto isin rua nebee foin kanotak moras atu tuur ahi.
Ema iha nasaun hotu-hotu sei odi imi tanba imi tuir Hau. Sira sei entrega imi ba ema seluk atu halo terus imi i oho imi.<a href='#note-302' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nee mos ema nebee fiar mai Hau, barak sei fila kotuk mai Hau. Sira sei odi malu i faan malu ba inimigu sira.
Profeta falsu barak sei mosu hodi bosok ema barak atu tuir sira.
Hahalok aat iha mundu nee aumenta ba beibeik too ema barak liu mak la hatudu domin ba malu tan.
Maibee see mak tuir nafatin Hau too rohan, Maromak sei salva nia.<a href='#note-303' class='key'>✡</a>
Liafuan Diak kona ba oinsaa Maromak ukun nudar Liurai, ema sei haklaken iha mundu tomak, atu nunee ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu bele hatene. Haklaken hotu tiha mak foin mundu nee remata.
Hori uluk profeta Daniel hakerek kona ba buat ida aat liu nebee sei tama ba iha fatin lulik iha uma kreda boot, halo too Maromak hakribi. See mak lee liafuan nee, kompriende ba! Bainhira imi haree buat aat nee,<a href='#note-304' class='key'>✡</a>
imi nebee iha provinsia Judeia tenki halai ona ba foho.
Iha loron nee, ema nebee iha hela liur, la bele tama baa foti sasaan iha uma laran.
I ema nebee iha hela toos, la bele fila baa foti nia hena iha uma.<a href='#note-305' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nee, feto isin rua ho inan sira nebee foo susu nia oan, sei terus teb-tebes.
Harohan ba Maromak atu loron nebee mak imi halai ba foho nee, la bele monu iha tempu malirin ka iha loron Sabadu, ita ema Judeu nia loron deskansa.
Tanba iha tempu nee, ema sei terus aat liu. Komesa hosi Maromak halo mundu too agora, seidauk iha terus aat ida hanesan nee. I kuandu terus boot nee liu tiha, sei la akontese tan hanesan nee.<a href='#note-306' class='key'>✡</a>
Se Maromak la habadak tempu terus nee, la iha tan ema ida mak moris. Maibee Nia sei habadak duni, tanba Nia hadomi ema nebee mak Nia hili tiha ona.
Iha tempu nee, se ema ruma dehan ba imi, ‘Haree took, Kristu iha nee’ ka ‘Kristu iha nebaa’, keta fiar.
Tanba ema sei mai bosok dehan sira mak Kristu ka sira Maromak nia profeta. Sira sei hatudu milagre bo-boot nebee halo ema admira, atu nunee sira bele lohi ema hotu-hotu atu lao sala dalan. Too ema nebee Maromak hili mos sira hakarak hamonu.
Entaun hanoin di-diak! Aban-bainrua buat sira nee akontese, lalika hakfodak, tanba Hau foo hatene ona ba imi.
Nunee se ema mai bosok imi dehan, ‘Haree ba, Kristu iha rai fuik maran nebaa’, lalika sai baa buka. Se ema dehan, ‘Kristu iha hela subar fatin nee’, lalika fiar.
Tanba bainhira Hau, Mane Maksoin fila fali mai hosi lalehan, ema hotu sei haree mo-moos, hanesan rai lakan nebee mak naroman hosi lorosae too loromonu.<a href='#note-307' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira imi haree manu metan semo hamutuk ba iha fatin ida, nee sinal hodi hatudu mo-moos katak iha mate isin dodok iha nebaa.”<a href='#note-308' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-309' class='key'>✡</a>
“Bainhira loron terus nee liu tiha, loromatan sai nakukun tiha, fulan mos la foo naroman tan. Fitun sira iha lalehan sei monu namtate, i forsa hotu-hotu iha kalohan leten sei nakdoko.<a href='#note-310' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema hotu-hotu iha mundu sei haree sinal ida iha lalehan hatudu sai katak Hau, Mane Maksoin atu mai ona. Haree nunee, sira nebee lakohi simu Hau sei tanis ho laran susar. Depois ema hotu-hotu sei haree Hau, Mane Maksoin tuun mai iha kalohan leten, ho kbiit boot ho naroman lalehan nian.<a href='#note-311' class='key'>✡</a>
I Hau sei haruka Hau nia anju ida huu korneta ho lian makaas hodi bolu anju sira atu halibur ema sira nebee mak Maromak hili tiha ona, hosi rai ulun too rai ikun, hosi tasi feto too tasi mane.”
“Hanoin took ai figeira, i aprende hosi ai nee. Bainhira ai figeira nia sanak komesa matak i nia dikin komesa sai, imi hatene katak bailoron besik ona.
Nunee mos bainhira imi haree buat sira nee hotu akontese, imi hatene katak Hau besik mai ona, Hau iha ona odamatan oin.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, hosi ema hotu nebee mak moris iha tempu nee, iha balu sei moris too buat sira nee hotu akontese.
“Kona ba loron ho oras nebee mak Hau atu fila fali mai, la iha ema ida mak hatene. Anju sira iha lalehan mos la hatene.<a href='#note-312' class='key'>†</a> So Hau nia Aman iha lalehan deit mak hatene.
Bainhira loron too atu Hau, Mane Maksoin fila fali mai, ema sei moris baibain hanesan iha Noé nia tempu uluk.<a href='#note-313' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nebaa, molok bee boot sae, ema haan-hemu i halo festa kazamentu hanesan baibain, too loron Noé tama ba roo boot laran.
Bainhira bee sae lori lakon tiha ema sira hotu foin sira nia matan nakloke hodi hatene saida mak akontese. Nunee mos bainhira Hau, Mane Maksoin fila fali mai.<a href='#note-314' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nee, ema nain rua servisu hela iha toos laran, Maromak sei lori tiha ida i husik hela ida seluk.
Iha feto nain rua fai hela hare, Maromak sei lori tiha ida, i husik hela ida seluk.
Entaun imi tenki matan moris, tanba imi la hatene saa loron mak Hau, imi nia Nai fila fali mai.
Hanoin di-diak! Se iha uma nain ida hatene lo-loos iha oras nebee mak naok-teen atu mai, nia matan moris nafatin atu naok-teen la bele tama.
Nee duni, imi tenki prontu nafatin. Tanba aban-bainrua Hau, Mane Maksoin sei fila fali mai derepenti deit iha oras nebee imi la hatene.”<a href='#note-315' class='key'>✡</a>
“Entaun imi tenki hanesan atan ida nebee matenek toma konta nia patraun nia sasaan, i foo laran ba nia patraun. Patraun sei foo fiar ba ema nee para fahe hahaan ba nia atan sira seluk tuir oras.
Bainhira patraun fila ba uma, haree atan nee badinas halao nia servisu, atan nee sorti boot.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, patraun sei foti nia hodi toma konta nia rikusoin hotu.
Maibee karik atan nee ema aat ida, nia hanoin dehan, ‘Patraun sei kleur mak fila.’
Depois nia komesa baku nia maluk atan sira seluk, i haan-hemu hamutuk ho ema lanu-teen sira.
Se nunee, iha loron nebee nia la hein, i oras nebee nia la hatene, derepenti deit nia patraun fila mai.
Depois patraun sei tetak rahun tiha atan nee i soe hamutuk ho ema sira nebee koalia oin ida hahalok oin seluk. Iha nebaa ema sei tanis hakilar i ruun nehan.”
Jesus koalia tan dehan, “Aban-bainrua Hau fila fali mai hodi ukun nudar Liurai, sei sai hanesan komparasaun ida nee: Iha kalan ida, ema atu halo festa kazamentu. Iha feto raan nain sanulu baa hein noivu iha liur, ida-idak lori nia ahi-oan.<a href='#note-316' class='key'>✡</a>
Hosi feto raan nain sanulu nee, nain lima matenek i nain lima seluk beik.
Nain lima beik nee lori deit ahi-oan, la lori mina rezerva.
Maibee nain lima matenek nee lori mina rezerva iha botir.
Sira hotu baa hein noivu. Maibee noivu nee kleur loos foin too, nunee sira matan dukur toba tiha.
Iha kalan boot ema ida hakilar dehan, ‘Noivu mai ona! Imi mai hasoru nia ona!’
Rona nunee, feto raan nain sanulu nee hadeer hodi prepara sira nia ahi-oan.
Nain lima beik nee, sira nia mina atu hotu ona. Nunee sira hatete ba nain lima matenek dehan, ‘Foo imi nia mina uitoan mai, tanba ami nia ahi besik atu mate.’
Maibee nain lima matenek nee hataan, ‘Ami la bele foo. Se ami foo, entaun ami nia ahi mos bele mate. Diak liu imi baa sosa iha ema sira nebee faan mina.’
Bainhira sira baa buka mina atu sosa, noivu mos too. I feto raan nain lima nebee prontu hela atu simu noivu nee, tama hamutuk ho noivu iha festa laran. Depois ema taka tiha odamatan.
Too ikus feto raan nain lima beik nee mos too mai iha odamatan oin hodi bolu dehan, ‘Senhor! Senhor! Favor loke odamatan mai ami.’
Maibee noivu hataan, ‘Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, hau la konhese imi.’ ”<a href='#note-317' class='key'>✡</a>
Konta hotu tiha, Jesus dehan, “Entaun matan moris neon nain nafatin ba. Tanba imi la hatene loron ho oras nebee mak Hau atu fila fali mai.”
Nia foo ba atan sira nee tuir ida-idak nia kapasidade. Atan ida, nia entrega osan mutin bornal lima. Ida seluk nia entrega osan mutin bornal rua. Ida seluk tan nia entrega osan mutin bornal ida. Fahe hotu tiha, nia sai ona ba rai liur.
Atan ida nebee simu osan mutin bornal lima nee, baa fila liman kedas, i nia manaan tan osan mutin bornal lima.
Nunee mos atan ida nebee simu osan mutin bornal rua. Nia baa fila liman i manaan tan osan mutin bornal rua.
Maibee atan ida nebee simu osan mutin bornal ida, nia baa kee rai kuak hodi hakoi subar tiha nia patraun nia osan.
Kleur loos mak foin atan sira nia patraun fila. Too iha uma, patraun bolu sira hodi husu tuir, sira ida-idak manaan fali osan hira.
Atan ida nebee simu osan mutin bornal lima nee mai uluk. Nia lori osan mutin bornal sanulu hodi dehan, ‘Patraun, uluk patraun entrega osan mutin bornal lima mai hau. Agora haree took, hau manaan tan bornal lima.’
Nia patraun hatete ba nia, ‘Diak loos! O nee atan diak, i foo laran ba hau duni. O halo buat kiik-oan nee ho loos, nunee hau sei foo tan buat boot atu o tau matan. Mai haksolok hamutuk ho hau.’
Nunee mos atan nebee mak simu osan mutin bornal rua. Nia mai dehan, ‘Patraun, uluk patraun entrega osan mutin bornal rua mai hau. Haree took, hau manaan tan bornal rua.’
Nia patraun hataan, ‘Diak loos! O nee atan diak, i foo laran ba hau duni. O halo buat kiik-oan nee ho loos, nunee hau sei foo tan buat boot atu o tau matan. Mai haksolok hamutuk ho hau.’
Depois atan nebee simu osan mutin bornal ida deit mai dehan, ‘Patraun, hau hatene ita boot siak-teen. Ita boot gosta kuu buat nebee laos ita boot mak kuda, i simu buat nebee laos ita boot nia kosar been.
Nee mak hau tauk, i hau baa hakoi subar tiha patraun nia osan. Haree ba, ita boot nia osan mak nee.’
Maibee nia patraun hataan, ‘Atan aat i baruk-teen! O hatene katak hau gosta kuu buat nebee laos hau mak kuda, i simu buat nebee laos hau nia kosar been.
Tuir lo-loos o rai hau nia osan iha banku para hau fila mai, bele simu fali osan nee ho nia funan.’
Depois patraun hatete ba nia atan seluk, ‘Foti tiha osan nee hosi nia hodi foo fali ba atan ida nebee mak iha ona osan mutin bornal sanulu.
Tanba ema nebee iha ona, sei simu tan too nakonu resin. Maibee ema nebee la iha, uitoan nebee nia iha mos, sei hasai tiha hosi nia.<a href='#note-318' class='key'>✡</a>
Agora kaer tiha atan la iha folin nee, soe sai ba iha fatin nakukun. Iha nebaa ema sei tanis hakilar i ruun nihan.’ ”<a href='#note-319' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hatutan tan dehan, “Hau, Mane Maksoin sei fila fali mai hosi lalehan ho naroman nabilan, i anju sira hotu mai hamutuk ho Hau. Hau sei tuur iha kadeira ukun nudar Liurai.<a href='#note-320' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju sira sei halibur ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu iha Hau nia oin, i Hau sei fahe ema sira nee ba grupu rua, hanesan bibi atan haketak bibi malae ho bibi timur.
Ema nebee moris loos, Hau tau iha Hau nia sorin loos, sira seluk Hau tau iha Hau nia sorin karuk.
Nudar Liurai, Hau sei hatete ba ema sira nebee mak iha Hau nia sorin loos dehan, ‘Imi sira nee mak hetan bensaun hosi Hau nia Aman, mai tama ona ba imi nia fatin iha reinu lalehan. Fatin nee prepara nanis ona ba imi bainhira Maromak halo mundu nee.
Tanba uluk bainhira Hau hamlaha, imi foo hahaan mai Hau. Hau hamrook, imi foo Hau hemu. Hau hanesan ema lao rai ida iha imi nia rain, imi simu Hau iha imi nia uma.
Hau la iha hena atu hatais, imi foo hena mai Hau. Hau moras, imi tau matan mai Hau. Hau dadur iha komarka, imi baa vizita Hau.’
Depois ema nebee moris loos nee husu, ‘Nai, hori bainhira mak ami haree Ita Boot hamlaha, i foo hahaan ba Ita, ka Ita hamrook i ami foo Ita hemu?
Hori bainhira mak Ita Boot hanesan ema lao rai, depois ami simu Ita iha uma? Hori bainhira mak Ita Boot la iha hena, i ami foo hena ba Ita?
Hori bainhira mak ami haree Ita Boot moras ka dadur iha komarka, depois ami baa vizita Ita?’
Hau sei hataan dehan, ‘Rona di-diak! Bainhira imi halo buat diak sira nee ba Hau nia maluk ida, maski ema kiik ida mos, nee hanesan imi halo ona mai Hau.’
Depois Hau hatete ba ema sira nebee mak iha Hau nia sorin karuk dehan, ‘Imi sira nee hetan ona malisan. Sai tiha hosi fatin nee, i baa tama iha ahi nebee mak nunka mate tinan ba tinan. Ahi nee prepara tiha ona ba diabu nia boot ho nia anju sira.
Tanba uluk bainhira Hau hamlaha, imi la foo hahaan mai Hau. Hau hamrook, imi la foo Hau hemu.
Hau hanesan ema lao rai ida iha imi nia rain, imi la simu Hau iha imi nia uma. Hau la iha hena atu hatais, imi la foo hena mai Hau. Hau moras ka dadur iha komarka, imi la tau matan ba Hau.’
Hau sei hataan, ‘Rona di-diak! Bainhira imi la halo buat diak sira nee ba Hau nia maluk ida, maski ema kiik ida mos, nee hanesan imi la halo mai Hau.’
Hotu tiha ema sira nee sei sai hosi Hau nia sorin hodi hetan kastigu tinan ba tinan. Maibee ema nebee mak moris loos sei hetan moris rohan-laek.”<a href='#note-321' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira Jesus hanorin tiha hotu buat sira nee, Nia hatete ba Nia eskolante sira dehan,
“Imi hatene katak, hela deit loron rua atu festa Paskua. Iha tempu nee, ema sei entrega Hau, Mane Maksoin ba ema aat atu prega mate iha krus.”<a href='#note-322' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nebaa nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nian sira halibur hamutuk iha nai lulik boot Kaifás nia uma.
Sira kombina malu atu kaer Jesus nonook deit hodi oho.
Maibee sira hatete, “La bele kaer Nia iha loron festa nee, se lae povu bele halo rungu-ranga.”
Jesus baa iha aldeia Betánia hodi haan iha Simão ida nebee uluk moras lepra nia uma.
Bainhira Jesus haan hela, feto ida mai lori botir ida halo hosi fatuk murak, mina morin karun teb-tebes mak iha laran. Nia baa besik Jesus hodi fui mina morin nee ba iha Jesus nia ulun.
Bainhira Jesus nia eskolante sira haree, sira hirus hodi dehan ba malu, “Nusaa mak nia estraga deit mina morin folin karun nee?
Se mina morin nee ita faan karik, ita bele hetan osan barak hodi ajuda ema kiak sira.”
Maibee Jesus hatene hela sira nia hanoin, nunee Nia dehan, “Imi keta hirus feto nee, tanba nia halo ona buat furak mai Hau.
Ema kiak sira sempre iha imi nia leet, maibee Hau laos atu hela nafatin ho imi.<a href='#note-323' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia fui mina morin nee ba Hau nia isin para Hau mate karik, hein hakoi deit.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, aban-bainrua bainhira ema foo sai Liafuan Diak iha mundu tomak, sira mos sei konta kona ba buat nebee mak nia halo mai Hau, atu ema hanoin nafatin nia.”
Depois Judas Iscariotes, eskolante ida hosi sanulu resin rua nee, baa hasoru nai lulik nia ulun sira.
Too iha nebaa nia husu, “Se hau entrega Nia ba imi nia liman, imi sei foo saida ba hau?”
Entaun sira sura osan mutin tolu-nulu hodi foo ba nia.<a href='#note-324' class='key'>✡</a>
I Judas sai kedas hodi buka dalan atu entrega Jesus ba sira.
Festa Paun la Tau Fermentu hahuu ona. Iha loron primeiru Jesus nia eskolante sira baa husu Nia dehan, “Ita boot hakarak ami baa prepara atu haan festa Paskua iha nebee?”<a href='#note-325' class='key'>*</a>
Jesus hataan, “Baa iha sidade laran, iha nebaa imi sei hasoru ema ida. Hatete ba nia nunee: ‘Mestri hameno katak, Nia loron nebee Maromak desidi nee besik ona, i Nia hakarak selebra festa Paskua hamutuk ho Nia eskolante sira iha ita nia uma.’ ”
Depois Nia eskolante sira baa halo tuir buat nebee mak Jesus haruka. Sira halo preparasaun ba festa Paskua iha nebaa.
Bainhira kalan ona Jesus tuur hamutuk ho Nia eskolante nain sanulu resin rua iha meza.
Sira haan daudaun, Nia dehan, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, hosi imi sira nee, ida sei faan Hau ba Hau nia inimigu sira.”
Rona nunee, Nia eskolante sira tristi teb-tebes. I sira ida-ida komesa husu ba Nia dehan, “Nai, laos hau, loos ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “Ida nebee agora haan lisuk ho Hau iha manko, nia mak sei faan Hau.<a href='#note-326' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau, Mane Maksoin tenki mate duni tuir buat nebee hakerek tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu. Maibee ema nebee faan Hau nee, sei terus teb-tebes. Diak liu uluk kedas nia lalika moris.”
Depois Judas, ida nebee atu faan Jesus nee husu, “Mestri, laos hau, loos ka lae?”
Jesus hataan, “O duni.”
Depois Nia foti tua kalis ida. Nia foo agradese ba Maromak, i foo ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Imi hotu hemu ba.
Tua nee Hau nia raan. Liu hosi Hau nia raan fakar mak Maromak kumpri Nia promesa hodi hamoos ema barak nia sala.<a href='#note-327' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete ba imi, Hau sei la hemu tan tua nee. Bainhira Hau nia Aman iha lalehan ukun Nia povu hotu mak foin Hau hemu fali tua foun hamutuk ho imi.”
Hotu tiha Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira kanta hamutuk hodi hahii Maromak. Depois sira sai hodi baa iha foho Oliveira.
Iha dalan klaran Jesus hatete ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Iha kalan nee kedas, imi hotu-hotu sei halai husik hela Hau tanba imi haree saida mak akontese mai Hau. Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek tiha ona dehan,
‘Hau sei oho tiha bibi atan,
i bibi sira sei halai namkari hotu.’<a href='#note-328' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau sei mate duni. Maibee bainhira Hau moris fali, Hau baa hein imi iha provinsia Galileia.”<a href='#note-329' class='key'>✡</a>
Pedro hataan, “Maski sira hotu halai namkari tanba buat nebee mak akontese ba Ita Boot, maibee hau sei la halai.”
Jesus dehan ba nia, “Hau hatete lo-loos ba o, iha kalan nee duni, molok manu kokoreek, o sei nega Hau dala tolu.”
Pedro hataan fali, “Maski hau tenki mate hamutuk ho Ita Boot mos, hau sei la nega.” Eskolante sira seluk mos hatete nunee.
Depois Jesus lao hamutuk ho Nia eskolante sira baa iha fatin ida naran Getsemani. Too iha nebaa, Nia hatete ba sira, “Imi tuur iha nee, Hau sei baa halo orasaun iha nebaa.”
Nia lao tan uitoan, lori ho Pedro ho Zebedeu nia oan nain rua, Tiago ho João. Iha tempu nee Jesus nia laran susar teb-tebes i la hakmatek.
Jesus hatete ba sira nain tolu, “Hau nia laran susar teb-tebes, too senti atu besik mate ona. Imi hein Hau iha nee hodi hadeer nafatin.”
Jesus lao tan uitoan hosi sira, depois Nia taka rabat ba rai hodi harohan dehan, “Hau nia Aman, se bele karik hasai tiha terus ida nee hosi Hau. Maibee la bele halo tuir Hau nia hakarak, halo tuir deit Ita Boot nia hakarak.”
Depois Nia fila fali ba nia eskolante nain tolu nee, Nia haree sira toba dukur hela. Nia hatete ba Pedro, “Imi atu hadeer deit oras ida hamutuk ho Hau mos la bele ka?
Hadeer hodi halo orasaun atu imi la bele monu ba tentasaun. Tanba imi nia laran hakarak atu halo buat nebee loos, maibee imi ema nebee fraku.”
Dala ida tan Jesus baa halo orasaun dehan, “Hau nia Aman! Se Hau tenki simu terus nee, entaun halo tuir Ita Boot nia hakarak ba.”
Bainhira Nia fila fali, Nia haree sira nain tolu toba fali, tanba sira nia matan dukur loos.
Entaun Nia husik sira i fila fali hodi halo orasaun ba dala tolu. Nia harohan hanesan ohin.
Hotu tiha Nia fila fali ba Nia eskolante sira hodi dehan, “Imi sei toba ka? Agora tempu too ona atu ema faan Hau, Mane Maksoin ba iha ema aat nia liman.
Hadeer ona. Haree ba! Ema nebee mak faan Hau ba ema aat nee mai daudaun ona. Mai ita baa hasoru sira.”
Jesus sei koalia hela, Judas, eskolante ida hosi sira nain sanulu resin rua nee, too mai. Ema barak mai hamutuk ho nia, lori surik ho ai dona. Ema sira nee, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira mak haruka.
Molok too iha nebaa, Judas foo tiha ona sinal ba sira dehan, “Ema nebee mak hau rei, Nia mak nee, imi kaer Nia.”
Entaun Judas baa kedas kumprimenta Jesus dehan, “Mestri.” I nia rei Jesus.
Jesus hatete, “Belun, halo tuir o nia planu ba.” Depois ema sira nee mai kaer Jesus.
Derepenti Jesus nia eskolante ida losu nia surik hodi tesi kotu tiha ema ida nia tilun. Ema nee nai lulik boot nia atan.
Haree nunee, Jesus hatete, “Hatama tiha o nia surik nee ba iha nia fatin. Tanba see mak hodi surik hasoru ema, nia sei mate mos ho surik.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba o, se Hau husu tulun ba Hau nia Aman iha lalehan, Nia haruka kedas anju barak teb-tebes, liu fali batalhaun sanulu resin rua, para ajuda Hau.
Depois Jesus hatete ba ema barak nee dehan, “Nusaa mak imi mai lori surik ho ai dona atu kaer Hau? Imi hanoin Hau ema aat ka? Afinal lor-loron Hau iha hela area uma kreda boot hodi hanorin, i imi la kaer Hau.<a href='#note-330' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee buat sira nee hotu akontese hodi kumpri saida mak profeta sira foo sai tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu.” Depois Jesus nia eskolante sira husik hela Nia hodi halai namkari hotu.
Depois ema nebee kaer Jesus lori Nia ba iha nai lulik boot Kaifás nia uma. Iha nebaa mestri relijiaun sira ho katuas lia nain sira halibur hamutuk ona atu foo justisa ba Jesus.
Pedro lao tu-tuir Jesus hosi dook deit, i tama liu ba moru laran. Nia tuur hamutuk ho ema seguransa sira iha uma oin, atu hatene tuir saida mak akontese ba Jesus.
Iha uma laran, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho justisa nain relijiaun Judeu sira seluk buka hela ema atu foo sasin falsu para bele kastigu mate Jesus.
Maski ema barak mai hamriik iha oin hodi duun Nia, maibee justisa nain sira la hetan sala ida atu bele kastigu Nia. Too ikus ema nain rua tan baa hamriik iha oin
hodi foo sasin dehan, “Ema nee hatete hanesan nee: ‘Hau bele halo rahun Maromak nia uma kreda boot nee, depois iha loron tolu nia laran Hau bele harii fila fali.’ ”<a href='#note-331' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois nai lulik boot hamriik hodi dehan ba Jesus, “Ema sira nee foo sasin tiha ona kona ba O nia sala. Nusaa mak O la hataan sira?”
Maibee Jesus nonook deit.
Nunee nai lulik boot dehan, “Jura took hodi Maromak Moris nia naran, O mak Kristu, Maromak nia Oan, ka?”<a href='#note-332' class='key'>†</a>
Jesus hataan, “Ita dehan nee loos. Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, aban-bainrua imi sei haree Hau, Mane Maksoin tuur iha Maromak Kbiit Nain nia sorin loos. I imi sei haree Hau tuun mai hosi lalehan iha kalohan laran.”<a href='#note-333' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, nai lulik boot nee hirus too lees tiha nia batina hodi dehan ba justisa nain sira, “Agora imi rona rasik ona Nia liafuan. Nia hatete aat Maromak! Nusaa mak ita hein tan sasin seluk?
Imi foo justisa oinsaa?”
Sira hataan, “Nia merese hetan kastigu mate.”<a href='#note-334' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois sira tafui kabeen ba Jesus nia oin i baku Nia. Balu basa Nia hasan<a href='#note-335' class='key'>✡</a>
hodi husu, “He, Kristu, Profeta, foo sai took, see mak baku O nee?”
Pedro sei tuur hela iha uma oin, iha kriada ida mai besik nia dehan, “O mos hamutuk ho Jesus, Ema Galileia nee, loos ka lae?”
Maibee Pedro nega iha ema hotu nia oin dehan, “Hau la hatene buat nebee o koalia nee.”
Depois Pedro sai ba iha portaun, kriada ida tan haree nia i hatete ba ema nebee mak besik dehan, “Ema nee ohin hamutuk ho Jesus, Ema Nazaré.”
Pedro nega tan dala ida hodi dehan, “Hau jura, hau la konhese Ema nee.”
La kleur, ema sira nebee hamriik iha nebaa mai besik Pedro hodi dehan, “O nee Nia ema duni. Tanba o koalia hanesan ema Galileia.”
Maibee Pedro jura dehan, “Hau la konhese Ema nee. Se hau bosok karik, husik Maromak kastigu hau ba.” Derepenti manu kokoreek.
Rona nunee, Pedro hanoin fila fali liafuan nebee uluk Jesus dehan, “Molok manu kokoreek, o sei nega Hau dala tolu.” Entaun Pedro sai hosi nebaa i tanis ho laran dodok.
Dadeer-saan deit, nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira foti desizaun atu kastigu mate Jesus.
Depois sira futu Nia, i lori Nia ba iha governador Pilatus.<a href='#note-336' class='key'>*</a>
Bainhira Judas, eskolante nebee mak faan Jesus nee, hatene katak sira atu kastigu mate Jesus, nia laran tristi teb-tebes. Nunee nia entrega fali osan mutin tolu-nulu nee ba nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira.
Nia hatete, “Hau halo sala ona! Ema ida nebee la iha sala sei mate tanba hau mak faan.”
Maibee sira hataan, “Ami la interese. O halo sala ka lae, nee o mak hatene.”
Entaun Judas soe osan nee ba iha uma kreda boot laran. Depois nia sai baa tara aan mate tiha.
Entaun sira desidi uza osan nee hodi sosa rai pedasuk nebee uluk badaen sanan rai nian. I sira foo rai nee atu sai fatin hodi hakoi ema estranjeiru.
Too agora ema bolu rai nee ‘Rai Raan’.<a href='#note-337' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee sira halo tuir liafuan nebee profeta Jeremias hakerek hori uluk dehan, “Ema Israel sira desidi tiha ona katak Nia folin mak osan mutin tolu-nulu. Entaun sira foti osan nee
hodi sosa rai nebee uluk badaen sanan rai nian, tuir orden nebee mak Nai Maromak foo mai hau.”<a href='#note-338' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira Jesus hamriik iha governador Pilatus nia oin, governador husu ba Nia, “Loos ka, O mak ema Judeu sira nia Liurai ka?”
Jesus hataan, “Ita dehan nee loos.”
Maibee bainhira nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira duun Jesus iha Pilatus nia oin, Jesus la hataan buat ida.
Entaun Pilatus hatete ba Jesus dehan, “O la rona ka? Ema sira nee foo sasin oi-oin hodi hasoru O!”
Maibee Nia la hataan, uitoan mos lae, halo governador Pilatus admira loos.
Tin-tinan, bainhira ema Judeu halo festa Paskua, governador sempre hasai ema dadur ida tuir povu nia hakarak.
Iha tempu nebaa, iha ema dadur ida naran Barabás, ema hotu konhese nia kriminozu boot ida.
Entaun bainhira ema barak halibur hamutuk ona, Pilatus husu ba sira dehan, “Imi hakarak hau husik ida nebee? Barabás ka Jesus nebee ema bolu Kristu?”
Pilatus koalia nunee tanba nia hatene hela nai ulun Judeu sira laran moras ba Jesus, nee mak sira entrega Jesus ba nia.
Bainhira Pilatus tuur iha kadeira juiz nian atu tesi Jesus nia lia, nia feen haruka lia menon dehan, “Keta halo buat ruma ba Ema nee tanba Nia la sala ida. Hau ohin mehi aat kona ba Nia, halo hau hanoin barak.”
Maibee nai lulik nia ulun sira ho katuas lia nain sira obriga deit ema barak nee husu ba Pilatus atu husik Barabás, i oho Jesus.
Depois governador Pilatus husu fali dehan, “Hosi ema nain rua nee, imi hakarak hau husik ida nebee?”
Sira hataan, “Barabás!”
Rona nunee Pilatus husu tan, “Entaun hau atu halo saida ba Jesus nebee ema bolu Kristu nee?”
Sira hotu hakilar, “Prega tiha Nia ba krus!”
Depois Pilatus husu, “Tansaa? Nia halo krimi saida?”
Maibee sira hakilar makaas liu tan, “Prega tiha Nia ba krus!”
Pilatus haree katak ema barak nee atu halo rungu-ranga, i nia la bele halo buat ida. Entaun nia foti bee hodi fasi nia liman iha ema barak nee nia oin dehan, “Kona ba Ema nee nia mate, hau la hatene! Imi mak sei lori todan.”<a href='#note-339' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira hotu hataan, “Husik ba, Ema nee nia raan, ami ho ami nia jerasaun sira mak lori.”
Entaun Pilatus halo tuir sira nia hakarak hodi hasai Barabás hosi kadeia. I nia haruka ema baku Jesus ho sikoti, depois entrega Jesus ba soldadu sira atu prega iha krus.
Hotu tiha soldadu sira lori Jesus ba iha governador Pilatus nia uma i sira halibur sira nia maluk soldadu sira seluk nebee hela iha nebaa hodi mai haleu Nia.
Sira kolu tiha Jesus nia hena hodi foo hatais fali batina kor mean ida hanesan liurai sira baibain hatais.
Sira mos dulas ai tarak halo kabuar hanesan koroa liurai nian hodi tau iha Nia ulun. Sira tau ai sanak lotuk ida iha Nia liman loos hanesan ai tonka. Sira hakneak iha Nia oin hodi hamoe Nia dehan, “Viva, ema Judeu sira nia Liurai!”
Sira mos tafui kabeen ba Nia i foti fali ai sanak nee hosi Nia liman laran hodi baku Nia ulun fila-fila.
Sira hamoe Nia nunee, depois kolu tiha batina mean hodi foo hatais fali Nia hena rasik. Hotu tiha sira lori Nia sai atu baa prega iha krus.
Sira too iha fatin ida naran Golgota, katak “Fatin Ulun Ruin”.
Iha nebaa sira kahur tua ho ai moruk hodi foo ba Jesus. Nia koko tiha maibee lakohi hemu.<a href='#note-340' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois sira prega Jesus iha krus. I soldadu sira dada rifa atu hatene see mak bele hetan Jesus nia hena.<a href='#note-341' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha sira tuur hodi hein Nia.
Sira mos iha ai kabelak ida nebee hakerek nunee: “Ema nee Jesus, ema Judeu sira nia Liurai.” Nee foo hatene razaun saida mak Jesus simu kastigu mate. I sira prega ai kabelak nee iha Nia ulun leten.
Sira prega tan ema naok-teen boot nain rua iha krus, ida iha Jesus nia sorin loos i ida iha sorin karuk.
Ema nebee liu hosi fatin nee, sira doko ulun hodi hatete aat Jesus.<a href='#note-342' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira hatete, “Uluk O dehan atu halo rahun uma kreda boot, depois harii fali iha loron tolu nia laran. Se O Maromak nia Oan duni, entaun salva took O nia Aan hodi tuun hosi krus nee.”<a href='#note-343' class='key'>✡</a>
Nai lulik nia ulun sira, mestri relijiaun sira ho katuas lia nain sira mos hatete aat Jesus dehan,
“Nia salva ona ema seluk, maibee Nia la bele salva Nia Aan rasik. Nia dehan, Nia mak ema Israel nia Liurai, entaun diak liu agora Nia tuun hosi krus atu ita fiar.
Nia fiar ba Maromak, se Maromak gosta Nia, entaun ita haree took Maromak mai salva Nia ka lae. Tanba Nia rasik hatete katak Nia Maromak nia Oan.”<a href='#note-344' class='key'>✡</a>
Naok-teen nain rua nebee mak iha Jesus nia sor-sorin mos tarata aat Jesus nunee.
Komesa meiudia, nakukun taka metin rejiaun nee tomak too tuku tolu lokraik.
Iha tuku tolu lokraik, Jesus hakilar ho lian makaas dehan, “Eli, Eli, lama sabaktani?” Nee dehan, “Hau nia Maromak! Hau nia Maromak! Tansaa mak Ita husik Hau mesak?”<a href='#note-345' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, ema balu nebee hamriik besik dehan, “Nia bolu profeta Elias.”
Sira ida halai kedas baa foti esponza rohan ida habokon ho tua siin, tau ba ai naruk ida hodi lolo ba iha Jesus nia ibun atu hemu.<a href='#note-346' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee sira seluk dehan, “Keta foo lai! Ita haree took, Elias mai salva duni Nia ka lae.”
Depois Jesus hakilar dala ida tan ho lian makaas, i Nia hakotu Nia iis.
Bainhira Jesus nia iis kotu, kortina boot nebee taka fatin lulik iha uma kreda boot, naklees hosi leten too kraik fahe tiha ba rua. Rai nakdoko makaas i fatuk bo-boot sira nakfera tiha.<a href='#note-347' class='key'>✡</a>
Rate sira mos nakloke. I Maromak nia ema balu nebee mate tiha ona, Nia halo moris fali.
Sira ida-idak sai hosi sira nia rate. Bainhira Jesus moris fila fali, sira mos tama iha sidade santu Jerusalém, i ema barak haree.
Bainhira komandante Roma ho soldadu sira nebee hein Jesus nee haree rai nakdoko ho buat seluk nebee akontese, sira tauk teb-tebes hodi dehan, “Loos duni! Ema nee Maromak nia Oan.”
Iha nebaa iha senhora barak asisti hosi dook deit. Sira nee uluk tuir Jesus hosi Galileia too iha Jerusalém hodi serbi Nia.
Sira nee mak Maria Madalena, Maria ida seluk (Tiago ho José nia inan), Zebedeu nia feen (Tiago ho João nia inan) ho mos sel-seluk tan.<a href='#note-348' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha mos ema riku ida hosi sidade Arimateia, naran José. Nia mos Jesus nia eskolante ida. Loromatan atu monu ona,
nia baa hasoru Pilatus hodi husu Jesus nia mate isin atu hakoi. Entaun Pilatus haruka soldadu sira entrega Jesus nia mate isin ba José.
Depois José simu Jesus nia mate isin, i falun ho hena mutin diak nian nebee foun.
Nia lori Jesus nia mate isin baa haloot iha rate nebee nia prepara tiha ona ba nia aan rasik. Fatin nee fatuk lolon nebee ema bahat tiha ona atu sai rate. Depois nia duir fatuk boot ida hodi taka rate nee. Hotu tiha nia fila.
Maibee Maria Madalena ho Maria ida seluk tuur hela hodi hateke ba rate nee.
Sira dehan, “Senhor, ami hanoin hela Ema bosok-teen nee nia liafuan. Uluk Nia sei moris, Nia dehan katak too iha loron tolu Maromak sei halo Nia moris fali.<a href='#note-349' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee haruka ita boot nia soldadu sira baa halo seguransa iha rate too iha loron tolu. Keta halo be Nia eskolante sira mai naok tiha Nia mate isin, depois sira dehan, Maromak halo Nia moris fali ona hosi mate. Se ida nee mak akontese, entaun sira nee bosok aat liu fali sira nia Mestri.”
Pilatus hataan, “Entaun lori soldadu balu ba iha rate hodi halo seguransa metin iha nebaa.”
Nunee nai ulun Judeu sira hamutuk ho soldadu sira baa iha rate. Sira tau sinal ba rate nee nia odamatan atu ema keta tama. Depois soldadu sira halo seguransa nafatin iha nebaa.
Aban fali iha loron Domingu dadeer-saan nakukun, Maria Madalena ho Maria ida seluk baa haree rate.
Derepenti rai nakdoko makaas teb-tebes tanba Nai Maromak nia anju ida tuun mai hosi lalehan hodi duir tiha fatuk nebee taka rate nee. Depois nia tuur iha leten.
Anju nee nia oin nabilan hanesan rai lakan, i nia hena mutin loos.
Haree nunee, seguransa sira tauk teb-tebes too sira nakdedar i monu tiha ba rai hanesan ema mate.
Depois anju hatete ba senhora nain rua nee dehan, “La bele tauk. Hau hatene imi buka hela Jesus, Ida nebee ema prega tiha ona ba krus nee.
Nia la iha nee ona, tanba Maromak halo moris fali ona Nia, tuir buat nebee uluk Nia hatete tiha ona. Mai haree fatin nebee mak ema tau Nia mate isin nee.
Haree tiha, imi baa lalais foo hatene Nia eskolante sira dehan, ‘Maromak halo moris fali ona Jesus hosi mate. Nia sei baa iha Galileia hodi hein imi, i imi sei haree Nia iha nebaa.’ Keta haluha hau nia lia menon nee.”
Nunee senhora nain rua nee husik kedas rate. Sira tauk maibee sira mos haksolok teb-tebes. Sira halai lalais atu baa foo hatene Jesus nia eskolante sira.
Iha dalan klaran, derepenti Jesus hasoru sira i kumprimenta sira. Entaun sira baa besik Nia i hakruuk hakuak Nia ain hodi adora Nia.
Depois Jesus hatete ba sira, “La bele tauk. Baa foo hatene Hau nia maluk sira atu sira baa iha Galileia. Iha nebaa sira sei haree Hau.”
Bainhira senhora sira nee lao dadauk, seguransa sira balu hamriik hodi baa iha sidade Jerusalém. Too iha nebaa, sira konta ba nai lulik nia ulun sira kona ba buat hotu-hotu nebee mak ohin akontese iha rate.
Entaun nai lulik nia ulun sira hasoru malu ho katuas lia nain sira hodi halo planu. Sira foo osan barak ba soldadu sira nebee kontrola rate nee.
I sira hameno dehan, “Imi tenki foo sai dehan, ‘Iha kalan boot bainhira ami toba dukur hela, Nia eskolante sira mai naok tiha Nia mate isin.’
Se governador rona karik, ami mak baa koalia ho nia atu nunee imi la bele hetan kastigu.”
Entaun ema seguransa sira simu osan nee i habelar lia falsu nebee mak hameno tiha ona ba sira. Too agora istoria nee ema Judeu sira sei konta nafatin.
Depois Jesus nia eskolante nain sanulu resin ida baa sae foho ida iha provinsia Galileia, tuir buat nebee Jesus hameno tiha ona ba sira.<a href='#note-350' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira sira haree Jesus, sira adora Nia. Maibee sira balu sei duvida hela.
Depois Jesus baa besik sira hodi dehan, “Maromak foo tiha ona kbiit tomak mai Hau atu ukun buat hotu-hotu iha lalehan ho rai.
Tanba nee, baa hanorin ema iha nasaun hotu-hotu atu sira sai Hau nia eskolante. Foo sarani sira hodi Aman, Oan ho Espiritu Santu sira nia naran.<a href='#note-351' class='key'>✡</a>
Hanorin sira atu halo tuir buat hotu-hotu nebee mak Hau hatete ona ba imi. Keta haluha, Hau sempre hamutuk ho imi too mundu nee remata.”
Jesus moris iha aldeia Belém iha provinsia Judeia. Iha tempu nebaa liurai Herodes mak ukun rai nee. Iha loron ida matenek nain balu nebee hatene siik sinal iha fitun, sira mai hosi rai dook, hosi parte lorosae. Too iha sidade Jerusalém,
sira husu, “Kosok Oan nebee moris atu sai ema Judeu sira nia liurai nee iha nebee? Ami haree tiha ona fitun ida iha parte lorosae nebee foo sinal kona ba Nia moris. Tanba nee mak ami mai atu adora Nia.”
Bainhira liurai Herodes rona sira nia liafuan nee, nia laran susar teb-tebes, nunee mos povu iha Jerusalém tomak.
Depois Herodes halibur nai lulik nia ulun sira ho mestri relijiaun sira hotu hodi husu, “Kristu, Salvador nebee Maromak promete hori uluk ona atu haruka mai nee, sei moris iha nebee?”
Sira hataan, “Iha aldeia Belém iha provinsia Judeia. Tanba hori uluk kedas Maromak nia profeta hakerek dehan,
keta hanoin dehan imi mak kiik liu iha rai Judeia nee.
Tanba ukun nain ida sei mai hosi imi nia rain,
Nia mak sei sai bibi atan ba Hau nia povu Israel.’ ”<a href='#note-98' class='key'>✡</a>
Rona nunee, Herodes bolu nonook matenek nain sira nee hodi husu ba sira, hori-bainhira loos mak fitun nee mosu. I sira mos esplika ba nia.
Depois nia haruka sira baa Belém. Nia hameno hela dehan, “Senhor sira baa buka di-diak Labarik nee. Bainhira hetan ona Nia, mai fali foo hatene hau, para hau mos bele baa adora Nia.”
9-10 Rona tiha liurai nia liafuan, matenek nain sira nee komesa lao baa dadauk. Derepenti fitun nebee sira uluk haree iha lorosae nee, mosu fila fali iha sira nia oin. Haree nunee, sira mos kontente teb-tebes. I sira lao tuir fitun nee too fitun para iha Labarik nee nia uma leten.
Too iha nebaa, sira tama iha uma laran haree Labarik nee ho Nia inan Maria, i sira hakneak hakruuk too rai hodi adora Nia. Depois sira hasai sira nia prezente karun teb-tebes, sira foo ba Labarik nee osan mean, ai been morin ho mina morin diak nian.
Hotu tiha Maromak foo hanoin ba sira liu hosi mehi katak sira la bele fila fali ba Herodes. Entaun sira fila ba sira nia rain liu hosi dalan seluk.
Bainhira matenek nain sira fila tiha, Nai Maromak nia anju mai hatudu aan ba José liu hosi mehi. Anju nee foo hatene dehan, “Hadeer ona! Lori Labarik nee ho Nia inan halai ba iha rai Ejitu, tanba Herodes buka hela Labarik nee atu oho Nia. Hela iha nebaa too hau foo hatene fali ba o katak imi bele fila.”
Iha kalan nee kedas, José hadeer lori Labarik nee ho Nia inan halai ba Ejitu,
i sira hela iha nebaa too Herodes mate. Uluk kedas Nai Maromak koalia liu hosi Nia profeta dehan, “Hau bolu Hau nia Oan sai hosi Ejitu.” Agora sai duni nunee.<a href='#note-99' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira liurai Herodes hatene katak, matenek nain sira halo beik tiha nia hodi fila liu hosi dalan seluk, nia hirus teb-tebes. Nia foo orden ba soldadu sira atu baa Belém vila ho rai nebee besik hodi oho hotu labarik mane kiik-oan nebee tinan rua mai kraik. Nia foo orden nunee tuir informasaun hosi matenek nain sira kona ba tempu nebee mak sira haree fitun nee mosu.
Buat nee akontese tuir saida mak Maromak nia profeta Jeremias foo sai uluk kedas dehan,
“Iha ema tanis hakilar iha aldeia Rama.
Raquel tanis halerik tanba nia oan sira la iha ona.
Ema hamaus nia atu la bele tanis
maibee nia lakohi rona.”<a href='#note-100' class='key'>✡</a>
Ikus mai liurai Herodes mate. Iha tempu nebaa Nai Maromak nia anju hatudu aan ba José liu hosi mehi iha rai Ejitu.
Anju nee dehan, “Hadeer ona! Lori Labarik nee ho Nia inan fila fali ba rai Israel, tanba ema nebee hakarak oho Labarik nee mate tiha ona.”
Entaun José hadeer i lori Labarik nee ho Nia inan fila fali ba Israel.
Maibee too iha nebaa, José rona katak liurai Herodes nia oan Arquelau mak ukun fali iha provinsia Judeia, nunee nia tauk atu fila ba nebaa. Maromak mos foo hanoin ba nia liu hosi mehi. Entaun sira baa hela fali iha provinsia Galileia,
iha aldeia ida naran Nazaré. Nunee buat nebee profeta sira uluk koalia akontese duni. Sira dehan, “Ema sei bolu Nia Nazaré oan.”<a href='#note-101' class='key'>✡</a>
Molok Jesus hahuu Nia knaar, João Sarani Nain komesa hanorin ema iha rai fuik maran iha rai Judeia.
Nia foo sai dehan, “Hakribi ona imi nia sala, tanba tempu besik ona atu Maromak ukun imi.”<a href='#note-102' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk liu Maromak nia profeta Isaias hakerek ona kona ba João dehan,
“Iha ema ida foo sai ho lian makaas iha rai fuik maran dehan,
‘Imi tenki hadia dalan para simu ita nia Nai.
Halo loos tiha dalan nebee kleuk para Nia lao tuir.’ ”<a href='#note-103' class='key'>✡</a>
João nia hena halo hosi kuda kamelu nia fulun, i nia sintu halo hosi animal nia kulit. Nia hahaan mak gafanhotu ho bani been.<a href='#note-104' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira foo sai sira nia sala, i João foo sarani sira iha mota Jordaun.
Iha mos ema barak hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu ho Saduseu mai atu João foo sarani sira. Maibee bainhira João haree sira, nia siak sira dehan, “He! Samea nia oan! Maromak sei kastigu imi tanba imi nia hahalok aat. Karik ema bosok imi dehan imi bele sarani para sees aan hosi kastigu nee.<a href='#note-105' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi tenki muda imi nia hahalok hodi hatudu katak imi husik duni imi nia sala.
I lalika hanoin dehan, imi loos ona tanba deit imi Abraão nia jerasaun. Lae! Hau hatete ba imi: fatuk sira nee mos, Maromak bele halo sai Abraão nia jerasaun.<a href='#note-106' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak hanesan toos nain nebee kaer hela baliu atu tesi ona ai huun too abut. Ai huun hotu-hotu nebee la foo fuan diak, Nia sei tesi tiha hodi soe ba ahi laran.<a href='#note-107' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau foo sarani imi ho bee deit para hatudu katak imi hakribi ona imi nia sala. Maibee la kleur tan, Ema ida boot liu hau sei mai. Atu lori deit Nia sandalias mos, hau la serve. Ema nee laos foo sarani imi ho bee, maibee Nia sei foo sarani imi hodi Espiritu Santu ho mos ahi.
Nia hanesan natar nain nebee prontu ona atu haketak hare isin ho hare kulit sira nee. Hotu tiha, hare isin Nia sei rai di-diak iha armazen, maibee kulit nia soe tiha ba ahi ida nebee nunka mate.”
Iha tempu nebaa Jesus mai hosi rai Galileia ba iha mota Jordaun para João foo sarani Nia.
Maibee João lakohi. Nia dehan, “Tuir lo-loos Ita Boot mak foo sarani hau. Nusaa mak Ita Boot mai fali iha hau?”
Jesus hataan, “Husik ba, agora nee ita mak foo sarani Hau para halo tuir Maromak nia hakarak.” João mos simu.
Sarani hotu tiha Jesus sai kedas hosi mota nee. Derepenti lalehan nakloke, i Nia haree Maromak nia Espiritu hanesan manu pombu tuun ba iha Nia.
Depois lian ida hosi lalehan hatete,
“Ida nee Hau nia Oan Doben.
Nia halo Hau nia laran haksolok teb-tebes.”<a href='#note-108' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha, Maromak nia Espiritu domina Jesus i lori Nia ba iha rai fuik maran atu diabu nia boot bele koko Nia.<a href='#note-109' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha nebaa Jesus jejun durante loron haat-nulu, kalan haat-nulu, too Nia hamlaha atu mate.
Depois diabu tentador mai koko Jesus. Diabu nee dehan, “Se O Maromak nia Oan duni, haruka fatuk sira nee sai paun.”
Maibee Jesus hataan, “Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek,
‘Ema kriatura laos moris hosi hahaan deit,
maibee presiza mos Maromak liafuan hotu-hotu.’ ”<a href='#note-110' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois diabu nia boot lori Jesus ba iha Jerusalém, Maromak nia sidade. Diabu lori Nia baa hamriik iha uma kreda boot nia tutun,
i dehan, “Se O Maromak nia Oan duni, soe aan tuun ba rai. Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan,
‘Maromak sei haruka Nia anju sira mai kuidadu O.’
‘Sira sei lolo liman hodi tane O, atu O nia ain la bele kona fatuk.’ ”<a href='#note-111' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Jesus hataan dehan, “Iha Livru Sagradu mos bandu ema dehan,
‘La bele koko Maromak, o nia Nai.’ ”<a href='#note-112' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois diabu nia boot lori tan Jesus ba iha foho ida aas teb-tebes nia tutun, i hatudu ba Jesus nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu tomak ho sira nia rikusoin hotu.
Diabu dehan ba Jesus, “Buat sira nee hotu hau sei foo ba O, naran katak O hakneak hodi adora hau.’ ”
Maibee Jesus hataan fali dehan, “Satanás, sai tiha hosi nee! Tanba iha Livru Sagradu haruka ema hotu-hotu nunee,
i serbi mak Nia deit.’<a href='#note-113' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha diabu nia boot husik tiha Jesus, i anju sira mai serbi Nia.
Iha loron ida, Jesus rona katak ema kaer tiha João Sarani Nain hodi baa dadur iha komarka. Nunee Jesus husik tiha provinsia Judeia baa fali iha provinsia Galileia.<a href='#note-114' class='key'>✡</a>
Too iha nebaa, Nia baa uluk iha Nia aldeia Nazaré, depois baa hela fali iha sidade Kafarnaum. Sidade nee iha tasi Galileia nia sorin, iha rai Zebulon ho Naftali.<a href='#note-115' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee Jesus halo tuir saida mak Maromak nia profeta Isaias hakerek nanis ona dehan,
“Rai Zebulon ho rai Naftali,
besik tasi Galileia, iha mota Jordaun nia sorin ba,
rai Galileia, ema nebee laos Judeu nia hela fatin.
Iha rai nee, ema uluk moris iha nakukun laran,
maibee agora sira hetan ona naroman boot.
Iha sira nia rain, uluk nakukun atu lori sira ba mate tinan ba tinan,
maibee agora naroman mosu ona hodi leno sira.”<a href='#note-116' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nebaa, Jesus komesa foo sai ba ema dehan, “Hakribi ona imi nia sala, tanba tempu besik ona atu Maromak ukun imi.”<a href='#note-117' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida Jesus lao hela iha tasi ibun Galileia nian. Nia haree peskador nain rua soe hela dai iha tasi. Sira nain rua nee maun-alin, maun naran Simão, ema mos bolu nia Pedro. Alin naran André.
Jesus dehan ba sira, “Mai tuir Hau! Imi uluk peskador ba ikan, maibee agora Hau sei hanorin imi atu sai peskador ba ema.”
Sira mos husik kedas sira nia dai hodi tuir Jesus.
Jesus lao nafatin, Nia haree tan ema nain rua, Tiago ho nia alin João. Sira nain rua hadia hela redi iha roo laran hamutuk ho sira nia aman Zebedeu. Jesus bolu tan sira nain rua atu tuir Nia.
Tiago ho João mos husik kedas sira nia aman ho sira nia roo hodi tuir Jesus.
Jesus lao iha provinsia Galileia tomak hodi hanorin iha ema Judeu sira nia uma kreda. Nia foo sai Liafuan Diak kona ba oinsaa Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. I ema nia moras oi-oin deit, Nia kura hotu kedas.<a href='#note-118' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat nebee Jesus halo, ema konta iha nebee-nebee too iha provinsia Síria tomak. Ema barak mai lori sira nia maluk nebee moras oi-oin, balu diabu tama iha laran, balu moras bibi maten, liman-ain mate ho moras selu-seluk tan. I Jesus kura moras sira nee hotu.
Ema barak teb-tebes mak tuir Jesus. Iha ema hosi Galileia, hosi rai Dekápolis, hosi sidade Jerusalém ho provinsia Judeia, balu tan mai hosi mota Jordaun nia sorin ba.
Iha loron ida Jesus haree ema barak mai hobur Nia, entaun Nia baa sae iha foho ida. Too iha nebaa Nia tuur, i Nia eskolante sira mai haleu Nia.
Depois Nia komesa hanorin sira.
Jesus hanorin nunee:
“Ema sira nebee hatene aan dehan sira presiza hela Maromak,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba sira nee Maromak nia reinu.
Ema sira nebee tanis ho laran susar, sira hetan bensaun,
tanba Maromak sei hamaran sira nia matan been.<a href='#note-119' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema sira nebee haraik aan,
Ema sira nebee hakarak teb-tebes atu moris loos,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba Maromak sei foo tuir sira nia hakarak nee.<a href='#note-121' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema sira nebee mak hatudu laran diak ba ema seluk,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba Maromak sei hatudu Nia laran diak ba sira.
Ema sira nebee laran moos,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba sira sei haree Maromak.<a href='#note-122' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema sira nebee gosta tulun ema seluk atu moris iha dame nia laran,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba Maromak sei bolu sira nee Nia oan.
Ema nebee hetan terus tanba moris tuir Maromak nia hakarak,
sira hetan bensaun, tanba sira nee Maromak nia reinu.<a href='#note-123' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira ema hatete aat imi i halo terus imi tanba imi tuir Hau, ka sira bobar lia tuun-sae hodi hatete aat imi nia naran tanba Hau, imi hetan bensaun.<a href='#note-124' class='key'>✡</a>
Kuandu ema halo imi terus nunee, simu ho haksolok i kontenti deit ba, tanba Maromak sei foo premiu boot ba imi iha lalehan. Keta haluha katak, Maromak nia profeta sira nebee moris iha tempu uluk mos, ema halo terus sira hanesan nee.”<a href='#note-125' class='key'>✡</a>
“Imi hanesan masin ba mundu. Maibee se masin nee sai miis ona karik, ita la bele halo meer fila fali, la iha folin tan ona. Ita soe tiha deit i ema sama.<a href='#note-126' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi mos hanesan ahi-oan nebee foo naroman ba mundu. Imi nia naroman hanesan sidade nebee mak harii iha foho leten, ema hotu-hotu bele haree.<a href='#note-127' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos bainhira ema sunu ahi-oan, nia nunka taka fali ho sanan. Maibee ahi-oan tenki tau iha fatin aas para bele foo naroman ba ema hotu nebee iha uma laran.<a href='#note-128' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nia moris mos tenki nunee, imi tenki sai naroman ba ema seluk atu nunee sira bele haree buat diak nebee imi halo. Nunee sira sei hahii imi nia Aman iha lalehan.”<a href='#note-129' class='key'>✡</a>
“La bele hanoin katak, Hau mai iha mundu nee atu halakon Moisés nia lei ho profeta sira nia liafuan. Lae! Hau mai laos atu halakon maibee atu kumpri lo-loos buat hotu-hotu nebee mak sira hakerek tiha ona.
Hau hatete lo-loos ba imi, bainhira lalehan ho rai sei iha, buat hotu nebee hakerek iha lei nee, buat kiik-oan ida mos sei la lakon, too buat hotu nebee Maromak hatete, sai realidade.<a href='#note-130' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, see mak kontra lei ruma tanba dehan lei nee kiik-oan deit, depois hanorin ema seluk atu lalika halo tuir, Maromak sei konsidera nia ema kiik liu iha Nia reinu. Maibee see mak moris tuir lei nee i hanorin ema seluk mos atu halo tuir, Maromak sei konsidera nia ema boot iha Nia reinu.
Hau dehan ba imi, imi tenki moris loos liu fali mestri relijiaun sira ho ema Farizeu sira. Se lae imi la bele tama iha Maromak nia reinu.”
Jesus hanorin nafatin Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Imi rona ona katak uluk ita nia bei-ala sira hetan lei ida nebee dehan, “La bele oho ema. See mak oho ema, nia sei hetan kastigu.’<a href='#note-131' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, ‘See mak hirus ema seluk, nia sei hetan kastigu. See mak hirus ema seluk too tolok, nia sei baa hataan iha tribunal. I see mak hirus ema seluk dehan, ‘O beik-teen’, ema nee lao dadauk ona ba iha ahi infernu.
Nunee, se o baa iha altar atu foo o nia oferta ba Maromak, maibee too iha nebaa o hanoin hetan ema ruma hirus o tanba o nia hahalok,
husik lai o nia oferta iha altar oin. Depois baa dame malu ho ema nee lai mak foin fila fali mai hodi foo oferta nee ba Maromak.
Se ema ruma atu lori o ba iha tribunal, diak liu molok too tribunal o dame malu kedan ho nia. Se lae ema nee bele entrega o ba iha juiz, juiz bele entrega o ba iha polisia, i polisia hatama o iha kadeia.
Hau dehan lo-loos ba o, o selu kotu tiha multa mak foin bele sai fali hosi kadeia.”
“Imi rona ona lei nebee dehan, ‘La bele halo sala seksual ho ema nia feen ka laen.’<a href='#note-132' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, se mane ida fihir feto ida hodi hanoin foer ba nia, mane nee halo ona sala seksual ho nia iha nia laran.
Se o nia matan sorin loos halo o monu ba sala karik, sukit sai o nia matan nee i soe tiha. Diak liu o moris ho matan sorin deit, duke o tama ba iha infernu ho matan kompletu.<a href='#note-133' class='key'>✡</a>
“Iha lei ida nebee dehan, ‘See mak hakarak soe nia feen, tenki halo surat deklarasaun ida foo ba nia.’<a href='#note-135' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, mane so bele soe nia feen kuandu nia feen halo ona sala seksual ho ema seluk. Se nia feen la sala ida, maibee mane nee soe nia, nee dehan katak, mane nee mak dudu nia feen atu halo sala seksual. Tanba se nia feen hola fali mane seluk, nee sala ona. I se mane ida kaben fali ho feto nebee nia laen soe tiha nee, mane nee mos halo sala seksual.”<a href='#note-136' class='key'>✡</a>
“Nunee mos imi rona ona katak, uluk ita nia bei-ala sira simu lei ida nebee dehan, ‘Buat nebee mak o jura ba Nai Maromak, o tenki halo tuir duni, la bele kontra fali.’<a href='#note-137' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, la bele halo juramentu saida deit. La bele jura temi lalehan, tanba lalehan nee fatin hodi Maromak tuur kaer ukun.<a href='#note-138' class='key'>✡</a>
La bele jura temi rai, tanba rai nee fatin hodi Maromak tau Nia ain. La bele jura temi Jerusalém, tanba Jerusalém nee Liurai Boot nia sidade.<a href='#note-139' class='key'>✡</a>
I la bele jura temi imi nia ulun rasik, tanba imi nia fuuk lahan ida mos, imi la bele halo metan ka halo mutin.
Entaun se imi promete atu halo buat ruma, dehan deit, ‘Sin, hau sei halo.’ Se lae, dehan deit, ‘Lae.’ Se imi aumenta tan para haforsa imi nia promesa, entaun liafuan sira nee mai hosi aat nain.”
“Imi rona ona lei nebee dehan, ‘Matan tenki selu ho matan, nehan tenki selu ho nehan.’<a href='#note-140' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, la bele halo aat fali ba ema nebee mak halo aat imi. Se ema ruma basa imi nia hasan sorin loos karik, foo tan hasan sorin ba nia.
Se iha ema ruma hakarak hadau imi nia faru, foo mos imi nia faru manas ba nia.
Se iha militar ruma mak obriga imi atu hulan nia sasaan lao too kilometru ida, kontinua lao ho nia too kilometru rua.
Se ema husu imi nia sasaan ruma, foo deit ba. Se ema hakarak empresta buat ruma hosi imi, foo empresta ba.”
“Imi rona ema dehan, ‘Hadomi o nia maluk, odi o nia inimigu.’<a href='#note-141' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Hau hatete ba imi, hadomi imi nia inimigu sira, i harohan para Maromak tulun ema nebee mak halo terus imi.
Se imi halo nunee, imi hatudu katak imi halo tuir imi nia Aman iha lalehan. Tanba Nia halo loro matan sae hodi foo naroman ba ema diak ho mos ema aat. I Nia foo udan ba ema nebee moris loos ho mos ema nebee moris iha sala laran.
Se imi hadomi deit ema nebee mak hadomi imi, imi atu manaan saida? Tanba kobrador impostu sira gosta han-matak ema maibee sira mos hadomi ema nebee mak hadomi sira.
Se imi kumprimenta deit imi nia maluk, imi nia hahalok nee diak liu ema seluk ka? Lae! Ema nebee la fiar Maromak mos halo ida nee.
Imi tenki laran diak teb-tebes, hanesan mos imi nia Aman iha lalehan laran diak.”<a href='#note-142' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hanorin nafatin nunee: “Kuidadu, keta foti aan hatudu imi nia hahalok diak iha ema nia oin atu sira bele haree. Se imi halo nunee, imi nia Aman iha lalehan sei la selu imi nia kolen.<a href='#note-143' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira o foo buat ruma ba ema kiak, la bele konta tuun-sae hanesan fali ema nebee buka oin. Sira sempre konta tuir sira nia diak iha uma kreda laran ho mos iha estrada ibun para ema bele gaba sira. Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, sira simu hotu ona sira nia kolen.
Maibee bainhira o foo buat ruma ba ema kiak, saida mak o nia liman loos foo, o nia liman karuk lalika hatene.
Nunee, o foo sub-subar deit. O nia Aman iha lalehan haree hotu saida mak ema halo sub-subar, i Nia sei selu o nia kolen.”
“Bainhira imi halo orasaun, la bele hanesan ema nebee buka oin. Sira gosta hamriik halo orasaun iha uma kreda laran ho mos iha estrada boot atu ema bele haree. Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, sira simu hotu ona sira nia kolen.<a href='#note-144' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee bainhira imi halo orasaun, tama iha kuartu laran, taka odamatan i halo orasaun ba imi nia Aman iha lalehan. Imi nia Aman nee, ema ida la haree. Maibee Nia haree hotu saida mak ema halo sub-subar, i Nia sei selu imi nia kolen.
Bainhira imi halo orasaun, la bele koalia fila ba fila mai hanesan fali jentiu sira, tanba sira hanoin dehan harohan ho liafuan naruk mak foin sira nia maromak simu.
La bele halo orasaun hanesan sira, tanba molok imi husu buat ruma ba imi nia Aman iha lalehan, Nia hatene uluk ona buat nebee mak imi presiza.
Nunee, halo orasaun hanesan nee:
“Ami nia Aman iha lalehan,
tulun ema atu foti aas Ita Boot nia naran santu.
Tulun ema iha mundu nee atu halo tuir Ita Boot nia hakarak,
hanesan sira iha lalehan mos halo tuir.
Foo ai haan natoon mai ami iha loron ida nee.
Perdua ami nia sala,
hanesan ami mos perdua ona ba ema nebee halo sala mai ami.
Keta husik ami atu monu ba tentasaun,
maibee hasai ami hosi buat aat.
[Ita Boot mak Liurai,
Ita Boot mak Kbiit Nain,
Ita boot mak serve atu ema hotu-hotu hahii,
too tinan ba tinan. Amen.]<a href='#note-145' class='key'>*</a>
Se imi perdua ema nebee mak halo sala hasoru imi, entaun imi nia Aman iha lalehan mos sei perdua imi nia sala.
Maibee se imi la perdua ema nebee mak halo sala hasoru imi, imi nia Aman mos sei la perdua imi nia sala.”<a href='#note-146' class='key'>✡</a>
“Bainhira imi halo jejun, la bele halo imi nia oin tristi hanesan fali ema sira nebee buka oin. Sira hatudu aan nunee para ema bele hatene katak sira jejun hela. Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, sira simu hotu ona sira nia kolen.
Maibee bainhira imi halo jejun, fasi imi nia oin halo moos i sui imi nia fuuk halo kabeer,
para ema nebee haree imi la nota katak imi jejun hela. So imi nia Aman iha lalehan mak hatene. Ema ida la haree Nia, maibee Nia haree hotu saida mak ema halo sub-subar, i Nia sei selu imi nia kolen.”
“La bele rai rikusoin mundu nian ba imi nia aan, tanba iha mundu nee nehek mutin bele haan, bele fuhuk tiha, i naok-teen bele tama baa foti.<a href='#note-147' class='key'>✡</a>
Diak liu rai rikusoin ba imi nia aan iha lalehan. Iha nebaa, nehek mutin la haan, la fuhuk, i naok-teen mos la tama baa foti.
Tanba imi nia rikusoin tau iha nebee, imi nia laran mos iha nebaa.”
“Imi nia matan hanesan ahi-oan nebee foo naroman ba imi nia aan tomak. Se imi nia matan haree moos, imi nia aan mos naroman.
Maibee se imi nia matan aat, imi nia aan mos sai nakukun tiha. I kuandu naroman nebee iha imi nia aan la iha ona, entaun imi nia moris nakukun teb-tebes.”
“La iha ema ida mak bele serbi patraun nain rua. Tanba nia sei odi ida, i hadomi ida seluk. Nia sei foo laran ba ida, i lakohi interese ida seluk. Nunee mos imi la bele serbi Maromak i serbi osan dala ida.
Tanba nee Hau hatete ba imi, lalika preokupa ho imi nia moris loro-loron, atu haan saida, ka atu hemu saida ka atu hatais saida. Ita nia moris folin liu hahaan, i ita nia isin lolon folin liu ropa.
Haree took manu fuik sira nebee semo iha leten nebaa. Manu sira nee la kuda batar, la silu batar, la rai hahaan iha armazen. Maibee imi nia Aman iha lalehan foo ai haan ba sira. Imi folin liu manu sira nee.
Se imi preokupa kona ba imi nia moris, nee bele aumenta imi nia tinan ka? Lae! Atu aumenta oras ida deit mos la bele.
Entaun nusaa mak imi preokupa kona ba imi nia ropa? Haree took ai funan nebee moris iha rai fuik nebaa. Ai funan nee la halo servisu, la soru tais.
Maibee Hau dehan ba imi, Liurai Salomão, maski riku teb-tebes, nia hatais kapaas halo nusaa mos, ai funan sira nee kapaas liu nafatin.
Duut nebee ohin loron matak iha rai fuik, aban ema soe fali ba ahi laran mos, Maromak halo furak. Saa tan imi! Nia sei foo ropa ba imi hatais. Entaun nusaa mak imi nia fiar fraku hanesan nee?!<a href='#note-148' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni, lalika preokupa dehan, ‘Ita atu haan saida?’ ka, ‘Ita atu hemu saida?’ ka, ‘Ita atu hatais saida?’
Hakaas aan liu-liu atu serbi Maromak nudar imi nia Liurai hodi moris loos iha Nia oin mak Maromak sei foo tan buat sira nee ba imi.
Entaun lalika preokupa kona ba loron aban, tanba loron aban nee preokupasaun ketak fali. Susar nebee ita hetan iha loron ida nee, too ona ba loron nee.”
Jesus hanorin nafatin Nia eskolante sira dehan, “La bele ansi foo sala ba ema, atu nunee Maromak la foo sala ba o.
Imi tetu ema seluk nia sala oinsaa, Maromak mos sei tetu imi nunee. I sasukat nebee mak imi uza ba ema seluk, Maromak sei uza fali sasukat nee ba imi.<a href='#note-149' class='key'>✡</a>
Nusaa mak o haree ai uut iha ema seluk nia matan, maibee ai kabelak nebee taka o nia matan rasik, o la senti?
Oinsaa mak o brani dehan ba o nia maluk, ‘Mai hau hasai tiha ai uut nee hosi o nia matan.’ Afinal iha ai kabelak ida taka hela o nia matan rasik.
Imi nee koalia oin seluk, hahalok oin seluk! Hasai tiha uluk ai kabelak iha o nia matan rasik, mak foin o haree hetan para bele hasai ai uut hosi o nia maluk nia matan.
Buat nebee Maromak nian, la bele foo ba ema nebee lakohi rona. Nee hanesan imi foo fali ba asu, ka foo buat murak-mean ba fahi. Se imi halo nunee, fahi sei sama tiha ba rai, i asu sei fila hodi ataka imi.”
“Husu beibeik ba Maromak,
Nia sei foo.
Buka beibeik,
o sei hetan.
Tuku beibeik odamatan,
odamatan sei nakloke ba o.”
Tanba see mak husu beibeik ba Maromak, nia sei simu. See mak buka beibeik, nia sei hetan. See mak tuku beibeik odamatan, Maromak sei loke ba nia.
Imi aman sira, bainhira imi nia oan husu paun, imi foo fali fatuk ka?
Se nia husu ikan, imi foo fali samea ka? Nunka!
Maski imi ema aat, maibee imi hatene foo buat diak ba imi nia oan sira. Saa tan imi nia Aman iha lalehan! Bainhira imi husu, Nia sei foo buat diak teb-tebes ba imi.”<a href='#note-150' class='key'>✡</a>
“Saida mak o hakarak atu ema seluk halo ba o, o mos tenki halo buat nee ba ema seluk. Ida nee mak Moisés nia lei ho profeta sira nia livru hanorin hori uluk kedas.”
“Atu tama ba moris rohan-laek, tenki liu hosi odamatan kloot. Tanba odamatan ba infernu luan, nia dalan mos fasil atu ema liu, i ema barak mak tama liu hosi odamatan nee.
Maibee odamatan atu tama ba moris rohan-laek kloot, nia dalan mos susar, i ema uitoan deit mak buka odamatan nee too hetan.”
“Kuidadu ho ema nebee bosok dehan, sira Maromak nia profeta. Sira finji maus hanesan bibi malae, afinal sira gosta estraga ema hanesan asu fuik.
Imi sei hatene sira hosi sira nia hahalok, hanesan ita hatene ai huun ida hosi nia fuan. Ai tarak nunka foo fuan fali uvas ka ai fuan figeira.
Ai huun nebee diak sei foo fuan nebee diak. I ai huun nebee la diak sei foo fuan nebee aat.
Ai huun diak la bele foo fuan nebee mak aat. I ai huun nebee aat la bele foo fuan diak.
Ai nebee mak la foo fuan diak, sei tesi tiha hodi soe ba ahi.<a href='#note-151' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos ho profeta falsu sira, imi bele konhese sira hosi sira nia hahalok.”<a href='#note-152' class='key'>✡</a>
“Ema barak bolu Hau dehan, ‘Nai, Nai!’ Maibee laos sira hotu-hotu mak sei tama ba Maromak nia reinu. So sira nebee moris tuir Hau nia Aman iha lalehan nia hakarak mak bele tama.
Iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, ema barak sei mai dehan, ‘Nai, Nai, ami uluk foo tutan Maromak nia lia tatoli hodi Nai nia naran. Ami mos temi Ita Boot nia naran hodi duni sai diabu hosi ema, i halo milagre oi-oin.’
“Ema nebee rona Hau nia liafuan nee i halo tuir, nia hanesan ema matenek ida nebee harii nia uma iha fatuk leten.
Depois udan boot mai, mota tuun, anin boot mos baku makaas uma nee. Maibee uma nee la monu, tanba harii metin iha fatuk leten.
Ema nebee rona Hau nia liafuan maibee la halo tuir, nia hanesan ema beik ida nebee harii nia uma iha rai henek leten.
Depois udan boot mai, mota tuun, anin boot mos baku makaas uma nee. I uma nee naksobu tiha too rai.”
Bainhira Jesus hanorin tiha hotu, ema barak nebee rona nee admira,
tanba Nia hanorin ho kbiit, la hanesan ho mestri relijiaun sira nia hanorin.<a href='#note-154' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus lao tuun mai hosi foho, ema lubun boot nee mos lao tuir Nia.
Derepenti ema ida moras lepra mai hakneak iha Jesus nia oin hodi husu tulun dehan, “Nai, Ita Boot iha kbiit atu kura hau nia moras hodi halo hau nia isin sai moos fali, naran katak Ita Boot hakarak.”
Jesus lolo liman ba tau iha nia isin hodi dehan, “Hau hakarak. O diak ona ba!” I ema nee nia isin moos kedas.
Depois Jesus dehan ba nia, “La bele konta sai buat nee ba ema seluk. Maibee baa aprezenta aan iha nai lulik, atu nia haree katak o nia isin moos ona. Depois foo oferta tuir lei Moisés nian, para ema hotu bele hatene katak o diak ona.”<a href='#note-155' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus tama ba iha sidade Kafarnaum. Iha nebaa, komandante Roma ida mai hasoru Jesus hodi husu tulun
dehan, “Nai, Hau nia atan mane ida moras todan iha uma. Nia la bele book aan hodi hadeer hosi toba fatin, nia terus atu mate.”
Jesus hataan, “Hau sei baa kura nia.”
Maibee komandante nee hataan fali dehan, “Nai, hau la serve atu simu Ita Boot iha hau nia uma. Nai foo deit orden ba moras nee mak moras nee sai hosi hau nia atan.
Hau hatene nunee tanba hau nia komandante sira mos iha kbiit atu foo orden mai hau. Nunee mos, hau iha kbiit atu foo orden ba hau nia soldadu sira. Se hau manda hau nia soldadu ida dehan, ‘Baa nebaa!’, nia mos baa. Se hau hatete, ‘Mai iha nee!’, nia mai. I se hau haruka hau nia atan dehan, ‘Halo ida nee!’, nia halo duni.”
Rona nunee, Jesus admira, i Nia hatete ba ema sira nebee tuir Nia, “Hau dehan lo-loos ba imi, Hau seidauk haree ema Israel ida nebee fiar makaas hanesan ema Roma nee.
Rona mai. Ema barak sei mai hosi fati-fatin, hosi lorosae-loromonu, sira sei mai tuur haan hamutuk ho Ita nia bei-ala Abraão, Isác ho Jacó iha Maromak nia festa boot iha lalehan.
Hori uluk Maromak hili ema Israel atu sai Nia reinu hodi tama iha nebaa. Maibee barak mak Nia sei soe sai ba iha fatin nakukun. Iha nebaa sira sei tanis hakilar i ruun nihan.”<a href='#note-156' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus dehan ba komandante nee, “Bele baa ona. Buat nebee ita fiar nee sei akontese duni.” Iha oras nee kedas komandante nia atan hetan fali isin diak.<a href='#note-157' class='key'>✡</a>
Loron ida, Jesus baa iha Pedro nia uma. Nia tama baa haree Pedro nia banin feto toba hela, tanba nia isin manas.
Jesus kaer nia liman, derepenti nia isin manas lakon tiha, i nia hadeer kedas baa prepara hahaan foo ba Jesus.
Bainhira kalan ona, ema barak mai lori sira nia maluk nebee mak diabu tama iha laran. Depois Jesus foo orden deit, diabu sira nee sai kedas. Nia mos kura ema moras hotu-hotu.
Nunee Nia halo tuir saida mak Maromak nia profeta Isaias hakerek nanis ona dehan,
“Nia rasik hasai ita nia moras.
Ita nia moras aat, Nia mak lori.”<a href='#note-158' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha loron ida, Jesus haree ema barak mai haleu Nia. Entaun Nia haruka Nia eskolante sira prepara roo para baa iha tasi sorin.
Jesus seidauk sae roo, mestri relijiaun ida mai dehan ba Nia, “Mestri, Ita Boot baa nebee deit, hau prontu atu tuir.”
Jesus hataan, “Asu fuik iha nia fatin hodi hela. Manu fuik mos iha nia knuuk. Maibee Hau, Mane Maksoin la iha fatin ida hodi tau Hau nia ulun ba.”
Iha tan ema ida nebee baibain tuir Jesus dehan ba Nia, “Nai, husik hau fila baa hakoi hau nia aman lai mak foin hau tuir Ita Boot.”<a href='#note-159' class='key'>*</a>
Hotu tiha Jesus sae roo, i Nia eskolante sira mos tuir Nia.
Iha tasi klaran derepenti anin boot mai, too laloran boot halo tasi been tama iha roo laran. Maibee Jesus dukur hela.
Nia eskolante sira fanu Nia dehan, “Nai, salva lai ami, ita atu mout ona!”
Jesus hataan, “Imi nee fiar fraku. Nusaa mak imi tauk hanesan nee?” Depois Nia hadeer hodi siak anin ho laloran boot nee. Anin para kedas, tasi mos hakmatek fali.
Nia eskolante sira admira dehan, “Ema nee see loos mak too anin ho laloran mos rona Nia?”
Depois Jesus too iha tasi sorin, iha ema Gadara<a href='#note-160' class='key'>†</a> sira nia rain. Iha nebaa, iha mane nain rua diabu tama iha sira nia laran. Sira nee siak loos, too la iha ema ida mak brani atu lao liu hosi nebaa. Sira sai mai hosi fatuk kuak nebee ema halo ba rate, i hasoru Jesus.
Sira hakilar dehan, “Maromak nia Oan, O hakarak halo saida mai ami? Tempu seidauk too mos, O atu kastigu ami ka?”
Iha momentu nebaa, iha fahi barak teb-tebes haan hela iha foho lolon, laduun dook hosi fatin nee.
Diabu sira husu fila-fila ba Jesus, “Se O atu duni sai ami karik, entaun haruka ami tama ba iha fahi sira nebaa.”
Jesus haruka sira dehan, “Baa ona!” Entaun diabu sira sai tiha hosi ema nain rua nee hodi tama fali iha fahi. Derepenti fahi sira nee halai saruntu malu tuun hosi foho nee, monu hotu ba tasi laran, i mout too mate hotu.
Haree nunee, fahi atan sira halai ba vila laran hodi konta sai kona ba ema nain rua nebee uluk diabu domina nee, ho mos istoria nee tomak.
Depois ema hotu sai mai hosi vila hasoru Jesus, i sira husu fila-fila atu Nia sai ona hosi rai nee.
Hotu tiha Jesus sae fali roo hodi fila ba tasi sorin, iha Nia sidade.
Iha nebaa, ema balu mai hulan mane ida liman-ain mate, latan hela iha nia toba fatin. Sira lori nia ba Jesus. Bainhira Jesus haree sira nia fiar, Nia dehan ba ema isin mate nee, “Oan, laran metin ba! O nia sala hamoos tiha ona.”
Mestri relijiaun sira rona liafuan nee, sira murmura dehan, “Ema nee foti aan hanesan fali Maromak.”
Maibee Jesus hatene hela sira nia hanoin, entaun Nia dehan, “Nusaa mak imi hanoin aat nunee?
Se Hau dehan ba ema nee katak, nia sala hamoos tiha ona, imi seidauk hatene, sai duni nunee ka lae. Maibee se Hau haruka nia hamriik ona hodi lao, imi bele haree ho matan.
Agora Hau sei hatudu mo-moos ba imi katak, iha mundu nee, Hau, Mane Maksoin iha kbiit hodi hamoos ema nia sala.” Depois Jesus hatete ba ema isin mate nee, “Hamriik ona! Foti o nia toba fatin hodi fila ba uma.”
Ema nee mos hamriik kedas hodi lao ba uma.
Ema barak haree buat nebee Jesus halo nee. Sira hakfodak ho tauk, i sira hahii Maromak tanba Nia foo tiha ona kbiit hanesan nee ba ema.
Depois Jesus husik tiha fatin nee. Nia lao dadauk, Nia hetan ema kobrador impostu ida naran Mateus, tuur hela iha nia servisu fatin. Jesus dehan ba nia, “Mai tuir Hau!” I Mateus hamriik hodi tuir Jesus.
Depois Jesus baa haan iha Mateus nia uma, i kobrador impostu barak ho ema aat sira seluk mai haan hamutuk ho Jesus ho Nia eskolante sira.
Ema hosi grupu relijiaun Farizeu sira haree, i sira husu ba Jesus nia eskolante sira, “Nusaa mak imi nia mestri haan hamutuk fali ho kobrador impostu ho ema aat sira nee?”<a href='#note-161' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee bainhira Jesus rona sira nia liafuan nee, Nia dehan, “So ema moras mak presiza doutor, ema isin diak lae.
Baa aprende di-diak Maromak nia liafuan nebee dehan, ‘Hau hakarak atu imi hatudu laran diak ba malu. Se lae imi lori sakrifisiu foo mai Hau mos la iha folin.’ Hau mai atu bolu ema ema aat sira, laos atu bolu ema nebee konsidera nia aan moris loos ona.”<a href='#note-162' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois João Sarani Nain nia eskolante sira mai husu Jesus nunee: “Ami nebee tuir João Sarani Nain halo jejun. Ema Farizeu sira nia eskolante sira mos hanesan. Maibee tansaa mak Ita Boot nia eskolante sira la jejun?”
Jesus hataan ho komparasaun dehan, “Hau hanesan noivu ida nebee halo festa kazamentu. Bainhira noivu sei hamutuk ho nia bainaka sira, sira la bele tristi. Maibee too iha loron ida, ema sei lori lakon tiha noivu nee. Iha loron nee mak nia bainaka sira sei jejun.
La iha ema ida uza hena foun hodi taka fali ba hena bosan nebee kuak. Se lae hena foun dada hamutuk sai kiik tiha too estraga fali hena bosan nee halo naklees liu tan.
Nunee mos ema halo tua, la tau iha tua fatin nebee halo hosi animal nia kulit nebee tuan ona. Tanba tua foun sempre nafurin sae, i sei halo kulit tuan nee nakfera tanba toos tiha ona. Nunee tua mos fakar sai. Tua foun, tenki tau iha tua fatin foun. Nunee tua fatin bele dura i tua mos la fakar sai.”<a href='#note-163' class='key'>*</a>
Entaun Jesus hamriik lao tuir responsavel nee, i Nia eskolante sira mos baa hamutuk ho Nia.
20-21 Iha dalan klaran, iha feto ida, nia fulan mai la para durante tinan sanulu resin rua. Feto nee hanoin nunee: “Naran katak hau kona kois deit Nia hena mos, hau nia moras sei diak.” Entaun nia bes-besik ba iha Jesus nia kotuk hodi kona Jesus nia hena rohan.
Jesus fila ba kotuk i haree feto nee hodi dehan, “Oan, laran metin ba! O hetan kura tanba o fiar mai Hau.” I nia moras diak kedas.
Bainhira Jesus too iha responsavel nia uma, Nia haree ema toka muzika mate nian i ema barak tanis halerik.
Jesus dehan ba sira, “Imi hotu sai. Menina nee la mate ida, nia toba deit.” Maibee sira hamnasa fali Nia.
Bainhira ema sira nee sai hotu, Jesus tama ba laran hodi kaer menina nee nia liman, i menina nee hadeer fali.
Buat nebee Jesus halo nee, ema konta lemo-lemo, too ema iha rejiaun nee tomak hatene.
Depois Jesus sai hosi fatin nee. Nia lao dadauk, iha ema matan delek nain rua lao tu-tuir Nia hodi bolu ho lian makaas dehan, “Liurai Davíd nia jerasaun, hadomi ami ba!”
Jesus tama iha uma laran, ema matan delek nain rua nee mos tama tuir Nia. Jesus husu ba sira dehan, “Imi fiar katak Hau bele kura imi nia matan ka?”
Sira hataan, “Ami fiar, Nai.”
Depois Jesus tau liman ba sira nia matan hodi dehan, “Tanba imi nia fiar mak imi hetan kura.”
Sira nain rua nia matan haree moos kedas. I Jesus bandu makaas sira dehan, “La bele foo hatene buat nee ba see-see deit.”
Maibee sira sai baa konta lemo-lemo kona ba Jesus iha rejiaun nee tomak.
Bainhira sira nain rua nee sai dadauk, ema lori tan sira nia maluk ida ba Jesus. Ema nee diabu domina ona too nia koalia la diak.
Jesus duni sai tiha diabu, ema nee bele koalia kedas. Ema barak nebee haree buat nee, sira hotu admira dehan, “Buat ida hanesan nee foin mak akontese iha rai Israel.”
Maibee ema Farizeu sira dehan, “Nia duni sai diabu tanba diabu nia xefi mak foo kbiit ba Nia.”<a href='#note-164' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus lao hosi sidade ba sidade ho aldeia ba aldeia hodi hanorin iha uma kreda laran. Nia foo sai Liafuan Diak kona ba oinsaa Maromak ukun nudar Liurai. I ema nebee moras oi-oin Nia kura tiha hotu.<a href='#note-165' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira Jesus haree ema barak nee, Nia hanoin loos sira, tanba sira la hatene atu halo oinsaa, i la iha ema ida atu tulun sira. Sira hanesan bibi malae nebee la iha bibi atan atu hatudu dalan ba sira.<a href='#note-166' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Jesus soe lia ba Nia eskolante sira dehan, “Batar iha toos laran maran tiha ona. Batar nee barak teb-tebes, maibee ema atu silu, uitoan deit.
Tanba nee harohan ba Toos Nain para haruka tan ema hodi silu batar nee.”<a href='#note-167' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-168' class='key'>✡</a>
1-2 Surat nee hosi hau, Pedro, nudar Jesus Kristu nia apostolu.
Hau hakerek surat nee ba imi hotu nebee mak Nai Maromak hili tiha ona. Imi sai ema lao rai, namkari iha fatin-fatin iha rai Pontus, Galásia, Kapadósia, Ázia ho mos Bitínia. Hori uluk kedas Aman Maromak hili tiha ona imi atu sai Nia ema para imi moris tuir Jesus Kristu nia hakarak. Jesus hisik Nia raan ba imi hodi hamoos imi nia sala. I Maromak nia Espiritu halo imi sai ema nebee moris loos.
Hau harohan para Nai Maromak loron ba loron hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi, i foo paz ho hakmatek ida ke boot teb-tebes ba imi.
Mai ita hahii Nai Maromak! Nia mak ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu nia Aman, i Jesus mos adora Nia. Nai Maromak hadomi teb-tebes ita, too Nia foo moris foun mai ita. Ita bele simu moris foun nee tanba Nia halo moris fali ona Jesus Kristu hosi mate. Nunee agora ita moris ho esperansa ida nebee metin
hodi hein atu simu rikusoin nebee mak Maromak prepara ona ba ita iha lalehan. Riku-soin nee nunka mohu, nunka dodok, i nunka menus.
Tanba imi nia fiar ba Nai Maromak, Nia sei kuidadu nafatin imi hodi Nia kbiit too imi simu salvasaun nebee Maromak prepara tiha ona atu hatudu sai bainhira mundu nee remata.
Tanba nee imi nia laran haksolok, maski iha imi nia moris agora imi laran susar tanba tenki hasoru tentasaun oi-oin, maibee tentasaun nee la kleur ida.
Imi hetan tentasaun nee para bele hatudu katak imi fiar metin duni ba Nai Maromak. Imi nia fiar nee bele kompara ho osan mean. Osan mean nee too loron ida sei aat. Maski la dura, maibee ita koko ho ahi. Saa tan imi nia fiar. Imi nia fiar folin aas liu fali osan mean. Nee mak Nai Maromak husik imi hasoru tentasaun para koko imi nia fiar nee. Se imi fiar nafatin, entaun aban-bainrua bainhira Jesus Kristu fila fali mai hosi lalehan iha ema hotu-hotu nia oin, Maromak sei gaba imi, respeita imi i foti aas imi nia naran.
Maski imi nia matan seidauk haree Jesus, maibee imi hadomi Nia. Maski imi seidauk haree Nia mos, imi fiar Nia. Imi nia laran haksolok liu too imi la hatene atu koalia oinsaa,
Nai Maromak nia profeta sira uluk foo sai ona katak Nai Maromak atu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi. Sira buka tu-tuir para bele hatene diak liu tan oinsaa mak Nai Maromak atu salva imi.
Iha momentu nebaa, Kristu nia Espiritu hela iha sira nia laran i foo hatene katak, aban-bainrua Kristu sei hetan terus mak foin Nai Maromak foti aas Nia. Entaun profeta sira buka hatene bainhira loos mak buat sira nee atu akontese i atu akontese oinsaa.
Kristu nia Espiritu foo hatene ba sira katak, buat nebee sira foo sai nee, laos sira mak atu haree, maibee imi mak sei haree. Liafuan Diak nebee profeta sira foo sai nee, ikus mai imi mos rona hosi ema seluk. Sira nee simu kbiit hosi Maromak Nia Espiritu hosi lalehan para haklaken Nia Liafuan Diak nee ba imi. Afinal anju sira mos hakarak teb-tebes atu hatene buat sira nee.
Tanba nee, matan moris neon nain hodi kompriende di-diak buat sira nee hotu. Imi tenki matan moos. I hein ho laran metin nafatin atu Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi bainhira Jesus Kristu fila fali mai iha ema hotu-hotu nia oin.
Imi tenki rona di-diak Nai Maromak, hanesan labarik ida rona nia inan-aman. La bele halo tuir fali imi nia hakarak aat uluk nian bainhira imi seidauk konhese Nai Maromak.
Nia bolu ona imi atu sai Nia ema, i Nia nee laran moos. Nunee iha imi nia moris tomak, imi mos tenki moris ho laran moos.
Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek nunee: “Imi tenki moris ho laran moos, tanba Hau laran moos.”<a href='#note-1381' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira imi halo orasaun, imi bolu Nai Maromak imi nia Aman. Ida nebee imi bolu Aman nee sei tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia tuir ida-idak nia hahalok, Nia la fihir ba ema. Tanba nee imi tenki hamtauk ho respeita Nia iha imi nia moris nudar ema lao rai iha mundu nee.
Uluk imi moris tuir dalan nebee mak imi nia bei-ala sira hatudu hela ba imi, i dalan nee la iha folin. Maibee imi hatene katak Kristu selu kotu ona hodi hasai imi hosi imi nia moris ida uluk nee. Nia laos selu imi nia moris nee ho buat ruma nebee too ikus sei mohu, hanesan osan mean ka osan mutin.
Maibee Nia selu ho Nia raan rasik. Nia raan nee folin karun teb-tebes! Kristu mate hanesan bibi malae oan nebee ema oho hodi halo sakrifisiu ba Nai Maromak. Nia sai sakrifisiu ida ke moos loos, sala uitoan mos la iha.
Uluk liu, molok Nai Maromak halo mundu nee, Nia hili tiha ona Kristu atu selu kotu imi. Agora, mundu besik atu remata ona, foin Nai Maromak haruka Kristu mai para tulun imi.
Liu hosi Kristu mak imi fiar ba Nai Maromak. Tanba Maromak halo moris fali ona Kristu hosi mate hodi foti aas Nia, atu ita fiar ba Nia, i laran metin ba Nia promesa.
Imi hamoos ona imi nia aan hodi hatudu imi nia domin lo-loos ba maluk sarani sira, tanba imi moris tuir buat nebee mak loos. Agora hau husu atu imi hadomi malu nafatin ho fuan ho laran,
tanba imi hetan ona moris foun. I moris foun nee, laos mai hosi ema nebee la kleur tan sei mate, maibee hosi Nai Maromak, imi nia Aman nebee moris tinan ba tinan. Moris foun nee imi hetan liu hosi Maromak nia liafuan, tanba Nia liafuan nee iha nafatin too tinan ba tinan hodi foo moris ba ita ema.
Iha Livru Sagradu dehan nunee:
“Ema hotu-hotu hanesan duut.
Sira nia furak hanesan ai funan nebee moris iha rai fuik.
Duut sei namlaik, nia funan sei monu ba rai.
Maibee Nai Maromak nia liafuan iha nafatin.”
Nia liafuan nee mak Liafuan Diak nebee ema foo sai tiha ona ba imi.<a href='#note-1382' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee, soe tiha hahalok aat hotu-hotu! La bele bosok, la bele koalia oin ida hahalok oin seluk, la bele laran moras ba ema, i la bele hatete aat ema seluk.
Hanesan bebee ida nebee foin moris hamrook atu susu, nunee mos imi tenki hamrook ba Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Tanba Nia liafuan hanesan susu been diak nian ba imi nia klamar, halo imi loron ba loron buras ba beibeik, too imi hetan salvasaun.
Tanba imi senti ona Ita nia Nai nia laran diak.<a href='#note-1383' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus Kristu hanesan fatuk isin nebee moris. Ema lakohi simu fatuk nee, maibee Maromak hili Nia i konsidera Nia folin teb-tebes. Imi hakbesik ona ba Jesus Kristu.
Nunee imi ida-ida mos hanesan fatuk isin nebee moris, i Maromak hada dadauk imi hotu too imi hamutuk sai uma ida para Nia Espiritu hela. Maromak mos halo imi sai hanesan nai lulik nebee moris ho laran moos hodi foo sakrifisiu espiritual ba Nia. I sakrifisiu nee Nia simu ho haksolok, liu hosi Jesus Kristu.
Tanba iha Livru Sagradu Nai Maromak dehan,
“Haree ba! Hau tau hela fatuk ida
iha sidade Siaun.
Fatuk nee folin boot teb-tebes,
See mak fiar ba Nia
sei la moe.”<a href='#note-1384' class='key'>✡</a>
Fatuk nee mak Jesus Kristu. Nia folin boot ba imi nebee fiar Nia. Maibee ba ema nebee la fiar, Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan,
“Fatuk ida nebee badaen sira lakohi uza hodi halo uma,
agora sai fali fatuk nebee prinsipal iha uma nee.”<a href='#note-1385' class='key'>✡</a>
I hakerek mos nunee:
“Fatuk nee halo ema sidi,
i halo sira monu.”<a href='#note-1386' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira sidi iha fatuk nee tanba sira lakohi rona Nai Maromak nia liafuan. I Nai Maromak mos desidi nanis ona atu sira sai nunee.
Maibee imi nee laos nunee. Imi nee Nai Maromak hili tiha ona hodi sai Nia povu. Imi hanesan nai lulik nebee mak serbi liurai. Imi hanesan nasaun ida nebee moris loos. Imi Maromak nia povu. Maromak hili imi nunee para imi bele konta sai buat diak nebee mak Maromak halo tiha ona ba imi. Tanba Nia mak bolu imi sai hosi nakukun hodi tama ba iha Nia naroman ida nebee furak teb-tebes.<a href='#note-1387' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk imi laos Nai Maromak nia povu, maibee agora imi sai tiha ona Nia povu. Uluk imi seidauk hatene Maromak nia domin, maibee agora imi hatene ona.<a href='#note-1388' class='key'>✡</a>
Maluk doben sira, imi nee ema lao rai deit, imi hela iha mundu nee la kleur ida. Tanba nee hau husu atu imi hadook aan tiha hosi imi nia hakarak nebee aat, tanba imi nia hakarak aat sempre halo funu hasoru imi nia aan.
Imi tenki hakaas aan para moris loos iha jentiu sira nia oin. Nunee, se sira duun matak imi, sira bele haree deit imi nia hahalok diak, i bainhira Jesus fila fali mai hosi lalehan, jentiu sira nee sei foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran.
Ita nia Nai Jesus hakarak imi tenki hakruuk ba ukun nain hotu-hotu iha mundu nee. Imi tenki hakruuk ba liurai, tanba nia mak ukun nain nebee boot liu.
Hakruuk mos ba ukun nain sira seluk, tanba liurai foti sira para kastigu ema nebee mak halo aat i gaba ema nebee mak hahalok diak.
Tanba Nai Maromak hakarak para imi halo buat nebee diak, atu ema beik-teen sira nebee mak la hatene buat ida, la iha liafuan ida atu koalia hasoru imi.
Imi simu ona liberdade hosi Maromak. Nunee imi tenki moris hanesan ema nebee livre ona. La bele uza imi nia liberdade nee hodi taka fali imi nia hahalok aat, maibee moris hanesan Maromak nia atan.
Hatudu respeitu ba ema hotu-hotu, hadomi imi nia maluk sarani sira, hamtauk Nai Maromak, i respeita liurai.
Atan sira, hakruuk ba imi nia patraun, i respeita sira. La bele hakruuk deit ba patraun nebee mak laran diak i ibun midar. Maibee hakruuk mos ba patraun nebee mak siak-teen.
Tanba se ema kastigu imi maski imi la sala, i depois imi aguenta ho pasiensia nafatin tanba imi hanoin Maromak, entaun imi nia hahalok nee halo haksolok Maromak nia laran.
Se karik imi halo sala mak ema baku, i imi simu terus nee ho pasiensia, imi manaan saida? Maibee se imi hetan terus tanba halo buat diak, depois imi aguenta, ida nee mak halo haksolok Maromak nia laran.
Maromak bolu imi para moris nunee, tanba Kristu mos terus ba imi. Nunee Nia sai ezemplu atu imi lao tuir nia ain fatin.
Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek nunee:
“Nia nunka halo sala.
Liafuan bosok nunka sai hosi Nia ibun.”<a href='#note-1389' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira ema tolok Nia, Nia la hataan. Bainhira ema halo Nia terus, Nia la ameasa atu halo aat fali sira. Maibee Nia entrega Nia Aan ba Nai Maromak nia liman, tanba Maromak mak tesi lia ho lo-loos.<a href='#note-1390' class='key'>✡</a>
Kristu rasik mak lori ita nia sala iha ai krus leten para ita bele livre hosi sala hodi moris loos. Nia kanek nee mak kura ona imi.<a href='#note-1391' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk imi hanesan bibi malae nebee mak lao sala dalan. Maibee agora imi fila fali ona ba imi nia Bibi Atan, i Nia mak tau matan ba imi.
1-2 Hanesan ita hotu tenki hakruuk ba ita nia ukun nain sira, nunee mos imi feen sira tenki hakruuk ba imi nia laen. Nunee se imi nia laen sira la fiar ba Maromak nia liafuan karik, sira bele haree imi nia moris nebee hatudu laran moos ho respeitu. Too ikus sira mos bele fiar, laos hosi imi nia liafuan, maibee hosi imi nia hahalok nee.<a href='#note-1392' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee buat nebee mak halo imi feto sira sai furak mak imi nia laran. Feto nebee laran maus ho kalma, sira nee mak furak ba nafatin, i Maromak mos foo folin ba sira nia hahalok nee.
Feto sira nebee uluk moris ho laran moos hodi laran metin ba Maromak, sira nia furak mos nunee. Sira hakruuk ba sira nia laen,
hanesan Sara. Nia rona nia kaben Abraão hodi respeita nia too bolu nia “patraun”. Imi mos sai hanesan Sara nia oan, se imi halo buat nebee mak loos i la tauk buat ida.<a href='#note-1394' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos imi laen sira. Imi tenki uza matenek oinsaa mak atu moris hamutuk ho imi nia feen. Hatudu imi nia respeitu ba sira tanba imi kompriende katak sira nia forsa la hanesan imi nian, i imi hamutuk sei simu moris rohan-laek tanba Maromak nia laran diak ba imi. Halo nunee para Maromak rona nafatin imi nia orasaun.<a href='#note-1395' class='key'>✡</a>
Agora hau husu para imi hotu neon ida laran ida, hadomi imi nia maluk sarani sira, hatudu laran maus ba malu i haraik aan.
Se ema ruma halo aat ba imi, la bele halo aat fali ba sira. Se ema ruma hatete aat imi, la bele hatete aat fali sira, maibee harohan atu Nai Maromak halo buat diak ba sira. Tanba Nai Maromak bolu imi atu halo nunee para imi mos hetan bensaun hosi Nia.
Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan,
“Ema nebee mak buka moris diak,
i buka moris naruk,
nia tenki kuidadu nia ibun para la bele koalia aat,
i la bele koalia bosok.
Nia tenki fila kotuk ba buat aat
hodi halo buat nebee diak.
Nia tenki hakaas aan atu moris dame malu ho ema hotu-hotu,
i buka nafatin dame too hetan.
Tanba Nai Maromak tau matan ba ema nebee mak moris loos,
Nia see tilun ba sira nia orasaun.
Maibee Nai Maromak kontra ema nebee mak halo aat.”<a href='#note-1396' class='key'>✡</a>
Se imi hakaas aan halo buat nebee diak, ema atu halo aat imi ka?
Maibee bele mos akontese. I se imi halo duni buat nebee loos mak ema halo terus imi, entaun imi sorti boot. Se nunee, la bele tauk ema i la bele hanoin barak.<a href='#note-1397' class='key'>✡</a>
Respeita ho tauk mak Kristu, tanba imi tau tiha ona Kristu iha imi nia laran nudar imi nia Nai.
Se ema ruma husu imi, tanba saa mak imi laran metin ba Nai Maromak, imi tenki prontu hataan. Maibee hataan ho liafuan mamar ho respeitu.<a href='#note-1398' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nia laran tenki moos. Karik ema balu koalia aat imi hodi kritika buat diak nebee mak imi halo tanba imi tuir Kristu. Maibee se imi halo diak nafatin, too ikus sira rasik moe ba sira nia liafuan nee.
Se Nai Maromak hakarak para ita hetan terus tanba halo buat diak, ida nee diak liu duke hetan terus tanba halo buat aat.
Kristu mate dala ida deit
tanba ita ema nia sala.
Ida nebee moris loos mate ba sala nain sira
para lori imi ba Nai Maromak.
Nudar ema nebee iha isin ho raan, ema oho tiha Nia,
Maromak nia Espiritu mos foo kbiit ba Kristu hodi baa foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan ba matebian sira nebee sei dadur hela.
Sira nee mak uluk lakohi halo tuir Nai Maromak nia liafuan iha Noé nia tempu. Bainhira Noé halo roo boot, Nai Maromak hein ho pasiensia para ema sira nee hakribi sira nia sala, maibee sira lakohi arepende. Too ikus bee sae, i ema nain walu deit mak hetan salvasaun iha roo laran.<a href='#note-1399' class='key'>✡</a>
Bee boot nee hanesan ezemplu kona ba batizmu, tanba agora nee batizmu mak foo salvasaun ba imi. Bainhira imi simu batizmu, bee nee laos atu hasai foer iha imi nia isin, maibee bee nee signifika katak, imi harohan para Nai Maromak hamoos imi nia neon ho laran. Batizmu nee bele foo salvasaun ba imi tanba Jesus Kristu moris fali ona hosi mate.
Agora Nia sae tiha ona ba lalehan hodi tuur iha Nai Maromak nia sorin loos. I anju sira ho espiritu bo-boot sira nebee kaer ukun, sira hotu-hotu hakruuk ba Nia.
Bainhira Kristu sei iha mundu, Nia hetan terus ho susar oi-oin. Entaun imi mos tenki prontu simu terus, tanba ema nebee mak terus iha nia moris, nia la halo tan sala.
Nunee, agora ba oin imi nia moris iha mundu nee sei tuir deit Nai Maromak nia hakarak, imi nia hakarak rasik imi la tuir tan ona.
Tanba uluk imi soe tempu barak hodi moris hanesan ema nebee la konhese Nai Maromak. Iha tempu nebaa imi moris la hatene moe, imi kaan atu halo sala seksual, imi sai lanu-teen, i halo festa hemu lanu too halo arbiru tuun-sae. Imi mos adora lulik, maski adora lulik nee halo Nai Maromak hakribi.
Agora ema nebee la konhese Maromak, sira la kompriende nusaa mak imi la halo tuir ona sira nia hahalok aat oi-oin nee, i sira hatete aat imi.
Maibee aban-bainrua sira tenki hataan iha Nai Maromak nia oin. Nia prontu atu tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, atu ema nebee mak mate tiha ona ka ema nebee mak sei moris.
Tanba nee mak uluk Jesus baa foo sai Liafuan Diak ba ema nebee mate tiha ona. Nunee maski nudar ema sira hetan kastigu iha mundu nee, maibee aban-bainrua sira nia klamar bele moris hamutuk ho Nai Maromak.
Mundu nee besik remata ona. Tanba nee imi tenki hanoin klean i domina aan para bele halo orasaun ho diak.
Importante liu tan mak imi tenki hadomi malu ho laran tomak. Tanba bainhira ita hadomi malu, ita hatene perdua ita nia maluk, maski nia halo sala barak hasoru ita.<a href='#note-1400' class='key'>✡</a>
Simu ema seluk iha imi nia uma ho laran haksolok.
Nai Maromak foo kbiit ba imi ida-idak la hanesan. Uza di-diak kbiit nebee Nia foo ba imi nee hodi serbi ema seluk.
See mak hetan kbiit para koalia, nia tenki koalia liafuan hosi Maromak. I see mak hetan kbiit para serbi ema seluk, nia tenki serbi ho forsa tomak nebee nia hetan hosi Maromak. Se imi halo nunee, ema sei haree katak imi halo buat hotu-hotu tanba Jesus Kristu, i sira sei hahii Nai Maromak. Mai ita foti aas Nia naran too tinan ba tinan. Nia ukun la hotu la remata. Amen.
Maluk doben sira, agora dadauk imi terus hela, i terus nee koko imi. La bele hakfodak, i la bele hanoin dehan ema nebee fiar Nai Maromak sei la hetan terus.
Maibee haksolok ba, tanba imi bele hetan terus hanesan Kristu uluk mos terus. Se imi haksolok nunee, aban-bainrua bainhira ema hotu-hotu haree Jesus Kristu fila fali mai ho naroman lalehan nian, imi sei haksolok liu tan.
Bainhira ema hatete aat imi tanba imi fiar ba Kristu, imi sorti boot, tanba Espiritu naroman lalehan nian hela iha imi. Espiritu nee mak Maromak nia Espiritu.
Keta halo be imi terus tanba imi sai oho-door, ka naok-teen, ka halo buat aat saida deit, ka sai ema nebee mete ema nia moris.
Maibee se imi hetan terus tanba imi sai Kristaun, la bele moe. Diak liu imi hahii Nai Maromak tanba imi lori Kristu nia naran.
Tempu too ona atu Nai Maromak tesi ema nia lia. Nia sei foo justisa uluk ba Nia oan sira. Se ita mos hetan justisa, saa tan ema nebee mak lakohi rona Maromak nia Liafuan Diak! Sira nia kastigu sei todan.
Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan,
“Se ema nebee moris loos mos susar atu hetan salvasaun,
saa tan ema nebee la interese Maromak hodi moris iha sala nia laran!”<a href='#note-1401' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun se imi terus tanba Nai Maromak hakarak nunee, imi tenki halo nafatin buat nebee mak diak hodi entrega imi nia aan tomak ba Nia, tanba Nia mak imi nia Kriador i Nia sempre halo tuir Nia promesa.
Agora hau hakerek ba responsavel sarani sira. Hau mos responsavel sarani hanesan imi. Hau rasik akompanha Kristu nia terus. I aban-bainrua bainhira ema hotu-hotu haree Kristu fila fali mai ho naroman lalehan nian, hau mos sei simu naroman lalehan nee. Hau husu ba imi responsavel sira,
tau matan di-diak ba ema nebee mak Nai Maromak entrega ona ba imi, hanesan bibi atan nebee tau matan ba nia bibi sira. Haree di-diak sira, laos tanba imi nia obrigasaun, maibee hosi imi nia laran, tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak. Imi la bele servisu hanesan ema nebee mak hakarak manaan osan deit, maibee tenki servisu ho badinas hodi serbi sarani sira.<a href='#note-1402' class='key'>✡</a>
La bele foti aan hodi manda tuun-sae sarani sira nebee mak Nai Maromak foo ba imi atu tau matan. Maibee imi tenki sai ezemplu nebee diak para sira bele halo tuir.
Se imi halo nunee, aban-bainrua bainhira bibi atan sira nia Xefi fila fali mai, imi sei simu premiu naroman lalehan nian, i premiu nee dura ba nafatin.
“Nai Maromak kontra ema nebee mak foti aan,
maibee Nia hatudu Nia laran diak ba ema nebee mak haraik aan.”<a href='#note-1403' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee haraik aan ba Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain, para bainhira too iha nia tempu, Nia foti aas imi.<a href='#note-1404' class='key'>✡</a>
La bele preokupa ba imi nia problema, maibee entrega hotu ba Nai Maromak, tanba Nia sempre tau matan ba imi.
Matan moris neon nain, tanba imi nia inimigu diabu nia boot hakarak estraga imi, hanesan leaun nebee mak lao baa-mai ho lian makaas hodi buka ema atu haan.
Imi tenki hamriik firmi hasoru nia hodi kaer metin imi nia fiar, tanba imi hatene katak imi nia maluk sarani sira iha mundu tomak mos hetan terus hanesan imi.
Maski agora imi terus, maibee la kleur tan Nai Maromak rasik sei halo imi diak fila fali. Nia sei foo forsa ba imi, i halo imi hamriik metin hodi aguenta nafatin. Tanba Nia sempre hatudu Nia laran diak ba ita ema i Nia rasik mak bolu imi atu simu Nia kbiit ho naroman lalehan nian too tinan ba tinan, hamutuk ho Kristu.
Maromak deit mak iha kbiit hodi ukun buat hotu-hotu too tinan ba tinan. Amen.
Silas mak ajuda hau hakerek surat badak nee. Nia nee ita nia maluk sarani nebee hau konfia.<a href='#note-1405' class='key'>*</a> Hau hakerek surat nee ba imi para hametin imi nia laran, i foo sasin lo-loos kona ba Maromak nia laran diak. Hamriik metin ba, i la bele fila kotuk ba Nia laran diak nee.
Sarani sira hosi Babilónia foo kumprimentus ba imi. Nai Maromak hili sira hanesan mos Nia hili imi. Marcos mos foo kumprimentus. Hau haree nia hanesan hau nia oan rasik.<a href='#note-1406' class='key'>✡</a>
Kumprimenta malu ho domin. Hau harohan para imi hotu nebee fiar ba Kristu bele moris iha paz ho hakmatek.
Surat nee hosi hau, Simão Pedro, nudar Jesus Kristu nia atan ho mos Nia apostolu.
Hau hakerek surat nee ba imi nebee simu tiha ona fiar ida ke folin boot, hanesan mos ami. Imi simu fiar nee tanba Jesus Kristu sempre halo buat nebee mak loos. Nia mak ita nia Maromak ho ita nia Salvador.
Hau harohan para Nai Maromak loron ba loron hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi i foo paz ho hakmatek ida ke boot teb-tebes ba imi. Imi sei simu buat sira nee tanba imi konhese ona Nai Maromak i konhese mos ita nia Nai Jesus.
Ita konhese ona Nai Maromak. Tanba nee, hosi Nia kbiit rasik Nia foo mai ita saida deit mak ita presiza atu ita bele moris loos tuir Nia hakarak. Nia mos bolu ona ita sai Nia ema, tanba Nia mak boot teb-tebes i diak liu.
Hosi Nia boot ho Nia diak nee mak Nia foo mai ita promesa nebee boot ho folin teb-tebes. Hodi Nia promesa nee mak ita bele livre tiha hosi hakarak aat hotu-hotu nebee estraga ema mundu nee nia moris, i ita nia laran bele sai hanesan fali Maromak nian.
Tanba nee imi tenki hakaas aan moris loos para halo kompletu imi nia fiar. Moris loos mos seidauk too, imi presiza hatene tan saida mak loos i saida mak sala.
Laos atu hatene deit, imi mos tenki domina aan i hatene aguenta nafatin para la bele hakiduk. Esforsa aan mos atu moris halo tuir Maromak nia hakarak.
Laos nee deit, imi mos tenki laran diak ba imi nia maluk sarani sira, i hatudu domin ba ema hotu-hotu.
Se hahalok diak sira nee hotu buras ba beibeik iha imi nia moris, entaun imi sei konhese diak liu tan ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu, i imi nia moris iha folin i la saugati.
Maibee se ema ruma la moris tuir buat diak sira nee, entaun nia la haree saida mak iha nia oin, nia hanesan fali ema matan delek. Nia haluha katak Maromak hamoos tiha ona nia sala uluk nian.
Nunee maun-alins sira, sai badinas liu tan para hahalok diak sira nee buras iha imi nia moris. Hahalok nee hatudu katak Maromak hili tiha ona imi i bolu tiha ona imi para sai Nia ema. Se imi moris nunee, imi sei la monu,
i aban-bainrua Nai Maromak sei simu imi ho laran tomak hodi tama iha Jesus Kristu nia reinu. Jesus Kristu mak ita nia Nai ho ita nia Salvador, i Nia ukun la hotu la remata.
Imi hatene buat sira nee ona, imi mos hamriik metin ona tanba imi fiar ba buat nebee mak loos. Maski nunee maibee hau hakarak foo hanoin fila-fila ba imi.
Hau hanoin hau iha obrigasaun para foo hanoin buat sira nee ba imi durante hau sei moris iha mundu.
Tanba hau hatene katak la kleur tan hau sei mate, tuir saida mak ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu foo sai tiha ona ba hau.
Nunee hau hakaas aan para foo hatene buat sira nee ba imi para aban-bainrua hau mate husik hela imi, imi la bele haluha.
Uluk ami foo sai ba imi katak ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu sei fila fali mai hosi lalehan ho kbiit boot. Momentu nebaa ami laos konta tuir ai knanoik nebee mak ema inventa. Maibee ami rasik haree Nia kbiit nee ho matan,
17-18 bainhira ami hamutuk ho Nia iha Maromak nia foho. Iha nebaa Aman Maromak rasik foo respeitu i foti aas Jesus nia naran iha ami nia oin. Ami rona Maromak Aas Liu nia lian tuun mai hosi lalehan dehan, “Nee Hau nia Oan doben. Nia halo haksolok Hau nia laran.”<a href='#note-1407' class='key'>✡</a>
Liu-liu imi tenki hatene katak, profeta sira nia lia tatoli nebee hakerek iha Livru Sagradu, laos mai hosi sira nia matenek rasik.<a href='#note-1408' class='key'>*</a>
Tanba profeta sira nia lia tatoli nunka mai hosi ema mundu nee nia hakarak. Maibee sira hatoo liafuan hosi Maromak tuir saida mak Espiritu Santu hatudu ba sira.
Uluk profeta falsu mosu iha povu Israel nia leet. Nunee mos agora, iha mestri falsu iha hela imi nia leet. Sira taka falta hodi hanorin lia falsu too nega mos ita nia Nai Jesus. Afinal Nia mak sosa kotu tiha sira. Derepenti mestri sira nee sei rahun hotu. I se imi halo tuir sira, imi mos sei rahun.
Maski nunee, ema barak sei tuir mestri falsu sira nee hodi halo arbiru too la hatene moe. Bainhira ema seluk haree sira nia hahalok aat nee, sira sei hamnasa fali Maromak nia dalan loos.
Mestri falsu sira nee matan osan liu. Sira inventa istoria tuun-sae para han-matak imi. Maibee hori uluk kedas Maromak desidi ona atu kastigu sira, i la kleur tan sira sei rahun.
Hanoin took! Uluk bainhira anju balu halo sala, Maromak la haluha kastigu sira. Nia soe sira ba dadur iha rai kuak nakukun. Iha nebaa sira hein hela too Maromak foo justisa ba sira.
Nunee mos Maromak la haluha kastigu ema sira nebee moris iha Noé nia tempu uluk. Iha tempu nebaa Maromak halo rai nabeen hodi halo mate ema hotu nebee la interese Nia. Maromak salva deit Noé ho nia familia ema nain hitu. Noé nee ema ida nebee moris loos, i hanorin mos ema seluk para moris loos.<a href='#note-1409' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos povu sidade Sodoma ho Gomora. Nai Maromak kastigu sidade rua nee ho ahi too sai tiha ahu kdesan hotu. Nee hanesan ezemplu ida hodi hatudu katak, Maromak sei foo kastigu todan ba ema nebee mak la interese Nia.<a href='#note-1410' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu nebaa Maromak salva deit Ló. Ló nee ema ida ke moris loos, i nia laran tristi teb-tebes tanba povu kontra buat nebee mak loos hodi moris iha sala foer nia laran.<a href='#note-1411' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski Ló moris loos, maibee nia moris iha ema aat sira nia leet. Loro-loron nia haree i rona beibeik sira nia hahalok aat nee, halo nia laran susar teb-tebes.
Ezemplu hirak nee hatudu katak, Nai Maromak hatene salva ema nebee mak halo tuir Nia hakarak, bainhira sira hasoru tentasaun. Nia mos hatene foo kastigu ba ema nebee mak moris la loos. I Nia dadur nafatin sira too tempu atu Nia tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia.
Kastigu nebee todan liu sei monu ba ema nebee toman halo buat foer tuir sira nia hakarak aat i lakohi rona see-see deit mak ukun iha lalehan ka iha rai.
Mestri falsu sira nee la tauk ema ida. Sira foti aan liu, too sira mos brani atu koalia aat Maromak nia anju sira.
Afinal anju sira nee boot liu i forsa liu mestri falsu sira. Maski nunee anju sira la foo sala ba mestri sira nee hodi koalia aat sira iha Nai Maromak nia oin.
Maibee mestri falsu sira nee gosta koalia aat buat nebee mak sira rasik la kompriende. Sira hanesan animal nebee mak la iha neon maibee tuir deit sira nia hakarak rasik. Sira hanesan animal nebee too ikus tama ba lasu i rahun.
Maromak sei foo terus ba sira tuir terus nebee mak sira foo ona ba ema seluk. Mestri falsu sira nee, iha loron manas boot mos halo festa arbiru deit too halo sala oi-oin. I bainhira sira haan hamutuk ho imi mos, sira halo tuir deit sira nia hakarak aat. Sira nia hahalok nee halo moe deit ita.
Sira nia matan halai tuun-sae hodi buka feto nebee mak atu halo sala foer ho sira. Sira sempre kaan atu halo sala. Sira buka ema nebee mak fiar seidauk metin hodi lohi ema nee para lao sala dalan. Sira nia laran toman ona kaan sasaan. Nai Maromak foo ona malisan ba sira!<a href='#note-1412' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira sees ona hosi dalan loos hodi tuir fali Balaão, Beor nia oan. Balaão nee gosta liu manaan osan hosi nia hahalok aat.
Maibee iha loron ida, nia kuda buru rasik siak nia para la bele halo tan nia hahalok beik-teen nee. Maski kuda buru nee la hatene koalia, maibee derepenti deit nia bele koalia hanesan fali ema.<a href='#note-1413' class='key'>✡</a>
Mestri falsu sira nee hanesan bee matan nebee maran hela. Sira hanesan abu-abu nebee anin huu halo lakon tiha. Maromak prepara tiha ona ba sira fatin ida nebee nakukun liu.
Tanba sira tebe rai loos, maibee koalia liafuan mamuk deit. Sira gosta buka ema nebee mak foin komesa husik nia sala. Depois sira dada ema nee para moris tuir fali buat aat saida deit mak ema nee kaan atu halo.
Mestri falsu sira nee promete katak ema nebee tuir sira sei moris livre. Afinal sira rasik sai tiha ona atan ba sira nia hahalok aat. Tanba ita ema sai atan ba saida deit mak ukun ita.
Ema nebee konhese ona Nai Jesus Kristu ita nia Salvador, nia husik tiha ona buat aat iha mundu nee. Maibee se nia monu fali ba hahalok aat too hahalok nee ukun fali nia, entaun too ikus nia moris aat liu fali uluk nian.
Diak liu uluk kedas ema nee la hatene dalan moris loos nian, duke nia hatene tiha maibee too ikus fila kotuk fali ba Maromak nia ukun fuan nebee nia rona tiha ona.
Iha ema soe lia nunee: “Bainhira asu muta, nia rasik sei lambe fila fali.” Iha mos seluk dehan, “Fahi nebee foo haris moos tiha ona sei duir aan fali iha tahu laran.”<a href='#note-1414' class='key'>✡</a>
Maluk doben sira, ida nee hau nia surat segundu ba imi. Iha hau nia surat rua nee, hau foo hanoin ba imi kona ba buat nebee imi hatene ona, tanba hau hakarak dudu imi ba hanoin nebee mak loos.
Hau hakarak atu imi hanoin nafatin Maromak nia profeta sira nia liafuan uluk. Imi tenki hanoin mos hanorin nebee ita nia Salvador Nai Jesus foo ba imi liu hosi Nia apostolu sira.
Liu-liu imi tenki hatene katak, bainhira mundu nee besik remata ona, sei iha ema nebee gosta goza imi. Sira sei moris tuir deit sira nia hakarak aat, i sei abuza imi<a href='#note-1415' class='key'>✡</a>
dehan, “Jesus promete atu mai fali. Agora Nia iha nebee? Komesa hosi ita nia bei-ala sira mate too ohin loron mos buat ida la muda. Hotu-hotu lao nafatin, komesa hosi Maromak halo lalehan ho rai.”
Hodi bee mos Nai Maromak uluk kastigu ema iha mundu nee, bainhira Nia halo bee sae makaas hodi halo lakon tiha buat hotu-hotu.<a href='#note-1417' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos Maromak foo orden mak lalehan ho rai nebee agora dadauk iha nee, hein hela too loron nebee mak Nia tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia. Iha loron nebaa Maromak sei uza ahi hodi sunu tiha lalehan ho rai too halo mate mohu ema nebee mak la interese Nia.
Maluk doben sira, keta haluha buat nee: Ita nia Nai la sura tempu hanesan ita. Tuir Nia, loron ida hanesan fali tinan rihun ida. I tinan rihun ida hanesan fali loron ida.<a href='#note-1418' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun, se ita nia Nai seidauk halo tuir Nia promesa, nee laos dehan Nia demora, maski ema balu hanoin hanesan nee. Maibee tuir lo-loos Nia sei pasiensia ho imi. Nia hakarak atu ema hotu-hotu tenki hakribi sira nia sala, tanba Nia lakohi atu ema ida mate tinan ba tinan.
Maibee ita nia Nai sei mai derepenti deit hanesan naok-teen. Lalehan sei tarutu makaas loos too lakon tiha. Loro-matan, fulan ho fitun sira iha lalehan, ahi haan hotu kedas. I mundu ho buat hotu-hotu iha mundu nee mos sei lakon hotu.<a href='#note-1419' class='key'>✡</a>
Se buat hotu-hotu sei lakon tiha nunee, entaun imi tenki moris oinsaa? Imi tenki moris ho laran moos hodi tuir Maromak nia hakarak,
i hein nafatin atu Maromak nia loron too lalais. Iha loron nee, lalehan ahi haan mohu tiha. I loro matan, fulan ho fitun sira iha lalehan mos nabeen hotu tanba manas liu.
Maibee ita hein hela lalehan foun ho mundu foun, tuir buat nebee Nai Maromak promete tiha ona. Fatin nee so ba ema nebee mak moris loos.<a href='#note-1420' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, maluk doben sira, durante imi hein hela buat sira nee, imi tenki hakaas aan para sai ema nebee mak moos liu, livre hosi sala, i moris diak malu ho Nai Maromak.
Hanoin took. Kuandu Maromak pasiensia ho ita ema, nee dehan katak Nia foo tempu ba ita para ita bele hetan salvasaun. Ita nia maluk doben Paulo mos hakerek ona ba imi nunee, ho matenek nebee mak nia simu hosi Nai Maromak.
Iha Paulo nia surat hotu-hotu nia koalia hanesan nee. Iha nia surat laran iha buat balu mak susar atu kompriende. Ema nebee beik-teen i fiar la metin bobar fali nia liafuan nee, hanesan mos sira bobar liafuan iha parte seluk iha Livru Sagradu. Ema hanesan nee sei rahun.
Maluk doben sira, imi hatene ona buat sira nee. Nunee kuidadu! Mestri falsu sira nee kontra buat nebee mak loos. Kuidadu para sira la bele lori imi sees hosi dalan loos. Tanba imi hamriik metin ona, maibee se imi tuir sira, imi sei monu.
Hakaas aan para loron ba loron konhese diak liu Nai Jesus Kristu ita nia Salvador, i hatene liu tan Nia laran diak.
Mai ita foti aas Nia naran agora i too tinan ba tinan. Amen.
Surat nee hosi hau, Paulo, hamutuk ho ita nia maluk sarani Timóteo. Hau dadur hela iha kadeia laran tanba hau tuir Kristu Jesus.
Ami hakerek surat nee ba ami nia belun diak Filemon, senhor halao Nai Maromak nia servisu hanesan ami.
Surat nee mos ba sarani sira nebee baibain halibur malu halo orasaun iha senhor nia uma, ho mos ba ami nia maluk feto Afia ho ami nia maluk luta nain Arkipu.<a href='#note-1250' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau harohan ba ita nia Aman Maromak ho Nai Jesus Kristu, para hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba imi, i foo paz ho hakmatek ba imi.
Senhor Filemon, bainhira hau halo orasaun, hau sempre temi ita nia naran, i foo agradese ba Maromak.
Tanba hau rona katak ita hadomi Maromak nia povu hotu i ita mos fiar lo-loos ba Nai Jesus.
Senhor nia fiar nee halo senhor moris neon ida laran ida ho sarani sira seluk. Hau harohan atu liu hosi imi nia domin nee, imi bele kompriende klean liu tan bensaun hotu-hotu nebee Maromak foo mai ita tanba ita laran ida ho Kristu.
Senhor hadomi Maromak nia povu hodi halo sira nia laran haksolok. Hahalok nee halo hau nia laran mos haksolok teb-tebes, i foo forsa mai hau.
8-9 Tanba nee hau hakarak husu buat ida. Nudar Kristu Jesus nia apostolu, hau iha direitu atu manda senhor halo buat nebee mak loos. Maibee hau lakohi manda, so husu deit, tanba senhor hadomi Maromak nia povu. Hau mos katuas ona, i hau dadur hela iha kadeia laran tanba hau tuir Kristu Jesus.
Nee mak hau husu atu senhor simu fali ita nia atan Onésimu ho diak. Iha komarka nee nia sai hanesan hau nia oan rasik, tanba hau mak lori nia atu fiar ba Jesus.<a href='#note-1251' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk Onésimu nee la iha folin ba senhor, maibee agora nia iha folin, laos deit ba senhor, maibee iha folin mos mai hau.<a href='#note-1252' class='key'>*</a>
Hau hadomi teb-tebes nia, maibee la iha buat ida, agora hau haruka nia fila fali ba senhor.
Hau iha kadeia laran nee tanba hau foo sai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak. Tuir loos hau hakarak atu Onésimu hela nafatin ho hau para bele foo ajuda mai hau hodi senhor nia naran.
Maibee hau lakohi foti desizaun se senhor seidauk hataan. Hau hakarak atu tulun nebee ita foo mai hau sai hosi ita nia laran, laos tanba hau mak obriga.
Uluk Onésimu halai lakon tiha hosi senhor nia uma. Dala ruma Maromak husik nia halai sai iha tempu badak para agora nia bele fila fali baa hela metin ho senhor.
Nee duni, se senhor konsidera hau nudar ita nia kolega servisu, entaun hau husu atu senhor simu Onésimu hanesan mos ita simu hau.
Se Onésimu uluk halo sala ruma hasoru senhor, ka nia iha tusan ruma, hau mak selu.
Hau hakerek ho hau nia liman rasik: Hau, Paulo, promete atu selu hotu Onésimu nia tusan ba Filemon. Maibee keta haluha katak, senhor nia tusan ba hau nee boot liu, tanba liu hosi hau mak ita hetan moris foun hosi Maromak.
Entaun belun, halo ida nee para ajuda hau, tanba ita nain rua laran ida ona ho ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu. Nunee ita sei halo hau nia laran haksolok.
Hau hakerek surat nee ho kontenti tanba hau hatene katak senhor sei halo tuir, i sei halo liu fali buat nebee mak hau husu.
Iha tan buat ida. Prepara fatin ida mai hau, tanba hau hein katak Maromak sei rona imi nia orasaun hodi loke dalan atu hau bele baa fali haree imi.
Epafras dadur hela hamutuk ho hau tanba nia mos foo sai kona ba Kristu Jesus. Nia haruka kumprimentus ba senhor.<a href='#note-1253' class='key'>✡</a>
Marcos, Aristarco, Demas, ho Lucas servisu hamutuk ho hau, i sira mos foo kumprimentus.<a href='#note-1254' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau harohan atu Nai Jesus Kristu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi hotu.
Surat nee hosi Paulo ho Timóteo, Kristu Jesus nia atan.
Ami haruka surat nee ba Maromak nia povu iha sidade Filipi nebee laran ida ho Jesus Kristu, ba responsavel sarani sira, ho mos ba ema nebee ajuda responsavel sira.
Ami harohan ba ita nia Aman Maromak ho Nai Kristu Jesus, para hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba imi, i foo paz ho hakmatek ba imi.
Hau sempre agradese ba Nai Maromak bainhira hau hanoin imi.
Hau sempre halo orasaun ba imi ho laran haksolok,
tanba hosi loron primeiru imi simu Maromak nia Liafuan Diak too agora, imi ajuda hau hodi foo sai Liafuan Diak nee.
Nai Maromak hahuu ona halo servisu diak iha imi. I hau laran metin katak, Nia sei kontinua nafatin too Nia servisu nee hotu iha loron nebee Kristu Jesus fila fali mai hosi lalehan.
Hau senti nunee, tanba imi iha hau nia laran. Maromak foo fiar ba imi atu servisu hamutuk ho hau. Bainhira Hau defende Nia Liafuan Diak hodi hatudu ba ema katak Liafuan nee loos, imi sempre halo parte iha servisu nee. Bainhira hau iha dadur laran mos, imi halo parte nafatin.
Nai Maromak rasik hatene katak, hau hakarak teb-tebes atu haree imi, i hau hadomi imi hanesan Kristu Jesus mos hadomi imi.
Hau halo orasaun ba Nai Maromak para imi nia domin ba malu bele buras ba beibeik. Hau mos husu atu Nia aumenta beibeik matenek ba imi hodi halo imi hatene saida mak loos, saida mak sala.
Nunee imi bele hili saida mak diak hodi moris loos i livre hosi sala too Kristu fila fali mai.
Ho Jesus Kristu nia tulun, imi sei hatudu hahalok diak iha imi nia moris tomak. Hodi nunee, ema sei foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran hodi hahii Nia.
Maun-alin sira, hau hakarak atu imi hatene katak, maski ema halo susar hau, maibee hau nia terus nee halo ema barak liu tan fiar ba Nai Jesus nia Liafuan Diak.
Seguransa sira iha rezidensia ulun boot sira nian ho ema sira seluk iha nee mos hatene dehan, hau dadur hela tanba serbi Jesus Kristu.<a href='#note-1154' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba hau iha dadur laran mos sarani sira barak liu mak laran metin ba Nai Jesus. Agora sira brani liu, i la tauk tan atu foo sai Maromak nia liafuan.
Iha duni ema balu foo sai kona ba Kristu ho hanoin nebee diak, maibee iha mos balu halo nunee tanba sira laran moras hau i hakarak para ema tuir deit sira.
Sira nebee ho hanoin diak, sira foo sai kona ba Kristu tanba sira hadomi hau. Sira hatene katak, Maromak tau hau iha fatin nee para defende Liafuan Diak.
Maibee sira nebee laran moras hau, sira foo sai kona ba Kristu para buka naran deit, laos ho objetivu nebee diak. Sira hanoin atu foo todan liu tan mai hau iha kadeia nee.
Maibee husik deit ba. Ema atu hanorin ho laran moos ka la moos, la buat ida, naran katak sira hanorin kona ba Kristu. Ida nee mak halo hau nia laran haksolok.
I hau sei haksolok nafatin,
Hau hakarak ho laran metin atu hau brani nafatin foo sai kona ba Kristu, hanesan mos uluk, atu nunee hau la bele moe. Atu hau moris ka, hau mate, la buat ida. Naran katak Maromak uza hau hodi foti aas Kristu nia naran.
21-23 Hau hanoin nunee: se hau moris, entaun moris ba Kristu, i hau bele halo servisu ida ke iha folin. Maibee se hau mate, hau sorti liu tan, tanba hau bele husik mundu nee hodi baa moris hamutuk ho Kristu. Nee mak hau la hatene atu hili ida nebee loos.
Maibee imi sei presiza hau iha nee, entaun diak liu hau hela lai iha mundu.
Entaun hau laran metin katak, hau sei moris i sei hela ho imi nafatin, para tulun imi atu fiar metin liu tan ba Maromak ho laran haksolok.
Nunee imi sei foti aas Jesus Kristu nia naran, tanba Nia mak loke dalan atu hau bele baa haree fali imi.
Bele halo nusaa mos, imi tenki moris tuir lo-loos Kristu nia Liafuan Diak. Nunee, se hau rasik baa vizita fali imi ka rona deit hosi ema mos, hau bele hatene katak, imi hamriik metin ho neon ida laran ida. I hau bele hatene katak, imi hotu servisu makaas para ema seluk mos fiar Kristu nia Liafuan Diak nee.
Bainhira ema kontra imi, la bele tauk sira. Imi nia brani nee hatudu ba sira katak, Nai Maromak rasik sei salva imi maibee sei halo lakon tiha sira.
Maromak nee diak teb-tebes. Nia loke ona dalan ba imi para fiar ba Kristu. Laos nee deit, maibee Nia mos bolu imi atu terus tanba tuir Nia.
Imi nia luta hanesan ho hau nia luta. Uluk imi haree hau terus ba Kristu, i agora mos imi rona dehan hau hasoru nafatin situasaun hanesan nee.<a href='#note-1155' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi laran metin tanba imi sai ona ida ho Kristu. Imi nia laran hakmatek tanba Kristu hadomi imi. Imi lao hamutuk ho Maromak nia Espiritu. Imi laran diak ba malu, i hadomi malu.
Imi moris nunee, halo hau nia laran haksolok. Agora hau husu atu imi hanoin ida deit, i hadomi malu ho neon ida laran ida atu nunee hau bele haksolok liu tan.
La bele halo saida deit hodi buka naran. La bele foti aan, maibee tenki haraik aan hodi konsidera ema seluk diak liu fali imi.
La bele servisu deit ba imi nia interese privadu, maibee imi ida-idak mos tenki haree ba ema seluk nia interese.
Imi nia haraik aan hanesan Kristu Jesus.
Nia Maromak.
Maski nunee Nia prontu husik Nia pozisaun nudar Maromak.
Nia husik tiha buat hotu-hotu
hodi sai ema
i moris hanesan atan.
Nia sai tiha ema,
Nia haraik Aan
hodi moris tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak too mate.
Maski ema oho Nia iha krus hanesan fali ema aat ida mos,
Nia simu.
Tanba nee, Nai Maromak foti aas Nia liu buat hotu-hotu,
i foo ba Nia, naran ida nebee boot liu naran hotu-hotu.
Maromak halo nunee
atu kriatura hotu-hotu iha lalehan ho iha rai,
ema moris ho ema mate,
Hotu-hotu sei hatete, “Jesus Kristu mak Nai!”
Ho nunee sira foti aas Aman Maromak nia naran.<a href='#note-1156' class='key'>✡</a>
Maluk doben sira, uluk hau sei hamutuk ho imi, imi sempre rona hau hodi halo tuir Maromak nia hakarak. Agora hau dook hosi imi mos, imi tenki hakaas aan liu tan atu moris nunee. Maromak salva tiha ona imi. Nee duni, esforsa aan ho tauk ho respeitu para tuir Nia hakarak, atu imi nia salvasaun bele too iha rohan.
Tanba Nai Maromak rasik servisu iha imi nia laran. Nia halo imi prontu atu tuir Nia hakarak, i foo mos kbiit ba imi atu bele halo tuir.
Imi halo saida deit, la bele murmura, i la bele istori malu.
Nunee, nudar Maromak nia oan, imi bele moris ho laran moos, livre hosi sala, buat aat ida mos la iha. Imi moris iha ema aat sira nia leet. Entaun imi tenki sai hanesan naroman hodi leno dalan ba sira, hanesan fitun iha lalehan.<a href='#note-1157' class='key'>✡</a>
Hatoo ba sira, Maromak nia liafuan nebee foo moris. Se imi halo nunee, entaun aban-bainrua bainhira Jesus Kristu fila fali mai, hau nia laran sei haksolok, tanba hau nia servisu ho hau nia kolen la saugati.
Tanba imi fiar ba Kristu, imi mos serbi Maromak hodi entrega imi nia aan tomak sai hanesan sakrifisiu ba Nia. Se aban-bainrua ema oho hau tanba hau nia fiar karik, mak hau nia mate mos sai hanesan sakrifisiu ida hodi foo ba Nai Maromak.<a href='#note-1158' class='key'>✡</a> Bele nunee mos, hau nia laran haksolok hamutuk ho imi.
Imi mos tenki haksolok hamutuk ho hau.
Hau hein katak, la kleur tan Nai Jesus foo dalan atu hau haruka Timóteo baa iha imi. Bainhira fila fali mai, nia bele konta mai hau kona ba imi, hodi halo hau nia laran haksolok.
Iha nee la iha ema seluk hanesan Timóteo. So nia deit mak iha interese teb-tebes ho imi.
Sira seluk so hanoin deit sira nia aan. Buat nebee Jesus Kristu hakarak, sira la interese.
Maibee imi rasik hatene, Timóteo servisu makaas hodi foo sai Nai Jesus nia Liafuan Diak. Nia servisu hamutuk ho hau, hanesan oan ida servisu ho nia aman.
Nee duni hau hakarak hein too hau rona buat nebee mak atu akontese mai hau, depois mak hau haruka kedas nia ba imi.
I Nai Jesus halo hau laran metin katak, la kleur tan, hau mos bele baa vizita imi.
Uluk imi hili Epafroditu para mai tau matan ba hau. Durante nee nia sai hanesan hau nia alin ida hodi halao Maromak nia servisu hamutuk ho hau, i nia luta hamutuk ho hau hanesan funu nain ida. Maibee agora, hau hanoin hau tenki haruka nia fila fali ba imi.
Tanba nia hanoin teb-tebes imi hotu-hotu, i nia mos preokupa hela ho imi tanba imi rona dehan nia moras.
Loos duni, momentu nebaa, nia moras todan besik atu mate, maibee Nai Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak ba nia, i kura tiha nia moras. Hanesan nee Maromak mos hatudu Nia laran diak mai hau, para hau la bele tristi liu tan.
Tanba nee mak hau hakarak liu tan haruka Epafroditu fila fali ba imi, para imi haree nia, imi sei haksolok, i hau mos laran hakmatek.
Imi tenki simu nia ho haksolok teb-tebes, nudar imi nia maluk sarani. I imi mos tenki respeita ema hotu nebee hahalok hanesan nia.
Tanba nia halao Kristu nia servisu too nia besik atu mate. Nia foo aan ba mate, para bele ajuda hau hodi imi nia fatin.
Maun-alin sira, haksolok ba, tanba imi laran ida ona ho Nai Jesus. Maski hau hakerek fali buat nebee uluk hau hakerek tiha ona, maibee hau la baruk foo hanoin dala ida tan ba imi, atu imi keta monu ba ema nia liafuan bosok.
Kuidadu ho asu sira nee - ema sira nebee halo buat aat hodi bosok dehan tenki sunat mak foin Maromak simu ita.<a href='#note-1159' class='key'>*</a>
Afinal ita nee mak Maromak nia ema lo-loos. Ita mak adora Maromak hodi Nia Espiritu nia tulun. Ita foti aas Kristu Jesus nia naran, i ita la depende ba saida deit mak ita ema halo.
Se karik Maromak bele simu ita tanba ita nia hahalok ka ita nia huun, entaun hau rasik bele dehan, hau loos tiha ona. Karik ema seluk gaba aan kona ba buat sira nee, hau bele gaba aan liu fali nia.
Hau moris mai, iha loron walu ema sunat hau tuir lei relijiaun. Hau ema Ebreu isin, hosi suku Benjamim, hosi ema Israel. Uluk hau seidauk tuir Kristu, hau nudar ema grupu Farizeu badinas teb-tebes halo tuir lei relijiaun,
too la iha ema ida foo sala mai hau. Laos nee deit, iha tempu nebaa hau mos halo terus sarani sira, tanba hau hanoin ema sira nee soe tiha ona ita nia lei relijiaun.<a href='#note-1160' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk hau hanoin dehan, buat sira nee folin boot mai hau. Maibee agora hau konsidera la iha folin ida, tanba hau tuir Kristu.
Ida nebee hau konsidera folin boot liu mak nee: Hau bele konhese Kristu Jesus hau nia Nai. Buat sira seluk, hau husik tiha ona, i konsidera hanesan lixu deit, para hau bele besik liu Kristu,
Hau hakarak konhese Kristu liu tan. Hau hakarak para Maromak servisu iha hau nia laran ho kbiit ida nebee Nia uza hodi halo Kristu moris fali hosi mate. Hau hakarak halo parte iha Kristu nia terus. Kona ba mate mos, hau hakarak sai hanesan Nia.
Tanba hau laran metin katak, aban-bainrua Nia sei halo moris fali hau hosi mate.
Hau laos hatete katak, hau hetan ona buat sira nee ka hau moris loos ona. Maibee hau hakaas aan nafatin atu moris tuir Kristu Jesus nia hakarak, tanba ho objetivu nee mak Nia hili hau sai Nia ema.
Maun-alin sira, hau la hanoin katak hau too ona objetivu nee. Maibee buat nebee hau halo mak nee: hau haluha tiha buat nebee iha kotuk hodi halai makaas ba oin.
Hau hakaas aan ba oin nafatin too rohan para manaan premiu. Hau nia premiu mak nee: aban-bainrua Nai Maromak bolu hau tama iha lalehan, tanba Kristu Jesus mate mai hau.
Tuir loos ita hotu nebee abut metin ona iha Kristu, tenki hanoin hanesan nee. Maibee se imi balu iha hanoin ruma la hanesan maka Nai Maromak sei foo hanoin ba nia.
Bele halo nusaa mos, ita tenki halo tuir buat hotu nebee Maromak hatudu ona mai ita.
Maun-alin sira, imi tenki moris tuir hau nia ezemplu, i aprende di-diak hosi ema seluk nebee tuir ona ezemplu nebee hau foo.<a href='#note-1161' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatete dala barak ona ba imi katak, iha ema barak moris hanesan Kristu nia inimigu, i la foo folin ba Nia mate iha krus. I agora hau foo hanoin tan ho matan been.
Too ikus Maromak sei halo lakon tiha ema sira nee. Sira so buka halo kontenti deit sira nia isin. Hahalok aat nebee sira halo, tuir loos halo ema moe, maibee sira tebe rai dehan, diak loos. Sira hanoin deit buat mundu nian.
Maibee ita la bele nunee, tanba ita sai ona ema lalehan nian. Agora ita hein hela ita nia Salvador Nai Jesus Kristu tuun fila fali mai hosi lalehan.
Iha mundu nee, ita nia isin lolon fraku, i sei mate. Maibee bainhira Jesus Kristu mai, Nia sei troka tiha ita nia isin lolon fraku nee, sai fali forti ho furak teb-tebes hanesan Nia isin lolon rasik, i ita sei la mate tan. Nia bele halo ida nee tanba Nia iha kbiit hodi ukun buat hotu-hotu.
Tanba nee, maun-alin doben sira, imi tenki hamriik metin ho Nai Jesus. Hau hakarak teb-tebes atu haree imi, tanba imi hanesan premiu ida hosi hau nia servisu, i imi halo hau nia laran haksolok.
Hau husu boot ba imi, Evódia ho Síntike, atu la bele istori malu tan, maibee tenki neon ida laran ida, tanba imi nain rua Nai Jesus nia ema.
Hau nia kolega servisu nebee hau konfia, hau husu o ajuda hela senhora nain rua nee para diak malu. Tanba uluk sira servisu makaas ajuda hau foo sai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak, hamutuk ho Clemente ho kolega sira seluk. Sira hotu nia naran, Maromak hakerek tiha ona iha lista ema moris rohan-laek nian.<a href='#note-1162' class='key'>*</a>
Loron-kalan haksolok deit ba, tanba imi Nai Jesus nia ema. Dala ida tan hau hatete: haksolok nafatin ba!
Hatudu laran maus ba ema hotu-hotu, tanba Nai Jesus besik fila mai ona.
La bele preokupa kona ba saida deit. Maibee iha situasaun nebee deit, halo orasaun husu Nai Maromak nia tulun. I bainhira imi husu, keta haluha foo agradese ba Nia.
Kuandu imi halo nunee, mak Maromak sei halo imi nia laran hakmatek. Hakmatek nebee Nia foo nee, ita ema sukat la too. Ho hakmatek nee, Maromak sei kuidadu imi nia neon ho laran para imi la bele preokupa ona, tanba imi Kristu Jesus nia ema.
Entaun, maun-alin sira, imi tenki kuidadu di-diak imi nia hanoin. Hanoin beibeik kona ba buat nebee mak loos, ho buat nebee iha valór. Hanoin kona ba buat diak nebee halo haksolok Maromak nia laran ho buat furak nebee foo ksolok ba ema. Saida deit mak diak loos i saida deit mak ita bele gaba, nee mak imi tenki hanoin.
Halo tuir buat nebee imi aprende ona hosi hau, liu hosi hau nia koalia ka hau nia hahalok. Kuandu imi halo nunee mak Maromak sei akompanha imi, i foo laran hakmatek ba imi.
Hau haksolok teb-tebes hodi hahii Nai Jesus, tanba dala ida tan imi ajuda hau. Hau hatene katak, uluk kedas imi hadomi hau, maibee kleur ona imi la iha oportunidade hodi tulun.
Hau hatete nunee, laos tanba hau falta buat ruma, lae. Hau aprende ona moris kontenti ho buat nebee mak hau iha.
Hau hatene ona moris iha susar nia laran, i hatene mos moris ho buat hotu-hotu kompletu. Hau aprende ona segredu nee: oinsaa bele moris ho kontenti iha situasaun saida deit. Atu kabun bosu ka kabun mamuk, atu iha buat barak ka iha deit uitoan, hau kontenti nafatin.
Hau bele simu buat hotu-hotu, tanba Kristu mak foo forsa mai hau.
Maski nunee, foin dadauk imi ajuda hau iha susar laran, nee buat diak ida.
Uluk mos, bainhira imi foin simu Nai Jesus nia Liafuan Diak, i hau sai hosi provinsia Masedónia, so imi iha sidade Filipi deit mak foo ajuda mai hau. Sarani sira seluk lae. Maibee imi hatene ona istoria nee.
Bainhira hau sei iha sidade Tesalónika mos, imi haruka osan mai hau dala rua hodi suporta hau.<a href='#note-1163' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau koalia hanesan nee, laos tanba hau hakarak atu imi foo tan. Maibee hau hakarak para Maromak foo bensaun ba imi, tanba imi nia laran diak.
Hau nia Maromak riku teb-tebes. I Nia sei foo ba imi, buat hotu-hotu nebee imi presiza, tanba imi laran ida ho Kristu Jesus.
Mai ita foti aas ita nia Aman Maromak nia naran, too tinan ba tinan! Amen.
Hatoo hau nia kumprimentus ba ema hotu-hotu nebee tuir Kristu Jesus iha nebaa. Kumprimentus mos hosi maluk sarani sira nebee hamutuk ho hau,
ho mos sarani sira seluk iha sidade nee, liu-liu sira nebee servisu ba liurai boot César.
Hau harohan atu Nai Jesus Kristu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi hotu.
Maun-alin sira, hau hakarak teb-tebes atu hau nia maluk ema Israel sira hetan salvasaun, i hau harohan beibeik atu Maromak salva sira.
Hau hatete lo-loos, sira nia laran hakarak teb-tebes serbi Maromak, maibee sira la hatene dalan loos.
Sira la kompriende dalan nebee mak Maromak foo atu sira diak malu fali ho Nia, maibee sira tuir fali sira nia dalan rasik. Dalan nebee mak Maromak hatudu, sira la simu.
Kristu kumpri ona Moisés nia lei tomak. Nunee see-see deit mak fiar ba Kristu, Maromak simu nia.
Iha Livru Sagradu, Moisés hakerek dehan, ema bele diak malu ho Maromak se sira halo tuir Maromak nia lei tomak. Nia hakerek nunee: “Ema nebee mak halo tuir buat sira nee hotu, nia sei hetan moris.”<a href='#note-913' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee kona ba diak malu ho Maromak liu hosi fiar ba Jesus Kristu, Livru Sagradu dehan, “Keta hanoin iha imi nia laran dehan, see mak atu sae ba lalehan (para lori Kristu tuun mai salva ita)?
Lalikan husu, see mak atu tuun ba iha matebian sira nia fatin (atu fanu Kristu fila fali hosi mate)?”
Lalika buka Nia iha fatin dook, tanba iha Livru Sagradu mos hakerek dehan, “Maromak nia liafuan besik loos imi, iha imi nia ibun, ho mos iha imi nia laran.” Liafuan nee mak ami baibain foo sai kona ba fiar, nunee:<a href='#note-914' class='key'>✡</a>
Se o nia ibun foo sai dehan, “Jesus mak Nai”, i o fiar iha o nia laran katak, Maromak halo moris fali ona Jesus hosi mate, o sei hetan salvasaun.
Tanba imi nia laran fiar ba Kristu mak Maromak simu imi hodi deklara katak imi nia sala moos tiha ona. I tanba imi nia ibun foo sai dehan, “Jesus mak Nai” mak Maromak salva imi.
Hanesan hakerek iha Livru Sagradu dehan, “See-see deit mak fiar ba Nia, sira nia fiar la saugati.”<a href='#note-915' class='key'>✡</a>
Atu ema Judeu ka laos Judeu, hanesan deit. Tanba ita hotu iha Nai ida deit, Nia mak Nai ba ema hotu-hotu, i Nia hatudu Nia laran diak teb-tebes ba see-see deit mak husu tulun ba Nia.
Hanesan hakerek ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan, “Ema see deit mak husu tulun ba Nai, Nia sei salva sira.”<a href='#note-916' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee oinsaa mak ema bele husu tulun ba Ema ida se sira la fiar ba Nia? Oinsaa mak sira bele fiar se nunka rona kona ba Nia? Oinsaa mak sira bele rona kona ba Nia se la iha ema ida mak baa foo sai ba sira?
I oinsaa mak ema bele baa foo sai ba sira, se la iha ema ida mak haruka? Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan, “Ita haksolok teb-tebes simu ema nebee mak lori liafuan diak mai ita.”<a href='#note-917' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski ema Israel rona Liafuan Diak, maibee balu deit mak simu. Hanesan profeta Isaias dehan, “Nai, ema uitoan deit mak fiar ba liafuan nebee mak ami foo sai.”<a href='#note-918' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, ema rona Liafuan Diak mak foin bele fiar. I atu rona, tenki iha ema ruma mai foo sai ba sira kona ba Kristu.
Entaun hau hakarak husu, ema Israel nunka rona kona ba Kristu ka? Sira rona tiha ona! Hanesan hakerek iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Liafuan diak foo sai tiha ona iha mundu tomak,
hosi rai ulun too rai ikun.”<a href='#note-919' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau husu tan: Keta halo be ema Israel la kompriende liafuan nebee mak sira rona nee? Sira kompriende! Primeiru, Moisés hatoo Maromak nia liafuan ba ema Israel dehan,
“Hau sei foo bensaun ba ema nebee laos Judeu,
halo imi laran moras ba sira.
Hau sei hatudu laran diak ba povu nebee beik,
Tuir mai, profeta Isaias brani hakerek Maromak nia liafuan kona ba ema nebee mak laos Judeu nunee:
“Ema nebee la buka Hau, hetan ona Hau.
Hau hatudu ona Hau nia Aan ba ema nebee mak la buka hatene kona ba Hau.”<a href='#note-921' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee kona ba ema Israel, Nia dehan,
“Loron-kalan Hau nia liman nakloke atu simu sira,
maibee sira ulun toos i lakohi rona Hau.”<a href='#note-922' class='key'>✡</a>
Agora hau husu tan: Entaun Maromak fila kotuk ba Nia povu Israel ka? Lae liu! Hau rasik ema Israel, hau Abraão nia jerasaun, hosi suku Benjamim.<a href='#note-923' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak nunka fila kotuk ba Nia povu. Sira nee Nia hili hori uluk kedas. Imi hatene saida mak hakerek iha Livru Sagradu kona ba profeta Elias bainhira nia kesar ema Israel ba Maromak dehan,
“Nai, ema oho hotu ona Ita Boot nia profeta, i halo rahun Ita Boot nia meza sakrífisiu. Hela deit hau mesak i ema atu oho tan hau!”<a href='#note-924' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Maromak hataan dehan, “Laos o mesak! Hau salva hela Hau nia ema rihun hitu. Sira nee nunka hakneak adora estatua Baal.”<a href='#note-925' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos agora, sei iha ema Israel balu nebee tuir Maromak nafatin; sira nee Maromak hili ona tanba Nia laran diak.
Nia hili sira tanba deit Nia laran diak, laos tanba buat diak nebee mak sira halo. Se Maromak hili ema bazeia ba sira nia hahalok karik, entaun bele dehan Nia laran diak la vale ona. Maibee laos nunee.
<a href='#note-926' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun oinsaa? Ema Israel hakaas aan atu diak malu ho Maromak, maibee barak la konsege. So sira nebee Maromak hili tiha ona mak hetan. Maibee ema Israel sira seluk sai ulun toos liu tan.
Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek kona ba ema sira nee dehan,
“Hori uluk too agora
Maromak halo sira nia neon sai beik,
sira nia matan la haree,
sira nia tilun la rona.”<a href='#note-927' class='key'>✡</a>
Liurai David mos hakerek,
“Husik atu sira halo festa haan-hemu,
molok hakfodak sira monu tama ba lasu laran
hodi hetan kastigu tuir sira nia hahalok aat.
Husik sira nia matan sai delek
atu sira la bele haree.
Husik sira lori todan,
too sira nia kotuk bonko tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-928' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun hau husu nunee: Bainhira ema Judeu sira sidi, sira monu too la bele hamriik ka? Laos nunee! Maibee tanba sira lakohi rona Maromak mak dalan nakloke ba ema nebee laos Judeu atu hetan salvasaun. Nee para ema Judeu bele laran moras hodi hakarak atu sira mos simu salvasaun nee.
Entaun ema Judeu nia sala lori fali bensaun ba ema iha mundu tomak. Nunee ema Judeu lakon, i ema seluk mak hetan bensaun fali. Se ema Judeu nia sala lori bensaun, saa tan aban-bainrua ema Judeu tomak fila fali ba Maromak! Nee lori bensaun liu tan!
Hau hein katak hau nia servisu nee bele halo hau nia maluk Judeu sira laran moras hodi hakarak atu sira mos bele hetan bensaun nebee ema laos Judeu simu nee. Nunee sira balu bele hetan salvasaun.
Bainhira Maromak la simu ema Judeu, nee loke dalan atu ema iha mundu tomak bele diak malu ho Maromak. Saa tan aban-bainrua, Maromak simu fali sira, nee hanesan ema mate moris fali!
Hau foti ezemplu kona ba ema Judeu. Bainhira ema halo paun, sira oferese ida primeiru ba Maromak, nunee paun nee hotu sai Maromak nian. Nunee mos, se ema oferese ai nia abut ba Maromak, ai huun nee tomak sai Maromak nian.<a href='#note-929' class='key'>*</a>
Ita mos bele kompara ema Judeu ho ai oliveira nebee ema kuda iha toos laran. Maromak tesi sai tiha ona ai nee nia sanak balu. Maibee imi nebee mak laos Judeu, imi hanesan ai oliveira fuik nia sanak nebee Maromak taka iha ai huun hakiak nee. Nunee imi sanak hosi ai huun fuik hetan moris hosi ai huun hakiak nee.
Maibee la bele foti aan dehan, imi hosi liur nee diak liu fali sanak nebee mak Maromak tesi soe tiha ona nee! Keta haluha, imi nee ai sanak deit! Laos sanak mak hametin ai huun. Maibee ai nee nia huun mak halo metin nia sanak.
Karik imi ida hakarak dehan, “Maibee Maromak tesi sai tiha ai sanak balu atu Nia bele taka fali hau iha sira nia fatin.”
Loos duni, maibee keta haluha katak, Maromak soe tiha ona ai sanak sira nee tanba sira lakohi fiar ba Kristu. I o troka fali sira tanba o fiar. Entaun la bele foti aan. Diak liu kuidadu!
Tanba ai sanak orijinal mos Nia bele tesi sai tiha, saa tan imi!
Nunee ita haree katak, Maromak laran diak, maibee Nia mos hatene foo kastigu todan. Nia foo kastigu ba ema nebee lakohi rona Nia. Maibee ba imi, Nia hatudu Nia laran diak, naran katak imi la fila kotuk ba Nia laran diak nee. Se imi fila kotuk karik, Nia mos sei tesi sai tiha imi hosi huun.
Nunee mos se ema Judeu sira desidi fiar ba Kristu, Maromak sei taka fila fali sira iha ai huun orijinal nee, tanba Nia iha kbiit hodi halo buat nee.
Tuir loos ai sanak hosi ai oliveira fuik la bele taka ba iha ai oliveira hakiak, maibee Maromak konsege halo duni. Saa tan ai sanak nebee Nia uluk tesi tiha ona hosi ai oliveira hakiak nee. Nia iha kbiit atu taka fila fali ba iha nia huun rasik.
Maun-alin sira, hau hakarak atu imi hatene Maromak nia planu nebee uluk segredu hela, para imi la bele foti aan. Nia planu mak nee: agora dadauk ema Israel barak ulun toos hasoru Maromak. Sira sei ulun toos too ema seluk nebee Maromak hili ona tama hotu ba Maromak nia povu, foin sira mos sei fiar ba Nia.
Nunee, Maromak sei salva ema Israel hotu, hanesan Nia dehan tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu,
“Iha Salvador ida sei mai hosi foho Siaun,
Nia sei halo Jacó nia jerasaun hakribi sira nia hahalok aat hasoru Hau.<a href='#note-930' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-931' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau nia promesa ba sira mak nee:
Hau sei hamoos sira nia sala hotu.”<a href='#note-932' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba ema Judeu la simu Liafuan Diak, entaun sira sai inimigu ba Maromak, nee loke dalan ba imi nebee laos Judeu atu bele simu salvasaun. Maski nunee, Maromak hadomi nafatin sira, tanba uluk kedas Nia hili sira nia bei-ala sira.
Tanba bainhira Maromak foo buat ruma, Nia nunka foti fila fali. I bainhira Nia bolu ema ida sai Ninian, Nia nunka nega fali.
Imi nebee laos Judeu, uluk lakohi rona Maromak. Maski nunee, agora Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi, tanba durante nee ema Judeu lakohi rona.
Nunee mos, maski ema Judeu agora nafatin lakohi rona Maromak, maibee aban-bainrua Nia sei hatudu Nia laran diak ba sira, tanba Nia hatudu uluk ona ba imi.
Nunee, Maromak husik ema hotu-hotu sai atan ba sala, para Nia bele hatudu Nia laran diak ba sira hotu.
Nai Maromak nia matenek klean liu,
Nia kompriende hosi huun too rohan.
La iha ema ida mak bele kompriende Nia desizaun,
la iha ema ida mak bele hanoin hetan Nia dalan.<a href='#note-933' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak bele hatene tuir Nai Maromak nia hanoin?
See mak bele hanorin fali Nia?<a href='#note-934' class='key'>✡</a>
See mak bele foo prezenti ba Maromak
Tanba buat hotu-hotu iha lalehan ho rai mai hosi Nia,
i sei iha nafatin tanba Nia,
Nia halo buat hotu-hotu atu hahii Nia.
Mai ita foti aas Nia naran too tinan ba tinan. Amen.<a href='#note-936' class='key'>✡</a>
Maun-alin sira, tanba Maromak hatudu ona Nia laran diak ba ita, nunee hau husu atu foo imi nia aan tomak ba Nia, hanesan sakrífisiu ida nebee sei moris, sakrífisiu ida nebee moos i halo haksolok Maromak nia laran. Liu hosi hahalok nee mak imi adora Maromak ho lo-loos.
La bele halo tuir ema iha mundu nee nia hahalok. Maibee husik Maromak halo foun imi nia hanoin hodi muda imi nia laran. Nunee imi bele hatene lo-loos Maromak nia hakarak ba imi. Maromak nia hakarak nee buat ida nebee diak, loos i halo Nia laran haksolok.
Tanba Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak mai hau too Nia hili hau sai apostolu, hau foo hanoin ba imi ida-ida: la bele foti aan. Diak liu kompriende kbiit nebee mak Maromak foo tiha ona ba imi ida-idak tanba imi nia fiar, atu nunee imi bele hatene imi nia aan.
Hau foo ezemplu ida hosi ema nia isin lolon. Isin lolon ida iha parte oi-oin, i parte ida-idak nia knaar la hanesan.
Nunee mos ita sarani sira. Ita barak, maibee tanba ita laran ida ho Kristu, ita hamutuk hanesan isin lolon ida deit.<a href='#note-937' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak foo kbiit ba ita ida-ida, tuir Nia laran diak. Kbiit nebee ita simu nee la hanesan. Ema nebee mak simu kbiit atu foo tutan Maromak nia lia menon, nia tenki koalia tuir liafuan nebee mak nia fiar katak Maromak foo tiha ona ba nia.
Ema nebee simu kbiit atu serbi ema seluk, nia tenki serbi duni. Ema nebee mak simu kbiit atu hanorin, nia tenki hanorin.
Ema nebee mak simu kbiit atu hametin ema nia laran, nia tenki halo nunee. Ema nebee mak simu kbiit atu foo tulun ba ema seluk ho buat nebee mak nia iha, nia tenki foo ho laran. Ema nebee simu kbiit atu sai responsavel, nia tenki sai responsavel nebee badinas. Ema nebee mak simu kbiit atu ajuda ema seluk nebee susar, nia tenki ajuda ho laran haksolok.<a href='#note-938' class='key'>✡</a>
Hatudu imi nia domin lo-loos ba ema seluk, la bele finji. Hakribi buat nebee aat, kaer metin buat nebee mak diak.
Hadomi malu hanesan maun-alin. Haraik aan hodi hatudu respeitu ba malu.
La bele baruk maibee foo aan serbi Nai Jesus nafatin ho laran tomak.
Imi tenki haksolok tanba imi laran metin ba Maromak. Aguenta ho pasiensia iha susar laran. Halo orasaun beibeik.
Uza buat nebee imi iha hodi ajuda maluk sarani sira nebee presiza. Simu ema seluk iha imi nia uma ho laran tomak.
Se iha ema ruma halo terus imi, husu atu Maromak foo bensaun ba sira. Tenki husu bensaun, la bele husu atu Nia foo malisan.<a href='#note-939' class='key'>✡</a>
Se iha ema ruma laran kontenti, kontenti hamutuk ho sira ba. I se iha ema ruma tanis tanba tristi, tanis hamutuk ho sira ba.
Imi tenki moris neon ida, laran ida. La bele halo aan, maibee hamaluk ema kiik. Keta foti aan dehan, o mesak mak hatene.<a href='#note-940' class='key'>✡</a>
Se ema ruma halo buat aat ba imi, la bele halo aat fali ba ema nee. Hakaas aan halo buat nebee ema seluk mos konsidera diak.
Buka atu moris dame malu ho ema hotu-hotu.
Maluk doben sira, la bele halo aat ba ema nebee mak halo aat imi. Husik atu Maromak mak kastigu sira. Tanba iha Livru Sagradu hakerek ona,
“Nai Maromak dehan,
‘Hau mak iha direitu atu kastigu ema,
Hau mak bele halo kastigu ema nebee mak halo aat imi.’ ”<a href='#note-941' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee imi tenki moris tuir liafuan nebee dehan,
“Se o nia inimigu hamlaha, foo hahaan ba nia.
Se nia hamrook, foo nia hemu.
Entaun keta husik buat aat manaan imi. Maibee halo beibeik buat diak, atu nunee imi bele manaan buat aat.
Ita hotu tenki hakruuk ba nai ulun sira, tanba nai ulun sira hotu-hotu simu kbiit hosi Maromak atu kaer ukun. Maromak mak foti sira.
Nunee, ema nebee kontra nai ulun, nia kontra saida mak Maromak desidi ona. Hosi nia hahalok nee, nia sei hetan kastigu.
Ema nebee halo buat loos, nia sei la tauk nai ulun sira, so ema nebee halo sala mak tauk. Entaun se imi lakohi moris iha tauk nia laran, diak liu halo buat nebee loos, para sira bele gaba imi.
Tanba nai ulun sira nee Maromak nia atan para halo diak ba imi. Maibee se imi halo sala, imi tenki tauk, tanba sira iha kbiit atu kastigu imi. Sira nee Maromak nia atan, Nia haruka sira kastigu ema nebee mak halo sala.
Nunee imi tenki hakruuk ba nai ulun sira, laos deit tanba imi lakohi atu simu kastigu, maibee tanba imi hatene katak hahalok nee mak loos.
Nunee mos imi tenki selu taxa, tanba nai ulun sira nee serbi Maromak, i foo sira nia aan hodi ukun imi.
Entaun foo ba nai ulun sira tuir imi nia obrigasaun. Se imi tenki selu taxa, selu ba. Se imi tenki selu impostu, selu ba. Se ema ruma serve atu imi respeita, respeita nia ba. Se ema ruma serve atu imi gaba, gaba nia ba.<a href='#note-944' class='key'>✡</a>
Se imi deve osan ruma karik, tenki selu hotu, para hela obrigasaun ida deit, obrigasaun nee mak tenki hadomi malu. Tanba see mak hadomi nia maluk, nia kumpri ona Maromak nia lei hotu.
Maromak nia ukun fuan dehan, “La bele halo sala ho ema nia feen ka laen, la bele oho ema, la bele naok, la bele kaan ema nia sasaan.” Ukun fuan hirak nee ho ukun fuan sira seluk nia huun mak nee: “O tenki hadomi ema seluk hanesan o hadomi o nia aan rasik.”<a href='#note-945' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee mak hadomi nia maluk, la halo aat ba nia. Nunee se ita hadomi ita nia maluk, nee dehan katak ita halo tuir Maromak nia lei tomak.
Imi tenki halo buat sira nee hotu tanba imi kompriende tempu agora nee oin seluk ona. Oras too ona para imi hadeer. Tanba loron nebee Maromak atu salva ita besik dadauk ona, laos hanesan uluk bainhira ita foin fiar ba Kristu.
Oras kalan atu liu ona, rai besik loron ona. Nunee ita tenki soe tiha hahalok nakukun nian hodi uza fali ekipamentu funu hanesan tropas naroman nian.
Mai ita moris loos, hanesan ema nebee moris iha naroman. La bele halo festa haan-hemu too lanu arbiru tuun-sae. La bele halo sala seksual ho buat foer oi-oin. La bele istori malu, i la bele laran moras ema.
Maibee imi tenki halo tuir Nai Jesus Kristu nia moris. I la bele hanoin tan atu halo tuir imi nia hakarak aat.
Simu di-diak sarani sira nebee mak sei duvida, i la bele diskuti malu ho sira kona ba sira nia duvida nee.
Ema sarani balu fiar katak ita bele haan hahaan saida deit. Balu sei duvida, sira haan modo tahan deit tanba sira hanoin dehan naan nee lulik ba sira.
Ema nebee dehan bele haan saida deit, nia la bele hatuun ema nebee mak lakohi haan naan. Nunee mos, ema nebee mak lakohi haan naan, la bele foo sala ba ema nebee haan naan nee, tanba Maromak simu tiha ona nia.
Imi nee see fali mak imi foo sala ba Patraun seluk nia atan? Sira nia patraun mak Maromak. Entaun Maromak deit mak bele tesi sira nia lia dehan, sira nee hamriik ka monu. I Nia mak bele tulun sira para sira hamriik.
Nunee mos, iha ema balu konsidera katak, loron balu loron boot, loron seluk loron baibain deit. Maibee iha ema seluk dehan, loron hotu-hotu hanesan deit iha Maromak nia oin. Ema ida-idak tenki desidi rasik kona ba buat nee.
Ema nebee konsidera liu loron balu, nia halo nunee atu hatudu nia respeitu ba ita nia Nai. I ema nebee haan naan, nia haan naan atu hatudu respeitu ba ita nia Nai, tanba nia foo agradese ba Maromak. Nunee mos ba ema nebee mak lakohi haan naan, nia mos halo nunee atu hatudu respeitu ba ita nia Nai, i nia mos foo agradese ba Maromak.<a href='#note-946' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba durante ita moris, ita moris laos deit ba ita nia aan. Ita mate mos laos mate ba ita nia aan deit.
Kuandu ita sei moris, ita moris ba ita nia Nai. I kuandu ita mate mos, ita mate ba ita nia Nai. Nunee atu ita moris ka ita mate, ita nafatin Nai Maromak nian.
Tanba nee duni mak Kristu mate i moris fila fali, atu Nia bele sai Nai ba ema nebee mak mate tiha ona ho mos ba ema nebee mak sei moris.
Se nunee nusaa mak imi foo sala ba imi nia maluk sarani? Nusaa mak imi hatuun sira? Afinal ita hotu-hotu sei hamriik iha Maromak nia oin para Nia tesi ita nia lia,<a href='#note-947' class='key'>✡</a>
hanesan mos hakerek iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Nai Maromak dehan,
‘Hau, Maromak Moris, jura katak,
ema hotu-hotu sei hakruuk mai Hau,
Entaun ita ida-idak tenki responsabiliza iha Maromak nia oin kona ba ita nia hahalok rasik.
Tanba nee, la bele foo sala ba malu tan. Maibee kuidadu di-diak para imi nia hahalok la bele halo too imi nia maluk sarani sidi ka monu ba sala.
Tanba hau laran ida ho Nai Jesus, hau fiar metin katak, hahaan saida deit Maromak la bandu. Maibee se ema ida hanoin katak Maromak bandu hahaan ruma, entaun ema nee la bele haan duni.
Se karik o haan buat nee iha nia oin, nia sei laran susar. Nunee bainhira o halo ida nee, o la hatudu domin ba nia. La bele estraga fali o nia maluk tanba deit o hakarak haan buat nee. Tanba Kristu mos mate ba nia.
Kuidadu, keta halo be o nia hahalok nebee o konsidera diak nee, halo ema seluk hatete aat fali o.
Tanba ba Maromak, saida mak ita haan-hemu nee, laos problema. Maromak ukun ita nudar Liurai, i Nia hakarak para ita moris loos, dame malu, i laran haksolok, tanba Espiritu Santu hela iha ita.
Ema nebee serbi Kristu nunee, nia halo haksolok Maromak nia laran, i ema seluk mos gaba nia.
Tanba nee, ita hotu tenki hakaas aan tulun malu atu moris iha dame nia laran, i hametin ita nia maluk sira nia fiar.
La bele estraga Maromak nia servisu iha ema seluk nia moris tanba deit problema haan-hemu. Hahaan saida deit Maromak la bandu. Maibee se o haan buat ruma mak halo o nia maluk sidi, o sala.
Diak liu ita la bele haan naan ka hemu tua ka halo saida deit mak halo too ita nia maluk monu.
Husik Maromak deit mak hatene o nia hanoin kona ba buat sira nee. Se o fiar katak buat nebee o halo nee loos hela, i senti nee la sala ida, nee bensaun ida hosi Maromak.
Maibee se o haan buat ruma ho duvida katak, hahaan nee Maromak keta bandu karik, entaun Maromak foo sala ba o, tanba o la kumpri saida mak o rasik fiar. Tanba ema nebee la kumpri buat nebee nia rasik fiar, nia halo sala.
Ita nebee fiar metin tenki iha pasiensia hodi ajuda maluk sira nebee mak sei duvida kona ba saida mak ita sarani sira bele halo. Ita la bele halo haksolok deit ita nia aan.
Maibee ita ida-idak tenki halo haksolok ita nia maluk hodi halo diak ba nia, para nia fiar bele metin liu tan.
Tanba Kristu rasik mos la moris halo haksolok deit Nia Aan. Iha Livru Sagradu, Kristu dehan ba Maromak, “Liafuan aat nebee ema hatete ba Ita Boot monu kona mos Hau.”<a href='#note-949' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat hotu-hotu nebee hakerek nanis ona iha Livru Sagradu, hakerek atu hanorin ita. Livru Sagradu nee tulun ita atu aguenta iha terus laran i foo korajen mai ita, atu nunee ita laran metin ba Maromak.
Maromak sempre tulun ita atu aguenta iha terus laran i foo korajen ba ita. Hau harohan atu Nia halo imi moris neon ida laran ida hodi tuir Kristu Jesus.
Nunee mak imi hamutuk lian ida hodi foti aas Maromak nia naran. Nia mak ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu nia Aman.
Tanba nee imi tenki simu malu, hanesan Kristu simu tiha ona imi. Bainhira ema haree imi simu malu, sira sei foti aas Maromak nia naran.
La bele haluha, Kristu foo Nia Aan para serbi ema Judeu hodi hatudu ba sira katak, Maromak sempre halo tuir Nia promesa. Maromak nia promesa ba ita nia bei-ala sira, Kristu rasik mak kumpri.
Nunee ema nebee laos Judeu mos sei foti aas Maromak nia naran tanba Nia mos hatudu nia domin ba sira. Nee hanesan hakerek ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Tanba nee hau sei hahii Ita Boot iha ema nebee laos Judeu nia leet.
Hau sei hananu foti aas Ita Boot nia naran.”<a href='#note-950' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha fatin seluk hakerek dehan,
“Imi sira nebee laos Judeu,
haksolok hamutuk ho Maromak nia povu.”<a href='#note-951' class='key'>✡</a>
Hakerek mos dehan,
“Imi nebee laos Judeu, hahii ita nia Nai!
Ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu, hananu foti aas Nia naran!”<a href='#note-952' class='key'>✡</a>
“Jessé nia Jerasaun ida sei mai,
Nia sei ukun nasaun hotu-hotu.
Ema nebee laos Judeu laran metin ba Nia.”<a href='#note-953' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak rasik mak halo ita laran metin ba Nia. Hau harohan atu Nia halo imi haksolok teb-tebes i foo paz ho hakmatek ba imi, tanba imi fiar ba Nia. Nunee kbiit Espiritu Santu nian sei halo imi laran metin liu tan ba Maromak.
Maun-alin sira, hau fiar katak, imi nia laran diak teb-tebes, imi kompriende ona buat barak, i imi bele ona hanorin malu.
Maski nunee, iha surat nee hau koalia mo-moos ba imi kona ba buat balu, tanba hau hakarak foo hanoin fila fali ba imi. Hau brani hakerek nunee tanba Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak mai hau.
Nia foti hau sai Kristu Jesus nia atan para serbi ema nebee laos Judeu. Hau kaer knaar hanesan nai lulik ida hodi foo sai Maromak nia Liafuan Diak. Nunee ema nebee laos Judeu bele sai hanesan oferta ida nebee diak ba Maromak, oferta ida nebee Nia hakarak simu tanba Espiritu Santu halo sira sai moos tiha ona.
Nee mak hau nia laran haksolok loos ho hau nia servisu ba Maromak, tanba hau laran ida ho Kristu Jesus.
Hau la brani koalia buat seluk, hau so brani foo sai deit kona ba buat nebee Kristu halo ona liu hosi hau. Ema nebee laos Judeu agora rona ba Maromak tanba hau nia liafuan ho hau nia hahalok,
ho sinal ho milagre bo-boot nebee mak hau halo ho Maromak nia Espiritu nia kbiit. Hau foo sai tiha ona Liafuan Diak kona ba Kristu hosi Jerusalém too iha provinsia Ilíriku, hau nia servisu iha rai nee hotu ona.
Hori uluk kedas hau nia hakarak mak nee: atu foo sai Liafuan Diak iha fatin nebee mak ema seidauk rona kona ba Kristu, tanba hau hakarak harii uma mesak, laos kontínua deit halo uma nebee ema seluk hahuu harii ona.
Nunee hau halo tuir liafuan nebee hakerek iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Ema nebee seidauk rona kona ba Nia,
sira sei hatene.
Ema nebee seidauk simu Nia Liafuan,
sira sei kompriende.”<a href='#note-954' class='key'>✡</a>
Durante tinan barak nia laran hau hakarak teb-tebes atu baa haree imi, maibee too agora la konsege tanba hau nia servisu iha nee.<a href='#note-955' class='key'>✡</a>
Agora servisu nee hotu ona,
i hau iha planu atu baa iha rai Espanha. Hau hakarak vizita lai imi para kontenti hamutuk ho imi lai, depois imi bele ajuda hau baa liu Espanha.
Maibee agora, hau baa Jerusalém lai, atu lori osan entrega ba Maromak nia povu sira iha nebaa.
Tanba sarani sira iha provinsia Masedónia ho Akaia hakarak foo tulun ba Maromak nia povu nebee mak kiak iha Jerusalém.<a href='#note-956' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira foo ho kontenti, i sira iha duni obrigasaun atu foo. Tanba sira nebee laos Judeu simu tiha ona bensaun hosi Maromak liu hosi ema Judeu. Tanba nee mak ema nebee laos Judeu iha obrigasaun atu ajuda ema Judeu.<a href='#note-957' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun hau baa entrega lai osan nebee mak sira foo. Entrega tiha hotu, hau baa vizita imi mak foin baa liu iha Espanha.
Hau laran metin katak bainhira hau baa vizita imi, hau lori bensaun boot hosi Kristu.
Maun-alin sira, tanba Jesus Kristu sai ona ita nia Nai, i tanba Maromak nia Espiritu halo ita hadomi malu, nunee hau husu boot atu imi harohan makaas hamutuk ho hau para Maromak tulun hau.
Husu atu Maromak kuidadu hau iha provinsia Judeia, atu ema nebee mak lakohi fiar ba Maromak la bele halo aat hau. I husu atu bainhira hau entrega osan ba sarani sira iha Jerusalém, sira bele simu ho di-diak.
Depois, se Maromak hakarak, hau bele baa vizita imi ho laran haksolok, i ita nia laran bele hakmatek hamutuk.
Hau harohan atu Maromak Dame Nain akompanha imi hotu. Amen.
Liu hosi surat nee hau foo konhese ita nia irmán Febe. Nia nee serbi sarani sira iha sidade Senkreia.
Hatoo hau nia kumprimentus ba Priscila<a href='#note-958' class='key'>*</a> ho nia laen Akila. Sira nain rua halao Kristu Jesus nia servisu hanesan ho hau.<a href='#note-959' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk sira atu mate sal-sala bainhira sira salva hau. Laos hau mesak deit mak foo obrigadu ba sira, maibee sarani sira hotu nebee laos Judeu mos foo obrigadu ba sira nia laran diak.
Kumprimentus ba sarani sira nebee baibain halibur malu halo orasaun iha Priscila ho Akila nia uma.
Kumprimentus ba hau nia belun diak Epenetus. Nia mak ema primeiru nebee fiar ba Kristu iha provinsia Ázia.
Kumprimentus ba Maria, nia servisu makaas ba imi.
Kumprimentus ba Andróniku ho Júnias. Sira nee hau nia maluk Judeu, ami uluk dadur hamutuk iha komarka. Sira mak fiar uluk ba Kristu, bainhira hau seidauk fiar. Sira nain rua naran boot iha apostolu sira nia leet.
Kumprimentus ba Amplíatu. Hau hadomi nia tanba ami nain rua laran ida ho ita nia Nai.
Kumprimentus ba Urbano. Nia halao Kristu nia servisu hamutuk ho ami. Kumprimentus mos ba hau nia belun diak Estákis.
Kumprimentus ba Apeles, nia liu ona provasaun hodi fiar metin nafatin ba Kristu.
Kumprimentus ba ema hotu nebee hela iha Aristóbulo nia uma.
Kumprimentus ba Herodiaun, hau nia maluk Judeu.
Kumprimentus ba maluk sira iha Narciso nia uma nebee fiar ba ita nia Nai.
Kumprimentus ba ita nia maluk feto Trifena ho Trifosa. Sira nain rua servisu makaas ba ita nia Nai.
Kumprimentus ba hau nia belun diak Pérsida. Irmán nee mos servisu makaas loos ba ita nia Nai.
Kumprimentus ba Rufu, ita nia Nai mak hili nia. Kumprimentus mos ba nia inan, hau konsidera nia hanesan hau nia inan rasik.<a href='#note-960' class='key'>✡</a>
Kumprimentus ba Asínkritu, Flegonte, Hermes, Pátrobas, Hermas ho mos maluk sarani sira seluk nebee baibain halibur hamutuk ho sira.
Kumprimentus ba Filólogu, Júlia, Nereu ho nia feton, ba Olimpas ho mos ba sarani sira seluk nebee mak baibain halibur hamutuk ho sira.
Rei malu tuir dalan sarani sira nian. Kristu nia povu iha fat-fatin mos foo kumprimentus ba imi.<a href='#note-961' class='key'>✡</a>
Maun-alin sira, hau husu atu imi kuidadu teb-tebes ho ema nebee mak hakarak halo imi sarani sira fahe malu i halo imi nia fiar nakdoko. Sira kontra fali hanorin nebee imi simu tiha ona. Nunee hadook aan hosi ema hanesan nee.
Tanba ema hanesan nee laos serbi Kristu ita nia Nai, maibee serbi deit sira nia aan. Sira uza liafuan midar i kos-kose ema, ho nunee sira konsege bosok ema nebee mak la hatene buat diak ka buat aat.
Ema hotu-hotu rona tiha ona katak imi moris tuir Maromak nia hakarak. Nee halo hau nia laran haksolok. Maibee Hau hakarak atu imi mos matenek halo buat nebee mak diak, i lalika halo buat aat.
La kleur tan Maromak Dame Nain sei sama rahun tiha diabu nia boot iha imi nia ain okos. Hau harohan atu ita nia Nai Jesus hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi.
Timóteo, hau nia kolega servisu, foo kumprimentus ba imi, nunee mos Lúcio, Jasom ho Sosípatru, sira nee hau nia maluk Judeu.
<a href='#note-962' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau, Tércio mak hakerek Paulo nia liafuan iha surat nee. Hau foo kumprimentus ba imi, tanba ita hotu tuir ita nia Nai.
Gaio mos foo kumprimentus ba imi. Hau, Paulo hela iha nia uma, i hau nia maluk sarani sira baibain halibur malu halo orasaun iha nee.
Erastu, xefi finansas iha sidade nee, ho ita nia maluk Quarto mos foo kumprimentus ba imi.<a href='#note-963' class='key'>✡</a>
[Hau harohan atu ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi hotu. Amen.]<a href='#note-964' class='key'>†</a>
Hahii Nai Maromak! Nia mak iha kbiit atu halo ita sai forti, liu hosi Liafuan Diak nebee mak hau foo sai kona ba Jesus Kristu. Hori uluk liu, ema la hatene Maromak nia planu kona ba Kristu, tanba sei segredu hela.
Nia deit mak Maromak, Nia deit mak hatene buat hotu-hotu. Mai ita foti aas Nia naran too tinan ba tinan liu hosi Jesus Kristu. Amen.
Surat nee hosi hau, Paulo. Hau Kristu Jesus nia atan. Maromak mak hili hau sai Jesus nia apostolu hodi haruka hau foo sai Nia Liafuan Diak.
Liafuan Diak nee hori uluk kedas Maromak promete tiha ona liu hosi Nia profeta sira, i sira hakerek iha Livru Sagradu.
3-4 Liafuan Diak nee koalia kona ba Maromak nia Oan Jesus Kristu, ita nia Nai. Nudar ema, Jesus moris mai hosi liurai David nia jerasaun. Maibee Maromak hatudu mo-moos katak, Jesus nee mos Maromak nia Oan. Ita hatene nunee tanba Espiritu nebee mak iha Jesus nee santu teb-tebes, hanesan Maromak, i Maromak mos halo Jesus moris fali hosi mate.
Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak mai hau liu hosi Jesus too Nia hili hau sai apostolu. Nia hili hau para lori ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu bele fiar ba Jesus i halo tuir Nia liafuan, atu nunee ema hotu-hotu bele foti aas Nia naran.
Nunee mos imi iha Roma, Maromak mos hili ona imi atu sai Jesus Kristu nia ema.
Hau haruka surat nee ba imi. Maromak hadomi imi, i hili ona imi sai Nia povu.
Hau harohan para ita nia Aman Maromak ho mos ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba imi, i foo paz ho hakmatek ba imi.
Uluk nanain, hau foo agradese ba hau nia Maromak hodi Jesus Kristu nia naran tanba imi hotu fiar ba Jesus. Tanba ema iha nebee-nebee deit konta kona ba imi nia fiar nee.
Maromak rasik hatene katak hau harohan beibeik ba imi. Maromak nee mak hau serbi ho laran tomak hodi foo sai Liafuan Diak kona ba Nia Oan.
Bainhira hau halo orasaun, hau sempre harohan ba imi. I hau mos husu atu Maromak bele loke dalan mai hau atu baa haree imi, tanba kleur ona hau hakarak nunee.
Hau hakarak teb-tebes atu baa vizita imi, para hau bele fahe ba imi kbiit nebee hau hetan hosi Maromak. Nunee imi nia fiar bele metin liu tan.
Hau hakarak atu hau nia fiar bele foo forsa ba imi, i imi nia fiar mos bele foo forsa mai hau.
Maun-alin sira, hau hakarak para imi hatene katak, dala barak ona hau halo planu atu baa vizita imi, maibee too agora sempre iha buat ruma mak taka dalan. Hau hakarak baa para hau bele lori ema barak iha nebaa hodi fiar metin ba Kristu, hanesan mos hau lori ona ema nebee mak laos Judeu iha fatin selu-seluk atu fiar metin ba Nia.<a href='#note-856' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau iha obrigasaun atu foo sai Liafuan Diak ba ema hotu-hotu: atu ema nebee tuir kultura Gregu ka ema fuik, atu ema matenek ka ema beik.<a href='#note-857' class='key'>*</a>
Tanba nee mak hau hakarak teb-tebes baa foo sai Liafuan Diak mos ba imi iha Roma.
Hau la moe foo sai Jesus nia Liafuan Diak. Tanba Liafuan Diak nee iha kbiit hosi Maromak hodi salva see-see deit mak fiar, primeiru ba ema Judeu sira, depois ba ema hosi nasaun sira seluk.<a href='#note-858' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba Liafuan Diak foo sai oinsaa Maromak bele simu ita hodi deklara katak ita nia sala moos tiha ona. Nia dalan mak nee: ita tenki fiar ba Nia. Dalan seluk la iha. Nee hanesan buat nebee hakerek ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan, “Ema tenki fiar ba Maromak mak foin Maromak simu nia i foo moris rohan-laek ba nia.”<a href='#note-859' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak iha lalehan hatudu sai katak, Nia hirus teb-tebes too kastigu ema nebee mak la interese Nia ho ema nebee mak hahalok aat. Sira nia hahalok aat nee taka ema seluk nia matan atu la bele haree dalan loos.
Tuir loos buat nebee ita ema bele hatene kona ba Maromak, ema aat sira nee mos hatene, tanba Maromak hatudu mo-moos ona ba sira.
Tanba desde Maromak halo lalehan ho rai, ita ema bele hatene klaru katak Nia nee Maromak i Nia kbiit la hotu la remata, maski ita nia matan la haree. Nunee la iha razaun ida ba sira atu dehan katak sira la hatene Maromak, tanba sira bele hatene liu hosi buat nebee mak Nia halo tiha ona nee.
Maski sira hatene Maromak, maibee sira lakohi foti aas Nia naran nudar Maromak, i lakohi foo agradese ba Nia. Sira nia hanoin la loos ona, sira nia neon mos nakukun tiha.<a href='#note-860' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira foti aan dehan, sira ema matenek, afinal sira sai beik-teen.
Sira la adora Maromak ida nebee makaas teb-tebes i moris tinan ba tinan. Maibee sira adora fali estatua nebee ema halo tuir modelu oi-oin, hanesan ema, manu, animal ain haat ho animal nebee dolar iha rai. Afinal buat sira nee hotu tenki mate.<a href='#note-861' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee mak Maromak husik tiha liman para sira moris tuir deit sira nia hakarak hodi halo buat aat oi-oin nebee iha ona sira nia laran. Sira foo sira nia isin lolon ba malu hodi halo sala foer oi-oin ba malu.
Maromak ida nebee loos, sira troka tiha ho buat nebee falsu. Sira la adora Maromak ida nebee halo buat hotu-hotu, maibee sira adora fali buat nebee mak Maromak halo. Tuir lo-loos Maromak nee mak ita tenki hahii too tinan ba tinan. Amen.
Tanba nee mak Maromak husik tiha liman para sira bele halo sala foer saida deit tuir sira nia hakarak, too feto sira mos la hola mane hanesan baibain, maibee hola fali sira nia feto maluk.
Nunee mos mane sira husik tiha relasaun seksual ho feto hodi kaan fali sira nia mane maluk, too mane ho mane halo sala foer. Tanba nee sira hetan ona kastigu tuir sira nia hahalok aat nee.
Ema sira nee la interese atu hanoin tan Maromak ona. Nee mak Maromak husik tiha liman para sira hanoin mak buat aat deit, i halo buat nebee tuir lo-loos la bele halo.
i hatete aat ema seluk. Sira odi Maromak, malkriadu, foti aan i halo aan. Sira hanoin aat hela deit, i gosta kontra sira nia inan-aman.
Sira lakohi atu hatene saida mak loos, i la halo tuir buat nebee mak sira promete. Sira la hatene hadomi ema, i la iha karidade.
Sira hatene ona Maromak nia lei nebee dehan, ema nebee halo buat aat nunee, merese hetan kastigu mate. Maski sira hatene ona lei nee, maibee sira halo nafatin buat aat sira nee. Laos nee deit, maibee sira gosta atu ema seluk mos halo tuir buat sira nee.
Entaun, belun, se o tesi lia mesak katak o nia maluk merese hetan kastigu, kuidadu! O nia liafuan nee hamonu fali o. Tanba o mos halo sala hanesan nia. Nunee bainhira o hatudu liman ba nia, o deklara katak o rasik mos tenki hetan kastigu nee.<a href='#note-862' class='key'>✡</a>
Ita hatene, bainhira Maromak desidi atu foo kastigu ba ema nebee halo buat aat sira nee, Nia desizaun nee sempre loos.
Nunee, se o hatudu liman ba ema seluk, maibee o rasik halo aat hanesan ema nee, keta hanoin dehan o bele halai sees hosi Maromak nia kastigu!
O hatene katak, Maromak laran diak teb-tebes i Nia aguenta hela ho pasiensia naruk. Nusaa mak o la respeita Nia laran diak nee? Keta halo be o la kompriende katak, Nia hatudu Nia laran diak ba o para o bele hakribi o nia sala hodi fila fali ba Nia.
Maibee o ulun toos i lakohi hakribi o nia sala. Nunee iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak hatudu Nia hirus hodi kastigu ema nebee mak halo sala, o nia kastigu sei todan liu tan. Iha tempu nebaa ema hotu-hotu sei haree katak, Maromak tesi lia ho lo-loos.
Nia sei foo ba ema ida-ida tuir nia hahalok.<a href='#note-863' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha ema balu halo buat diak beibeik tanba sira hakarak atu Maromak respeita i foti aas sira nia naran i halo sira moris tinan ba tinan. Ba sira nee Maromak sei foo moris rohan-laek.
Maibee iha mos ema balu mak hanoin sira nia aan deit, i lakohi halo tuir buat nebee mak loos, sira halo aat hela deit. Ba sira nee Maromak sei hirus teb-tebes too foo kastigu todan.
Ema sira nebee halo buat aat, sira sei hetan susar ho terus. Atu ema Judeu ka laos ema Judeu, sira hetan hotu.
Maibee ema sira nebee halo buat diak, Maromak sei respeita i foti aas sira nia naran, i foo paz ho hakmatek ba sira. Atu ema Judeu ka laos ema Judeu, sira hotu simu,
tanba Maromak la fihir ema.<a href='#note-864' class='key'>✡</a>
See-see deit mak halo sala sei hetan kastigu, nia sei mate haketak aan hosi Maromak. Ema nebee laos Judeu, la hatene lei nebee Maromak foo ba Moisés. Maromak kastigu sira, la bazeia ba lei nee. Maibee ema Judeu hatene lei Moisés nian, i Maromak sei kastigu sira tuir lei nee.
Se ita ema atu moris loos iha Maromak nia oin, ita rona Nia lei hosi tilun deit la too, maibee Maromak dehan, ema nebee moris tuir lei, sira mak moris loos.
Maski ema nebee laos Judeu la hatene Maromak nia lei, maibee dala ruma sira halo tuir duni buat nebee lei nee haruka tanba sira rasik hanoin hahalok nee loos. Nee hatudu katak, sira nia neon rasik hanesan lei ida ba sira nia moris.
Buat nebee ema laos Judeu halo nee hatudu katak saida mak Maromak tau iha Nia lei, iha tiha ona sira nia neon ho laran. Tanba dala ruma sira rasik hatene katak sira nia hahalok sala, i dala ruma mos sira rasik hatene dehan sira halo buat nebee mak loos.
Tuir Liafuan Diak nebee hau baibain hanorin katak, iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak foti Jesus Kristu para tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia, Nia sei tesi tuir sira ida-idak nia hahalok. Too ema nia segredu mos Nia sei foo justisa hotu.
Entaun, oinsaa ho imi nebee ema Judeu? Imi laran metin katak imi diak ona tanba imi hatene Maromak nia lei, i imi gaba aan kona ba imi nia relasaun ho Maromak.
Imi hatene Maromak nia hakarak, i hatene saida mak diak liu, tanba mestri sira hanorin ona ba imi hosi Maromak nia lei.
Imi fiar aan dehan, imi bele hatudu dalan ba ema matan delek. Imi konsidera imi nia aan hanesan naroman nebee leno ema nebee moris iha nakukun laran.
Imi hanoin katak imi bele hanorin ema beik i imi bele sai mestri ba labarik kiik-oan nebee la hatene buat ida. Imi hanoin nunee tanba hosi Maromak nia lei nee ema bele hatene buat loos.
Imi hanorin ona ema seluk, nusaa mak imi la hanorin imi nia aan rasik? Imi koalia makaas dehan keta naok, maibee imi la naok ka?
Imi dehan, la bele halo relasaun seksual ho ema nebee laos o nia feen ka laen. Afinal imi rasik halo buat nee. Imi hakribi teb-tebes adora lulik, maibee imi naok fali sasaan hosi uma lulik.
Imi foti aan dehan imi mak hatene Maromak nia lei, maibee imi rasik kontra fali lei nee hodi hatuun Maromak nia naran.
Hori uluk hakerek ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan, “Tanba imi ema Judeu nia hahalok mak ema nebee laos Judeu hatete aat Maromak nia naran.”<a href='#note-865' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira imi ema Judeu sunat, nee hatudu katak imi tama ona ba Maromak nia povu. Nunee se imi halo tuir Maromak nia lei, sunat iha folin ba imi. Maibee se imi la halo tuir Nia lei, imi hanesan ema nebee la sunat.
Se iha ema ruma nebee la sunat maibee nia moris tuir Maromak nia lei, entaun Maromak sei simu nia hanesan fali ema nebee sunat tiha ona.
Ema Judeu isin, laos haree hosi liur. I sunat lo-loos laos buat nebee ema halo iha isin lolon deit.
Maibee ema Judeu isin, haree hosi nia laran. I sunat nebee loos mak sunat hosi laran, nebee Maromak nia Espiritu mak halo, laos sunat iha isin deit tuir lei. Ema nebee sunat hosi laran nee, Maromak mak gaba nia, laos ema mak gaba.<a href='#note-866' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun, sai ema Judeu iha folin ka lae? I sunat tuir lei Judeu nian iha folin saida?
Iha folin boot oi-oin! Ida boot liu mak Maromak foo fiar ba ema Judeu atu kuidadu di-diak Nia liafuan.
Maski nunee, ema Judeu balu la moris tuir Maromak nia liafuan. Kuandu sira la moris tuir, Maromak halo saida? Nia halo tuir nafatin Nia liafuan ka lae?
Nia kumpri nafatin! Maski ema hotu-hotu iha mundu bosok tuun-sae mos, Maromak loos nafatin. Nee hanesan hakerek tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Iha ema balu foo sala dehan,
Maromak tesi lia la loos.
Maibee sira sei haree mo-moos katak,
saida mak Nia koalia sempre loos,
i Nia sempre tesi lia ho lo-loos.”<a href='#note-867' class='key'>✡</a>
Keta halo be ema ruma hanoin nunee: “Kuandu ita halo buat aat, nee hatudu katak, Maromak la hanesan ita ema, Nia sempre halo buat nebee mak loos. Se nunee, nusaa mak Maromak kastigu nafatin ita bainhira ita halo buat aat?” Nee ema kriatura nia hanoin deit.
Maibee laos nunee! Tanba se Maromak la iha direitu atu kastigu ema, oinsaa mak Nia bele foo justisa ba ema hotu-hotu iha mundu?
Keta halo be ema ruma dehan tan nunee: “Kuandu hau bosok, ida nee halo ema seluk hahii liu tan Maromak, tanba Maromak sempre koalia lia loos. Entaun se hau nia sala halo ema seluk hahii Maromak, nusaa mak Nia foo sala fali hau dehan hau nee sala nain?”
Se ida nee loos karik, entaun bele mos dehan, “Diak liu ita halo buat aat, atu buat nebee diak mos bele aumenta.” Iha ema balu duun hau dehan hau mak hanorin hanesan nee. Ema nebee koalia hanesan nee, merese duni hetan kastigu nebee Maromak atu foo ba sira.
Nunee, oinsaa ho ita nebee ema Judeu? Ita diak liu fali ema nebee laos Judeu ka? Lae liu! Hau esplika ona ba imi katak, sala ukun ita ema hotu-hotu, atu ema Judeu ka laos Judeu.
Hanesan hakerek ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“La iha ema ida mak moris loos,
ida mos la iha.
La iha ema ida mak kompriende kona ba Maromak,
la iha ema ida mak buka Nia.
Hotu-hotu sees ona hosi dalan nebee loos,
sira hotu la iha folin ona.
La iha ema ida mak halo buat nebee diak,
ida mos la iha.<a href='#note-868' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira nia liafuan dodok dois
hanesan rate nebee ema kee fila fali.
Sira nia ibun so hasai deit liafuan bosok.
Liafuan nebee sai hosi sira nia ibun
Sira nia ibun nakonu ho liafuan aat,
sira gosta hotar ema.<a href='#note-870' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira lalais loos atu oho ema.
Sira estraga door,
i sempre halo ema seluk laran susar.
Sira la hatene moris hakmatek,<a href='#note-871' class='key'>✡</a>
i la hatene hamtauk Maromak.”<a href='#note-872' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun, ita hatene katak, liafuan hotu-hotu nebee hakerek iha Maromak nia lei koalia kona ba ema Judeu, tanba ema Judeu mak moris iha lei nia okos. Maromak foo lei nee para ema ida la bele defende aan dehan nia moris loos. Aban-bainrua ema hotu-hotu iha mundu tenki hataan iha Maromak nia oin.
La iha ema ida mak halo tuir Maromak nia lei tomak too Maromak bele dehan, ema nee moris loos. Maibee hosi lei nee ita bele hatene mo-moos katak ita ema sala nain.<a href='#note-873' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee agora nee Maromak hatudu ona dalan ba ita, oinsaa mak ita bele diak malu ho Nia. Dalan nee la haree ba ita atu moris tuir lei ka lae. Uluk kedas Moisés nia lei ho mos profeta sira nia livru hakerek kona ba dalan nee.
Dalan mak nee: See mak fiar ba Jesus Kristu, Maromak simu nia hodi deklara katak nia sala moos tiha ona. Atu nia ema Judeu ka laos Judeu, Maromak la haree ba ida nee.<a href='#note-874' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba ema hotu-hotu halo sala. Maromak nia hakarak mai ita aas teb-tebes, maibee la iha ida mak too iha nebaa.
Maibee tanba deit Maromak nia laran diak mai ita mak Nia simu ita hodi deklara katak, ita nia sala moos tiha ona. Nia simu ita nunee tanba Kristu Jesus selu kotu ona ita.
Maromak foo Jesus para fakar Nia raan too mate hanesan sakrifisiu ida hodi hamoos ita nia sala, naran katak ita fiar ba Nia mate nee. Maromak halo nunee hodi hatudu katak, Nia sempre tesi lia ho lo-loos. Tanba uluk Nia sei pasiensia ho ema nia hahalok aat, Nia seidauk kastigu sira.
Maibee agora, liu hosi Jesus nia mate, Maromak hatudu Nia justisa, para ema bele haree katak Nia sempre tesi lia ho lo-loos. I liu hosi Jesus nia mate nee, ita mos haree katak, Maromak simu ema nebee mak fiar ba Jesus.
Se nunee, ita bele gaba aan ka? La bele! Tansaa mak la bele? Tanba laos ita tuir Maromak nia lei mak Maromak simu ita. Maibee Nia simu ita tanba ita fiar ba Jesus.
Tanba ita hatene katak, ema nebee Maromak simu mak ema nebee fiar ba Jesus, Nia laos simu ita tanba ita halo tuir Nia lei.
Maromak nee ema Judeu nia Maromak deit ka? Lae. Nia ema hotu-hotu nia Maromak.
Maromak nee ida deit. Nia simu ema Judeu kuandu sira fiar ba Nia. I ema nebee laos Judeu mos, Nia simu tanba sira nia fiar.<a href='#note-875' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun, se ita fiar ba Jesus Kristu, nee dehan katak ita soe tiha Maromak nia lei ka? Lae liu! Ita respeita liu tan lei nee.
Ita bele aprende hosi ita nia bei-ala Abraão.
Tansaa mak Maromak simu nia? Tanba nia halo buat nebee diak ka? Se nunee, Abraão bele iha razaun atu foti aan dehan nia mak diak liu, maski iha Maromak nia oin ita ema la bele foti aan. Maibee laos nunee.
Iha Livru Sagradu hakerek dehan, “Abraão fiar ba Maromak, nee mak Maromak simu nia hodi deklara katak nia sala moos tiha ona.”<a href='#note-876' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee servisu, bainhira patraun selu nia kolen, osan nee laos prezente, nia patraun iha obrigasaun atu foo.
Maibee ita ho Maromak laos nunee. Ita laos halo tuir Maromak nia lei para Nia tenki simu ita. Maibee ita fiar deit ba Nia, tanba ita laran metin katak, Maromak mak bele simu ema aat hodi deklara katak sira nia sala moos tiha ona. Nunee, Maromak simu ita tanba deit ita nia fiar.
Liurai David mos hatete nunee. Nia dehan, se Maromak la haree ba ema ida nia hahalok, maibee simu nafatin ema nee, entaun ema nee sorti boot. David dehan nunee:
“Se ema kontra Maromak nia lei maibee Maromak foo perdaun,
ema nee sorti boot.
Se nia halo sala maibee Maromak hamoos tiha nia sala,
Se Nai Maromak la husu tuir ona nia sala,
ema nee sorti boot.”<a href='#note-877' class='key'>✡</a>
Sorti nee so ba ema Judeu nebee sunat ka? Ema seluk lae ka? Laos nunee! Ami foo hanoin ba imi ona katak, tanba Abraão fiar ba Maromak mak Maromak simu nia hodi deklara katak nia nia sala moos tiha ona.
Hori-bainhira mak Maromak simu nia? Molok Abraão sunat ka, depois? Molok nia sunat, laos depois!
Maromak simu Abraão tanba nia fiar, depois mak nia sunat. Sunat nee hanesan sinal ida atu hatudu katak Maromak simu tiha ona nia tanba nia fiar ba Maromak. Nunee Abraão sai aman ba ema hotu-hotu nebee fiar ba Maromak maibee la sunat, atu nunee Maromak mos simu sira hodi deklara katak sira nia sala moos tiha ona tanba sira nia fiar.<a href='#note-878' class='key'>✡</a>
Abraão mos sai aman ba ema Judeu nebee sunat, naran katak ita fiar ba Maromak, hanesan ita nia bei-ala Abraão mos fiar bainhira nia seidauk sunat.
Maromak promete ba Abraão ho nia jerasaun dehan, aban-bainrua mundu nee sei sai sira nian. Maromak promete nunee laos tanba Abraão moris tuir lei, maibee tanba nia fiar ba Maromak. Hosi Abraão nia fiar nee mak Maromak simu nia hodi deklara katak nia sala moos tiha ona.<a href='#note-879' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba se ita ema halo tuir Maromak nia lei mak foin bele simu buat nebee Maromak promete, entaun ita nia fiar ba Maromak la iha folin, i Maromak nia promesa mos la vale buat ida.<a href='#note-880' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba se lei iha, entaun ita ema halo sala kontra lei nee, halo Maromak fakar Nia hirus mai ita. Maibee se lei la iha karik, entaun sala kontra lei mos la iha.
Nee mak ita tenki fiar ba Maromak mak foin bele simu buat nebee Nia promete atu foo. Nunee, nudar Abraão nia jerasaun, ita bele laran metin katak, Maromak sei foo ba ita ho gratis. Atu ita ema Judeu nebee moris tuir lei ka, ita moris fiar ba Maromak hanesan Abraão, ita hotu sei simu. Tanba Abraão mak sai aman ba ita hotu.<a href='#note-881' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Livru Sagradu, Maromak promete ba Abraão dehan, “Hau sei halo o sai nasaun barak nia aman.” Abraão fiar Maromak, tanba Maromak mak halo moris fali ema mate, i Nia koalia deit, buat nebee la iha, bele iha.<a href='#note-882' class='key'>✡</a>
Abraão laran metin hodi hein nafatin Maromak nia promesa, maski tuir ita ema nia haree la bele akontese. Tanba nee nia sai duni nasaun barak nia aman, hanesan Maromak hatete ona ba nia dehan, “O nia jerasaun sei sai barak teb-tebes.”<a href='#note-883' class='key'>✡</a>
Abraão fiar metin nafatin, maski nia hatene aan katak, nia katuas liu ona, maizoumenus tinan atus ida, i nia feen Sara mos la bele hetan oan ona.<a href='#note-884' class='key'>✡</a>
Abraão nia fiar la nakdoko, nia la duvida katak Maromak sei kumpri Nia promesa. Maibee nia fiar metin liu tan i nia foti aas Maromak nia naran.
Nia laran metin katak Maromak iha kbiit atu halo saida mak Nia promete tiha ona.
Nee mak Livru Sagradu dehan, “Maromak simu nia hodi deklara katak nia nia sala moos tiha ona.”
Liafuan nebee hakerek nee, laos ba Abraão deit,
maibee mos ba ita. Maromak mos sei simu ita tanba ita fiar ba Nia. Maromak nee mak halo moris fali ita nia Nai Jesus hosi mate.
Nia entrega Jesus ba ema oho tanba ita ema nia sala. Depois Maromak halo moris fali Nia para Maromak bele simu fali ita.<a href='#note-885' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak simu ona ita tanba ita fiar ba Kristu. Liu hosi ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu mak agora ita moris dame malu ona ho Maromak.
Kristu mos halo ita hatene Maromak nia laran diak mai ita iha ita nia moris agora, tanba ita fiar. Ita nia laran mos haksolok, tanba ita laran metin katak, aban-bainrua Maromak sei foo naroman lalehan nian mai ita.
Laos nee deit, maibee ita nia laran mos haksolok iha terus laran, tanba ita hatene katak, hosi terus nee ita aprende atu aguenta liu tan.
Se ita aguenta iha terus laran, ita nia moris halo haksolok Maromak nia laran. Se ita moris halo haksolok Nia laran, nee halo ita laran metin liu tan ba Maromak nia promesa.
Ita nia laran metin nee la saugati, tanba Maromak foo ona Nia Espiritu Santu mai ita, nunee ita hatene Maromak nia domin boot teb-tebes mai ita.
Iha tempu nebee mak ita ema la interese Maromak i la iha kbiit atu salva aan, iha tempu nee mak Kristu mate hodi troka ita.
Ita ema atu mate troka ema ida nebee moris loos, susar. Karik iha ema ida-rua prontu atu mate troka ema nebee laran diak teb-tebes.
Maibee Maromak hatudu Nia domin boot teb-tebes mai ita nunee: Kristu mate iha ita nia fatin bainhira ita sei moris iha sala nia laran.
Maromak simu ona ita tanba Kristu nia raan fakar too mate ba ita. Nunee ita hatene ona katak, Kristu sei salva ita iha loron ikus bainhira Maromak fakar Nia hirus mai mundu.
Uluk bainhira ita sei inimigu ho Maromak, Nia halo ita dame malu ho Nia liu hosi Nia Oan nia mate. Saa tan agora ita dame malu ona, ita sei hetan salvasaun tanba Nia Oan moris fila fali.
Hori uluk liu, sala tama iha mundu tanba ema ida deit, ema nee mak Adão. Nia mate tanba nia sala. Too ikus, ema hotu-hotu iha mundu tenki mate tanba sira hotu mos halo sala tuir nia.<a href='#note-886' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk, bainhira Maromak seidauk foo Nia lei ba Moisés, ema iha mundu nee halo ona sala. Maibee tanba seidauk iha lei, entaun ema nia sala ida-ida seidauk sura.
Maski nunee, hosi tempu Adão too tempu Moisés nian, mate ukun ona ema hotu-hotu. Laos deit ema nebee kontra Maromak nia orden hanesan Adão mak mate, maibee ema nebee halo sala selu-seluk mos mate hotu.
Adão nee ita bele kompara ho Ema ida nebee mak atu mai, nee mak Kristu.
Maibee Maromak nia diak la hanesan Adão nia sala. Adão nee ema ida deit, maibee tanba nia kontra Maromak nia orden, entaun ema hotu-hotu tenki mate. Jesus Kristu mos Ema ida deit, maibee tanba Kristu nia laran diak, entaun Maromak mos hatudu mo-moos Nia laran diak ba ema hotu, ida nee hanesan prezente ida nebee Nia foo ba ita gratis deit.
Prezente nebee Maromak foo ba ita nee, la hanesan ho buat nebee ita hetan hosi Adão nia sala. Bainhira ema ida nee halo sala, Maromak foo justisa dehan ita ema tenki hetan kastigu. Maibee agora ita ema halo sala barak liu ona. Maski nunee, Maromak foo Nia prezente mai ita nunee: Nia simu nafatin ita hodi deklara katak ita nia sala moos tiha ona.
Uluk ema ida Adão nee kontra Maromak nia orden, nunee mate ukun ema hotu-hotu. Maibee agora Ema ida seluk, Jesus Kristu, halo mudansa boot liu tan. Nia hatudu Nia laran diak teb-tebes mai ita too Nia simu ita hodi deklara katak ita nia sala moos tiha ona. Nunee Nia lori ita ba moris rohan-laek hodi foti ita kaer ukun hamutuk ho Nia.
Nunee, ema ida halo sala, lori Maromak nia kastigu ba ema hotu-hotu. I Ema ida seluk halo buat nebee loos, halo Maromak simu ita hodi halo ita moris tinan ba tinan.
Ema ida lakohi halo tuir Maromak nia liafuan, halo ema barak sai sala nain. Ida seluk halo tuir Maromak nia liafuan, i nunee sei halo ema barak diak malu ho Maromak.
Maromak foo Nia lei ba Moisés para ema hotu-hotu bele hatene lo-loos, sala nee saida. Maibee bainhira ema nia sala aumenta, Maromak mos hatudu liu tan Nia laran diak.
Uluk sala domina ema hotu-hotu, lori sira ba mate. Maibee agora Maromak nia laran diak domina ita, too Maromak mos simu fali ita, i lori ita ba moris rohan-laek liu hosi ita nia Nai Jesus Kristu.
Nunee, agora atu dehan saida? Keta halo be ema ruma hanoin nunee: “Se Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak ba ema nebee mak halo sala, entaun diak liu ita halo sala nafatin atu nunee Maromak hatudu liu tan Nia laran diak mai ita.”
Laos nunee! Ita atu moris nafatin iha sala nia laran, la bele ona! Tanba kona ba sala, ita hanesan mate tiha ona, i ema nebee mate la halo tan sala ona.
Tuir lo-loos imi hatene, momentu ita simu batizmu para ita sai laran ida ho Kristu Jesus, nee hanesan ita mos mate hamutuk ho Nia.
Bainhira ita simu batizmu, ita hanesan mate tiha ona i hakoi hamutuk ho Kristu. Ita tenki mate uluk ho Nia atu ita bele moris tuir fali dalan foun, hanesan mos Kristu moris fali ona ho Aman Maromak nia kbiit boot.<a href='#note-887' class='key'>✡</a>
Ita sai laran ida ona ho Kristu tanba ita hanesan mate tiha ona hamutuk ho Nia. Entaun klaru katak aban-bainrua ita mos sei moris fali hanesan Nia.
Ita hatene katak, uluk ita hakarak halo buat aat oi-oin. Maibee agora, bele dehan, ita nia aan ida uluk nee, la iha tiha ona, tanba mate tiha ona iha krus hamutuk ho Kristu. Nunee ita laos ona atan ba sala,
tanba ema nebee mate tiha ona, nia livre ona hosi sala.
Entaun, se ita mate ona ho Kristu, ita fiar katak ita mos sei moris hamutuk ho Nia.
Ita hatene katak, tanba Kristu moris fali ona hosi mate, entaun Nia sei la mate tan. Mate la ukun ona Nia.
Nia mate dala ida hodi halakon tiha sala nia kbiit. Maibee agora, Nia moris fali hodi foti aas Maromak nia naran.
Imi mos tenki konsidera imi nia aan nunee: Kona ba sala, imi hanesan mate tiha ona, maibee kona ba moris, imi moris hodi foti aas Maromak nia naran liu hosi Kristu Jesus.
Nee duni, la bele husik atu sala ukun imi nia isin nebee too loron ida sei mate nee. La bele tuir fali buat aat sira nebee mak imi nia isin hakarak halo.
La bele foo imi nia isin lolon para halo sala, hanesan fali sasaan nebee ema uza hodi halo buat aat. Maibee foo imi nia aan tomak ba Maromak. Nia lori ona imi hosi mate ba moris. Nunee entrega imi nia isin lolon ba Nia para Nia uza hodi halo buat nebee mak loos.
Tanba sala la ukun ona imi. Agora imi la moris ona iha Moisés nia lei nia okos, maibee Maromak nia laran diak mak domina fali imi.
Se ita la moris ona iha lei nia okos, maibee Maromak nia laran diak mak domina fali ita, entaun ita bele moris nafatin iha sala nia laran ka? La bele!
Imi hatene katak, se imi foo imi nia aan ba ema seluk atu halo tuir nia hakarak, nee hanesan imi sai ona atan ba ema nee. Nunee mos se imi foo aan atu halo sala, imi sai atan ba sala, i too ikus sala nee halo imi mate tinan ba tinan. Se imi foo aan atu halo tuir Maromak nia hakarak, imi sei moris loos.
Hau foo agradese ba Nai Maromak, maski uluk imi atan ba sala, maibee agora ho laran tomak imi moris tuir ona hanorin loos nebee imi simu tiha ona.
Maromak hasai ona imi hosi sala nia laran, i agora imi sai fali atan ba moris loos nian.
Uluk bainhira imi sei atan ba sala, imi la hatene moris loos.
Iha tempu nebaa imi simu buat diak saida hosi imi nia sala nee? La iha! Imi nia sala so halo moe deit imi, i too ikus lori imi ba mate.
Maibee agora nee Maromak halo imi livre ona hosi sala, i imi sai fali Maromak nia atan. Buat diak nebee imi simu mak nee: Imi sai ema nebee moris ho laran moos, nunee aban-bainrua imi sei hetan moris rohan-laek.
Tanba ema nebee mak atan ba sala, nia sei simu kastigu mate tinan ba tinan. Maibee ema nebee mak laran ida ho Kristu Jesus ita nia Nai, nia sei simu moris rohan-laek; ida nee Maromak foo mai ita gratis deit.
Maun-alin sira, imi ema nebee hatene lei, entaun imi kompriende katak, lei so vale ba ema moris deit.
Hau foti ezemplu hosi lei kazamentu nian. Tuir lei nee dehan, feto nebee kaben ona la bele husik nia laen durante nia laen sei moris. Maibee se nia laen mate, feto nee livre ona hosi lei kazamentu.
Nunee, se nia hola fali mane seluk bainhira nia laen sei moris hela, nia halo sala seksual. Maibee se nia laen mate tiha ona, nia livre ona hosi lei kazamentu. Nia kaben fali ho ema seluk mos, la sala ida.
Maun-alin sira, agora ita laos moris iha lei nia okos. Tanba kona ba lei, ita hanesan mate tiha ona hamutuk ho Kristu. Maibee ita sai fali atan ba Patraun ida seluk, Patraun nee mak Kristu. Nia moris fali ona hosi mate, atu ita bele serbi Maromak.
Uluk bainhira ita nia hakarak aat sei domina ita, lei foo hanoin mai ita atu la bele halo sala. Maibee bainhira ita hatene tuir tiha lei nee, ita hakarak atu kontra liu tan, too ita halo sala oi-oin, i sala nee lori ita ba mate tinan ba tinan.
Maibee agora ita livre ona hosi lei, tanba kona ba lei ita hanesan mate tiha ona. Nunee agora ita bele serbi Maromak laos tuir dalan uluk nian mak halo tuir deit lei nebee hakerek iha livru. Maibee ita serbi Nia liu hosi dalan foun, dalan nee mak Maromak nia Espiritu.
Nunee, agora ita atu dehan saida? Maromak nia lei nee buat aat ida ka? Lae liu! Tanba hosi lei nee mak foin hau hatene, sala nee saida. Por ezemplu, iha lei ida dehan, “La bele kaan ema nia sasaan.” Hosi lei ida nee mak foin hau kompriende katak, kaan sasaan nee buat aat ida.<a href='#note-888' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee sala iha nanis ona iha hau nia laran, nunee bainhira lei nee bandu atu la bele kaan ema nia sasaan, nee halo hau kaan buat oi-oin deit. Se la iha lei nebee bandu, sala mos la iha kbiit atu domina ita.
Uluk hau moris seidauk kompriende Maromak nia lei. Maibee bainhira hau aprende lei nee, sala mak buras fali iha hau nia moris,
halo hau hanesan mate haketak aan hosi Maromak. Uluk hau hanoin dehan, Maromak nia lei bele lori hau ba moris rohan-laek, afinal lori hau ba mate.
Tanba sala nebee iha hau nia laran nee, uza fali lei nee atu lohi hau i halo mate hau.<a href='#note-889' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun Maromak nia lei nee santu, i buat hotu-hotu iha lei nia laran mos santu, loos ho diak.
Se nunee, lei nebee diak nee mak halo hau mate ka? Lae! Sala nebee iha hau nia laran mak uza fali lei nee hodi halo mate hau. Nunee mak foin hau bele hatene katak, hau nia hahalok aat nee sala duni i Maromak hakribi teb-tebes.
Ita hatene katak, lei nee Maromak nia Espiritu mak foo. Maibee hau ema kriatura fraku ida, i sala kesi metin hau hanesan fali nia atan.
Hau la kompriende hau nia hahalok. Buat nebee hau hakarak halo, hau la halo. Buat nebee hau hakribi, ida nee mak hau halo fali.<a href='#note-890' class='key'>✡</a>
Sala nebee hau halo nee, hau rasik lakohi halo. Nee hatudu katak, hau konkorda ho Maromak nia lei.
Entaun, bele dehan, ida nebee halo buat aat nee, laos ona hau, maibee sala nebee iha hau nia laran mak halo.
Hau hatene katak, nudar sala nain la iha buat diak ida iha hau nia laran. Tanba hau hakarak duni halo buat nebee mak diak maibee la konsege.
Buat diak nebee hau hakarak halo, hau la halo. Buat aat nebee mak hau lakohi halo, nee mak hau halo fali.
Nunee se hau baibain halo buat nebee mak hau lakohi atu halo, nee hatudu katak, ida nebee halo buat aat nee, laos ona hau, maibee sala nebee iha hau nia laran mak halo.
Entaun buat nebee hau haree iha hau nia moris mak nee: Bainhira hau hakarak halo buat diak, buat aat iha hau nia laran sempre kontra.
Hau nia laran haksolok teb-tebes ho Maromak nia lei,
hau nia neon mos konkorda ho lei nee. Maski nunee, maibee hau haree katak sala mak servisu fali iha hau nia aan hodi kontra lei nee. Sala nee kesi metin hau hanesan dadur ida.
Koitadu! Hau susar liu! See mak bele salva hau hosi buat aat iha hau nia aan nebee lori hau ba mate tinan ba tinan?
Obrigadu ba Maromak! Nia mak salva hau liu hosi Jesus Kristu ita nia Nai.
Ita nebee laran ida ho Kristu Jesus, Maromak nia kastigu la kona tan ita.
Tanba uluk sala ukun ita, lori ita ba mate, maibee agora liu hosi Kristu Jesus, Maromak nia Espiritu hasai tiha ona ita hosi sala nia ukun hodi lori ita ba moris.
Lei Moisés nian la bele hasai ita hosi sala nia ukun, tanba ita ema sala nain la iha kbiit atu halo tuir lei nee hotu. Maibee Maromak bele hasai ita duni. Nia haruka Nia Oan rasik mai iha mundu para sai ema kriatura hanesan fali ita ema sala nain sira, i mate nudar sakrífisiu ida hodi halakon sala hosi ita ema nia laran.
Maromak halo nunee atu loke dalan ba ita para bele halo tuir Nia hakarak nebee hakerek tiha ona iha Nia lei. Ita bele halo tuir tanba ita moris tuir Maromak nia Espiritu, laos ona tuir ita nia hakarak aat.
Ema sira nebee moris tuir sira nia hakarak aat, sira so hanoin buat aat deit. Maibee ema nebee moris tuir Maromak nia Espiritu, sira so hanoin buat nebee Nia Espiritu hakarak.
Se o nia hakarak aat domina o nia hanoin, o sei mate tinan ba tinan. Maibee se Maromak nia Espiritu mak domina o nia hanoin, o sei moris i o nia laran sei hakmatek.
Se o nia hanoin nakonu ho buat aat, o sai inimigu ho Maromak, o la hakruuk ba Maromak nia lei, i la bele duni.
Se o moris tuir o nia hakarak aat, o la bele halo haksolok Maromak nia laran.
Maibee imi laos nunee. Imi la moris tuir imi nia hakarak aat, maibee moris tuir Maromak nia Espiritu, tanba Nia Espiritu hela iha imi nia laran. See mak la iha Kristu nia Espiritu, ema nee laos Kristu nian.
Imi nia isin lolon sei mate tanba imi nia sala. Maibee agora Kristu moris iha imi nia laran, nunee imi nia klamar sei moris nafatin, tanba Maromak simu ona imi hodi deklara katak, imi nia sala moos tiha ona.
Maromak mak halo Jesus Kristu moris fali hosi mate. Agora Nia Espiritu hela iha imi. Nunee aban-bainrua bainhira imi mate tiha ona, Maromak mos sei halo imi nia isin lolon moris fali, liu hosi Nia Espiritu nebee hela iha imi nia laran.<a href='#note-891' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni maun-alin sira, ita iha obrigasaun, maibee ita nia obrigasaun nee laos atu moris tuir ita ema nia hakarak aat.
Tanba se imi moris tuir imi nia hakarak aat, imi sei mate tinan ba tinan. Maibee se imi hamate hahalok aat hodi Espiritu Santu nia kbiit, imi sei hetan moris.
Tanba ema nebee moris tuir dalan nebee Maromak nia Espiritu hatudu ba nia, ema nee mak Maromak nia oan.
Espiritu nebee ita simu nee, laos halo ita sai fali hanesan atan nebee moris iha tauk nia laran. Maibee Espiritu nee halo ita hatene katak ita nee Maromak nia oan. Nee mak ita brani bolu Maromak “Apaa doben”.<a href='#note-892' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak nia Espiritu rasik hametin ita nia laran katak ita Maromak nia oan.
Se ita sai ona Maromak nia oan, nee dehan katak aban-bainrua ita sei simu rikusoin nebee mak Maromak rai hela ba Nia oan sira, hanesan mos Kristu simu. Naran katak ita mos hola parte iha Kristu nia terus, para aban-bainrua Maromak bele foti aas ita hanesan mos Nia foti aas Kristu.<a href='#note-893' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hanoin, terus nebee ita hetan agora hanesan buat kiik ida se ita kompara ho naroman lalehan nian nebee Maromak sei hatudu sai ba ita aban-bainrua.
Lalehan ho rai, ho buat hotu-hotu iha nia laran, buat sira nee hotu hein hela atu haree Maromak hatudu sai see-see loos mak sai Nia oan.
Mundu ho buat hotu-hotu iha nia laran la konsege halo tuir Maromak nia planu, tanba Maromak mak desidi nunee, laos tanba mundu rasik mak hakarak. Bele nunee mos, mundu nee sei iha esperansa nunee:<a href='#note-894' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski agora dadauk buat hotu-hotu tenki rahun ka mate, maibee aban-bainrua buat sira nee la rahun i la mate tan, tanba Maromak sei foo liberdade ba buat hotu-hotu, hanesan mos Nia foo ba Nia oan sira. I liberdade nee furak teb-tebes.
Ita hatene katak hori uluk liu too agora nee, mundu ho buat hotu nebee mak Maromak halo, hotu-hotu halerik hanesan feto ida nebee mak kanotak moras atu tuur ahi.
Laos mundu deit mak halerik. Maibee ita nebee simu ona Maromak nia Espiritu, ita mos halerik hodi hein hela atu simu tan direitu tomak nudar Maromak nia oan hakiak, nee dehan katak ita nia isin lolon livre ona, mate la ukun tan.<a href='#note-895' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba komesa ita foin simu salvasaun, ita hein ho laran metin atu Maromak foo buat nee mai ita. Maibee se buat nebee ita hein, ita hetan ona, ita sei la hein tan. Tanba ema la hein tan buat nebee mak nia hetan ona.
Maibee se ita seidauk hetan, ita hein ho pasiensia nafatin.
Nunee mos, Maromak nia Espiritu tulun ita, tanba ita ema nebee fraku. Ita la hatene saida mak ita atu husu ba Maromak liu hosi ita nia orasaun. Maibee Maromak nia Espiritu rasik halerik ba Maromak hodi harohan mai ita. Buat nebee Nia harohan, ita ema nia liafuan la too.
Maromak hatene ita nia laran, Nia mos hatene Nia Espiritu nia hanoin. Bainhira Espiritu harohan ba Maromak nia povu, buat nebee Nia husu sempre tuir Maromak nia hakarak.
Ita hatene katak, se ita hadomi Maromak, entaun saida mak akontese iha ita nia moris, Maromak uza buat sira nee hotu ba ita nia diak. Tanba Maromak bolu ona ita sai Nia ema, tuir Nia planu rasik.
Hori uluk liu, Nia konhese ona ita, i hili ita para sai hanesan Nia Oan Jesus, nunee Jesus mak maun boot, i ita sai Nia alin sira.
Nunee, ita atu dehan tan saida kona ba buat sira nee? Maromak defende ita, entaun see mak bele kontra ita?
Maromak laran luak teb-tebes, too Nia Oan rasik mos Nia foo para mate iha ita hotu nia fatin. Hosi nee ita bele hatene katak, Nia sei foo tan mai ita buat hotu-hotu nebee diak.
Maromak mak hili ita. Entaun see mak brani foo sala mai ita iha Maromak nia oin? Maromak simu ona ita hodi deklara katak, ita nia sala moos tiha ona.
Entaun see mak atu hamonu kastigu mai ita? La iha! Tanba Kristu Jesus mate ona ba ita, maibee laos nee deit, Nia moris fali ona, i agora Nia iha Maromak nia sorin loos hodi harohan mai ita.
Entaun see mak bele haketak ita hosi Kristu nia domin? La iha! Bele ita hetan problema ka susar oi-oin, bele ita hetan terus tanba tuir Kristu, bele ita hamlaha ka la iha hena para hatais, bele ita iha situasaun perigu nia laran ka ema atu oho ita ho surik, maibee buat sira nee hotu sei la hakotu Kristu nia domin mai ita.
Nee hanesan hakerek tiha ona iha Livru Sagradu dehan,
“Maromak, loron-kalan ema buka dalan atu oho ami
tanba ami tuir Ita Boot.
Sira haree ami
hanesan bibi malae nebee mak sira atu oho.”<a href='#note-896' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski ita hetan susar oinsaa mos, ita manaan ona, ita manaan liu dook tanba Kristu hadomi teb-tebes ita.
Hau fiar metin katak la iha buat ida mak bele haketak ita hosi Maromak nia domin. Atu mate ka moris, atu anju ka forsa nakukun, atu buat nebee mosu agora ka buat nebee mosu aban-bainrua, atu forsa saida deit,
atu buat iha loro leten ka iha rai, atu buat selu-seluk nebee Maromak halo, la iha ida mak bele hakotu Maromak nia domin nebee Nia hatudu ona mai ita liu hosi ita nia Nai Kristu Jesus.
Agora hau hakarak hatoo hau nia laran tristi ba imi. Nudar Kristu nia ema, hau koalia lo-loos ba imi, hau la bosok. Espiritu Santu mos hametin hau nia laran katak, buat nebee mak hau atu koalia nee loos.
Loron-kalan hau tristi teb-tebes, hau nia laran dodok,
tanba hau nia maluk Israel sira nebee lakohi simu Kristu.<a href='#note-897' class='key'>*</a> Se karik Maromak bele kastigu hau iha sira nia fatin hodi soe hau dook hosi Kristu para sira bele hetan salvasaun, hau prontu simu.
Tuir lo-loos sira nee sorti ona, tanba sira ema Israel, Maromak hili ona sira sai Nia oan. Nia hatudu Nia naroman lalehan nian ba sira. Nia halo promesa oi-oin ho sira i foo Nia lei ba sira. Nia hanorin sira oinsaa atu adora Nia, i promete buat barak ba sira.<a href='#note-898' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira nia bei-ala sira naran boot. Tuir raan, Kristu nebee Maromak promete hori uluk atu haruka mai nee mos hosi sira nia jerasaun. Maibee Kristu nee mos Maromak, Nia boot liu buat hotu-hotu. Mai ita hahii Nia too tinan ba tinan. Amen.<a href='#note-899' class='key'>✡</a>
Maski ema Israel barak seidauk simu Kristu, maibee keta hanoin dehan, Maromak la halo tuir Nia promesa. Tanba laos ema Israel hotu mak sai Maromak nia povu.
I laos ita nia bei-ala Abraão nia jerasaun hotu mak Maromak hili. Tanba Maromak dehan tiha ona ba Abraão, “Liu hosi Isác mak o sei hetan jerasaun nebee Hau promete ona.”<a href='#note-900' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee dehan katak, Maromak laos hili Abraão nia jerasaun tuir raan para sai Nia oan. Maibee Nia so hili deit jerasaun nebee mak Nia promete tiha ona atu foo.
Nia promesa mak nee: “Tinan oin Hau fila fali mai, o nia kaben Sara iha ona oan mane ida.”<a href='#note-901' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos ho ita nia bei-ala Isác ho nia kaben Rebeca, sira hetan oan mane kaduak.
11-12 Molok labarik sira nee moris, sira seidauk halo buat diak ka buat aat, maibee Maromak hatete ona ba Rebeca, “Maun sei serbi ba nia alin.” Nee hatudu katak, bainhira Maromak hili ema ida, Nia la haree ba ema nee nia hahalok, maibee Nia hili tuir Nia planu rasik.<a href='#note-902' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Livru Sagradu, Maromak dehan kona ba oan kaduak nee, “Hau hadomi Jacó, maibee Esaú lae.”<a href='#note-903' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, ita atu dehan saida? Maromak tesi lia la loos ka? Laos nunee!
Uluk Maromak foo hatene ba Moisés dehan,
“Hau sei hatudu domin ba ema nebee mak Hau rasik hakarak hadomi.
I Hau sei hatudu Hau nia laran diak ba ema nebee mak Hau rasik hili.”<a href='#note-904' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Livru Sagradu, Maromak dehan ba liurai Ejitu nunee: “Hau foti o sai liurai, tanba Hau hakarak uza o hodi hatudu Hau nia kbiit atu ema iha mundu tomak bele foti aas Hau nia naran.”<a href='#note-905' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee, se Maromak hakarak hatudu Nia domin ba ema ida, Nia halo deit. I se Nia hakarak halo ema ida nia fuan toos, Nia halo deit.<a href='#note-906' class='key'>✡</a>
Karik imi ida protesta mai hau dehan, “Se Maromak hakarak halo ita nunee, nusaa mak Nia foo sala nafatin mai ita? Ita atu kontra Nia hakarak la bele.”
Maibee o nee see fali mak brani koalia hasoru Maromak hanesan nee? O nee ema deit! Hanoin took, kuandu ema halo sanan rai, sanan nee la bele husu fali ba ema nee, “Nusaa mak o halo hau hanesan nee?”<a href='#note-907' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee halo sanan rai, nia iha direitu atu halo sanan tuir nia hakarak. Hosi rai mean kabuar ida, nia bele halo sanan rai oi-oin, balu diak nian, balu hodi uza ba foer fatin deit.
Maromak mos iha direitu nunee. Nia hakarak hatudu sai Nia kbiit boot hodi fakar Nia hirus ba ema nebee mak Nia atu kastigu, sira nee mak merese atu Nia harahun. Maski Nia atu kastigu sira, maibee Nia sei aguenta hela ho pasiensia.
Nia pasiensia lai ho sira nunee para hatudu ba ema hotu-hotu katak, Nia laran diak teb-tebes ba ita nebee mak Nia hadomi; ita nee mak Nia prepara antes tiha ona atu aban-bainrua Nia sei foti aas ita.
Nia bolu ita nanis ona atu sai Nia ema. Nia laos bolu deit ema Judeu maibee Nia bolu mos ema nebee laos Judeu.
Uluk profeta Hoseia hakerek Maromak nia liafuan kona ba ema nebee mak laos Judeu nunee:
“Ema nebee uluk laos Hau nia povu,
Hau sei bolu ‘Hau nia povu’,
ema nebee uluk Hau la hadomi,
Hau sei dehan ‘Hau hadomi imi.’ ”<a href='#note-908' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia mos hakerek nunee:
“Iha fatin nebee mak uluk Maromak dehan ba sira, ‘Imi laos Hau nia povu’,
iha fatin nee duni mak Maromak Moris sei bolu sira ‘Hau nia oan’.”<a href='#note-909' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee kona ba ema Israel, profeta Isaias halerik nunee:
“Ema Israel sira barak teb-tebes hanesan rai henek iha tasi ibun,
maibee uitoan deit mak sei hetan salvasaun.
Tanba too nia tempu, Nai Maromak sei hamonu kedas Nia kastigu mai mundu.
Nia sei la demora.”<a href='#note-910' class='key'>✡</a>
Profeta Isaias mos foo hatene nanis ona kona ba ema Israel dehan,
“Se uluk Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain la husik ita nia povu balu moris karik,
entaun ita mate mohu ona hanesan ema sidade Sodoma ho Gomora.”<a href='#note-911' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee ita atu dehan saida? Ema nebee laos Judeu, sira uluk la hakaas aan atu diak malu ho Maromak. Too ikus Nia simu sira tanba sira fiar ba Jesus Kristu.
Maibee ema Israel hakaas aan moris tuir lei atu sira bele diak malu ho Maromak, i la konsege.
Nusaa mak sira la konsege? Tanba sira buka diak malu fali ho Nia liu hosi sira nia hahalok rasik, laos liu hosi fiar. Nee hanesan sira sidi ba fatuk.
Fatuk nee mak Jesus Kristu. Iha Livru Sagradu, Maromak koalia kona ba Jesus Kristu nunee:
“Haree ba! Hau tau hela fatuk ida
Fatuk nee halo ema sidi,
i halo sira monu.
Maibee see mak fiar ba Nia,
sira nia fiar la saugati.”<a href='#note-912' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree anju forte ida tan tuun mai hosi lalehan. Kalohan falun metin nia isin, i arkuiris ida haleu nia ulun. Nia oin nabilan loos hanesan loro matan, i nia ain hanesan fali ahi lakan makaas.
Nia kaer hela livru kiik-oan ida. Livru nee baibain lulun maibee agora nakloke hela. Nia hamriik ain loos sama tasi, ain karuk sama rai maran.
Depois anju nee koalia ho lian makaas hanesan leaun nia lian. Nia koalia tiha hotu, rai tarutu simu malu too dala hitu hodi hataan ba nia.
Rai tarutu liu tiha, hau atu hakerek liafuan nebee mak sai hosi rai tarutu nee. Maibee hau rona fali lian ida hosi lalehan dehan, “O la bele konta sai buat nebee mak rai tarutu hitu nee foo sai, la bele hakerek nia liafuan.”
Depois anju nebee mak hamriik ain sorin sama tasi ho ain sorin sama rai maran nee foti nia liman loos ba lalehan.
I nia halo juramentu hodi Nai Maromak nia naran, tanba Nai Maromak moris tinan ba tinan i Nia mak halo lalehan, rai, tasi ho buat hotu-hotu iha laran. Nia jura dehan, “Maromak sei la demora tan.
Bainhira anju numeru hitu huu nia korneta, Nai Maromak sei halao Nia planu segredu, tuir lo-loos buat nebee uluk Nia foo hatene ona ba Nia atan sira nebee serbi Nia nudar profeta.”<a href='#note-1525' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois lian nebee mak hau ohin rona hosi lalehan nee koalia dala ida tan mai hau dehan, “Baa iha anju nebee mak hamriik ain sorin sama tasi ho ain sorin sama rai maran nee hodi simu livru lulun nebee mak nakloke hela iha nia liman laran.”
Depois hau baa iha anju nee hodi husu livru lulun kiik-oan nee. Nia dehan mai hau, “Simu ba hodi haan. Bainhira o haan livru nee, o nia kabun laran sei moruk, maibee iha o nia ibun sei midar hanesan bani been.”
Hau mos foti livru lulun nee hosi anju nia liman i hau haan. Loos duni, iha hau nia ibun senti midar hanesan bani been, maibee bainhira hau tolan tiha, iha hau nia kabun senti moruk.<a href='#note-1526' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona orden dehan, “O tenki foo sai fali Maromak nia lia tatoli kona ba saida mak sei akontese ba povu sira, nasaun sira, ema hosi lian oi-oin, ho liurai sira.”
Depois hau simu ai sukat ida, hau mos simu orden nunee: “O baa sukat Nai Maromak nia uma kreda boot, sukat mos nia meza sakrifisiu, i sura ema nain hira mak adora hela Maromak iha nebaa.<a href='#note-1527' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee lalika sukat area nebee haleu uma kreda boot iha moru laran, tanba area liur nee Nai Maromak foo tiha ona ba ema nebee mak la konhese Nia. Aban-bainrua sira nee sei sama hanehan Nai Maromak nia sidade nee too fulan haat-nulu resin rua.<a href='#note-1528' class='key'>✡</a>
I Maromak sei haruka Nia ema nain rua baa foo sasin kona ba Nia. Sira sei hatais hena lutu hodi foo sai Maromak nia lia menon durante fulan hirak nee hotu. Nee hamutuk loron rihun ida atus rua neen-nulu.”
Sasin nain rua nee hanesan ai huun oliveira rua ho mos ahi-oan riin rua nebee mak hamriik iha Nai Maromak nia oin, Nia mak ukun mundu tomak.<a href='#note-1529' class='key'>✡</a>
Se inimigu ruma atu halo aat sasin nain rua nee, ahi lakan sei sai hosi sira nain rua nia ibun laran hodi haan mutuk tiha sira. Ema hotu-hotu nebee hakarak halo aat sira sei mate hanesan nee.
Sira nain rua sei iha kbiit hodi taka kalohan para udan la bele tuun durante sira foo tutan Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Sira mos iha kbiit para halo bee sai fali raan, ho kbiit para halo dezastre selu-seluk tan iha mundu, tuir sira nia hakarak.<a href='#note-1530' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira sasin nain rua nee foo sai hotu tiha Nai Maromak nia lia menon, animal siak ida sei sai hosi rai kuak klean nakukun. Animal nee sei ataka sira nain rua, nia mak forti liu i oho tiha sira<a href='#note-1531' class='key'>✡</a>
iha sidade boot. Fatin nee mos uluk ema oho sasin nain rua nia Nai iha krus. Ema iha sidade nee hahalok aat teb-tebes hanesan ema Sodoma ho Ejitu uluk. Depois sasin nain rua nia mate isin husik hela deit iha estrada boot.
Ema hosi lian, suku ho nasaun hotu-hotu mai haree mate isin rua nee durante loron tolu ho balu, i sira la hataan para ema hakoi.<a href='#note-1532' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema iha mundu tomak kontenti tanba sasin nain rua nee mate tiha ona, tanba sira nain rua halo terus ema iha mundu. Nunee sira rame-rame halo festa i foo prezenti ba malu.
Liu tiha loron tolu ho balu, Nai Maromak foo fali iis ba sira nain rua, i sira hadeer hamriik fali. Ema hotu-hotu nebee mak haree, tauk teb-tebes.<a href='#note-1533' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois sira nain rua rona lian ida hosi lalehan dehan, “Sae mai iha nee!” Sira mos sae ba lalehan iha kalohan laran, iha sira nia inimigu sira nia oin.<a href='#note-1534' class='key'>✡</a>
Derepenti deit rai nakdoko makaas. Nunee se ita fahe sidade nee ba parte sanulu, parte ida rahun hotu. I ema rihun hitu mate. Ema nebee mak sei moris, tauk teb-tebes, i sira hahii Nai Maromak iha lalehan.<a href='#note-1535' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee terus boot numeru rua liu ona. Maibee terus boot numeru tolu besik atu mai ona.
“Ita nia Nai Maromak ho mos ita nia Salvador nebee mak Nia haruka mai
agora ukun ona mundu.
Nia sei ukun too tinan ba tinan nafatin.”<a href='#note-1536' class='key'>✡</a>
Katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat nebee tuur hela iha kadeira ukun iha Nai Maromak nia oin, sira hotu hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha Nai Maromak nia ain hodi adora Nia.
Sira dehan,
“Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain,
Ita Boot iha hori uluk kedas.
Ami agradese Ita Boot
tanba agora Ita Boot hatudu sai ona Ita nia kbiit makaas
hodi ukun mundu.
Povu sira nebee mak la konhese Maromak, sira laran nakali
maibee agora Ita Boot mos fakar sai Ita nia hirus,
i too ona tempu atu Ita Boot tesi ema mate sira nia lia.
Too ona tempu para Ita Boot foo premiu ba ema nebee mak uluk serbi Ita Boot,
hanesan Ita Boot nia profeta sira
ho mos Ita Boot nia povu sira kiik ho boot nebee mak foti aas Ita Boot nia naran.
Too ona tempu para Ita Boot halo rahun tiha ema sira nebee mak uluk halo rahun ema seluk iha mundu.”<a href='#note-1537' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Maromak nia uma kreda boot iha lalehan nia odamatan nakloke. I hau haree kaixoti promesa iha laran. Rai lakan mos fera ba-mai, rai tarutu makaas iha fati-fatin, rai nakdoko, i udan jelu fatuk bo-boot monu tuun mai rai.<a href='#note-1538' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha, iha sinal ida oin seluk liu mosu iha lalehan. Iha senhora ida, nia isin falun ho loron-matan, nia ain sama fulan. Iha nia ulun tau koroa liurai nian, koroa nee iha fitun sanulu resin rua.
Senhora nee isin rua hela, besik atu tuur ahi, i nia tanis hakilar tanba nia kanotak moras loos.
Iha tan sinal ida mosu iha lalehan. Iha samea mean boot ida, nia ulun hitu, dikur sanulu. Iha nia ulun hitu nee tau koroa liurai nian ida-ida.<a href='#note-1539' class='key'>✡</a>
Samea ulun hitu nee uza nia ikun hodi baku makaas fitun parte ida hosi parte tolu tuun ba mundu. Depois nia baa hamriik iha senhora isin rua nee nia oin para nia oan moris mai tolan kedas.<a href='#note-1540' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois senhora nee tuur ahi, nia Oan mane. Nia mak sei ukun nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu ho kroat. Maibee anju ida mai hadau tiha Labarik nee hosi nia inan, i lori baa iha Nai Maromak, iha Nia kadeira ukun.<a href='#note-1541' class='key'>✡</a>
Senhora nee halai kedas baa iha rai fuik maran, iha fatin ida nebee mak Nai Maromak prepara tiha ona ba nia. Nai Maromak sei tau matan ba nia iha fatin nee too tinan tolu ho balu, nee hamutuk loron rihun ida atus rua neen nulu.
Depois funu boot mosu iha lalehan. Maromak nia anju boot ida naran Miguel ho anju sira nebee mak tuir nia, halo funu hasoru samea ulun hitu nee. Samea ulun hitu nee mos iha nia anju, nunee sira funu hasoru Miguel ho nia anju sira.<a href='#note-1542' class='key'>✡</a>
Too ikus samea nee lakon, nunee nia ho nia anju sira la bele hela tan iha lalehan.
Miguel ho nia anju sira soe sai tiha samea ulun hitu nee hosi lalehan. Sira soe tiha samea mai mundu hamutuk ho nia anju sira hotu. Samea ulun hitu nee mak ema bolu ‘diabu nia boot’ ka ‘Satanás’. Hori uluk kedas samea nee lohi ema hotu iha mundu para lao sala dalan.<a href='#note-1543' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona lian makaas ida hosi lalehan dehan nunee:
“Agora tempu too ona atu Nai Maromak salva ema.
Ita nia Salvador nebee mak Nia haruka mai mos hatudu ona Nia kbiit.
Tanba uluk samea ulun hitu nee loron-kalan hamriik iha Nai Maromak nia oin
hodi foo sala ba ita nia maluk sarani sira,
maibee agora Maromak soe sai tiha ona nia hosi lalehan.<a href='#note-1544' class='key'>✡</a>
Ita nia maluk sarani sira manaan tiha ona samea ulun hitu nee,
tanba Bibi Oan nia raan fakar hodi salva sira,
i tanba sira foo sai nafatin Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
Maski ema atu oho sira mos sira la hakiduk.
Nunee lalehan ho buat hotu-hotu iha lalehan haksolok ba!
Maibee buat hotu-hotu nebee moris iha rai ho tasi sei terus,
tanba diabu nia boot tuun ona baa iha imi.
Nia laran nakali ona tanba nia hatene katak,
nia tempu para halo buat aat besik hotu ona.”
Bainhira samea ulun hitu nee hatene katak, sira soe tuun tiha ona nia iha mundu, nia baa buka tuir senhora nebee mak tuur ahi Oan mane nee, atu halo terus nia.
Maibee senhora nee simu liras rua hanesan manu makikit boot ida nia liras para semo ba fatin nebee prepara tiha ona ba nia iha rai fuik maran. Iha nebaa Nai Maromak sei hamahon nia durante tinan tolu ho balu para samea ulun hitu nee la bele halo buat aat ba nia.<a href='#note-1545' class='key'>*</a>
Haree nunee, samea ulun hitu nee fakar sai bee barak hanesan mota boot hosi nia ibun para mota bele lori senhora nee.
Maibee rai mak ajuda senhora nee hodi tolan tiha bee nebee mak sai hosi samea nia ibun.
Nunee samea ulun hitu nee hirus teb-tebes senhora nee, too nia baa buka senhora nee nia oan sira seluk. Sira nee mak ema nebee halo tuir Nai Maromak nia ukun fuan i foo sasin kona ba Jesus.
Depois samea nee baa hamriik iha tasi ibun.
Depois hau haree animal siak ida sai hosi tasi laran. Animal nee nia ulun hitu, dikur sanulu. Iha nia dikur sanulu nee tau koroa liurai nian ida-idak. Iha nia ulun ida-idak hakerek naran nebee hatete aat Nai Maromak.<a href='#note-1546' class='key'>✡</a>
Animal nebee mak hau haree nee, nia isin hanesan tigre. Nia ain boot hanesan animal fuik ursu nian, i nia ibun hanesan leaun nia ibun. Samea ulun hitu nee foo nia kbiit ba animal siak nee i entrega nia kadeira ukun ba nia.<a href='#note-1547' class='key'>✡</a>
Animal siak nee, nia ulun ida iha fitar, haree ba hanesan uluk kanek boot. Tuir lo-loos nia mate, maibee kanek nee diak fali ona. Ema hotu-hotu admira ho animal siak nee i tuir nia.
Sira hotu adora samea ulun hitu nee hanesan fali Maromak, tanba samea nee foo tiha ona kbiit ba animal siak nee. Sira mos adora animal siak nee hodi dehan, “La iha ida mak forsa hanesan animal nee! La iha ida mak bele manaan nia.”
Maromak husik deit animal siak nee foti aan i hatete aat Nai Maromak. Animal nee mos hetan lisensa para kaer ukun durante fulan haat-nulu resin rua, nee hamutuk tinan tolu ho balu.
Nia hatete aat Nai Maromak, hatete aat Nai Maromak nia naran ho Nia hela fatin, hatete aat mos hotu-hotu nebee hela iha lalehan.<a href='#note-1548' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak foo lisensa ba animal siak nee atu halo funu hasoru Maromak nia povu too manaan. Nia mos simu kbiit para ukun ema hotu-hotu hosi suku, povu, lian ho nasaun hotu-hotu.<a href='#note-1549' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema hotu-hotu iha mundu nee sei adora animal siak nee. So ema nebee naran hakerek ona iha lista ema moris rohan-laek nian mak la adora animal nee. Lista nee Maromak hakerek nanis ona molok Nia halo mundu. Lista nee Bibi Oan nian, Ida nebee mak ema oho.<a href='#note-1550' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak ba!
Se Maromak desidi ona katak, ema ruma tenki sai dadur,
Se Maromak desidi ona katak, ema ruma tenki mate ho surik,
nia sei mate duni ho surik.
Nee duni sarani sira tenki aguenta ho pasiensia nafatin i fiar metin too rohan.<a href='#note-1551' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree animal siak ida tan sai mai hosi rai. Animal segundu nee nia dikur rua, hanesan bibi malae oan nia dikur, maibee nia lian hanesan samea ulun hitu nia lian.
Nia simu kbiit hosi animal siak primeiru, ida nebee uluk kanek boot i tuir loos mate maibee diak fali ona. Nunee nia halao servisu hodi animal siak primeiru nia naran, i nia obriga ema hotu-hotu iha mundu adora fali animal siak primeiru nee.
Animal segundu nee halo milagre bo-boot halo ema hotu-hotu admira, too nia mos halo ahi monu tuun hosi lalehan iha ema barak nia oin.
Ho milagre nebee nia halo hodi animal siak primeiru nia naran nee, nia lohi ema hotu iha mundu. Nia haruka ema harii estatua animal primeiru nian para foti aas animal primeiru nee, ida nebee uluk ema halo kanek ho surik, maibee sei moris hela.
Maromak husik animal segundu halo estatua nee bele iha iis para bele koalia. I estatua nee haruka oho tiha ema hotu-hotu nebee lakohi adora nia.
Animal segundu nee obriga ema hotu-hotu, kiik-boot, riku-kiak, atan ka ema baibain, tenki simu marka iha sira nia liman loos ka iha sira nia reen toos.
Ema nebee la iha marka nee, sira la bele faan sasaan ka sosa buat ida. Iha marka nee hakerek animal siak primeiru nia naran, ka numeru nebee reprezenta nia naran.
Iha nee ita presiza uza matenek. Ema nebee hanoin klean bele kompriende kódigu numeru nee. Numeru nee mak “666”, i hatudu ba ema ida.<a href='#note-1552' class='key'>*</a>
Depois hau haree tan buat foun ida. Hau haree Bibi Oan hamriik hela iha foho Siaun nia tutun, hamutuk ho ema rihun atus ida haat-nulu resin haat. Iha sira hotu nia reen toos hakerek Bibi Oan nia naran ho mos Bibi Oan nia Aman nia naran.<a href='#note-1553' class='key'>✡</a>
I hau rona buat ida iha lalehan, hanesan laloran boot ka rai tarutu makaas. Lian nebee hau rona nee mos hanesan ema barak toka muzika ho viola.
Ema rihun atus ida haat-nulu resin haat nee hamriik hela iha Nai Maromak nia kadeira ukun nia oin ho animal moris haat ho katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat nee nia oin. Ema sira nee hananu kanta foun ida. Kanta nee ema seluk la hatene, so ema sira nee mak hatene, tanba hosi mundu tomak, sira nee mak Maromak sosa kotu tiha ona.
Ema sira nee moris loos, hanesan mane klosan ida nebee mak sempre kuidadu nia aan para la bele halo sala seksual ho feto. Sira sempre lao tu-tuir Bibi Oan. Sira nee Maromak sosa kotu ona para sai Nia povu. Sira mos hanesan batar fulin diak nian nebee toos nain taa uluk hodi oferese ba Nai Maromak ho mos ba Bibi Oan.
Ema sira nee nunka bosok, i sira livre hosi sala.<a href='#note-1554' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree anju ida semo aas lori Maromak nia Liafuan Diak nebee vale too tinan ba tinan. Nia baa para foo sai Liafuan Diak nee ba ema hotu-hotu hosi povu, suku, lian ho nasaun hotu iha mundu tomak.
Anju nee hatete ho lian makaas dehan, “Hotu-hotu tenki respeita Nai Maromak i foti aas Nia naran, tanba tempu too ona atu Nai Maromak tesi ema hotu-hotu nia lia. Adora Nia tanba Nia mak halo lalehan ho rai, tasi ho bee matan.”
Iha tan anju ida seluk semo tuir anju primeiru nee hodi dehan, “Sidade boot Babilónia rahun tiha ona! Rahun too rai! Uluk sidade nee hanesan feto luroon nebee obriga nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu hemu lanu too halo sala seksual tuun-sae. Maibee agora Maromak kastigu ona nia.”<a href='#note-1555' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju ida tan semo tuir anju rua nee. Anju nee foo sai ho lian makaas dehan, “See mak adora animal siak nee ho nia estatua, i simu nia marka iha sira nia reen toos ka liman,
Maromak sei fakar Nia hirus ba sira. Nia hirus nee hanesan fali tua ulun nebee manas teb-tebes. Maski manas, sira tenki hemu. Maromak sei halo sira terus teb-tebes iha ahi lakan boot nia laran, iha anju santu sira ho Bibi Oan nia oin.<a href='#note-1556' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema hotu-hotu nebee mak adora animal siak nee ho nia estatua i sira nebee iha marka animal nia naran, sei hetan terus loron-kalan iha ahi laran. I ahi nebee halo sira terus nee, nia suar sae la para too tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-1557' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun imi nebee sai ona Nai Maromak nia povu, imi nebee halo tuir Nai Maromak nia ukun fuan i fiar metin ba Jesus too rohan, imi tenki aguenta ho pasiensia nafatin.
Hotu tiha hau rona lian ida hosi lalehan dehan, “Hakerek nunee: Komesa agora, ema nebee laran metin ba Nai Jesus too rohan, bainhira sira mate, sira sorti boot.”
Maromak nia Espiritu hataan, “Loos duni, sira deskansa ona, tanba sira nia servisu ho sira nia terus hotu ona, i Nai Maromak sei selu fali sira nia kolen.”
Depois hau haree kalohan mutin ida. Iha kalohan nee nia leten hau haree hanesan Ema ida mak tuur. Iha Nia ulun iha koroa liurai nian halo ho osan mean, i Nia kaer hela tudik koa hare nian kroat loos.<a href='#note-1558' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju ida sai hosi uma kreda boot. Anju nee koalia ho lian makaas ba Ema nebee tuur iha kalohan leten dehan, “Hodi tudik nee lere ona ba, tanba hare hotu-hotu iha mundu tasak ona, tempu too ona atu lere.”<a href='#note-1559' class='key'>✡</a>
Entaun Ema nebee tuur iha kalohan leten nee, hodi Nia tudik kroat lere hare hotu-hotu iha mundu.
Depois iha anju ida tan sai hosi uma kreda boot, nia mos kaer tudik kroat ida.
Anju nee mos hodi nia tudik koa uvas hotu-hotu hosi nia sanak. Koa tiha hotu, nia soe ba iha tanki laran para sama hasai nia been. Sama uvas nee hatudu Maromak nia hirus.
Fatin sama uvas nee iha liur, laos iha sidade laran. I bainhira sira sama uvas nee, raan mak suli sai hosi fatin nee hanesan fali mota tuun. Mota raan nee nia naruk kilometru atus tolu, i nia klean metru ida ho balu.<a href='#note-1560' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha hau haree tan sinal ida iha lalehan halo hau admira teb-tebes. Iha anju hitu, ida-idak ho nia kbiit para haruka terus boot ida mai mundu. Terus boot hitu nee mak terus ikus ona, tanba liu tiha nee, Nai Maromak sei la fakar tan Nia hirus mai mundu.
Depois hau haree buat ida hanesan tasi, maibee haree hanesan fali vidru kahur ho ahi. Hau mos haree ema barak nebee mak manaan tiha animal siak ho nia estatua tanba sira la adora nia i la simu nia marka ho nia numeru nebee mak reprezenta nia naran. Ema sira nee hamriik iha tasi ninin i kaer hela viola nebee Nai Maromak foo ba sira.
Sira hotu hananu kanta ida hosi Nai Maromak nia atan Moisés ho Bibi Oan nunee:
“Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain,
buat hotu-hotu nebee mak Ita Boot halo makaas teb-tebes,
halo ema admira!
Ita Boot mak nasaun hotu-hotu nia Liurai,
Ita Boot halo saida deit sempre loos.<a href='#note-1561' class='key'>✡</a>
Nai, ema hotu-hotu tauk Ita Boot
i foti aas Ita Boot nia naran,
tanba so Ita Boot deit mak santu.
Ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu sei mai adora Ita Boot,
tanba ema hotu-hotu haree ona katak
Ita Boot halo saida deit sempre diak ho loos.”<a href='#note-1562' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira sira hananu hotu ona, hau haree iha lalehan, fatin nebee mak lulik liu iha tenda orasaun nia laran, odamatan nakloke.<a href='#note-1563' class='key'>✡</a>
I anju hitu nebee mak lori terus boot nee, sai hosi uma kreda laran. Sira hatais hena mutin nabilan i kesi hena naruk osan mean iha sira nia hirus matan.
Depois animal moris haat nee ida fahe manko osan mean ba anju hitu nee ida-idak. Manko nee nakonu ho kastigu nebee Maromak atu fakar mai mundu. Maromak nee moris tinan ba tinan nafatin.
La kleur tenda orasaun nee ahi suar nakonu tiha. Ahi suar nee hatudu Nai Maromak nia kbiit ho Nia forsa. La iha ema ida mak bele tama ba iha tenda orasaun nee. Too terus boot hitu nebee anju hitu atu fakar mai mundu nee hotu ona mak foin bele tama fali.<a href='#note-1564' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona lian makaas ida sai hosi uma kreda boot hodi haruka anju hitu nunee, “Baa ona! Lori manko hitu nee baa fakar tiha Maromak nia hirus ba mundu.”
Anju numeru ida fakar uluk Maromak nia hirus nebee iha nia manko laran nee ba mundu. Derepenti deit, ema sira nebee mak simu animal siak nia marka i adora nia estatua, sira nia isin sai kanek dodok hotu, halo sira senti moras loos.<a href='#note-1565' class='key'>✡</a>
Anju numeru rua fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba tasi. Derepenti tasi sai raan hanesan fali ema mate nia raan, i buat hotu-hotu nebee moris iha tasi laran mate mohu.
Anju numeru tolu fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba mota ho bee matan, halo bee hirak nee sai tiha raan.<a href='#note-1566' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona anju ida nebee toma konta bee hotu iha mundu dehan nunee:
“Nai Maromak santu,
Ita Boot iha hori uluk kedas i iha nafatin.
Kastigu nebee mak Ita Boot foo ba sira nee loos,
tanba sira oho Ita Boot nia povu ho profeta sira too sira nia raan fakar,
Sira merese duni hetan kastigu nee.”
Depois hau rona lian ida hosi meza sakrifisiu hataan nunee,
“Loos duni! Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain,
Ita Boot tesi lia ho loos.
Sira merese duni simu kastigu nebee Ita Boot foo ba sira.”
Hotu tiha anju numeru haat fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba loro matan. Derepenti loro matan simu kbiit para sai manas liu too sunu ema nia isin hanesan fali ahi.
Loro manas makaas halo sira nia isin kanek, i sira hatete aat Nai Maromak nia naran, tanba Nia mak iha kbiit hodi foo terus boot nee ba sira. Maski nunee, sira la hakribi sira nia sala, i lakohi foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran.
Anju numeru lima fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba animal siak nia kadeira ukun. Derepenti nakukun taka metin animal siak nee nia reinu hotu, i sira hotu-hotu tata nanaal tanba sira terus liu.<a href='#note-1567' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira hotu-hotu koalia aat Nai Maromak iha lalehan tanba sira nia kanek moras teb-tebes. Maski terus nunee, maibee la iha ema ida atu hakribi nia hahalok aat.
Anju numeru neen fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba mota boot Eufrates. Derepenti mota nee sai maran tiha, para loke dalan ba liurai sira hosi loro-sae bele liu.<a href='#note-1568' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree tan espiritu aat tolu, haree hanesan manduku. Ida sai hosi samea ulun hitu nia ibun, ida seluk sai hosi animal siak primeiru nia ibun, ida tan sai hosi profeta falsu nia ibun. Profeta falsu nee mak animal siak segundu.
Espiritu aat tolu nee iha kbiit hodi halo milagre oi-oin. I sira baa konvida liurai sira iha mundu tomak atu mai halibur hamutuk hodi halo funu hasoru Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain. Afinal tempu nebee sira marka atu funu nee mak Nai Maromak nia loron para kastigu Nia inimigu sira.
15-16 Fatin nebee liurai sira halibur atu halo funu nee ho lian Ebreu dehan Armagedon.
Jesus Kristu hatete, “Rona di-diak! Hau sei mai derepenti deit hanesan naok-teen. Ema nebee hadeer hela deit hodi hatais nia ropa, ema nee sorti boot. Se lae, bainhira Hau mai, nia moe loos tanba nia isin molik hela.”<a href='#note-1569' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju numeru hitu fakar Maromak nia hirus nebee mak iha nia manko laran ba anin. Derepenti lian makaas ida sai hosi kadeira ukun iha uma kreda boot dehan, “Hotu ona!”
Depois rai lakan fera ba-mai, rai tarutu makaas iha fati-fatin, rai mos nakdoko. Dezde Maromak halo ema, seidauk iha rai nakdoko makaas hanesan nee.<a href='#note-1570' class='key'>✡</a>
Sidade boot Babilónia nakfera fahe ba tolu, i sidade hotu-hotu iha nasaun sira seluk mos rahun. Nai Maromak la haluha ema Babilónia nia hahalok aat. Nee mak Nia fakar nia hirus ba iha kopu tua nian halo nakonu hodi obriga sira hemu.<a href='#note-1571' class='key'>✡</a>
Rai oan sira iha tasi klaran mout tiha i foho sira mos lakon hotu.<a href='#note-1572' class='key'>✡</a>
Udan jelu fatuk bo-boot monu hosi kalohan hanehan ema. Udan jelu fatuk nee nia todan too kilu haat-nulu. Ema sira nee hatete aat Nai Maromak nia naran tanba terus nebee sira simu nee todan liu.<a href='#note-1573' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-1574' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju ida hosi anju hitu nebee kaer manko sira nee, mai iha hau hodi dehan, “Mai para hau hatudu ba o oinsaa Nai Maromak kastigu sidade boot nebee harii besik mota barak. Sidade boot nee hanesan fali feto luroon nebee la hatene aan.<a href='#note-1575' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-1576' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk liurai sira hosi mundu tomak mai halo sala seksual ho nia. I povu hosi mundu tomak mos hemu nia tua too lanu hodi halo tuir nia hahalok aat.”<a href='#note-1577' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Maromak nia Espiritu domina hau, i anju nee lori hau ba rai fuik maran. Iha nebaa hau haree feto ida tuur hela iha animal siak mean lakan ida nia leten. Iha animal siak nee nia isin lolon tomak hakerek liafuan nebee hatete aat Nai Maromak. Animal nee iha ulun hitu, dikur sanulu.<a href='#note-1578' class='key'>✡</a>
Feto nee hatais hena folin karun teb-tebes, kor mean ho kor kafé. I nia tau osan mean, fatuk murak, ho morteen perola mesak karun. Nia kaer hela kopu osan mean ida. Kopu nee nakonu ho nia hahalok aat, hanesan sala seksual ho buat aat ho buat foer selu-seluk nebee mak nia halo.<a href='#note-1579' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha feto nee nia reen toos hakerek naran ida, nia signifikadu sei segredu hela. Nia naran nunee:
“Sidade boot Babilónia,
feto luroon hotu-hotu nia inan,
hahalok foer hotu-hotu iha mundu nia huun.”
Hau haree feto aat nee, raan mak lanu tiha nia. Nia gosta liu oho Nai Maromak nia ema sira, gosta oho ema nebee foo sasin kona ba Jesus Kristu.
Bainhira hau haree nia, hau admira teb-tebes.
Animal siak nee uluk moris iha mundu, maibee agora la iha tiha ona. Aban-bainrua nia sei mosu fali mai hosi rai kuak klean nakukun. Bainhira nia mosu fali mai, ema hotu-hotu iha mundu nebee naran la tau iha lista ema moris rohan-laek nian molok Maromak halo mundu nee, sira sei admira haree animal siak nee. Tanba animal siak nee uluk moris, depois la iha tiha ona, maibee too ikus mosu fali. Maski nunee Maromak sei halo rahun tiha nia.<a href='#note-1580' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema presiza uza matenek para bele kompriende animal siak nee. Nia ulun hitu nee hatudu ba foho hitu, feto nee baibain tuur iha foho hitu nee nia leten.
Nia ulun hitu nee mos hatudu ba liurai nain hitu. Nain lima monu tiha ona, nain ida agora ukun hela, i ida seluk seidauk mai, maibee bainhira nia mai, nia tenki ukun lalais deit.
Animal siak nebee mak uluk iha i agora la iha ona, nia mos uluk halo parte iha liurai nain hitu nee. Maibee aban-bainrua nia sei ukun fila fali para sai liurai numeru walu. Too ikus Maromak sei halo rahun tiha nia.
Dikur sanulu nebee o haree nee, hatudu ba liurai nain sanulu tan nebee seidauk kaer ukun. Sira sei hetan kbiit para ukun hamutuk ho animal siak nee, maibee ukun too oras ida deit.<a href='#note-1581' class='key'>✡</a>
Liurai nain sanulu nee laran ida deit hodi entrega sira nia kbiit ba animal siak nee.
Sira sei halo funu kontra Bibi Oan. Maibee Bibi Oan ho Nia povu sei manaan, tanba Bibi Oan nee mak nai hotu-hotu nia Nai, ho liurai hotu-hotu nia Liurai. Nia povu nee mak ema nebee Nia hili ho bolu tiha ona, i sira foo laran ba Nia.”
Anju nee esplika tan, “Ohin o haree feto luroon nee tuur iha mota barak. Mota nee hatudu ba ema hosi suku, povu, lian ho nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu.
Ohin o mos haree dikur sanulu nebee hatudu ba liurai nain sanulu, liurai sira nee ho animal siak sei odi feto luroon nee. Sira sei hadau tiha feto nee nia sasaan hotu-hotu too kolu molik tiha nia. Sira sei haan tiha nia isin, depois nia isin restu soe ba ahi laran.
Nai Maromak mak halo liurai nain sanulu nee laran ida foo sira nia kbiit ba animal siak nee hodi ukun. I sira sei tuir animal siak nee too planu nebee mak Maromak hatete tiha ona, sai realidade duni.
Feto luroon nebee o haree nee hatudu ba sidade boot nebee mak ukun liurai hotu-hotu iha mundu.”
Hotu tiha hau haree anju ida tan tuun mai hosi lalehan. Anju nee nia kbiit boot i nia nabilan too halo mundu nee sai naroman hotu.
Nia koalia ho lian makaas dehan,
“Sidade boot Babilónia rahun tiha ona!
Rahun too rai.
Sidade nee sai ona diabu sira nia hela fatin,
ho espiritu aat hotu-hotu nia subar fatin.
Manu buan ho manu fuik selu-seluk nebee ema hakribi,
halo nia knuuk iha nebaa.<a href='#note-1582' class='key'>✡</a>
Sidade nee rahun tiha ona,
tanba nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu,
mai hemu nia tua too lanu hodi halo sala seksual tuun-sae,
i liurai hotu-hotu iha mundu
mai halo sala seksual ho nia.
Ema Babilónia kaan atu sosa sasaan di-diak deit,
nunee halo kontratu nain sira hosi mundu tomak sai riku.”<a href='#note-1583' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona tan lian ida hosi lalehan dehan nunee:
“Hau nia povu,
sai tiha hosi sidade boot nee.
se lae imi mos hetan hotu kastigu hamutuk ho nia.<a href='#note-1584' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nia sala butuk aas ona too ona lalehan,
i Nai Maromak la haluha nia hahalok aat.<a href='#note-1585' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni, foo terus ba nia
tuir terus nebee mak nia foo ona ba ema seluk,
maibee nia hahalok aat nee,
tenki selu too dala rua.
Uluk nia kahur tua manas foo ba ema seluk hemu,
agora tenki obriga nia hemu tua nebee manas makaas liu dala rua.<a href='#note-1586' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk nia foti aan liu hodi moris goza deit,
agora tenki foo fali terus ho susar boot liu ba nia.
Feto luroon nee gaba aan dehan,
‘Hau nee liurai feto!
Hau nunka sai feto faluk,
i nunka hatene tristi.’
Tanba nee, iha loron ida deit, terus boot sei kona nia:
tanis lelir, hamlaha ho mate,
too ahi haan mutuk tiha nia isin.
Tanba Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain
mak foo justisa ba nia nunee.”<a href='#note-1587' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira ahi haan nia, liurai sira hosi mundu tomak nebee uluk mai halo sala seksual hodi moris goza hamutuk ho nia, sira sei haree ahi suar sae, i tanis lelir ba nia.
Sira tauk nia terus nee kona mos sira, entaun sira hamriik hosi dook deit hodi dehan,
‘Koitadu Babilónia!
Koitadu sidade boot ho forti nee!
Derepenti o hetan kastigu,
iha oras ida deit, o rahun tiha ona.’<a href='#note-1588' class='key'>✡</a>
Kontratu nain sira hosi mundu tomak mos tanis lelir ba sidade nee, tanba la iha tan ema ida atu sosa sira nia sasaan,<a href='#note-1589' class='key'>✡</a>
sira nia osan mean, osan mutin, fatuk murak, ka morteen perola, sira nia hena mesak furak, sira nia hena diak nian nebee kor mean ho kor kafé. Ema la sosa tan sira nia ai morin, sasaan oi-oin nebee halo hosi elefante nia nehan, ai nebee karu, riti, besi ka fatuk marmore.
Ema la sosa tan sira nia ai kanela ka temperus oi-oin, sira nia ai been morin ka mina morin oi-oin, sira nia tua, mina azeiti, trigu diak nian, ka trigu musan. La iha tan ema atu sosa sira nia karau, bibi malae ka kuda, sira nia kuda kareta ka sira nia atan.<a href='#note-1590' class='key'>✡</a>
‘Buat hotu-hotu nebee o kaan,
mohu tiha ona.
O nia rikusoin ho sasaan furak sira nee hotu-hotu nabeen tiha ona,
i o sei la hetan tan ona.’
Kontratu nain sira nee riku tiha ona, tanba uluk mai faan sira nia sasaan iha sidade nee. Sira hotu sei hamriik hosi dook deit, tanba tauk sidade nee nia terus kona mos sira. I sira sei tanis lelir dehan,
‘Koitadu! Koitadu sidade boot nee!
Uluk o hatais hena mesak furak, kor mean ho kor kafé ho folin karun teb-tebes.
Uluk o enfeita aan ho osan mean, fatuk murak ho morteen perola.<a href='#note-1591' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee iha oras ida nia laran deit,
o nia rikusoin sira nee mohu tiha hotu.’
Ema sira nebee kaer roo, ema nebee servisu iha roo laran, pasajeiru sira ho mos ema sira nebee mak buka moris iha tasi, sira hotu-hotu mos hamriik hosi dook<a href='#note-1592' class='key'>✡</a>
bainhira ahi haan sidade nee. Kuandu sira haree ahi suar sae, sira halerik ho lian makaas dehan, ‘La iha tan sidade seluk hanesan sidade boot ida nee!’<a href='#note-1593' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira raut rai rahun tau ba sira nia ulun hodi hatudu sira nia laran tristi, i tanis lelir dehan,
‘Koitadu! Koitadu sidade boot nee!
Ami nebee lori roo baa-mai iha tasi laran halo kontratu,
ami hotu sai riku ona hosi o nia rikusoin.
Maibee iha oras ida nia laran deit,
o rahun kedas.’ ”<a href='#note-1594' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona lian ida dehan,
“Imi nebee moris iha lalehan,
haksolok ba!
Maromak nia povu, Nai Jesus nia apostolu sira ho profeta sira,
haksolok ba!
Tanba Maromak kastigu ona sidade nee,
tuir saida mak nia uluk halo ba imi.”<a href='#note-1595' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha anju forti ida lori fatuk boot hanesan meza, nia riba tuun ba tasi laran hodi dehan,
“Hanesan nee mos Nai Maromak sei riba tuun sidade boot Babilónia,
i ema sei la haree tan.<a href='#note-1596' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha sidade nee, sei la rona tan ema kanta,
La iha tan badaen atu servisu tuir ida-idak nia area,
la iha ona ema dulas hare.<a href='#note-1597' class='key'>✡</a>
Ahi-oan sei la foo tan naroman ba sidade nee.
La iha tan festa kazamentu.
Sidade boot nee hetan kastigu nunee
tanba uluk nia kontratu nain sira mak sai ema boot liu iha mundu,
i nia ema uza ai kulit aat hodi bosok nasaun hotu-hotu.<a href='#note-1598' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk ema Babilónia halo Maromak nia profeta sira ho Nia povu sira seluk raan fakar too mate.
Ema sira nebee ema oho iha fatin selu-seluk mos,
Babilónia mak lori todan.”<a href='#note-1599' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha hau rona hanesan ema barak teb-tebes haklalak iha lalehan dehan,
“Aleluia! Hahii Nai Maromak iha leten aas ba!
Ita nia Maromak kbiit boot teb-tebes,
Nia mak salva ita.
Nia tesi lia ho lo-loos,
Nia foti ona desizaun atu kastigu feto luroon aat nee.
Feto aat nee dada ema hosi mundu tomak para halo sala seksual ho nia,
nunee ema sira nee mos sai aat hotu.
Nia mos oho Nai Maromak nia atan sira,
i agora Maromak foo ona kastigu ba nia.”<a href='#note-1600' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois ema barak nee haklalak tan dehan,
“Aleluia! Hahii Nai Maromak!
Ahi haan mutuk tiha ona feto luroon nee,
ahi nee nia suar sae beibeik too tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-1601' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat ho mos animal moris haat nee hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha Nai Maromak nia kadeira ukun nia oin hodi adora Nia dehan,
“Amen, aleluia! Hahii Nai Maromak!”
Depois lian ida mai hosi kadeira ukun nee dehan,
“Imi hotu-hotu nebee serbi Nai Maromak,
imi hotu kiik-boot nebee respeita Nia,
Depois hau rona buat ruma hanesan ema barak tebe-tebes nia lian, hanesan fali laloran boot, ka hanesan rai tarutu makaas. Lian nee dehan,
“Aleluia! Hahii Nai Maromak,
tanba Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain mak ukun.<a href='#note-1603' class='key'>✡</a>
Mai ita foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran
ho laran haksolok ho kontenti,
tanba Bibi Oan nia loron kazamentu too ona,
i Nia noiva hatais prontu ona atu kaben ho Nia.
Vestidu mutin nabilan nebee nia hatais nee Nai Maromak mak foo.”
Vestidu nabilan nee signifika sarani sira nia hahalok diak.
Depois anju nee dehan mai hau, “Hakerek nunee: See mak hetan konvite atu mai asisti Bibi Oan nia festa kazamentu nee, sira sorti boot.” Anju nee hatutan tan dehan, “Nai Maromak nia liafuan nee loos duni!”<a href='#note-1604' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha anju nee nia oin atu adora nia, maibee nia bandu dehan, “La bele! Adora mak Maromak deit! Tanba hau nee Maromak nia atan hanesan mos o ho o nia maluk sira seluk nebee foo sai nafatin Jesus nia hanorin. Tanba ita hotu hetan kbiit hosi Maromak nia Espiritu para ita foo sasin kona ba Jesus.”
Depois hau haree lalehan nakloke hela, i hau haree kuda mutin ida iha nebaa. Ema nebee tuur iha kuda leten nee, Nia naran mak “Kaer Metin Nia Promesa” ho “Ema Loos”. Bainhira Nia tesi ema nia lia, Nia tesi lia ho lo-loos, i bainhira Nia halo funu, Nia halo ho laran moos.<a href='#note-1605' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nee nia matan hanesan fali ahi nebee mak lakan makaas. Iha Nia ulun tau koroa liurai nian barak. Iha Nia isin lolon hakerek naran ida, maibee so Nia deit mak hatene naran nee, ema seluk la hatene.<a href='#note-1606' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia hatais hena nebee habokon tiha ho raan. Ema temi Nia naran “Maromak nia Liafuan”.
Iha mos tropas lalehan nian barak teb-tebes sae kuda mutin tuir Nia. Tropas sira nee hotu hatais hena mutin nabilan.
Ema nee iha surik kroat ida sai hosi nia ibun, i Nia uza surik nee hodi halo lakon nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu. Depois Nia sei ukun nasaun sira nee ho kroat. Nia sei sama sira hanesan fali ema sama uvas iha tanki laran hodi hasai nia been. Nia halo nunee hodi hatudu katak, Nai Maromak Kbiit Nain fakar Nia hirus ba sira.<a href='#note-1607' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Ema nee nia batina ho mos iha Nia kelen hakerek naran ida nunee:
“Liurai hotu-hotu nia Liurai,
nai hotu-hotu nia Nai.”
Depois hau haree tan anju ida hamriik hela iha loro matan leten. Anju nee koalia ho lian makaas ba manu fuik hotu-hotu nebee mak semo aas, hodi dehan, “Mai halibur hamutuk hodi haan rame-rame iha Nai Maromak nia festa boot.
Mai haan tiha ema hotu-hotu nia mate isin: liurai sira, komandante militar ho aswain sira, kuda ho soldadu sira nebee mak sae kuda, ema boot ho kiik, atan ho ema nebee livre. Mai haan sira hotu nia mate isin ba!”<a href='#note-1608' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree fali animal siak nebee uluk sai hosi tasi laran nee. Nia halibur hamutuk ho liurai sira iha mundu ho sira nia tropas hodi halo funu hasoru Ema ida nebee sae kuda mutin nee ho Nia tropas.
Maibee Ema nebee sae kuda mutin nee manaan tiha animal siak nee ho nia profeta falsu. Profeta falsu nee mak uluk hatudu nia milagre bo-boot hodi animal siak nia naran. Ho milagre sira nee nia bosok ema hotu-hotu nebee mak simu ona animal siak nia marka i adora animal nee nia estatua. Agora Ema ida nebee sae kuda mutin nee kaer animal siak nee ho nia profeta falsu, i soe moris sira nain rua ba iha ahi lakan boot nia laran.<a href='#note-1609' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois nia uza surik nebee sai hosi Nia ibun laran nee hodi oho ema hotu nebee mak tuir animal siak nee. I manu fuik mai rame-rame hodi haan tiha sira nia isin nee too bosu di-diak.
Iha livru nee hakerek kona ba buat nebee mak la kleur tan sei akontese. Nai Maromak foo hatene ona buat sira nee ba Jesus Kristu para foo sai ba ema sira nebee serbi Nai Maromak. Depois Jesus Kristu haruka Nia anju ida foo tutan ba Nia atan hau João.
Nunee agora hau mos konta sai hotu saida mak hau haree, nee mak Nai Maromak nia lia menon nebee Jesus Kristu hatudu sai.
See mak lee sai livru nee, nia sorti boot. I see mak rona hodi halo tuir, nia mos sorti boot. Tanba buat sira nee besik atu akontese ona.
4-5 Maluk sarani sira hosi sidade hitu iha provinsia Ázia, hau João harohan ba Nai Maromak ho Nia Espiritu ho mos Jesus Kristu para hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba imi i foo paz ho hakmatek ba imi. Maromak iha hori uluk kedas, agora iha, i iha nafatin too tinan ba tinan. Nia Espiritu nee hatudu Aan mai hau hanesan espiritu hitu nebee iha hela kadeira ukun nia oin.<a href='#note-1447' class='key'>*</a> I Jesus Kristu sempre foo sasin nebee loos, Nia mak ema primeiru nebee moris fali hosi mate, i Nia mak ukun liurai hotu-hotu iha mundu nee.<a href='#note-1448' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-1449' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus hadomi ita, nunee Nia raan fakar too mate para ita bele livre hosi sala.<a href='#note-1450' class='key'>✡</a>
Haree ba! Jesus sei tuun mai hosi lalehan iha kalohan laran, i ema hotu-hotu sei haree Nia, too ema nebee mak uluk sona Nia, sira mos sei haree. Ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu nee sei tanis tanba Nia. Loos duni, buat nee sei sai nunee duni. Amen.<a href='#note-1452' class='key'>✡</a>
Nai Maromak dehan, “Hau mak primeiru ho ikus. Hau iha hori uluk kedas, agora iha, i iha nafatin too tinan ba tinan. Hau mak kbiit nain.”<a href='#note-1453' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau João, imi nia maun. Ita hotu hetan susar ho terus tanba ita hakruuk ba Jesus nudar Liurai, maibee ita aguenta ho pasiensia nafatin. Ema kastigu hau iha rai oan Patmos tanba hau foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan i foo sasin kona ba Jesus.
Depois iha loron Domingu ida, Maromak nia Espiritu domina hau i hau rona lian makaas hanesan korneta lian iha hau nia kotuk.
Lian nee dehan nunee, “Buat nebee mak o haree, o tenki hakerek iha livru lulun ida, depois haruka ba sarani sira iha sidade hitu tuir mai nee: Éfezu, Esmirna, Pérgamu, Tiatira, Sardes, Filadélfia ho Laodiseia.”
Depois hau hateke ba kotuk atu haree see mak koalia mai hau nee. I hau haree fali ahi-oan riin hitu halo ho osan mean.
Ema ida hamriik hela iha ahi-oan riin hitu nee nia klaran. Nia hanesan Ida nebee ema baibain temi Mane Maksoin. Nia hatais batina naruk, iha nia hirus matan kesi hena naruk ida mak enfeita ho osan mean.<a href='#note-1454' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia fuuk mutin teb-tebes. Nia matan hanesan fali ahi nebee mak lakan makaas.<a href='#note-1455' class='key'>‡</a> <a href='#note-1456' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia ain lakan hanesan riti nebee mak ema sunu ba ahi. Nia lian tarutu makaas hanesan mota tuun.<a href='#note-1457' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha Nia liman loos Nia kaer hela fitun hitu, i iha surik ida oin-kotuk kroat hotu sai hosi Nia ibun. Nia oin nabilan hanesan loro matan iha loron manas boot.
Kuandu hau haree Nia, hau monu kedas iha Nia oin hanesan ema mate. Maibee Nia tau Nia liman loos ba hau hodi dehan, “Keta tauk. Hau mak huun ho rohan.<a href='#note-1458' class='key'>✡</a>
Uluk Hau mate, maibee agora, haree ba, Hau moris fali ona. Hau sei moris nafatin tinan ba tinan. I Hau mak kaer xavi hodi loke odamatan ba matebian sira nia fatin, Hau mak iha kbiit hodi halo moris fali ema mate.
Entaun o tenki hakerek buat hotu-hotu nebee o haree nee, kona ba buat nebee akontese agora dadauk ho mos buat nebee aban-bainrua sei mosu.
Ohin o haree fitun hitu iha Hau nia liman loos, ho ahi-oan riin osan mean hitu. Nia signifikadu mak nee: ahi-oan riin sira nee mak sarani sira iha sidade hitu. I fitun hitu nee mak anju hitu nebee tau matan ba sira.”
Depois hau haree anju ida tuun mai hosi lalehan lori hela xavi rai kuak klean nakukun nian ho mos korenti boot ida iha nia liman.
Anju nee kaer tiha samea ulun hitu. Samea antigu nee, ema mos bolu nia diabu nia boot ka Satanás. Anju nee kesi tiha samea ulun hitu ho korenti, atu hatama ba iha rai kuak klean nakukun laran too tinan rihun ida.<a href='#note-1610' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju nee soe nia ba rai kuak klean laran i xavi metin tiha para nia la bele lohi tan ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu. Liu tiha tinan rihun ida mak husik fali nia, maibee la kleur.
Depois hau haree kadeira ukun barak ho ema tuur hela iha kadeira ida-idak. Nai Maromak foo ona kbiit ba ema sira nee hodi foo justisa. Uluk sira sei moris iha mundu, ema tesi tiha sira nia kakorok tanba sira foo sasin kona ba Jesus Kristu i foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Sira nee nunka adora animal siak ho nia estatua, i lakohi simu animal nee nia marka iha sira nia reen toos ka iha sira nia liman. Maski ema oho tiha ona sira, maibee Nai Maromak halo moris fali sira, i sira ukun hamutuk ho Kristu too tinan rihun ida.<a href='#note-1611' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira nee mak ema primeiru nebee Nai Maromak halo moris fali hosi mate. Ema mate sira seluk tenki hein too tinan rihun ida nee hotu foin Nai Maromak halo moris fali sira.
Sira nebee moris fali primeiru nee, sira nee sorti boot. Sira sai ona Nai Maromak nia povu santu. Sira la hetan mate ba dala rua. Sira sei sai nai lulik hodi serbi Nai Maromak ho Jesus Kristu, i sei ukun hamutuk ho Kristu durante tinan rihun ida.
Bainhira tinan rihun ida nee hotu ona, Maromak sei haruka husik diabu nia boot Satanás hosi nia dadur fatin,
i diabu nia boot sei sai mai lohi nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu. Nasaun sira nee ema temi dehan, Gog ka Magog. Diabu nia boot sei bosok ema para sira halibur hamutuk hodi halo funu. Ema nebee mak halibur hamutuk nee barak teb-tebes, hanesan rai henek iha tasi ibun.<a href='#note-1612' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira lao mai hosi fatin hotu-hotu iha mundu hodi haleu Nai Maromak nia povu nia hela fatin para asalta sira. Fatin nee mak sidade nebee Nai Maromak hadomi. Maibee ahi lakan ida monu tuun hosi lalehan haan mutuk tiha sira hotu.
Diabu nia boot, ida nebee uluk bosok sira hotu, sei soe tama tiha iha ahi lakan boot nia laran. Iha nebaa nia sei terus loron-kalan hamutuk ho animal siak ho nia profeta falsu too tinan ba tinan.
Hotu tiha hau haree kadeira ukun mutin boot ida, ho mos Ida nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun nee. Derepenti deit lalehan ho rai halai sees hosi Nia futar oin too lakon tiha.
Hau haree ema sira nebee mate tiha ona, kiik-boot hotu-hotu hamriik hela iha kadeira ukun nia oin. Depois anju loke livru nebee mak hakerek ema hotu-hotu nia hahalok iha mundu. Anju mos loke livru ida seluk, iha livru nee hakerek ema nebee mak sei hetan moris rohan-laek. I Nai Maromak tesi ema ida-ida nia lia tuir sira nia hahalok nebee mak hakerek tiha ona iha livru laran.<a href='#note-1613' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee mak uluk mate iha tasi laran, tasi nee entrega fila fali. Ema mate sira seluk mos, Mate ho Matebian nia Fatin entrega fali. Depois Nai Maromak tesi sira ida-ida nia lia tuir saida mak sira uluk halo.
Hotu tiha Matebian nia Fatin soe tiha ba iha ahi lakan boot nia laran, i buat ida naran Mate mos soe hotu iha nebaa. Ahi lakan boot nee mak ema bolu dehan, “mate ba dala rua”.
Ema sira nebee naran la hakerek iha livru ema moris rohan-laek nian, mos soe tama hotu ba iha ahi lakan boot nee nia laran.
Hau haree Jerusalém foun tuun mai hosi Nai Maromak iha lalehan. Sidade nee sidade santu, i kapaas teb-tebes hanesan noiva ida nebee enfeita aan furak loos ona atu hasoru nia noivu iha sira nia loron kazamentu.<a href='#note-1615' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona lian makaas ida sai hosi kadeira ukun nee dehan,
“Haree ba!
Hahuu agora Nai Maromak nia hela fatin iha ema sira nia leet.
Nia hela hamutuk ho sira.
Nia sai sira nia Maromak
i sira sai Nia povu.
Maromak rasik hela hamutuk ho sira.<a href='#note-1616' class='key'>✡</a>
Nia sei hamaran sira nia matan been.
La iha tan terus,
la iha tan mate ka tanis lelir,
la iha tan tristi.
Tanba buat sira uluk nian nee liu tiha ona.”<a href='#note-1617' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Ida nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun nee dehan, “Rona mai! Agora Hau halo buat hotu-hotu sai foun.” Depois Nia koalia tan mai hau dehan, “Hakerek liafuan sira ohin nee, tanba aban-bainrua buat sira nee sei akontese duni, ema hotu-hotu bele fiar.”
Nia dehan tan,
“Buat sira nee kumpri tiha hotu ona!
Hau mak primeiru ho ikus,
huun ho rohan.
Ema nebee hamrook,
Hau sei foo hemu bee hosi bee matan nebee foo moris tinan ba tinan,
bee nee la selu.<a href='#note-1618' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema hotu-hotu nebee manaan,
sira sei simu bensaun sira nee hotu.
Hau sei sai sira nia Maromak,
i sira sei sai Hau nia oan.<a href='#note-1619' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee sira nebee hakiduk tanba tauk, sira nebee la fiar, ema nebee halo sala foer oi-oin, oho-door, ema nebee halo sala seksual, ema nebee kaer ai kulit aat, sira nebee adora lulik, ema bosok-teen, sira nee hotu-hotu Hau sei soe tama ba iha ahi lakan boot nia laran. Ida nee mak mate ba dala rua.”
Depois anju ida hosi anju hitu nebee kaer manko nakonu ho Nai Maromak nia kastigu ikus, mai dehan ba hau, “Mai, hau sei hatudu ba o noiva nebee mak atu kaben ho Bibi Oan.”
Derepenti Maromak nia Espiritu domina hau, i anju nee lori hau ba iha foho ida aas teb-tebes. Iha nebaa anju nee hatudu sidade santu Jerusalém tuun mai hosi Nai Maromak iha lalehan.<a href='#note-1620' class='key'>✡</a>
Sidade nee kapaas teb-tebes. Iha naroman lalehan nian sai hosi Nai Maromak, halo sidade nee nabilan hanesan fatuk murak nebee karu teb-tebes, hanesan fatuk murak jaspe, i moos loos hanesan vidru.
Portaun tolu see oin ba lorosae, tolu see oin ba loromonu, tolu see oin ba tasi feto i tolu tan see oin ba tasi mane.<a href='#note-1621' class='key'>✡</a>
Moru nee harii iha fatuk boot sanulu resin rua nia leten, iha fatuk ida-ida hakerek Bibi Oan nia reprezentate nain sanulu resin rua nia naran.
Anju nebee ohin koalia ho hau nee kaer hela ai sukat ida halo hosi osan mean, para sukat sidade nee tomak ho mos nia portaun ho moru.<a href='#note-1622' class='key'>✡</a>
Hodi nia ai sukat nee, anju nee sukat uluk sidade. Sidade nee nia naruk sasukat rihun sanulu resin rua, nia luan ho nia aas mos hanesan hotu.<a href='#note-1623' class='key'>*</a>
Depois anju nee sukat moru nia mahar tuir ita ema nia sasukat. Moru nia mahar sasukat liman atus ida haat-nulu resin haat.<a href='#note-1624' class='key'>†</a>
Moru nee halo hosi fatuk murak jaspe, sidade nee tomak halo hosi osan mean diak nian i lakan nabilan hanesan vidru.
Fatuk boot sanulu resin rua nebee tane moru nee, enfeita ho fatuk murak oi-oin. Fatuk murak sira nee lakan kór oi-oin i karu teb-tebes. Fatuk boot primeiru halo ho fatuk jaspe, numeru rua halo ho fatuk safira, numeru tolu halo ho fatuk kalsedonia, numeru haat halo ho fatuk esmeralda,
numeru lima halo ho fatuk sardoniu, numeru neen halo ho fatuk sardiu, numeru hitu halo ho fatuk krisolitu, numeru walu halo ho fatuk berilu, numeru sia halo ho fatuk topaziu, numeru sanulu halo ho fatuk krisoprazu, numeru sanulu resin ida halo ho fatuk jasintu, i numeru sanulu resin rua halo ho fatuk ametista.
Moru nee nia portaun sanulu resin rua halo ho morteen perola sanulu resin rua, portaun ida-idak halo hosi perola boot ida. Estrada iha sidade nee, halo ho osan mean diak nian i lakan nabilan hanesan vidru.<a href='#note-1625' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha sidade nee tomak hau la haree uma kreda ida, tanba Nai Maromak kbiit nain ho mos Bibi Oan, Sira rasik iha nebaa. Nunee la presiza ona uma kreda.
Iha sidade nee la presiza loro matan ho fulan para foo naroman. Tanba naroman lalehan nian sai hosi Nai Maromak, i Bibi Oan mos sai hanesan ahi-oan hodi leno sidade nee.<a href='#note-1626' class='key'>✡</a>
Nasaun hotu-hotu sei moris iha naroman nee nia laran. Liurai sira hosi mundu tomak sei lori sira nia rikusoin ba iha sidade nee.<a href='#note-1627' class='key'>✡</a>
Portaun atu tama sidade nunka taka, tanba iha nebaa la iha tan kalan.
Ema hosi nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu lori sira nia rikusoin mesak kapaas deit ba iha sidade nee hodi foo ba Nai Maromak i adora Nia.<a href='#note-1628' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee buat aat ida mos la bele tama iha nebaa. Ema nebee halo sala foer ka adora fali lulik, ho ema bosok-teen, sira hotu la bele tama. So ema nebee mak nia naran hakerek tiha ona iha Bibi Oan nia livru mak bele tama iha sidade nee, tanba livru nee hakerek see mak sei hetan moris rohan-laek.<a href='#note-1629' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju nee hatudu mota ida mai hau. Mota nee nia bee foo moris tinan ba tinan, i moos loos hanesan vidru. Bee nee sai hosi Nai Maromak ho Bibi Oan nia kadeira ukun,<a href='#note-1630' class='key'>✡</a>
suli liu hosi estrada boot nia klaran iha sidade nee. Iha mota nee nia sori-sorin iha ai nebee foo fuan, i ai fuan sira nee mos foo moris rohan-laek. Ai huun nee foo fuan tinan ida dala sanulu resin rua, fulan ida fuan dala ida. I ai nee nia tahan uza hanesan aimoruk hodi kura ema iha nasaun hotu-hotu iha mundu.<a href='#note-1631' class='key'>✡</a>
Buat nebee Nai Maromak foo malisan la tama iha sidade nee. Nai Maromak ho Bibi Oan nia kadeira ukun iha hela sidade nee nia laran, i Nai Maromak nia ema sira serbi Nia iha nebaa.<a href='#note-1632' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira haree Nia oin, i Nia naran hakerek iha sira nia reen toos.
Iha sidade nee, la iha tan kalan. Maromak nia povu la presiza ona loro matan ka ahi-oan, tanba Nai Maromak rasik mak foo naroman ba sira. I Nia povu sei ukun iha nebaa too tinan ba tinan.<a href='#note-1633' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju nee dehan mai hau, “Buat hotu-hotu nebee hau foo hatene ba o nee loos i ema hotu-hotu bele fiar. Nai Maromak sempre foo nia Espirítu ba Nia profeta sira para sira bele foo tutan Nia liafuan. Agora Nai Maromak haruka tan Nia anju mai hatudu ba Nia atan sira, saida mak la kleur tan sei akontese.”
Jesus dehan, “Rona mai! La kleur tan Hau sei mai. Ema nebee halo tuir Nai Maromak nia lia menon iha livru nee, sira sorti boot.”
Hau João, mak rona buat sira nee hotu, i haree rasik ho matan. Bainhira hau rona ho haree tiha hotu, hau hakneak i hakruuk too rai atu adora anju nebee mak hatudu buat sira nee mai hau.
Maibee anju nee bandu hau dehan, “La bele! Adora mak Maromak deit! Tanba hau nee Maromak nia atan hanesan mos o ho o nia maluk profeta sira seluk ho mos ema hotu-hotu nebee mak halo tuir liafuan iha livru nee.”
Depois anju nee dehan tan mai hau, “La bele taka liafuan sira nebee mak Nai Maromak foo sai tiha ona iha livru nee, tanba loron besik ona atu buat sira nee akontese.
Ema nebee halo buat aat,
husik sira halo buat aat nafatin ba.
Ema nebee halo buat foer,
husik sira halo buat foer nafatin ba.
sira tenki halo buat diak nafatin.
I ema nebee moris ho laran moos,
tenki moris ho laran moos nafatin.”<a href='#note-1634' class='key'>✡</a>
Jesus dehan, “Rona mai! La kleur tan Hau sei mai. Hau mai lori premiu hodi selu ema hotu-hotu tuir ida-idak nia hahalok.<a href='#note-1635' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau mak primeiru ho ikus, Hau mak hahuu ho remata, Hau mak huun ho rohan.<a href='#note-1636' class='key'>✡</a>
Ema nebee fasi tiha ona sira nia hena too moos, sira sorti boot. Tanba sira mak iha direitu tama ba sidade laran liu hosi portaun para bele haan ai fuan nebee mak foo moris rohan-laek.<a href='#note-1637' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee ema aat sira, ema nebee kaer ai kulit aat, halo sala seksual, oho-door, adora fali estatua lulik, ka gosta bosok, sira nee sei hela hotu iha liur.
Hau Jesus. Hau haruka ona Hau nia anju lori liafuan nee ba imi, para imi foo tutan ba sarani sira. Hau nee liurai David nia Jerasaun, Hau mak fitun dadeer, ida nebee lakan makaas.”<a href='#note-1638' class='key'>✡</a>
Maromak nia Espirítu ho noiva nee dehan, “Mai ona!” Ema nebee rona mos tenki koalia tuir, “Mai ona!”
See mak hamrook, mai ona. See mak hakarak hemu bee nebee foo moris tinan ba tinan, kuru deit tuir imi nia hakarak, lalika selu.<a href='#note-1639' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau, João, foo hanoin ba ema hotu-hotu nebee sei rona Maromak nia lia menon iha livru nee: Se ema ruma aumenta tan buat ruma ba lia menon nee, Nai Maromak mos sei aumenta kastigu todan ba nia, tuir kastigu nebee mak hakerek iha livru nee.
I se ema ruma hasai liafuan ruma hosi lia menon iha livru nee, Maromak mos sei hasai nia direitu atu tama ba iha sidade santu, i nia la bele haan ai fuan nebee foo moris tinan ba tinan, hanesan hakerek tiha ona iha livru nee.<a href='#note-1640' class='key'>✡</a>
Ida nebee foo sai buat sira nee hotu dehan, “Loos duni! La kleur tan, Hau mai ona.”
Amen. Nai Jesus, mai ona ba!
Hau harohan para Nai Jesus hatudu Nia laran diak ba Maromak nia povu hotu-hotu. Amen.
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Éfezu:
‘Hau mak kaer fitun hitu iha Hau nia liman loos, i Hau lao haleu ahi-oan riin osan mean hitu nee. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:
Hau hatene buat hotu-hotu nebee imi halo: Hau hatene imi servisu makaas hodi serbi Nai Maromak, i imi aguenta ho pasiensia iha terus nia laran. Hau mos hatene imi la simu ema aat iha imi nia leet. Se iha ema ruma mai lohi imi dehan, sira Hau nia apostolu, imi sempre koko sira i deskobre katak sira bosok.
Ema halo terus imi tanba imi fiar mai Hau, maibee imi aguenta nafatin, i la hakiduk.
Maibee iha buat ida mak Hau la simu: Imi la hatudu tan imi nia domin mai Hau hanesan uluk.
Imi monu aat liu ona! Agora, hanoin fila fali imi nia domin uluk. Hakribi tiha imi nia sala nee hodi moris fali tuir imi nia hahalok uluk nian. Se lae, Hau sei mai hasai imi nia ahi-oan riin.
Maski nunee, imi mos halo buat diak ida: imi la simu Nikolau nia ema sira nia hahalok, Hau mos la simu.
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira. Ema nebee manaan, aban-bainrua Hau sei foo direitu ba nia para bele haan ai fuan nebee mak lori nia ba moris rohan-laek. Ai fuan nee nia huun moris iha Nai Maromak nia toos.’ ”<a href='#note-1459' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Esmirna:
‘Hau mak huun ho rohan. Uluk Hau mate maibee agora Hau moris fali ona. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:<a href='#note-1460' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatene imi moris iha terus ho kiak nia laran. Maski nunee iha Maromak nia oin imi riku. Hau hatene ema balu hatete aat imi. Sira deklara sira nia aan dehan sira Maromak nia ema, afinal lae. Sira la hakruuk ba Maromak maibee hakruuk fali ba diabu nia boot Satanás.
Maski nunee imi lalika tauk kona ba terus nebee mak imi sei hetan. Hau hatete ba imi, diabu nia boot sei halo imi balu baa dadur iha kadeia para koko imi. Imi sei hetan terus too loron sanulu. Maibee imi tenki tuir nafatin Hau too mate, maski ema oho imi. Se imi halo nunee, Hau sei foo premiu moris rohan-laek nian ba imi.
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira. See mak manaan, aban-bainrua nia sei la tama ba iha ahi infernu. Tama ba ahi infernu nee mak ema bolu dehan “mate ba dala rua”.’ ”<a href='#note-1461' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Pérgamu:
Hau hatene imi nia hela fatin nee, diabu nia boot Satanás mak hela iha nebaa hodi ukun. Maski nunee imi kaer metin nafatin Hau nia naran. Iha imi nia sidade nee mos, ema oho tiha Antipas, ema ida nebee sempre foo sasin lo-loos kona ba Hau. Sira oho tiha nia mos, imi la husik imi nia fiar mai Hau.
Maibee iha buat balu mak Hau la simu: Imi balu tuir fali Balaão nia hanorin. Uluk Balaão hanorin ema ida naran Balak para lohi ema Israel monu ba sala. Nunee sira haan fali hahaan nebee mak ema foo haan tiha ba estatua lulik, i sira mos halo sala seksual.<a href='#note-1462' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi balu mos tuir hanorin falsu nebee Nikolau nia ema sira foo.<a href='#note-1463' class='key'>✡</a>
Hakribi ona imi nia sala nee! Se lae, la kleur tan Hau baa lori surik nebee mak iha Hau nia ibun laran nee hodi halo funu hasoru imi.
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira. See mak manaan, aban-bainrua Hau sei foo ai haan manaa. Ai haan nee sei subar hela. Hau mos sei foo fatuk mutin ba sira ida-ida. Iha fatuk nee hakerek naran foun, naran nee ema seluk sei la hatene, so ema nebee simu fatuk nee mak hatene.’ ”<a href='#note-1464' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Tiatira:
‘Hau Maromak nia Oan. Hau nia matan hanesan ahi lakan, i Hau nia ain lakan hanesan riti nebee mak ema sunu ba ahi. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:
Hau hatene buat hotu-hotu nebee imi halo: Imi hadomi imi nia maluk, i fiar metin mai Hau. Imi serbi ema seluk i aguenta ho pasiensia iha terus laran. Hau mos hatene, agora imi halao Hau nia servisu ho badinas liu fali uluk.
Maibee iha buat ida mak hau la simu: Imi husik deit feto Jezabel hanorin sala. Nia foti aan dehan nia Maromak nia profeta ida. Maibee nia hanorin sarani sira lao sala dalan, too sira mos halo sala seksual i haan fali hahaan nebee mak ema foo haan tiha ona ba estatua lulik.
Hau foo ona tempu ba Jezabel atu hakribi nia sala nee, maibee nia lakohi.
Nunee Hau sei riba tuun nia halo nia terus iha nia toba fatin. Ema nebee halo sala seksual ho nia mos, se sira la hakribi sira nia sala nee, Hau sei foo terus todan ba sira.
Sira nebee tuir Jezabel hanesan fali oan halo tuir nia inan, Hau sei oho sira. Nunee sarani sira iha nebee-nebee deit sei hatene katak, Hau konhese mo-moos ema nia neon ho laran i Hau foo todan ba ema ida-ida tuir nia hahalok.<a href='#note-1465' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee imi balu iha Tiatira la tuir feto nee nia hanorin aat. Maski ema balu dehan nia hanorin ‘Satanás nia segredu boot’ mos, imi lakohi rona. Ba imi sira nee, Hau la foo tan orden,
naran katak imi kaer metin nafatin imi nia fiar too Hau fila fali mai
26-27 Ema nebee manaan hodi halo tuir nafatin Hau nia hakarak too rohan, Hau sei foo ba sira kbiit nebee mak Hau hetan hosi Hau nia Aman. Hau foo kbiit ba sira para ukun nasaun sira nebee kontra Nai Maromak. Sira sei ukun ho rota nebee mak halo ho besi, i hodi rota nee sira sei halo rahun tiha povu hanesan fali ema halo rahun sanan rai.
Ba ema nebee halo tuir nafatin Hau nia hakarak too rohan, Hau sei foo tan fitun dadeer nian.<a href='#note-1466' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira.’ ”
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Sardis:
‘Hau mak kaer Maromak nia espiritu hitu, i kaer fitun hitu. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:<a href='#note-1467' class='key'>*</a>
Hau hatene buat hotu-hotu nebee imi halo: Ema dehan imi sei moris hela maibee imi hanesan ema nebee mate tiha ona. Hadeer ona! Imi nia fiar besik atu mohu, entaun hametin ona ba. Tanba Hau haree imi nia hahalok, la iha ida mak tuir lo-loos Maromak nia hakarak.
Tanba nee hanoin fila fali hanorin nebee mak uluk imi rona i simu. Imi tenki halo tuir hanorin nee, i hakribi imi nia sala. Se imi dukur nafatin, Hau sei mai derepenti deit hanesan naok-teen, imi sei la hatene bainhira loos mak Hau mai.<a href='#note-1468' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee hosi imi iha Sardis, iha balu mak laran moos nafatin, hanesan ema nebee la halo foer nia hena. Sira nee sei lao hamutuk ho Hau, hatais hena mutin, tanba sira serve duni.
See mak manaan, nia mos sei hatais hena mutin hotu. Hau sei la hasai nia naran hosi lista ema moris rohan-laek nian. I aban-bainrua iha Hau nia Aman nia oin ho mos anju sira nia oin, Hau sei foo sai katak, nia nee Hau nia ema.<a href='#note-1469' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira.’ ”
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Filadélfia:
‘Hau mak santu i loos. Hau mak kaer xavi liurai David nian. Kuandu Hau loke odamatan, la iha ema ida mak bele taka fali. I kuandu hau taka odamatan, la iha ema ida mak bele loke. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:<a href='#note-1470' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau hatene buat hotu-hotu nebee imi halo. Imi nia kbiit la too. Maibee imi tuir nafatin Hau nia liafuan, i la nega Hau. Haree ba! Hau loke tiha ona odamatan ba imi, i la iha ema ida mak bele taka fali.
Iha ema balu dehan sira Maromak nia ema, maibee sira bosok, sira la hakruuk ba Maromak maibee hakruuk fali ba diabu nia boot Satanás. Aban-bainrua Hau sei halo sira monu ain ba imi, i sira sei rekonhese katak Hau hadomi imi.<a href='#note-1471' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau uluk haruka imi aguenta ho pasiensia iha terus nia laran, i imi halo tuir duni Hau nia liafuan nee. Tanba nee aban-bainrua hau sei kuidadu di-diak imi iha tempu susar ho terus nebee mak sei mai iha mundu tomak. Maromak sei uza susar ho terus nee hodi koko ema hotu-hotu iha mundu.
See mak manaan, Hau sei halo nia sai hanesan ai riin boot iha Hau nia Maromak nia uma kreda boot, i nia sei hela metin iha nebaa too tinan ba tinan. Hau sei hakerek Hau nia Maromak nia naran iha ema nee nia isin lolon, ho mos Jerusalém foun nia naran. Jerusalém foun nee Maromak nia sidade, i aban-bainrua sidade nee sei tuun hosi lalehan, hosi Hau nia Maromak. Hau mos sei hakerek Hau nia naran foun iha ema nee nia isin lolon para hatudu katak, nia Hau nia ema.<a href='#note-1472' class='key'>✡</a>
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira.’ ”
Depois Ema nee hatete mai hau, “Hakerek hanesan nee ba sarani sira iha sidade Laodiseia:
‘Hau mak Ida nebee ema bolu dehan ‘Amen, loos duni’. Hau sempre foo sasin lo-loos. Hau mak huun ba lalehan ho rai ho buat hotu-hotu nebee Nai Maromak halo. Hau nia lia menon mak nee:<a href='#note-1473' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1474' class='key'>†</a> Hau hatene buat hotu-hotu nebee imi halo: Imi manas mos lae, malirin mos lae. Hau hakarak para imi manas karik, manas liu, malirin karik, malirin liu ba!
Maibee imi hanesan bee morna deit, la manas, la malirin. Nunee mak Hau atu tafui sai imi hosi Hau nia ibun.
Imi dehan imi riku ona, moris diak ona, la presiza tan buat seluk. Maibee imi la hatene katak, imi hanesan fali ema nebee susar liu, moris la diak, kiak rabat rai, matan delek, i isin molik.
Nunee diak liu imi sosa osan mean diak nian hosi Hau para imi sai riku. Imi sosa hena mutin hosi Hau hodi bele taka imi nia isin molik para imi la bele moe tan. I sosa aimoruk hosi Hau hodi kose ba imi nia matan delek sira nee para haree fali.
Ema nebee Hau hadomi, sira nee mak Hau koriji i Hau kastigu. Entaun imi tenki badinas hodi hakribi imi nia sala.<a href='#note-1475' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1476' class='key'>‡</a> Haree ba! Hau hamriik hela iha odamatan oin hodi tuku odamatan. Ema nebee mak rona Hau nia lian i loke odamatan mai Hau, Hau sei tama ba laran i ami sei haan hamutuk.
See mak manaan, Hau sei foo direitu ba nia para tuur ukun hamutuk ho Hau, hanesan mos Hau manaan tiha ona, i agora Hau tuur ukun hamutuk ho Hau nia Aman.
Imi nebee iha tilun, rona di-diak saida mak Maromak nia Espiritu hatete ba sarani sira.’ ”
Hotu tiha, hau, João haree tan buat seluk. Hau haree iha lalehan, odamatan ida nakloke hela. I hau rona fali lian ida nebee mak uluk hau rona, lian nee hanesan korneta lian. Agora lian nee hatete mai hau dehan, “Sae mai, Hau sei hatudu ba o saida maka sei akontese aban-bainrua.”
Iha momentu nee kedas Maromak nia Espiritu domina hau. Derepenti deit hau haree kadeira ukun ida iha lalehan, i Ema ida tuur hela iha kadeira nee.
Ema nee nabilan hanesan fatuk murak jaspe ho sardóniu. Iha arkuiris ida haleu hela kadeira ukun nee. Arkuiris nee nabilan hanesan fatuk murak esmeralda.<a href='#note-1477' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha mos kadeira rua-nulu resin haat mak haleu kadeira ukun nee, i katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat tuur hela iha kadeira sira nee. Sira hotu hatais hena mutin, sira nia ulun tau koroa liurai nian halo ho osan mean.
Rai lakan ho rai tarutu makaas sai hosi kadeira ukun nee. Iha mos ahi-oan hitu lakan hela iha kadeira ukun nee nia oin. Ahi-oan nee mak Maromak nia espiritu hitu.<a href='#note-1478' class='key'>*</a> <a href='#note-1479' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha kadeira ukun nia oin iha mos buat ida hanesan tasi maibee moos loos hanesan vidru.
Iha animal moris haat haleu hela kadeira ukun nee. Animal sira nee nia oin-kotuk matan nakonu. Animal primeiru hanesan leaun.<a href='#note-1480' class='key'>✡</a>
Ida tuir mai hanesan karau aman. Ida seluk, nia oin hanesan ema nia oin. Ida ikus liu hanesan manu makikit ida nebee semo hela.<a href='#note-1481' class='key'>†</a> <a href='#note-1482' class='key'>✡</a>
Animal moris haat nee ida-idak iha liras neen. Matan nakonu nakonu iha sira nia isin tomak. Loron-kalan animal haat nee hananu la para dehan,
“Santu, santu,
Nai Maromak mak santu.
Nia mak kbiit nain.
Nia iha hori uluk kedas,
agora iha,
i iha nafatin too tinan ba tinan.”<a href='#note-1483' class='key'>✡</a>
Animal moris sira nee hananu hodi hahii Ida nebee mak tuur iha kadeira ukun, Nia moris tinan ba tinan nafatin. Sira foti aas Nia naran hodi foo agradese ba Nia. Bainhira animal sira nee hananu,
katuas lian nain rua-nulu resin haat nee hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha kadeira ukun nee nia oin hodi adora Ida nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun nee, Nia moris too tinan ba tinan. Sira mos hasai sira nia koroa liurai nian i tau iha kadeira ukun nia oin hodi hahii Nia dehan,
Ita Boot mak serve atu ema hotu-hotu hahii foti aas Ita nia naran,
tanba Ita Boot mak forsa teb-tebes,
Ita Boot mak halo buat hotu-hotu.
Buat sira nee hotu iha
tanba Ita Boot mak hakarak.”
Depois hau haree Ida nebee mak tuur iha kadeira ukun nee kaer hela livru lulun ida iha Nia liman loos. Livru lulun nee nia liur-laran hakerek nakonu hotu, i taka metin tiha ho lilin been iha fatin hitu, tau mos karimbu tuir lilin been fatin hitu nee ida-idak.<a href='#note-1484' class='key'>✡</a>
I hau haree anju forti ida husu ho lian makaas dehan, “See mak iha direitu atu hasai karimbu fatin iha livru lulun nee hodi loke livru nee?”
Maibee la iha ema ida iha lalehan ka iha rai ka iha rai okos mak bele loke livru nee para bele haree saida mak hakerek iha livru laran.
Haree nunee, hau tanis tristi loos tanba la iha ema ida mak bele loke livru lulun nee para bele haree saida mak hakerek iha laran.
<a href='#note-1485' class='key'>*</a> Depois ema ida hosi katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat nee dehan mai hau, “Keta tanis. Haree ba! Liurai David nia Jerasaun ida makaas teb-tebes, ema bolu Nia ‘Leaun hosi suku Judá’, Nia manaan tiha ona. Nunee Nia mak iha direitu atu loke karimbu fatin hitu hodi loke livru nee.”<a href='#note-1486' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1487' class='key'>†</a> Depois hau haree Bibi Oan ida hamriik hela iha klaran besik kadeira ukun. I animal moris haat ho katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat nee, sira hotu haleu kadeira ukun. Bibi Oan nee, hau haree, iha fitar iha Nia isin, hatudu katak uluk ema oho tiha ona. Nia iha dikur hitu ho matan hitu. Matan hitu nee nia signifikadu mak Maromak nia espiritu hitu nebee mak Nia haruka ona ba iha mundu tomak.<a href='#note-1488' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1489' class='key'>‡</a> Bibi Oan nee baa iha Ida nebee mak tuur iha kadeira ukun hodi simu livru lulun nee hosi Nia liman loos.
Bainhira Bibi Oan simu livru nee, animal moris haat ho katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat nee hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha Nia oin. Sira ida-idak kaer buat ida hanesan viola, i kaer mos manko osan mean ida, ai been morin nakonu iha laran. Ai been morin nee mak Maromak nia povu sira nia orasaun.<a href='#note-1490' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira hotu hananu kanta foun ida hanesan nee:
“Ita Boot mak serve simu livru lulun nee
hodi loke nia karimbu fatin,
tanba ema oho tiha ona Ita Boot.
Hodi Ita Boot nia raan,
Ita Boot sosa kotu ona ema hosi suku, lian, povu ho nasaun hotu-hotu
para sai Nai Maromak nia povu.<a href='#note-1491' class='key'>✡</a>
Ita Boot foti sira sai Nai Maromak nia reinu,
i hili mos sira sai hanesan nai lulik para serbi ita nia Nai Maromak.
I sira sei kaer ukun iha mundu nee.”<a href='#note-1492' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree tan, iha anju rihun ba rihun, tookon ba tookon. Sira haleu hela kadeira ukun ho mos animal moris haat ho katuas lia nain sira. Hau rona<a href='#note-1493' class='key'>✡</a>
anju sira nee hananu ho lian makaas dehan,
“Bibi Oan nebee mak ema oho tiha ona nee,
Nia mak serve atu ema hotu-hotu respeita, hahii,
i foti aas Nia naran,
tanba Nia kbiit boot liu,
Nia matenek klean liu,
Nia forsa teb-tebes!”
Tuir mai, hau rona tan kriatura hotu-hotu iha lalehan, iha rai, iha rai okos ho mos iha tasi laran, sira hotu hananu hamutuk dehan,
“Ida nebee mak tuur iha kadeira ukun ho mos Bibi Oan,
Sira nee mak ami hahii, respeita i foti aas too tinan ba tinan.
Sira nia kbiit la iha rohan.”
Depois animal haat nee hataan, “Amen, loos duni!” I katuas lia nain rua-nulu resin haat hakneak i hakruuk too rai hodi adora Ida nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun ho mos Bibi Oan.
Hotu tiha hau haree Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin primeiru hosi karimbu fatin hitu nebee mak tau iha livru lulun nee. Depois hau rona animal ida hosi animal moris haat nee hatete ho lian makaas hanesan rai tarutu dehan, “Mai ona!”
Derepenti hau haree kuda mutin ida, ema ida sae hela kuda nee ema ida ke sempre manaan funu. Nia kaer hela rama, i agora simu tan koroa liurai nian. Depois nia baa tan para halo funu halakon nia inimigu sira seluk.<a href='#note-1494' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin numeru rua. I hau rona animal moris segundu hatete, “Mai ona!”
Kuda mean lakan ida mos sai mai. Ema nebee mak sae hela kuda nee, nia simu kbiit atu lori funu ba iha mundu para halo ema oho malu. Nia mos simu surik boot ida.<a href='#note-1495' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin numeru tolu. I hau rona animal moris numeru tolu hatete, “Mai ona!” Hau haree kuda metan ida, ema ida sae kuda nee kaer hela dasin ida atu tetu ai haan.<a href='#note-1496' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau rona buat ida hanesan ema nia lian sai hosi animal haat nee nia klaran dehan, “La kleur tan, rai sei hamlaha boot. Osan nebee ema manaan iha loron ida, sei too deit para sosa trigu kilu tolu. Se trigu diak nian, hetan deit kilu ida. Maibee keta estraga ai oliveira ho ai uvas.”<a href='#note-1497' class='key'>*</a>
Depois Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin numeru haat. I hau rona animal moris numeru haat hatete, “Mai ona.”
Hau haree tan kuda ida kor kamutis. Ema nebee mak sae kuda nee, nia naran ‘Mate’. Iha ema ida tan naran ‘Matebian sira nia Fatin’ lao tu-tuir nia. Sira nain rua simu kbiit atu baa oho ema lubuk ida iha mundu, uza surik, ho rai hamlaha, ho moras, ho mos animal siak. Se ita fahe ema hotu-hotu iha mundu ba parte haat, parte ida sei mate hotu.<a href='#note-1498' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin numeru lima. I hau haree ema barak nebee uluk ema oho, sira nia klamar iha meza sakrifisiu nia okos. Sira nee ema oho tanba sira foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan ho lo-loos.
Sira koalia ho lian makaas dehan, “Nai Maromak kbiit nain, Ita Boot mak santu i loos. Bainhira loos mak Ita Boot tesi lia ba ema iha mundu hodi kastigu ema sira nebee mak uluk oho ami?”
Depois sira ida-idak simu batina mutin naruk. Iha ida haruka sira hein tan uitoan, too sira nia numeru kompletu. Tanba hosi sira nia maluk sarani sira nebee sei serbi Kristu iha mundu, iha balu mak ema sei oho tan, hanesan mos sira uluk.
Depois hau haree Bibi Oan loke tan karimbu fatin numeru neen. Derepenti rai nakdoko makaas. Loro-matan sai nakukun hanesan hena metan, fulan sai mean hanesan raan.<a href='#note-1499' class='key'>✡</a>
Fitun sira monu tuun ba rai, hanesan fali ai fuan figeira matak mak monu ba rai bainhira anin huu makaas.
Hau haree lalehan lulun aan too lakon tiha, hanesan fali ema lulun surat tahan. Foho ho ilha mos hotu-hotu muda tiha hosi sira nia fatin.<a href='#note-1500' class='key'>✡</a>
Haree nunee, liurai sira iha mundu, nai ulun sira, komandante militar, ema riku, ema boot too ema baibain ho atan, sira hotu-hotu halai baa iha foho hodi subar iha fatuk kuak ka subar iha fatuk nia leet.<a href='#note-1501' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira halerik ba foho ho fatuk boot sira dehan, “Monu taka tiha ami ba! Subar ami para Nia nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun la bele haree ami, i Bibi Oan la bele kastigu ami.<a href='#note-1502' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba loron kastigu too ona. Agora Sira fakar Sira nia hirus mai ami, too la iha ema ida mak bele aguenta!”<a href='#note-1503' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha, hau haree anju haat hamriik hela iha mundu nia lidun haat hodi satan netik anin hosi rai ulun, rai ikun, tasi feto, tasi mane, para la bele huu ba rai maran ho tasi. Ai huun ida mos anin la kona.<a href='#note-1504' class='key'>✡</a>
Anju haat nee simu ona kbiit atu estraga rai ho tasi. Depois hau haree anju ida seluk mai hosi loro-sae lori hela karimbu hosi Maromak Moris. Anju nee koalia ho lian makaas ba anju haat nee
dehan, “Hein lai! Ami sei tau marka iha Nai Maromak nia ema sira nia reen toos lai. Marka hotu mak imi foin bele estraga rai maran ho tasi ho mos ai huun sira hotu.<a href='#note-1505' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1506' class='key'>*</a> Depois hau rona dehan, ema nebee simu marka nee, hamutuk rihun atus ida haat-nulu resin haat. Sira hosi suku Israel hotu, mak hanesan tuir mai nee:
hosi suku Judá, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Gade, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Aser, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Naftali, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Manassés, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Simeão, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Levi, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Isakar, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku Zebulón, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
hosi suku José, ema rihun sanulu resin rua;
i hosi suku Benjamim, ema rihun sanulu resin rua.
Hotu tiha, hau haree ema barak loos, too sura la bele. Ema sira nee hosi nasaun, suku, povu ho lian hotu-hotu iha mundu. Sira hotu hatais batina mutin, hamriik iha kadeira ukun nia oin ho Bibi Oan nia oin. Sira kaer ramus
hodi haklalak dehan, “Ami hetan salvasaun hosi Nai Maromak Ida nebee tuur iha kadeira ukun ho mos hosi Bibi Oan.”
Anju hotu-hotu hamriik haleu kadeira ukun nee ho katuas lia nain sira ho mos animal moris haat. Sira hotu hakneak i hakruuk too rai iha kadeira ukun nia oin hodi adora Nai Maromak
dehan,
“Amen, loos duni!
Ami hahii ho agradese,
ami foti aas Ita Boot nia naran.
Tanba Ita Boot mak kbiit nain,
Ita Boot forsa teb-tebes,
Ita Boot nia matenek klean liu.
Ita Boot deit mak ami adora too tinan ba tinan. Amen!”
Depois katuas lia nain ida hosi sira rua-nulu resin haat nee husu mai hau dehan, “Sira nebee hatais batina mutin nee, see? Sira mai hosi nebee?”
Hau hataan, “Hau la hatene senhor. Ita Boot mak hatene.”
Katuas nee hatete mai hau,
“Sira nee uluk hetan terus boot tanba sira nia fiar.
Sira fasi tiha ona sira nia batina ho Bibi Oan nia raan,
nee mak sira nia batina sai mutin.<a href='#note-1507' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee sira hamriik iha Nai Maromak nia kadeira ukun nia oin
hodi serbi Nia loron-kalan iha Nia uma kreda boot.
Sira sei la hamlaha tan
i sei la hamrook tan.
Loro manas sei la halo terus tan sira,
i rai manas sei la halo sira senti atu mutuk.<a href='#note-1508' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba Bibi Oan nebee mak hamriik iha klaran besik kadeira ukun nee mak sei sai sira nia bibi atan.
Nia sei lori sira ba bee matan
hodi foo hemu bee nebee foo moris rohan-laek.
I Nai Maromak sei hamaran sira nia matan been.”<a href='#note-1509' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha Bibi Oan loke karimbu fatin numeru hitu. Iha lalehan tomak nonook hotu maizoumenus oras sorin balu.
Depois hau haree anju hitu nebee mak baibain hamriik iha Nai Maromak nia oin, sira ida-idak simu korneta.
Depois iha anju seluk mai lori manko osan mean ida hamriik iha altar oin. Nia simu ai been morin barak iha nia manko atu hasae ba Maromak hamutuk ho Maromak nia povu nia orasaun. Nia sunu ai been morin nee iha altar osan mean iha kadeira ukun nia oin.<a href='#note-1510' class='key'>✡</a>
I ai been morin nia suar ho povu sira nia orasaun sae hamutuk hosi anju nia liman too iha Nai Maromak nia oin.
Depois anju nee mos foti ahi klaak iha altar leten hodi enxe nakonu ba iha manko osan mean laran, i nia riba tuun ba mundu. Derepenti rai tarutu makaas iha fat-fatin, rai lakan taa ba-mai, rai mos nakdoko.<a href='#note-1511' class='key'>✡</a>
Hotu tiha anju hitu nebee mak kaer hela korneta prepara aan atu huu sira nia korneta.
Anju primeiru huu nia korneta. Derepenti iha udan jelu fatuk ho ahi ho raan kahur malu fakar tuun mai iha mundu. Parte ida hosi parte tolu hosi mundu nee, ahi haan mutuk tiha. Nunee mos duut matak ho ai huun sira, ahi haan mutuk parte ida hosi parte tolu.<a href='#note-1512' class='key'>✡</a>
Anju numeru rua huu nia korneta. Derepenti iha buat boot ida hanesan fali foho boot nebee lakan makaas, riba tuun ba tasi laran. Tasi parte ida hosi parte tolu sai tiha raan.
Nunee ikan ho animal nebee moris iha tasi laran, parte ida hosi parte tolu mate. I roo nebee lao iha tasi laran mos, parte ida hosi parte tolu rahun.
10-11 Anju numeru tolu huu nia korneta. Derepenti fitun boot ida lakan hanesan ahi lakan, monu tuun hosi lalehan. Fitun nee nia naran ‘Moruk’. Nia monu tama ba mota ho bee matan, halo parte ida hosi parte tolu sai moruk. Too ikus ema barak mate tanba sira hemu bee moruk nee.<a href='#note-1513' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois anju numeru haat huu nia korneta. Derepenti hanesan buat ruma xoke loro matan, fulan ho mos fitun, halo parte ida hosi parte tolu sai nakukun tiha. Nunee, se oras loron ida nian ita fahe ba tolu, entaun oras rua naroman, oras ida nakukun. Kalan mos hanesan.<a href='#note-1514' class='key'>✡</a>
Depois hau haree manu makikit ida semo aas, i hau rona manu nee foo sai ho lian makaas dehan. “Aii, susar! Susar! Ema hotu-hotu iha mundu sei hetan susar boot liu tanba sei iha tan anju tolu mak sei huu sira nia korneta.”
Anju numeru lima huu nia korneta. Derepenti hau haree fitun ida monu tuun tiha ona ba rai. Fitun nee simu xavi ida para loke rai kuak klean nakukun.
Momentu fitun nee loke rai kuak klean nee, ahi suar makaas sai kedas hanesan suar sai hosi fornu boot. Suar nee taka metin loro matan, halo rai nakukun tiha.<a href='#note-1515' class='key'>✡</a>
Gafanhotu barak teb-tebes sai hosi ahi suar laran tuun mai mundu. Nai Maromak halo gafanhotu sira nee bele tata ema hanesan fali sakunar tata ema.<a href='#note-1516' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee Nia bandu sira la bele estraga duut ho ai huun ho ai horis selu-seluk. Sira so bele halo terus ema nebee mak la iha Nai Maromak nia marka iha sira nia reen toos.<a href='#note-1517' class='key'>✡</a>
Gafanhotu sira nee la simu lisensa atu oho ema sira nee maibee so halo terus deit durante fulan lima. Gafanhotu nee tata ema halo moras liu, hanesan fali sakunar mak tata.
Durante fulan lima nee nia laran, ema sira nee hakarak atu mate lalais, too sira buka dalan oi-oin, maibee la konsege mate.<a href='#note-1518' class='key'>✡</a>
Gafanhotu nee nia modelu hanesan kuda nebee prontu ona atu ema sae hodi baa halo funu. Iha sira nia ulun taka buat ruma hanesan koroa liurai nian halo ho osan mean. Sira nia oin hanesan fali ema nia oin.<a href='#note-1519' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira nia fuuk naruk hanesan feto nia fuuk, i sira nia nehan kroat hanesan leaun nia nehan.<a href='#note-1520' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira nia hirus matan taka ho buat ida hanesan besi funu nian. Sira nia liras tarutu makaas hanesan kuda kareta lubuk ida nebee halai makaas atu baa funu.<a href='#note-1521' class='key'>✡</a>
<a href='#note-1522' class='key'>*</a> Gafanhotu sira nia liurai mak anju ida nebee toma konta ba rai kuak klean nakukun. Nia naran ho lian Ebreu dehan, Ábadon, ho lian Gregu dehan, Apólion. Naran rua nee katak, “Harahun door”.
Terus boot primeiru liu ona. Maibee sei iha tan terus boot rua.
Hotu tiha anju numeru neen huu nia korneta. Hau rona lian ida sai hosi altar osan mean nia lidun haat, altar nee iha hela Nai Maromak nia oin.<a href='#note-1523' class='key'>✡</a>
Lian nee hatete ba anju numeru neen nee dehan, “Baa kore tiha anju haat nebee kesi hela besik mota boot Eufrates.”
Entaun anju nee baa kore tiha sira para sira bele baa oho ema. Tanba uluk kedas Maromak desidi katak anju haat nee mak tenki baa oho ema iha oras, loron, fulan ho tinan ida nee duni. Hosi ema hotu-hotu iha mundu, parte ida hosi parte tolu mak sira oho.
Anju haat nia tropas nebee sae kuda funu, barak teb-tebes, hau rona dehan, sira hamutuk tookon atus rua.
Hau haree tropas ho sira nia kuda funu nian hanesan nee: Tropa sira nia hirus matan taka ho besi funu kor tolu: mean lakan, azul tuan, ho kinur. Kuda sira nee nia ulun hanesan fali leaun nia ulun. Ahi lakan, ahi suar ho fatuk dois naran enxofre, sai hosi sira nia ibun laran.
Buat tolu nebee sai hosi kuda sira nia ibun nee halo ema parte ida hosi parte tolu iha mundu mate.
Kuda sira nee nia forsa iha sira nia ibun ho mos sira nia ikun, tanba sira nia ikun hanesan fali samea. Sira nia ikun nee mos iha nia ulun rasik, i sira uza ulun nee hodi tata halo terus ema.
Maski ema barak mate iha terus boot sira nee, maibee ema nebee sei moris lakohi hakribi sira nia hahalok aat. Sira adora nafatin diabu, adora mos estatua lulik nebee halo ho osan mean, osan mutin, riti, fatuk ho ai. Maski buat sira nee la book aan, la haree, i la rona, maibee sira adora nafatin.<a href='#note-1524' class='key'>✡</a>
Sira mos lakohi hakribi sira nia sala sira seluk hanesan oho ema, uza ai kulit aat, halo sala seksual ho naok.
Timóteo nebee diak.
Kumprimentus hosi hau, Paulo, Jesus Kristu nia apostolu. Nai Maromak ho Kristu Jesus mak foti hau. I Kristu Jesus halo ita laran metin katak Nai Maromak salva ona ita.
Timóteo, o hanesan hau nia oan rasik, tanba hau hatudu dalan para o fiar ba Kristu Jesus. Hau harohan atu ita nia Aman Maromak ho Kristu Jesus ita nia Nai, hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba o, hadomi o, i foo paz ba o.<a href='#note-1214' class='key'>✡</a>
Foin dadauk, bainhira hau atu sai hosi sidade Éfezu baa iha provinsia Masedónia, hau husu o hela nafatin iha Éfezu, hodi bandu ema sira nebee hanorin la loos, atu la bele hanorin tan buat nebee sala.
Ema sira nee lakon tempu konta ai knanoik nebee la iha folin, i dada lia kona ba bei-ala sira bara-barak. Buat sira nee so halo ema istori malu deit, i la ajuda ema fiar ba Maromak para sira bele halo tuir Nia hakarak.
Hau foo hanoin ba o hanesan nee, atu sarani sira bele moris hadomi malu. Atu hadomi malu lo-loos, ita tenki laran moos, hatene saida mak diak ho saida mak aat, i fiar tebe-tebes ba Nai Maromak.
Maibee iha mestri balu husik ona buat sira nee, hodi koalia fali buat nebee la iha folin.
Sira hatudu aan dehan sira matenek nain kona ba lei nebee Nai Maromak foo ba Moisés, maibee sira la kompriende buat nebee sira hanorin.
Ita hatene katak lei nee diak, naran katak ita uza tuir Maromak nia hakarak.
Lei nee laos hakerek foo ba ema nebee moris loos ona. Maibee foo ba ema sira nebee kontra lei, moris kontra Maromak, fila kotuk ba Maromak, sempre halo buat aat, la tuir Maromak nia hakarak, la respeita Maromak, i oho-door ema too oho sira nia inan-aman rasik.
Lei nee foo ba ema nebee halo sala seksual, ba ema nebee halo hahalok homo-seksual, ba sira nebee naok ema ba faan, ba bosok-teen sira, ba ema nebee jura falsu, ho sira nebee halo saida deit mak kontra hanorin nebee loos.
Hanorin loos nee mai hosi Nai Maromak nia Novidade Diak, nebee Nia entrega mai hau. Nai Maromak nee boot tebe-tebes i diak la-halimar.
Hau agradese ba Kristu Jesus ita nia Nai, tanba Nia foo fiar ho forsa mai hau hodi foti hau halao Nia servisu.
Nia foti hau, maski uluk hau hatete aat Nia i halo terus ema nebee tuir Nia, hodi sama sira too rai. Jesus la kastigu hau, tanba tempu nebaa hau seidauk fiar ba Nia i la hatene saida mak hau halo.<a href='#note-1215' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee ita nia Nai Kristu Jesus hatudu Nia laran diak mai hau la sukat. Nee mak hau bele fiar metin ba Nia, hadomi Nia i hadomi mos ema seluk.
Ita rona ona dehan, “Kristu Jesus mai iha mundu nee para salva ema sala nain.” Liafuan nee loos duni; ita tenki simu ho laran tomak. Hosi ema sala nain hotu-hotu, hau mak aat liu.
Maski nunee Nai Maromak la kastigu hau. Tan Nia hakarak uza hau hodi hatudu Kristu Jesus nia pasiensia boot liu mai hau. Bainhira sira haree nunee, sala nain sira seluk mos bele fiar ba Nia hodi moris nafatin ho Nia tinan ba tinan.
Mai ita hotu-hotu hahii Nai Maromak!
nebee ukun tinan ba tinan nafatin.
Nia moris rohan la iha;
Nia nunka mate.
Ema la bele haree Nia ho matan.
So Nia deit mak Maromak;
la iha tan seluk!
Mai ita hahii i foti aas Nia naran
tinan ba tinan nafatin.
Amen.
Hau nia oan Timóteo. Buat nebee hau haruka o halo nee, tuir lo-loos lia tatoli nebee uluk Nai Maromak hatoo ba Nia ema kona ba o nia servisu. Se o tuir Nia lia tatoli nee, entaun o sei luta nafatin hanesan funu nain diak ida.
Fiar metin ba Kristu, i kuidadu o nia aan para sempre halo buat nebee loos. Tanba iha ema balu hatene saida mak loos, maibee lakohi halo tuir. Too ikus, sira fila kotuk ba Maromak.
Hosi sira nee, nain rua mak Himeneu ho Alexandre. Nee mak hau entrega ona sira ba Satanás, para sira bele aprende atu la bele hatete aat tan Nai Maromak.
Hau husu boot atu imi halo orasaun ba ema hotu-hotu. Harohan atu Maromak tau matan ba sira i tulun sira. Agradese mos ba Nia.
Halo orasaun ba liurai sira ho ema hotu-hotu nebee kaer ukun, atu ita bele moris hakmatek ho dame, hodi adora Maromak i halo tuir Nia hakarak.
Orasaun hanesan nee diak. Nee halo haksolok Nai Maromak, nebee salva ita.
Nia hakarak atu ema hotu-hotu hetan salvasaun, i kompriende buat nebee mak loos. Mak nee:
So iha Maromak mesak ida deit.
I so iha Ema ida deit mak bele halo dame entre ita ema ho Nai Maromak.
Ema nee mak Kristu Jesus.
Nia foo Nia Aan hodi selu kotu ita nia tusan
hodi foo liberdade mai ita.
Ida nee mak liafuan diak nebee Nai Maromak agora foo sai mai ita ema.
I Nai Maromak hili ona hau sai Nai Jesus nia apostolu, hodi baa foo sai Novidade Diak ba sira nebee laos ema Judeu, i hanorin Maromak nia lia loos ba sira atu sira mos fiar ba Nai Jesus. Hau Jesus nia apostolu duni; hau la bosok.<a href='#note-1216' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira sarani sira halibur malu halo orasaun iha nebee-nebee, hau foo atensaun ba mane sira tenki diak malu. La bele hirus malu, la bele istori malu. Kuandu imi halo orasaun, imi nia laran tenki moos.
Nunee mos hau foo atensaun ba feto sira, hatais halo di-diak. Lalikan hatudu aan para ema fihir imi. Lalikan halo fuuk sai moda oi-oin, ka hatais hena nebee folin karu, ka uza osan mean osan mutin rebo-rebo.<a href='#note-1217' class='key'>✡</a>
Diak liu imi preokupa halo diak ba ema seluk. Nee mak serve ba feto nebee dehan, “Hau adora Nai Maromak.”
Bainhira ema hanorin Nai Maromak nia liafuan, imi feto sira tenki see tilun hodi rona i hakruuk ba hanorin nee. La bele bis-bisi malu ka halo estrundu.
Tuir hau, feto la bele manda mane ka hanorin fali sira. Diak liu nonook deit.
Tan Nai Maromak halo uluk Adão, depois foin halo Eva.<a href='#note-1218' class='key'>✡</a>
Maibee bele nunee mos, feto sira bele hetan salvasaun liu hosi hetan oan.<a href='#note-1220' class='key'>*</a> Naran katak sira fiar nafatin ba Kristu, sempre hadomi ema seluk, moris ho laran moos, i hatene aan.
Ita baibain rona dehan, “Ema nebee hakarak sai responsavel ba sarani sira, nia hakarak halo servisu ida ke iha valór.” Liafuan nee loos duni; ita tenki simu ho laran tomak.
Responsavel sarani nian tenki ema diak, nebee povu respeita. Nia tenki moris loos ho feen ida deit. Nia tenki hatene aan, domina aan, naran diak, simu bainaka iha uma ho laran tomak, i hatene hanorin.
Responsavel sarani nian la bele lanu-teen, i la bele liman kamaan baku ema, maibee tenki laran diak i gosta dame. Nia la bele matan fuan naklosu ba osan.
Nia tenki hatene eduka nia familia, i nia oan sira tenki respeita i rona ba nia.
Tanba se nia la hatene eduka nia familia uma laran, oinsaa mak nia bele tau matan ba Maromak nia povu?
La bele foti ema nebee foin fiar ba Nai Jesus sai responsavel. Se lae, nia bele foti aan dehan nia mak diak liu. Nunee, Maromak bele kastigu nia hanesan uluk Nia kastigu Satanás.
Responsavel tenki naran diak iha komunidade nia leet. Tanba se ema nebee laos sarani la respeita nia, sira bele hatete aat nia, too nia mos monu ba Satanás nia lasu.<a href='#note-1221' class='key'>✡</a>
Nunee mos ho ema nebee kaer knaar ajuda Maromak nia povu. Nia mos tenki ema nebee naran diak, la bele bosok-teen, la bele hemu tua barak, i la bele matan fuan naklosu ba osan.
Nia tenki laran moos i kaer metin lia loos nebee Maromak hatudu mai ita.
Bainhira atu foti ema ida kaer knaar ajuda Maromak nia povu, haree di-diak lai nia moris oinsaa. Se ema la hatudu liman ba nia, foin bele foti nia.
Nunee mos nia feen<a href='#note-1222' class='key'>*</a> tenki naran diak, domina aan, i la bele konta ema nia vida. Ema seluk mos konfia nia.
Ema nebee kaer knaar ajuda Maromak nia povu tenki moris loos ho feen ida deit. Nia mos tenki hatene hanorin nia oan sira ho nia ema uma laran tomak.
Sira nebee serbi sarani sira ho diak, ema sei respeita loos sira. Nunee sira sei brani liu tan koalia kona ba sira nia fiar ba Kristu Jesus.
Timóteo, hau hein katak la kleur tan, hau baa haree o. Maski nunee, hau hakerek surat nee ba o.
Nunee se hau demora karik, surat nee bele foo hanoin ba o katak, Maromak nia oan sira tenki moris oinsaa. Maromak nee mak Maromak moris. I Nia povu hanesan uma riin<a href='#note-1223' class='key'>†</a> nebee hamriik metin hodi apoia Maromak nia hanorin nebee loos.
Segredu nebee Maromak foo sai ona mai ita kona ba Jesus Kristu, diak teb-tebes. Segredu nee mak nee:
Jesus Kristu fila aan sai ema.
Maromak nia Espiritu hatudu katak, Jesus nee loos duni.
Maromak nia anju sira mos haree Nia.
Nai Maromak hasae ona Nia ba lalehan hodi foti aas Nia naran.
Ema foo sai kona ba Nia too iha nasaun-nasaun.
Iha mundu tomak, ema fiar ona ba Nia.
Maromak nia Espiritu foo hatene mo-moos mai ita katak, iha loron ikus, sarani balu sei husik tiha sira nia fiar ba Kristu, hodi tuir fali espiritu bosok-teen, ho diabu sira nia hanorin.
Iha mos mestri balu hanorin nunee. Sira bosok-teen, koalia oin ida, hahalok oin seluk. Tanba sira halo sala beibeik, agora sira la hatene ona saida mak diak, saida mak aat.
Sira hanorin dehan ema la bele kaben, i dehan hahaan balu lulik, la bele haan. Maski Nai Maromak halo hahaan sira nee hotu, para ema nebee fiar ba Kristu i hatene lia loos bele haan. Naran katak ita haan, foo agradese ba Nai Maromak.
Buat hotu-hotu nebee Nai Maromak halo, diak. Nunee la iha hahaan ida mak ita bele dehan lulik. Hotu-hotu ita bele haan ho laran ksolok, hodi agradese ba Nai Maromak.
Tanba liu hosi Nai Maromak nia liafuan ho mos ita nia orasaun, buat sira nee hotu la lulik.
Timóteo, hanorin buat sira nee hotu ba sarani sira. Se o halo nunee mak o serbi Kristu Jesus nudar nia atan ida nebee diak. Durante nee o halo tuir hanorin nebee loos, i simu Nai Maromak nia liafuan nebee halo ita fiar ba Nia, hanesan ema haan hahaan nebee diak hodi halo isin sai forti.
Ema dehan, treinu halo isin forti iha valór, maski laduun. Maibee treinu aan para moris tuir Maromak nia hakarak iha valór boot liu, tanba ajuda ema moris agora iha mundu nee, ho mos aban-bainrua iha mundu seluk.
Liafuan nee loos duni; ita tenki simu ho laran tomak.
Ita servisu makaas i hakaas aan liu tan, tanba ita laran metin ba Nai Maromak nebee moris. Nia mak salvador ba ema hotu-hotu, liu-liu ba ita nebee fiar ba Jesus.
Hanorin buat sira nee hotu, i haruka ema halo tuir.
Keta husik ema ida la konsidera o tan deit o foin-sae. O tenki hatudu ezemplu diak ba ema sarani sira, liu hosi o nia koalia, o nia hahalok, o nia domin, o nia fiar ba Jesus Kristu, ho o nia moris loos.
Durante hau seidauk too baa, o tenki foo aan hodi lee Maromak nia liafuan ba sarani sira, hanorin di-diak sira, i foo hanoin ba sira para halo tuir.
Uluk responsavel sarani sira harohan hodi tau liman ba o nia ulun. Momentu nee, sira foo tutan Maromak nia lia menon kona ba o nia knaar, i Maromak mos foo kbiit ba o para o bele halo knaar nee ho diak. Agora, uza lo-loos kbiit nee.
Halo buat sira nee hotu ho badinas, ho laran tomak, para ema bele haree katak o lao ba oin.
Kuidadu para o sempre moris loos, i sempre hanorin buat nebee loos. Kontinua hanesan nee nafatin, mak Maromak sei hasai o hosi buat aat, i nunee mos ema nebee rona o.
La bele siak mane sira nebee idade liu o. Maibee foo hanoin ba sira ho respeitu, hanesan ba o nia aman rasik. I konsidera mane foin-sae sira hanesan o nia maun-alin rasik.
Nunee mos ho feto sira. Koalia ho sira nebee idade liu o hanesan ho o nia inan rasik. I konsidera feto foin-sae sira hanesan o nia feton. O nia laran tenki moos ba sira.
3-5 Sarani sira tenki respeita ho tau matan ba feto faluk sira nebee la iha familia atu haree sira. Maibee se feto faluk ida iha oan ka bei-oan, entaun sira iha obrigasaun atu tau matan ba nia, hodi selu nia kolen. Nunee sira hatudu katak sira serbi Nai Maromak. I sira mos halo kontenti Maromak nia laran. Maibee feto faluk nebee mesak, la iha tan ema ida atu tau matan ba nia, nia so laran metin deit ba Nai Maromak. Loron-kalan nia harohan husu tulun ba Maromak. Sarani sira tenki tau matan ba faluk sira hanesan nee.
Maibee feto faluk nebee hakarak goza deit, nia hanesan ema nebee mate tiha ona, maski nia sei moris.
Haruka sarani sira halo tuir regra sira nee, para ema la bele foo sala ba sira.
Maibee see mak la haree nia familia rasik, liu-liu nia familia uma laran, hatudu katak nia husik ona nia fiar ba Nai Maromak. Nia aat liu fali ema nebee la fiar ba Kristu.
Bainhira halo lista feto faluk sira, hili deit ema hanesan tuir mai nee: nia tinan 60 ba leten, i uluk moris loos deit ho nia kaben.
Ema rekonhese nia hanesan ema ida ke sempre halo diak ba ema seluk. Nia tau matan ba nia oan sira ho diak, simu bainaka iha nia uma ho laran tomak, serbi sarani sira ho haraik aan, ajuda ema nebee iha susar laran, i sempre prontu halo buat di-diak deit.
La bele hatama feto faluk foin-sae sira ba iha lista faluk sira nian. Tanba keta halo be sira hakarak deit mak kaben fali, too la foo ona laran tomak ba Maromak, tuir sira promete ona ba Jesus Kristu.
Nunee ema bele foo sala ba sira tanba sira la kumpri ona sira nia promesa uluk ba Maromak.
Feto faluk foin-sae sira bele mos sai baruk-teen, hodi tama uma sai uma. Laos nee deit, sira mos bele konta ema nia vida, mete ema nia problema, i koalia buat nebee la serve atu koalia.
Tanba nee, hau hanoin diak liu feto faluk foin-sae sira kaben fali, iha oan, i tau matan ba sira nia uma kain. Nunee ema nebee la gosta ita, la iha razaun atu hatete aat ita.
Tan iha feto faluk foin-sae balu sees ona hosi dalan loos hodi tuir fali Satanás.
Se feto sarani ida nia familia ruma faluk, nia mak tenki tau matan ba. La bele husik sarani sira seluk mak ajuda feto faluk nee. Nunee, sarani sira bele ajuda faluk sira nebee la iha ema ida atu haree.
Responsavel sarani sira nebee halo servisu ho diak, merese para sarani sira respeita sira i selu sira nia kolen ho diak. Liu-liu sira nebee badinas hanorin sarani sira hodi foo hanoin ba sira para moris tuir.
Tanba iha Livru Sagradu dehan, “Se uza karau hodi sama hare, la bele kesi nia ibun, para nia bele haan.” Nunee mos, “See mak servisu, nia merese atu simu osan.”<a href='#note-1224' class='key'>✡</a>
Se ema nain ida foo sala ba responsavel sarani ruma, la bele rona lai. Tenki iha sasin rua ka tolu koalia hanesan, foin o rona hodi tetu.<a href='#note-1225' class='key'>✡</a>
Se nia halo sala duni, entaun koriji nia iha sarani sira nia oin, atu ema seluk la brani halo sala hanesan nia.
Bainhira koriji ema, la bele fihir ba ema nee see. Hau tau knaar nee ba o nia kabaas iha Nai Maromak ho iha Kristu Jesus nia oin. I anju sira nebee Maromak hili mos sai sasin.
La bele anxi tau liman foti ema ruma sai responsavel ba sarani sira. Maibee haree di-diak lai. Tanba se imi foti ema, i ema nee halo sala, imi mos sei lori todan. Kuidadu o nia aan para la bele sala.
Haree di-diak! Iha ema balu halo sala, seidauk lori ba justisa mos, ema hotu-hotu hatene tiha ona. Maibee iha ema balu halo sala, kleur mak foin ema hatene.
Nunee mos, bainhira ita halo buat diak, dala ruma ema hatene kedas. Se karik ema la haree mos, ikus mai ema sei hatene, tanba hahalok diak, atu subar mos la diak.
Atan nebee sarani tenki respeita nia patraun, para ema seluk la bele hatete aat Nai Maromak ka koalia aat ita nia hanorin.
Se nia patraun mos fiar ba Kristu, patraun ho atan hanesan maun-alin. Maski nunee, atan nee tenki respeita nafatin nia patraun, i serbi nia diak liu tan, tanba nia serbi ema sarani ida nebee nia hadomi.
Hanorin falsu, ho rikusoin lo-loos
Timóteo, hanorin buat sira nee ba sarani sira, i hametin sira nia laran para halo tuir.
Ema balu hanorin buat nebee sala, la haan malu ho Nai Jesus Kristu nia Liafuan nebee loos. Sira nia hanorin la ajuda ema moris tuir Maromak nia hakarak.
Ema hanesan nee foti aan, maibee la kompriende buat ida. Sira nia moras aat ida mak gosta diskuti malu ho istori malu kona ba liafuan. Hahalok nee halo ema laran moras malu, tarata malu, hatete aat ema, ho deskonfia ema nar-naran deit.
Sira so hatene mak istori malu. Sira nia hanoin la loos ona, i sira la hatene ona saida mak loos. Sira hanoin dehan, hanorin kona ba Maromak bele halo sira sai riku.
Loos duni, se ita moris halo haksolok Maromak nia laran, i ita kontenti ho buat nebee mak ita iha, ita sorti boot.
Tanba ita moris mai iha mundu nee, ita la lori buat ida. Ita mate mos, la lori buat ida.
Nunee, naran katak ita iha ai haan ho hena para hatais, ita kontenti ona ho ida nee.
Maibee ema nebee loron-kalan hanoin deit atu sai riku, monu ba tentasaun i monu ba lasu. Sira hakarak buat oi-oin nebee sala ho buat barak nebee bele estraga sira. Nee sei halo susar sira.
Ema nebee hanoin demais osan, prontu halo buat aat oi-oin. Iha ema balu buka demais osan, too sira husik tiha sira nia fiar. Nunee sira halo terus sira nia aan, hanesan sira rasik sona sira nia aan ho tudik.
Timóteo, o Nai Maromak nia ema. Nunee, hadook aan tiha hosi buat aat sira nee hotu, i hakaas aan atu moris loos, tuir Maromak nia hakarak. Esforsa aan atu fiar nafatin ba Jesus Kristu, hadomi ema seluk, aguenta iha terus laran, i laran maus.
Luta para fiar metin ba Maromak i sempre halo tuir Nia Liafuan. Uluk bainhira o deklara iha ema barak nia oin katak o fiar ba Jesus Kristu, Maromak bolu o tama iha moris nebee rohan la iha. Agora, kaer metin moris nee.
13-14 Hau haruka o halo tuir Nai Maromak nia orden hotu, too ita nia Nai Kristu Jesus fila mai hosi lalehan. La bele kontra orden ida mos; nunee ema la bele foo sala ba o. Hau foo orden nee iha Nai Maromak nia oin. Nia mak foo moris ba buat hotu-hotu. Ho mos iha Kristu Jesus nia oin. Nia mak foo sasin lo-loos kona ba Nia Aan iha governador Póntius Pilatus nia oin.<a href='#note-1226' class='key'>✡</a>
Nai Jesus sei fila fali mai
iha loron nebee Nai Maromak desidi.
Nai Maromak nee boot teb-tebes i diak la-halimar.
Nia mak kaer ukun.
Nia mak liurai hotu-hotu nia Liurai,
ho nai hotu-hotu nia Nai.
So Nia deit mak nunka mate.
Nia moris iha naroman ida ke makaas liu,
halo ema nia matan la aguenta atu haree.
Ema ida seidauk haree Nia,
i la iha ema ida mak bele haree Nia.
Ema hotu-hotu respeita Nia.
Amen.
Haruka ema nebee riku ho sasaan mundu nian, la bele foti aan, i la bele laran metin ba sira nia rikusoin. Tan rikusoin sira nee hotu loron ida sei mohu. Haruka sira laran metin ba Nai Maromak. Tan Nia mak foo buat hotu-hotu mai ita too res-resin, atu ita bele moris haksolok.
Hatete ba sira para halo buat barak nebee diak hodi tulun ema seluk. Sira la bele karak, maibee tenki prontu foo buat nebee mak sira iha.
Nunee sira nia hahalok diak nee sai hanesan rikusoin ba loron ikus, para sira bele hetan moris lo-loos, nebee la iha rohan.
Timóteo, kuidadu di-diak knaar nebee Nai Maromak tau ona iha o nia kabaas. Iha ema balu koalia la huun la dikin, i kontra Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Sira gaba aan dehan matenek, maibee lae. Lalikan diskuti malu ho sira.
Iha ema balu fiar ba sira nia liafuan bosok nee, too husik tiha sira nia fiar ba Nai Maromak.
Hau harohan ba Maromak atu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi hotu.
Hau nia liafuan too iha nee deit.
Hosi hau,
Paulo
Timóteo nebee diak.
Kumprimentus hosi hau, Paulo. Nai Maromak hili ona hau sai Nai Kristu Jesus nia apostolu, i haruka hau baa foo sai kona ba moris rohan la iha. Nia promete atu foo moris nee ba ema nebee fiar ba Kristu Jesus.
Timóteo, o hanesan hau nia oan rasik, nebee hau hadomi. Hau harohan atu ita nia Aman Maromak ho Kristu Jesus ita nia Nai, hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba o, hadomi o, i foo paz ba o.<a href='#note-1227' class='key'>✡</a>
Loron-kalan hau halo orasaun ba o, hodi foo agradese ba Nai Maromak. Hau serbi Nia ho laran moos, hanesan mos hau nia bei-ala sira.
Hau hanoin fali uluk, kuandu ita fahe malu, o nia matan been turu. Agora hau hakarak loos hasoru o, tanba bainhira hau haree fali o, hau sei haksolok teb-tebes.
Hau hanoin fila fali o nia fiar ho laran tomak ba Nai Jesus. Fiar nee hosi kedas o nia avoo feto Lóide ho o nia inan Eunice.<a href='#note-1228' class='key'>✡</a> I hau laran metin katak agora o mos fiar hanesan sira.
Uluk, bainhira hau tau liman ba o nia ulun hodi halo orasaun, Maromak foo kbiit ba o hodi halo Nia servisu. Tanba o fiar teb-tebes ba Jesus, agora hau foo hanoin fali ba o para uza kbiit nee ho di-diak.
Tanba Nai Maromak nia Espiritu nebee Nia foo mai ita, la halo ita tauk-teen. Maibee Nia foo poder mai ita, halo ita hadomi ema, i ajuda ita atu domina aan.
Tanba nee, la bele moe konta kona ba ita nia Nai Jesus. I la bele moe kona ba hau, maski hau dadur hela iha kadeia tanba hau serbi Nai Jesus. Maibee o tenki prontu simu terus hanesan hau, para bele foo sai Novidade Diak. I Maromak sei foo forsa ba o atu aguenta iha terus nee.
Nai Maromak mak salva ona ita,
i bolu ona ita sai Nia ema para ita moris ho laran moos.
Nia halo hanesan nee,
laos tanba ita hatudu hahalok diak ruma.
Maibee, Nia salva ho bolu ita tuir Nia planu rasik,
tanba Nia hakarak hatudu Nia laran diak mai ita.
Molok Nai Maromak halo mundu nee,
Nia desidi ona atu haruka Kristu Jesus mai,
para hatudu Nia laran diak mai ita.
Agora, Kristu Jesus nebee salva ita, mai tiha ona,
Mate nia poder, Nia halo rahun tiha ona!
I Nia foo sai liu hosi Nia Novidade Diak katak Nia loke dalan ba ita
atu moris nafatin tinan ba tinan ho Nai Maromak.
Nee mak Novidade Diak. I Nai Maromak foti hau sai Jesus Kristu nia apostolu, para foo sai i hanorin Novidade Diak nee.<a href='#note-1229' class='key'>✡</a>
Tanba nee mak hau terus iha kadeia. Maibee hau la moe, tanba hau konhese Kristu i fiar ba Nia. I hau hatene lo-loos katak Nia sei kuidadu Nia Novidade Diak nebee Nia tau ona iha hau nia kabaas, too Nia fila fali mai hosi lalehan.
Kaer metin hanorin loos nebee o simu ona hosi hau. Fiar ba Jesus nafatin i hadomi ema seluk, tanba o laran ida ona ho Kristu Jesus.
Defende di-diak hanorin nebee loos. Lia loos nee hanesan osan mean nebee Nai Maromak foo ona ba o para o kuidadu. I Espiritu Santu, nebee hela iha ita nia laran, sei ajuda o.
O hatene katak Fígelu ho Hermójenes ho sira seluk nebee hela iha provinsia Ázia<a href='#note-1230' class='key'>*</a> fila kotuk husik hela hau.
Maibee Onesiforu lae. Nunee hau harohan ba Nai Maromak para hatudu Nia laran diak ba Onesiforu ho nia familia tomak. Tanba nia mai vizita hau beibeik iha kadeia, hodi hametin hau nia laran. Nia la moe maski hau ema dadur.
Uluk, bainhira nia foin too iha sidade Roma nee, nia buka hau tuun-sae too hetan.
O rasik hatene, uluk hau sei iha sidade Éfezu mos, nia ajuda hau barak iha nebaa.
Husu boot, bainhira Jesus Kristu fila mai atu foo justisa ba ita ema, Nia sei foo desizaun diak ida ba Onesiforu.
Oan Timóteo mak hau hadomi, Kristu Jesus hatudu Nia laran diak hodi foo forsa mai ita. Nunee, sai forti ba!
Uluk hau hanorin iha ema barak nia oin, o mos iha. Buat nebee o rona hosi hau nee, o tenki foo tutan ba ema nebee o fiar, para sira mos bele hanorin fali ba ema seluk.
Nudar Kristu Jesus nia soldadu diak ida, o tenki aguenta iha terus laran, hanesan mos ami.
Soldadu nebee halo dadauk funu, nia la hanoin tan atu halo servisu seluk. Tanba nia hakarak halo kontente nia komandante.
Nunee mos, bainhira tuir jogu ida, tenki tuir regulamentu jogu nee nian. Se lae, la manaan premiu.
Haree mos ba toos nain. Nia servisu mate aan, nunee nia mak tenki hetan uluk rezultadu toos nian.
Hanoin di-diak ezemplu hirak nee. I Nai Maromak sei halo o kompriende buat sira nee hotu.
Hanoin beibeik kona ba Jesus Kristu, liurai David nia Jerasaun. Nia mate, maibee Nai Maromak halo moris fali ona. Ida nee mak Novidade Diak nebee hau hanorin.
Tanba hau foo sai Novidade Diak nee mak hau hetan terus, too ema kesi tan hau ho korenti hanesan fali ema nebee halo krimi. Maibee Nai Maromak nia liafuan, ema ida la bele kesi.
Tanba nee hau prontu simu terus hotu-hotu, para ema sira nebee Maromak hili ona bele fiar ba Kristu Jesus i hetan salvasaun. I Nai Maromak sei foti aas sira too tinan ba tinan.
Liafuan tuir mai loos duni; nee mak ita bele simu ho laran tomak:
“Se ita mate hamutuk ho Kristu,
ita mos sei moris hamutuk ho Nia.
Se ita aguenta iha terus laran,
ita mos sei kaer ukun hamutuk ho Nia.
Se ita nega Nia,
Nia mos sei nega ita.<a href='#note-1231' class='key'>✡</a>
maibee Nia foo laran nafatin mai ita.
Tanba Nia mak hanesan nee duni.”
Foo hanoin beibeik ba sarani sira kona ba buat sira nee. Hatete ba sira hodi Nai Maromak nia naran, la bele istori malu kona ba liafuan. Hahalok hanesan nee la iha folin, i so halo susar deit ema nebee rona.
Hakaas aan servisu di-diak, para Nai Maromak bele rekonhese o nudar Nia atan diak ida. I hanorin lo-loos Nai Maromak nia liafuan nebee loos. Nunee o sei la moe, tanba o servisu ho diak.
Hadook aan hosi koalia la huun la dikin nebee kontra Nai Maromak nia liafuan. Tan ema nebee koalia hanesan nee sei dook ba beibeik hosi Maromak.
Sira nia liafuan hanesan kanek dodok nebee aumenta ba beibeik. Himeneu ho Filetu sira nia koalia hanesan nee lo-loos!
Sira nain rua hanorin dehan, ema sira nebee mate, moris fali tiha ona. Nunee sira sees tiha hosi lia loos, i estraga ema balu nia fiar.
Maibee Nai Maromak nia povu fiar metin nafatin, hanesan uma nia riin nebee la nakdoko. Iha riin nee hakerek dehan, “Maromak hatene Nia ema sira.” Hakerek mos katak, “See mak dehan nia tuir Nai Maromak, tenki fila kotuk ba buat aat.”<a href='#note-1232' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha ema riku sira nia uma, iha bikan oi-oin. Balu halo ho osan mean ka osan mutin. Iha mos balu halo hosi ai ka hosi rai. Bikan diak nian, uma nain uza ba festa. Maibee bikan nebee laduun diak, sira uza hodi tau foer.
Nunee mos ho ema. See mak hadook aan hosi buat nebee aat, nia hanesan bikan diak sira nee, i Maromak sei uza nia ba servisu nebee diak. Tanba nia laran moos ona, serve para nia Nain bele uza, i prontu halo buat diak saida deit.
Timóteo, halai sees hosi buat aat nebee foin-sae sira balu gosta halo. Hakaas aan atu moris loos. Fiar nafatin ba Maromak, hadomi sarani sira i haree malu di-diak. Ema sira nebee adora Maromak ho laran moos, sempre halo hanesan nee, i o mos tenki moris hanesan sira.
Bainhira ema diskuti malu kona ba buat nebee la iha folin, o lalika tama iha laran. Tan so halo ema istori malu deit.
Nai Maromak nia atan la bele istori malu ho ema, maibee tenki laran diak ba ema hotu, hatene hanorin ema, i pasiensia ba ema nebee halo problema.
Ema nebee kontra nia, nia tenki koriji ho laran maus, tanba dala ruma Maromak bele halo sira husik sira nia sala, i bele ajuda sira simu hanorin nebee loos.
Nunee sira nia hanoin bele sai loos fali, i sira bele halai sai hosi Satanás nia liman, nebee kaer tiha ona sira hodi obriga sira halo tuir nia hakarak.
Timóteo, hanoin di-diak. Iha loron ikus, susar barak sei mosu.
Ema sei hadomi deit sira nia aan rasik, i matan fuan naklosu deit ba osan. Sira foti aan, la konsidera ema seluk, gosta hatete aat ema, la rona ba sira nia inan-aman, la hatene foo obrigadu, i la respeita Nai Maromak.
Sira la hatene hadomi ema, i lakohi foo perdaun ba ema. Sira konta aat ema nia vida, la domina aan, gosta halo violensia, i nunka gosta buat nebee diak.
Sira faan sira nia kolega ba ema aat, la hanoin naruk, i foti aan dehan boot. Sira la hadomi Nai Maromak, maibee hanoin mak goza deit.
Iha ema nia oin sira hatudu jeitu hanesan ema nebee fiar ba Maromak. Maibee bainhira Maromak hakarak foo poder ba sira para moris loos, sira lakohi. La bele liga sira.
Sira balu finji baa tama iha ema nia uma. Too iha uma laran, sira bosok feto balu nebee monu lalais ba lia falsu. Feto sira nee laran la hakmatek tanba sira halo sala barak ona, i sira sempre halo tuir sira nia hakarak aat oi-oin.
Sira gosta rona hanorin foun, maibee nunka hatene nebee mak loos i nebee mak sala.
Uluk Janes ho Jambres kontra Moisés.<a href='#note-1233' class='key'>*</a> Hanesan nee mos mestri sira nee kontra hanorin nebee loos. Sira nia hanoin sai aat tiha ona, i saida mak sira fiar nee la vale buat ida.
Maibee la kleur, ema sei la fiar tan mestri falsu sira nee. Tanba ema hotu sei hatene dehan, sira beik-teen. Hanesan mos uluk akontese ba Janes ho Jambres.
Timóteo, o akompanha ona hau nia moris tomak. O hatene hau nia hanorin, hau nia moris oinsaa, i hau nia objetivu saida. O haree ona hau nia fiar ba Jesus Kristu, hau nia pasiensia, hau nia hadomi ba ema seluk, i oinsaa hau aguenta ho pasiensia iha terus laran.
O mos hatene katak ema hanehan hau i halo terus hau. O hatene saida mak sira halo mai hau iha sidade Antiokia, Ikóniu ho Listra. Maibee Nai Jesus hasai ona hau hosi terus ho susar sira nee hotu.<a href='#note-1234' class='key'>✡</a>
Loos duni, ema hotu-hotu nebee fiar ba Kristu Jesus i hakarak moris loos tuir Maromak nia hakarak, ema sei halo terus sira.
Maibee ema aat ho ema bosok-teen sira sei sai aat ba beibeik. Sira bosok halo ema barak monu, afinal sira mos ema bosok.
Maibee o tenki kaer metin buat nebee o aprende tiha ona. O laran metin ona katak buat sira nee loos, tanba o hatene see mak hanorin ba o.<a href='#note-1235' class='key'>✡</a>
Liafuan hotu-hotu iha Livru Sagradu, Nai Maromak rasik mak foo ba ema hakerek. Liafuan sira nee serve para hanorin lia loos, hatudu ema nia sala, koriji ema, ho eduka ema para moris loos.
Nunee Nai Maromak prepara Nia ema atu halo buat hotu-hotu nebee diak.
Kristu Jesus sei fila fali mai hosi lalehan hodi ukun hanesan liurai. I Nia sei foo justisa ba ema sira nebee sei moris ho sira nebee mate ona. Nunee, iha Nai Maromak ho Kristu Jesus nia oin, hau haruka o
foo sai Nai Maromak nia liafuan; iha tempu diak ka la diak mos, o tenki prontu. Koriji ema nebee sala, i bandu sira para la bele halo tan. Hametin ema nia laran. Halo buat sira nee hotu ho pasiensia, liu hosi hanorin Nai Maromak nia liafuan.
Tanba too loron ida, ema lakoi rona ona hanorin nebee loos. Maibee sira sei tuir deit sira nia hakarak rasik, hodi rona mestri bara-barak nebee hanorin halo haksolok deit sira nia laran.
Sira sei taka tilun ba ema nebee hanorin loos. Maibee sira see tilun fali hodi rona ai knanoik nebee la iha folin.
Timóteo, o la bele nunee. Iha situasaun saida deit, o tenki domina aan. Aguenta ho pasiensia iha terus laran. Baa foo sai Novidade Diak ba ema sira nebee seidauk konhese Jesus Kristu. Halao servisu hotu-hotu nebee Nai Maromak tau ona iha o nia kabaas.
Kona ba hau nia aan, hau nia loron mate besik ona. Hau hanesan tua kopu ida nebee fakar ba altar leten hanesan oferta ida ba Maromak.<a href='#note-1236' class='key'>*</a>
Hau hakaas aan iha jogu laran too hotu ho diak. Hau halai taru too ona nia rohan. Hau kaer metin hau nia fiar ba Jesus Kristu too hau nia iis kotu.
Agora hau hein premiu nebee Nai Jesus prepara ona ba ema nebee moris loos. Ita nia Nai nee mak juis loos. I too iha loron nebee Nia tesi lia, Nia sei fahe premiu nee mai hau. Laos mai hau deit, maibee Nia mos sei foo ba ema hotu-hotu nebee ho laran tomak hein hela Nia atu fila mai.
Timóteo, hakaas aan mai lalais haree hau.
Tan Demas husik tiha ona hau hodi baa iha sidade Tesalónika, tanba hadomi liu buat mundu nian. Kresente baa tiha ona provinsia Galásia, i Tito mos baa tiha ona rai Dalmásia.<a href='#note-1237' class='key'>✡</a>
So Lucas deit mak sei hamutuk ho hau. O mai, lori ho Marcos, para nia bele ajuda hau halao hau nia servisu.<a href='#note-1238' class='key'>✡</a>
Hau haruka ona Tíkiku baa iha sidade Éfezu.<a href='#note-1239' class='key'>✡</a>
Bainhira o mai, lori ho hau nia faru manas nebee hau rai hela iha Karpu nia uma iha sidade Tróade. Lori mos hau nia livru, liu-liu livru nebee hakerek iha animal nia kulit.<a href='#note-1240' class='key'>✡</a>
Alexandre, badaen riti ida, halo ona buat aat barak mai hau. Maromak sei kastigu nia tuir nia hahalok.<a href='#note-1241' class='key'>✡</a>
O tenki kuidadu ho ema nee, tanba nia kontra makaas ita nia hanorin.
Bainhira hau primeira vés hamriik iha juis nia oin hodi defende hau nia aan, la iha ema ida mak ajuda defende hau. Sira hotu husik hela hau. Husu boot, Maromak la bele foo sala ba sira.
Bele nunee mos, Nai Jesus hamriik iha hau nia sorin hodi foo forsa mai hau, para hau bele foo sai Novidade Diak hotu. Nunee sira nebee laos ema Judeu mos bele rona. I Maromak mos hasai hau hosi liaun nia ibun.
Nai Maromak sei hasai hau hosi buat aat hotu. I Nia sei lori hau ho diak tama ba lalehan. Iha nebaa, Nia mak ukun.
Mai ita hotu-hotu foti aas Nai Maromak nia naran, too tinan ba tinan. Amen.
Hatoo kumprimentus ba Priscila<a href='#note-1242' class='key'>†</a> ho nia kaben Akila. Nunee mos ba Onesiforu nia uma kain.<a href='#note-1243' class='key'>✡</a>
Erastu hela nafatin iha sidade Korintu. Hau husik hela tiha Trófimu iha sidade Miletu, tanba nia moras.<a href='#note-1244' class='key'>✡</a>
Hakaas aan mai too iha nee molok tempu malirin. Eubulu, Pudente, Lino, Cláudia, ho sarani sira seluk haruka kumprimentus ba o.
Hau harohan atu Nai Jesus hamutuk ho o nafatin, i Maromak hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi.
Hau nia liafuan too iha nee deit.
Hosi hau,
Paulo
Tito mak hau hadomi.
Nunee, sira bele laran metin katak, iha loron ida sira sei moris hamutuk ho Maromak too tinan ba tinan. Nai Maromak promete buat nee nanis kedas molok Nia halo mundu nee, i Nia nunka bosok.
Too ona tempu nebee Nai Maromak desidi, Nia foo sai dehan, Nia hakarak salva ema sala nain sira para moris hamutuk ho Nia. Nunee Nia mos foo orden mai hau atu baa foo sai Novidade Diak nee.
Tito, o hanesan hau nia oan rasik, tanba ita nain rua fiar ba Jesus Kristu. Hau harohan ba Aman Maromak ho Jesus Kristu nebee salva ita, para Sira hatudu Sira nia laran diak ba o i foo paz ba o.<a href='#note-1245' class='key'>✡</a>
Iha tempu liu ba nee, hau husik hela o iha rai Kreta, para halo remata buat nebee sei falta iha nebaa, i foti responsavel sira hodi toma konta sarani sira iha vila ida-idak. La bele haluha buat nebee mak hau hatete tiha ona ba o,
katak ema nebee atu sai reponsavel sarani sira nian tenki hanesan tuir mai nee: Nia tenki livre hosi sala. Nia tenki foo laran ba nia kaben. Nia oan sira mos tenki fiar ba Jesus Kristu. Sira la bele naran foer hanesan ema nakar-teen ka ema nebee lakohi rona nia inan-aman.
Responsavel sarani sira nian toma konta Maromak nia servisu. Nee duni nia tenki livre hosi sala. La bele hakarak manaan mesak deit. Nia la bele nervozu-door, lanu-teen, baku-door ema, i matan la bele naklosu ba osan.
Nia tenki simu bainaka iha uma ho laran tomak, i gosta halo buat nebee diak. Tenki ema kalma, moris loos, laran moos i hatene domina aan.
Nia tenki kaer metin Nai Maromak nia liafuan loos, nebee uluk ita hanorin ona ba nia. Nunee nia bele hanorin tutan lia loos hodi tulun ema halo tuir Maromak nia hakarak, i koriji ema nebee mak hanorin la loos.<a href='#note-1246' class='key'>✡</a>
Tan iha ema barak kontra hanorin nebee loos. Liu-liu ema Judeu nebee tuir ona Kristu maibee dehan, atu hetan salvasaun, tenki sunat. Sira koalia nar-naran deit hodi bosok ema.
Bandu tiha sira para la bele hanorin tan. Tanba sira harahun uma kain barak ho sira nia hanorin sala nee, i sira so buka osan deit.
Uluk matan-dook ida hosi sira nia rai Kreta koalia kona ba nia ema rasik dehan,
“Ema Kreta sira mesak bosok-teen,
laran aat, baruk-teen, i so moris para foo haan kabun deit.”
Ema Kreta nunee duni! Tanba nee, o tenki hatete makaas ba sira katak sira sala, para sira bele soe tiha liafuan falsu hodi fiar metin ba lia loos.
Nunee sira la bele rona tan ema Judeu sira nia ai knanoik, i la bele tuir tan regra hosi ema nebee fila kotuk ba lia loos.
Ba ema nebee laran moos, buat hotu-hotu diak. Maibee ba ema nebee aat i la fiar ba Nai Jesus, la iha buat ida mak diak, tanba sira nia hanoin aat ona i sira la hatene ona saida mak diak, saida mak aat.
Mestri falsu sira nee dehan, konhese Nai Maromak, maibee sira nia hahalok hatudu katak sira la konhese Nia. Sira koalia oin ida, hahalok oin seluk. Ema sira nee hahalok aat. Sira lakohi halo tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak, i la bele halo buat ida nebee diak.
Maibee Tito, o la bele hanesan mestri falsu sira. O tenki foo tutan hanorin nebee loos.
Hanorin katuas sira atu domina aan, i hatene aan, para ema bele respeita. Sira tenki fiar metin ba Maromak, hadomi ema seluk ho laran tomak, i pasiensia iha terus nia laran.
Nunee mos ho ferik sira. Hatete ba sira para moris nudar ema nebee respeita Nai Maromak. Sira la bele konta aat ema nia vida, i la bele buka deit atu hemu tua. Maibee sira tenki hanorin buat nebee diak.
Nunee sira hanorin ho hatudu ezemplu diak ba alin feto maluk sira atu hadomi sira nia laen ho sira nia oan,
domina aan, moris loos, badinas kaer servisu uma laran nian, laran diak, i hakruuk ba sira nia laen. Se sira moris nunee, maka la iha ema ida atu hatete aat Maromak nia liafuan.
Nunee mos, hatete beibeik ba mane foin-sae sira atu domina sira nia aan.
Tito, o tenki halo diak ba ema iha buat hotu-hotu, hodi sai ezemplu diak ba foin-sae sira. Hanorin ho laran; la bele hanorin oin ida, halo oin seluk. Keta halimar ho o nia servisu nee.
Kuandu o hanorin, o tenki uza liafuan nebee loos, para ema la bele foo sala ba o. Nunee ema sira nebee kontra o, sei moe, tanba sira la iha razaun atu hatete aat ita.
Hanorin atan sira atu hakruuk ba sira nia patraun. Sira tenki hakaas aan halo haksolok patraun nia laran, la bele koalia hasoru nia,
i la bele naok nia sasaan. Maibee sira tenki hatudu katak, patraun bele foo fiar tomak ba sira. Ho nunee ema seluk nebee haree atan sira nia moris nee, sei foo valór ba ita nia hanorin kona ba Nai Maromak, ita nia Salvador.
Agora Maromak hatudu ona Nia laran diak ba ema hotu-hotu hodi loke dalan ba salvasaun.
Tanba Nai Maromak nia laran diak, Nia hanorin ita tenki soe tiha hahalok aat ho mundu nia hakarak aat hotu. Durante ita sei moris iha mundu, ita tenki domina aan, moris loos, i halo tuir Nai Maromak nia hakarak.
Nia foo aan ba mate hodi hasai ita hosi sala hotu-hotu, i halo ita laran moos, para sai Nia povu rasik, nebee sempre hakarak halo buat diak.<a href='#note-1247' class='key'>✡</a>
Nee duni hanorin buat sira nee hotu ba sarani sira, i hatete beibeik ba sira para halo tuir. See mak halo sala, o tenki hatete dehan, “Nee sala”. Keta husik ema la respeita o, tanba o iha direitu atu koriji sira.
Foo hanoin fali ba sarani sira atu hakruuk ba nai ulun sira. Sira tenki tuir lei, i sempre prontu atu halo buat diak.
La bele hatete aat ema i la bele istori malu. Hatudu laran maus ho laran diak ba ema hotu.
Tan uluk, bainhira ita seidauk konhese Nai Jesus, ita beik-teen hela, i fasil atu ema bosok ita. Ita lakohi rona Nai Maromak, i ita hakarak aat saida deit, ita halo ona. Ita nia moris nakonu ho hanoin aat, laran moras ema, i odi malu.
Maski ita nia hahalok aat nunee mos, Nai Maromak ita nia Salvador hatudu Nia laran diak ho domin mai ita.
Nia salva ita laos tanba ita halo buat diak ruma, maibee tanba Nia hadomi ita. Liu hosi nia Espiritu Santu, Nia hamoos tiha ona ita nia sala i halo foun ita nia moris, hanesan ita foin moris fila fali.
Tanba Jesus Kristu salva ona ita, Nai Maromak foo Nia Espiritu Santu mai ita hanesan bee ida fakar too nakonu resin.
Tanba Jesus nia laran diak, mak Nia dehan, “Ema nee nia sala la iha tiha ona.” Nunee ita sai Nia oan, i laran metin katak aban-bainrua ita sei moris hamutuk ho Nia tinan ba tinan nafatin. Ida nee mak ita nia rikusoin.
Hau nia liafuan sira nee loos duni.
Buat nebee hau hanorin nee diak, i iha folin ba ema hotu. Nee duni hau husu atu o hatete fila-fila buat sira nee ba ema sira nebee fiar ba Maromak, atu sira hotu-hotu hakaas aan halo diak ba ema.
Hadook aan hosi diskusaun sira nebee la huun la dikin. Lalikan dada lia kona ba ida-idak nia huun, ka istori malu kona ba lei relijiaun Judeu nian. Buat sira nee hotu la iha folin ida, so halo lakon tempu deit.
Se iha ema ruma fahe sarani sira, foo hanoin makaas ba nia too dala rua. Se nia halo nafatin nunee, lalika liga tan nia.
Ema hanesan nee hanoin aat ona, i nia hahalok rasik hatudu katak nia sala.
Hau atu haruka Artemas ka Tíkiku baa hasoru o iha rai Kreta. Bainhira nia too iha nebaa, hakaas aan baa lalais hasoru hau iha sidade Nikópolis. Tan hau desidi ona atu hela iha nebaa durante tempu rai malirin.<a href='#note-1248' class='key'>✡</a>
Hakaas aan atu ajuda advogadu Zenas ho nia kolega Apolo, nebee atu baa rai dook, para sira la bele falta buat ida iha dalan.<a href='#note-1249' class='key'>✡</a>
Ita nia maluk sarani sira tenki aprende hakaas aan halo diak ba ema, hodi ajuda ema nebee susar. Ho nunee sarani sira nia moris sei la saugati.
Tito, ami hotu iha nee hatoo ami nia kumprimentus ba o. Hatoo mos kumprimentus ba ita nia maluk sarani sira nebee hadomi ami.
Hau harohan ba Maromak atu hatudu Nia laran diak ba imi hotu.
Hau nia liafuan too iha nee deit.
Hosi hau,
Paulo
